INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (131,'WhastApp for Agriculture: When a Digital farmer speaks ,you see a need for digital Agriculture extension ','YEAN ubuhinzi bwacu post1.jpg','<p>I remember that time when I was asked to walk 10 km away from home to find a local buyer of Marakuja and papaya for my parents to pay my school fees, the buyer who will in turn walk 10 km to sell them in Kigali city capital of our country . There was no mobile phone to call each other, we had no any other option. If&nbsp;anyone wanted to spread pesticide in your coffee plantation, He/She must&nbsp;walk house by house asking who could be having the pumping machine. I think you can imagine how long it will take to ask the whole Village.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nowadays, opening my eyes and after praying the Almighty to blessing my day, I automatically open my Smartphone to check new message and chat from a group of young farmers on Whatsapp -that I actually call the hope for tomorrow- , to see the new conversation that was going on, new picture from a far farm that I can&rsquo;t reach myself , new farming videos , new farming techniques documents, notice from the Ministry of Agriculture and other Agriculture Agencies. I feed my day with this breakfast then I start my work full of commitment from inspiring young farmers. Around 250 very brilliant , committed , skillful and professional farmers , a platform by YEAN , an organization that spread agriculture information and Agriculture extension in young farmers to which I owe a big congratulation for bringing together the hope for tomorrow , a generation from an demographically young country. With this platform information is shared digitally and he who wants to grow crop, sell products, buy products , import agriculture products, export agriculture products gets information from there. It&rsquo;s a easy and smart way of connecting farmers among them, with buyers and policy makers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ubuhinzi-bwacu-snap\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1610\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2016/12/ubuhinzi-bwacu-snap.jpg?w=863\" style=\"height:383px; width:516px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A screen shoot of YEAN WhatsApp Group where a farmer from the North Province asking a Quick help to deal with a disease in his Tamarillo Plantation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Social media is bringing a new generation of professional farmers, I remember a friend of Mine who bought new seeds of papaya from Brazil just a commitment from that group and another young Ladies who started a duck farm . I can&rsquo;t imagine how young people are feeling Agriculture as their pride in spite of &nbsp;migrating to other so called social acceptable professions. It gives me hope that Africa will be able to feed 4 billion in 2100.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>YEAN has a mission of spreading agriculture information and facts to the community to inspire change for the pursuit of beauty and excellence in young agripreneurs and/or the community and shares stories from farmers to farmers or from Experts to farmers to inspire youth in leading the change in Agriculture and skills development that improves the living conditions of farmers for sustainable development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>YEAN Whatsapp Group is one among strategies YEAN uses to spread out information to their beneficiaries and the whole community. This method, with almost 250 farmers ,I can say that it is a powerful weapon to YEAN agriculture extension agency to meet its goals in a Rwandan Community .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>To YEAN how? &nbsp;To Rwanda farmers how? </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Worldwide millions of people are using Whatsapp application in mobile smart phones as their easy way of sending and receiving info where at least in two/three minutes probably people check for new messages they received.&nbsp; So after realizing this, in 2014 YEAN Rwanda took advantage of this easy way to reach farmers and creates a YEAN WhatsApp Group which brought together young farmers, Professional farmers, agriculture specialists, agriculture technicians, agriculture engineers, in order to easily/quickly spread information in a short period of time. So according to the mission of YEAN Rwanda that is <em>Spread agriculture information and facts to the community to inspire change for the pursuit of beauty and excellence in young agripreneurs and the community</em>. This Platforms is helping farmers to exchange ideas and quick help in farm, pictures, short movies, Audios of what is happening right away in the farms, farmers are no longer lonely or lack information due to the remote location of their farms , just drop a message and share what you are doing if in any case you face challenges another farmer or Agronomist is ready to help you remotely.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When I look carefully how this group works-because I am also a participant-, truly I can&rsquo;t hesitate to say that this method is a driven method: is accurate, easy, workable, cheap, fast, reliable, and very simple but again it has significantly a great role in transforming Agriculture Rwanda. Ideas shared critically discussed and each member has the right to express his/her ideas according to the experience from his/her farm .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This Group &nbsp;has an incredible success according to the&nbsp;interaction-discussion &ldquo;UBUHINZI BWACU&rdquo;&nbsp;a Kinyarwanda word that means&nbsp;&ldquo;Our farming Story&rdquo; this amazing weekly discussion is open on all YEAN social media Platforms (Facebook, twitter, WhatsApp) every Sunday from 8:00 AM up to 8:00 PM, but the remarkable conversation and touchable ideas appear on WhatsApp group, members are free and open, they extensively debate on a given topic and each member is motivated when you see how discussion &nbsp;is going on. During this discussion farmers are exchanging ideas about a given topic . One day after the discussion, the summary is made available to YEAN official website (yeanrwanda.org) to be shared again on social media such as Facebook, twitter, LinkedIn Google+. The discussion is purely in Kinyarwanda (Rwanda national language) this makes it to be enjoyable with a flow of more of&nbsp;technical and comprehensive terms that makes it to be&nbsp;suitable for local farmers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ubuhinzi-bwacu-capture\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1611\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2016/12/ubuhinzi-bwacu-capture.jpg?w=863\" style=\"height:381px; width:516px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Screen shoot of YEAN WhatsApp Group during a weekly&nbsp;&ldquo;Ubuhinzi Bwacu&rdquo; discussion</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I enjoy farming stories, keep enjoying with me and if in any case you read this blog and you are a participant of to this group , Kudos to you, your ideas matters . Enjoy how cool is Agriculture.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>A story by Etienne Niyigaba&nbsp;(niyigabat@gmail.com)</em></p>\r\n','4',2158,3,'2015-12-02 19:24:52','Ubuhinzi Bwacu',0,'online','','no'),(134,'RAB Yatangaje imbuto nshya z\'ibigori zera kugera kuri toni 8 kuri hegitari.','rab-maize.jpg','<p><em><span style=\"color:#000000\">RAB Yatangaje imbuto nshya z&rsquo;ibigori zera kugera kuri toni 8 kuri hegitari.</span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Amakuru dukesha <a href=\"http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2017-01-04/206809/\" target=\"_blank\">The New Times</a> agaragaza ko ikigo cy&rsquo;igihugu gishinzwe ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi RAB (Rwanda Agriculture Board) cyasohoye Imbuto nshya z&rsquo;Ibigori . Ibigori ni Igihingwa kimaze kugira uruhare rukomeye mu Buhinzi bwo mu Rwanda aho mbere kitakundaga guhingwa . Ibi byatewe na Gahunda y&rsquo;Imbaturabukungu mu buhinzi yo guhinga igihingwa cyagenwe hakurikijwe uturere. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Gutubura izi mbuto byaratangiye ku bufatanye n&rsquo;ibigo by&rsquo;imbuto bitandukanye mu rwego rwo kugabanya imbuto zitumizwa hanze y&rsquo;igihugu ho 60% mu mwaka w&rsquo;ingengo y&rsquo;imari wa 2018-2019 ndetse kugera kuri 100% mu mwaka w&rsquo;ingengo y&rsquo;Imari wa 2019-2020.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Imbuto zagaragajwe: </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">RHM104: Iyi mbuto igaragaza kwihanganira izuba kandi ikunda cyane ahantu h&rsquo;ubutumburuke buri murugero guhera kuri metero 900 kugera kuri metero 1800 z&rsquo;ubutumburuke. Yagaragaje gutanga umusaruro ugeze kuri toni 7.89</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">kuti hegitari imwe mu duce dutandukanye yageragerejwemo: Rubona (Huye), Cyabayaga (Nyagatare), Karama (Bugesera) na Bugarama (Rusizi) mu bihembwe by&rsquo;ihinga bya 2013A,2013B na 2014A.</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000\">Kugeza ubu imbuto zayo ziri gutuburwa na RAB- Ishami ry&rsquo;Imbuto ( Gasabo, Rubungo kuri hegitari 4.2 ) na Win Win Agri Tech Ltd (Ngoma , Karembo</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000\">kuri hegitari 2). Ikigo cya RISCO nacyo kiri gutubura iyi mbuto ku buso bwa hegitari 10 (Nyagatare, Karangazi, Gabiro). Barateganya gusarura toni 30 z&rsquo;imbuto zemewe muri Gashyantare 2017.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">RHM 1407 : Iyi mbuto yera </span><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">ahantu h&rsquo;ubutumburuke buri murugero guhera kuri metero 900 kugera kuri metero 1800 z&rsquo;ubutumburuke. Iyi mbuto yagaragaje kwihanganira indwara ya Maize Lethal Necrosis (MLN) . Iyi mbuto yageragejwe mu duce tune aritwo Rubona (Huye), Cyabayaga (Nyagatare), Karama (Bugesera) na Bugarama (Rusizi) mu bihembwe by&rsquo;ihinga bya 2015 A, 2015 B</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000\">na 2016 A. Yatanze umusaruro ungana na toni 7.87 kuri hegitari imwe muri rusange. Kugeza ubu imbuto z&rsquo;ibanze zayo ziri gutuburwa na na RAB ishami ry&rsquo;Imbuto (Rubilizi, hegitari 2), SOZO Company (Gasabo, Kimironko, Kibagabaga hegitari 3.5 ha) na EMFAGM Ltd (Gatsibo, Rwimbogo hegitari 2.5).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">RHT132</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">: Iyi mbuto iberanye n&rsquo;ubutumburuke bwa metero 1400-2000. Iyi mbuto kandi yagaragaje kwihanganira indwara ya Maize Lethal Necrosis (MLN). Yageragerejwe muri Rubona, Musanze, Nyagatare na Karama mu bihembwe by&rsquo;ihinga bya 2013 A, 2013 B na 2014 A igaragaza gutanga umusaruro wa toni 7.89. Imbuto z&rsquo;ibanze ziri gutuburwa na</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000\">RAB muri gahunda y&rsquo;Ibinyampeke (Rubona, Huye kuri hegitari 1 and Cyabayaga, Nyagatare)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">RHM1409: </span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Iberanye n&rsquo; ahantu h&rsquo;ubutumburuke buri murugero guhera kuri metero 900 kugera kuri metero 1700 z&rsquo;ubutumburuke. Nayo mwigeragezwa yagagaje kwihanganira indwara ya Maize Lethal Necrosis (MLN) . Yageragejwe ahantu hane : Rubona, Nyagatare-Cyabayaga, Karama na </span><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">Bugarama mu bihembwe by&rsquo;ibinga bya 2015A, 2015 B na 2016 A. Yatanze umusaruro ungana na Toni 8.67 kuri Hegitari imwe. Imbuto z&rsquo;ibanze ziri gutuburwa na RAB muri gahunda y&rsquo;Ibinyampeke.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">5.</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">RHM1402: </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Iberanye n&rsquo; </span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">ahantu h&rsquo;ubutumburuke buri murugero guhera kuri metero 900 kugera kuri metero 1800 z&rsquo;ubutumburuke. Yageragejwe ahantu hane : Rubona, Nyagatare-Cyabayaga, Karama na Bugarama mu bihembwe by&rsquo;ihinga bya 2015 B na 2016 A aho yatanze umusaruro ungana na Toni 8.59 kuri hegitari. Nta kigo cy&rsquo;imbuto cyari cyafata iyi mbuto ngo kiyitubure , kugeza ubu imbuto z&rsquo;ibanze ziri gutuburwa na RAB muri gahunda y&rsquo;Ibinyampeke.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">6.</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">RHMM111 : </span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Iyi mbuto</span> <span style=\"color:#000000\">iberanye n&rsquo;ahantu hahereye mu rugero kandi hadatumburutse cyane. Iyi mbuto yera vuba cyane kuko yerera muri rusange iminsi 100. Iyi mbuto yageragejwe ahantu hane : Rubona, Nyagatare-Cyabayaga, Karama na Bugarama mu bihembwe by&rsquo;ihinga </span><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">bya 2015A, 2015 B na 2016 A . Yatanze umusaruro ungana na Toni 6.16 kuri hegitari muri rusange . Iyi mbuto iracyari mw&rsquo;igeragezwa riri gukorwa na RAB gahunda y&rsquo;ibinyampeke n&rsquo;ikigo Seeds of Trust-Rwanda Ltd.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">7.</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">RHMMM113</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">: Iyi mbuto ibasha ahantu h&rsquo;ubutumburuke kuva kuri metero 900 &ndash; 1700. Iyi nayo ni imbuto yera vuba kuko yerera iminsi 110. Iyi mbuto yageragejwe ahantu hane: Rubona, Nyagatare-Cyabayaga, Karama na Bugarama mu bihembwe by&rsquo;ihinga bya 2015A, 2015 B na 2016 A. Yatanze umusaruro ungana na toni 8.23 kuri hegitari imwe . Imbuto ziyikomokaho zirategurwa na RAB gahunda y&rsquo;ibinyampeke na Seeds of Trust Rwanda ltd. Nta kigo kirafata iyi mbuto ngo kiyitubure.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">8.</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">RHMH1520: </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Iyi mbuto yo iberanye n&rsquo; ahantu hari k&rsquo;ubutumburuke bwo hejuru ya metero 1800. Yageragejwe ahantu hatandukanye harimo </span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Rwerere, Musanze na Rubona muri 2015 na 2016. Yatanze umusaruro ungana na toni 7.8. Imbuto zayo za mbere ziri gutuburwa na RAB gahunda y&rsquo;Ibinyampeke.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">9.</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">RHMH1521: </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Iyi mbuto nayo ikunda</span> <span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">ahantu hari k&rsquo;ubutumburuke bwo hejuru ya metero 1800. Yageragerejwe ahantu hatandukanye harimo Rwerere, Musanze and Rubona muri 2015 na 2016 . Imbuto zibanze ziri gutuburwa na RAB ishami ry&rsquo;imbuto na RAB gahunda y&rsquo;ibinyampeke. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#808080\">Byateguwe na <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/etienne-niyigaba\" target=\"_blank\">NIYIGABA Etienne</a> , <em>email:niyigabat@gmail.com</em></span></p>\r\n','1',2783,4,'2017-01-06 04:26:23','ibigori',0,'online','','no'),(140,'Ubuhinzi bwacu: Ibitekerezo by\'Abahinzi ku ngingo igira iti: IZAMUKA RY\'IBICIRO BY\'IBIKOMOKA KU BUHINZI N\'INGARUKA  ZABYO KU MUHINZI N\'UBUHINZI MURI RUSANGE','IMG-20160128-WA0004.jpg','<p>YEAN Rwanda mu murimo ikora wo gusakaza amakuru y&rsquo;ubuhinzi ku bahinzi yashyizeho umwanya wo kwakira ibitekerezo by&rsquo;abahinzi n&rsquo;abo bagahabwa ijambo mu bikorwa bya YEAN bakagaragaza ibyo batekereza ku buhinzi bakora buri munsi. Ibi rero binyuzwa mu kiganiro UBUHINZI BWACU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kuri iki cyumweru taliki ya 28 Kanama 2016 , hakozwe ikiganiro ku mbuga nkoranya mbaga za YEAN mu ruhererekane rw&rsquo;ikiganiro cyitwa &ldquo;Ubuhinzi Bwacu&rdquo; nk&rsquo;uko bisanzwe hategurwa ingingo runaka hanyuma abahinzi, abag0ronome ku nzego zitandukanye ndetse n&rsquo;abakunzi b&rsquo;ubuhinzi bagatanga ibitekerezo ndetse bakanungurana inama kuri iyo ngingo iba yatanzwe. Ikiganiro gikorwa amanywa yose ni ukuvuga guhera saa mbiri(8:00 AM) za mugitondo kugeza saa mbiri(20:00 PM) z&rsquo;umugoroba .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nk&rsquo;uko insanganyamatsiko rero ibigaragaza , Muri iyi minsi hagaragaye izamuka,ry&rsquo;ibiciro by&rsquo;ibikomoka ku buhinzi cyane cyane aha twagaruka ku birayi n&rsquo;ibindi byagiye bizamuka&nbsp;mu biciro haba mu gace utuyemo cyangwa mu gihugu hose&nbsp; , Impamvu zabiteye nazo zagiye zisobanurwa, aha twaganiriye ku ngaruka z&rsquo;abambi cyangwa nziza umuhinzi ahura nazo bivuye kuri iki kibazo. Abatanze ibitekerezo bagiye bagaruka ku ngaruka ariko bakavugako ingaruka zigaruka ku muhinzi ahanini ziba ari mbi, gusa hari n&rsquo;abavuga ko umusaruro wabo wagize agaciro nk&rsquo;aho uyu yagize ati &ldquo;umusaruro wibyo umuhinzi yejeje wagize agaciro bityo biramutera imbaraga zo gukora cyane&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingaruka ku muhinzi ni mbi gusa </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abatanze ibitekerezo hafi ya bose bavuzeko ingaruka ari mbi k&rsquo;umuhinzi .Uyu ni uwo muri Nyamagabe yagize ati &ldquo;Murakoze cyane kukiganiro cyiza mwateguye. Nikoko izamuka ry&rsquo;ibiciro kubikomoka ku buhinzi n&rsquo; ikibazo gihangayikishije twese. Ntanze urugero, ni ubwambere muri Nyamagabe&nbsp; I kilo cy&rsquo;ibirayi kiguze amafaranga 370 frw. Ntibyigeze bibaho. Ubu ingaruka byateye nuko abahinzi bagurishije umusaruro bakagera n&rsquo;aho bibagirwa kubika imbuto. Ubu I kilo cy&rsquo;imbuto y&rsquo;ibirayi kiragura amafaranga 670frw. Usibye ibirayi n&rsquo;ibindi bihingwa byarazamutse.&rdquo; Undi nawe ati &ldquo;Umuhinzi nta ngaruka nziza abona byose biza muri negative(ingaruka mbi) kuko niba ubutaka bugabanutse yahingagaho azabura aho akorera, niba nta makuru yabonye afatika ku ihindagurika ry&rsquo;ibihe azarumbya, niba nta fumbire CG imbuto nziza nta musaruro azabona. Nkaba mbona nta nyungu ashobora kubona.&rdquo;. Uyu Nawe ati &ldquo;Umuhinzi we ingaruka ni zose! Iyo uhinga ibigori ukenera ibirayi wahinga ibitoki ugakenera ibishyimbo! Iyo igiciro cy&rsquo;ibyo kurya cyazamutse buri wese bimugiraho ingaruka directly! Kuko umuhinzi we niwe biba byahereyeho kuko ubundi izamuka ry&rsquo;ibiciro by&rsquo;ibikomoka kukintu runaka cyane cyane ibiribwa bivuzeko iyo product Ku isoko ari nkeya kuba ibihingwa ari bike, bivuze byeze ari bikeya ,umuhinzi yarahinze ntiyeza! Ingaruka zo kurumbya cg kweza ibiri hasi y&rsquo;ibyakagombye kwera kuri unity area uba wahombye! Na season ikurikira akenshi umuhinzi nta bushobozi aba afite kuko yarumbije ishize so ntazahinga nanahinga azahinga nabi cyane kuko nta capital ya inputs afite&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kuzamuka kw&rsquo;ibiciro kandi byagaragajwe ko bifite ingaruka mbi ku muryango w&rsquo;umuhinzi aho atabasha kubona ibihaza umuryango we n&rsquo;ubwo aba ari umuhinzi bwose . Hagaragajwe ko bitewe n&rsquo;amafaranga menshi atangwa umuhinzi ahita agurisha ibyo yahinze byose akibagirwa no gusiga imbuto bityo hakazabaho kubura imbuto yo gutera mu ihinga ritaha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hagarutswe kandi no ku ngaruka ku Buhinzi muri rusange aho uyu yagize ati:&rdquo; ku buhinzi muri rusange ingaruka ni mbi ,Kutazabona imbuto cyangwa hagakoreshwa imbuto mbi ku bw&rsquo;igihemwe gitaha ; Kuba umuhinzi wabyejeje ashobora kwicwa n&rsquo;inzara kuko ibyo yejeje byose yabigurishije ;Kuba abantu bashobora guhinga ibirayi gusa bakibagirwa ibindi bihingwa ubutaha, ibi noneho bikaba byagira negative impact ku biciro byabyo ;Kugira ihinduka ry&rsquo;ibiciro bikabije bya hato na hato no mu gihe kizaza ndetse no ku bindi bihingwa&rdquo; .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Umuhinzi abona kwiyongera kw&rsquo;ibiciro biterwa n&rsquo;iki.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abatanze ibitekerezo bagiye bagaruka kuri izi ngingo zikurikira :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ihindagurika ry&rsquo;ikirere ; uyu yagize ati &ldquo;ni ukubera imihindagurikire y&rsquo;ibihe aho hamwe imvura yabaye nyinshi cyane ikangiza ibihingwa byinshi muburyo butandukanye kandi ikagwa igihe gito igacika kare aho ni muduce twinshi twa northern province, south and western! Naho uburasirazuba imvura yacitse muntangiriro z&rsquo;ukwa 5 ntakintu keze rwose.&rdquo; Iyi mpamvu akaba ari nayo igarukwaho cyane n&rsquo;abahinzi ku kuba yarateye igabanuka rikabije ry&rsquo;umusaruro .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uburyo bwo guhunika umusaruro bukiri ku rwego rwo hasi aho uyu yagize ati &ldquo;Ariko na none bifite aho bihuriye na technology nkeya muguhunika umusaruro kuko ku mwero umusaruro uba ugura abiri!&nbsp; Hanyuramo agahe Gato gusa ugasanga ibiciro byikubye&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hari abagarutse ku kuba abaturage biyongera ariko ubihinzi bukaba butabyara umusaruro wiyongera bikurikije uko abaturage biyongera ati &ldquo;Jye uko mbibona nuko umusaruro ugenda uba muke kandi abaturage bo biyongera umunsi ku munsi.Abakora ubuhinzi baracyabukora mu buryo bwa gakondo kuburyo batahaza isoko rizamuka buri munsi&rdquo; Abenshi aha bagarutse ku kongera umusaruro ku butaka buto buhingwa . aho uyu yagize ati &ldquo;Ibi bigomba kuba bikorwa hatitawe kuri demography kuko niba nkeneye Toni 10 singombwa guhinga hectare 10 kandi bishoboka kuri hectare 2 gusa&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Indi mpamvu yagarutsweho ni ukubura amakuru ahagije kandi aziye igihe ngo bituma umuhinzi atamenya Igihe imvura izagwira ndetse n&rsquo;igihe izacikira . Aha hagarutswe cyane kuri serivisi y&rsquo;ubumenyi bw&rsquo;ikirere. Hagarutswe kandi ku buryo bwo kwigisha umuhinzi uko bahinga igihingwa runaka ntibibe kumuha inyongeramusaruro ngo biherere aho. Bati &ldquo;Umuhinzi we aba yarakoze ibyo agomba gukora agoronome we akigumira kuri bureau gusa kandi umuhinzi amukeneye mu murima &ldquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikindi kintu kandi cyagarutsweho mubyaba bitera kwiyongera kw&rsquo;ibiciro harimo no kuba agaciro k&rsquo;ifaranga ry&rsquo;u Rwanda karagabanutse ,ati &ldquo;Ifaranga ryacu naryo ririmo kubigiramo uruhare nubwo ntahugukiwe cyane n&rsquo;ibya politike y&rsquo;amafaranga ariko ntekereza ko iyo ryataye agaciro bituma ibintu bigura menshi&rdquo; Undi ati &ldquo;tuzirikane ko izamuka ry&rsquo;igiciro ribayeho&nbsp; ubu ritigeze ribaho mu myaka icumi. Ibi bihurirana n&rsquo;itakara ryagaciro kifaranga katabayeho muri iyo myaka mvuze. Izamuka ry&rsquo;ibiciro rero&nbsp; ryahuriranye na phenomene 2: global economic crisis yatumye ibiciro ku isoko mpuzamahanga bihanuka maze ibihugu bikomeye bishyira imbaraga iwabyo ngo ubukungu bwabyo budahungabana. U Rwanda rubura aho rwohereza imusaruro. Tubyumve neza muri ibyo bihugu ibiciro ntibyazamutse kuko bo bihagije.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hagarutswe kandi ku kuba u Rwanda rutakibona ibyavaga mu Burundi byunganiraga ibyo ku masoko yo mu Rwanda aho uyu yagize ati &ldquo;Nubwo ari ibyavuba ariko ntitwakwirengagiza ko ibyabaye i Burundi byagize ingaruka kuko ibyunganiraga isoko ryacu byahagaze. MwaraBibonyeko ibiciro byimbuto byatumbagiye.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Abahinzi bagaragaje icyakorwa ngo ibi bibazo bibonerwe umuti </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&ldquo;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Guha umwanya umuhinzi no kumutega amatwi</li>\r\no<li>kongera ingufu mu bukangurambaga ku muryango (house to house sensitization)</li>\r\no<li>gukebura abakangurambaga ndetse na ba agro/ vet bakinjira kuri terrain not mu biro.</li>\r\no<li>gushishikariza urwego rwabikorers kugira uruhare mu kuzamura ubuhinzi. Niba ari campany igura ikanatunganya ibikomoka ku bigori yagombye no kwigisha abakiriya babo imihingire mizima</li>\r\no<li>Kwegereza abahinzi ubumenyi. Ibiganiro ku maradiyo ntibihagije bifatwa nk&rsquo;ivanjili. Inzego zibanze mu midugudu nutugari nibabigire ibyabo</li>\r\no<li>Korandebe iruta vuganumve. Abahinzi ntangarugero dufite si abo gusingizwa ahubwo nihakorwe ingendoshuri zabahinzi zigamije kungura ubumenyi ababukoraga mu kajagari</li>\r\no<li>ishingwa amatsinda y&rsquo;ubuhinzi (club agricoles)</li>\r\no<li>Service yiteganyagihe ikwiye kuva mu imenyesha n&rsquo;imibare ahubwo amakuru akegerezwa abahinzi binyuze mu tugari n&rsquo;imidugudu. (Decentralisation du service meteo et conversion du message visant la bonne comprehension par l&rsquo;agriculteur)</li>\r\no<li>Gutanga amakuru y&rsquo;iteganyagihe muri period ndende bitari iby&rsquo;icyumweru kimwe imbere cyangwa rikavugwa nk&rsquo;amateka kandi ayo makuru agashyirwa mu mvugo yumvwa n&rsquo;umuhinzi byoroshye</li>\r\no<li>Gushyira abahinzi mu byiciro bakitabwaho hakurikijwe ubumenyi bwabo n&rsquo;ubushobozi bafite .</li>\r\no<li>Gushyiraho amategeko n&rsquo;amabwiriza ku gihugu atuma abakora ubuhinzi bose n&rsquo;abafatanyabikirwa nabo bashyira mu bikorwa</li>\r\no<li>Kongera uburyo bwo Gukoresha ikoranabuhanga mu buhinzi (kuhira imyaka, gufumbira, kurwanya, &hellip;. ) ku buryo butanga umusaruro uhagije kandi urambye .</li>\r\no<li>Gutunganya ibishaka bikabyazwa umusaruro uhanije ku rugero rw&rsquo;ubuso hakoreshejwe amazi aboneka muri ibyo bishanga n&rsquo;inyongeramusaruro.</li>\r\no<li>Gushishikariza abagorome ku nzego zitandukanye gukunda ubuhinzi .<strong>&ldquo;</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byose ntago byagarajwe hano bitewe n&rsquo;uko ari ikiganiro kirekire cyane hagiye hatoranywamo imirongo migari ikavugwa muri make.</li>\r\no<li>Amazina yabatanze ibitekerezo ntago yagaragajwe muri iyi nkuru gusa amagambo yose ari mu utwuguruzo n&rsquo;utwugarizo (&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;) yose yandikuwe uko yanditse mu kiganiro.</li>\r\no<li>Ibiganiro nk&rsquo;iki biba buri ku Cyumweru.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Ushaka gukurikira ibi biganiro ukaba uri umuhinzi cyangwa umugoronome ku rwego urwo arirwo rwose nawe wasaba kujya k&rsquo;urubuga rwa YEAN Whatsapp unyuze kuri nimero ikurikira: +250 788 845 727.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','3',1604,40,'2016-01-10 03:30:21','Ubuhinzi Bwacu',0,'online','no','no'),(145,'Ubuhinzi bwacu: IHEREZO RY\'UMUSARURO W\'UMUHINZI','inyanya ffd.jpg','<div>\r\n<p>Bahinzi Borozi nshuti z&rsquo;ubuhinzi, Kuri iki cyumweru taliki ya 25/09/2016 hakozwe ikiganiro UBUHINZI BWACU . Nk&rsquo;uko bisanzwe ku Cyumweru saa mbiri ku mbuga za YEAN Rwanda tuba turi mu Kiganiro UBUHINZI BWACU , tukaba twari turi kuganira &nbsp;ku nsanganyamatsiko igira iti &rdquo; IHEREZO RY&rsquo;UMUSARURO W&rsquo;UMUHINZI&rdquo; . Gahunda yo gushishikariza abahinzi guhinga neza ngo babone umusaruro mwiza irakomeje , <strong>hanyuma dutekereze igihe umusaruro umaze kuboneka bigenda bite?</strong> <strong>Turibanda kuri ibi</strong>:<em> Ubwiza n&rsquo;ubwinshi bw&rsquo;umusaruro , Uburyo umusaruro ukoreshwa, Kongerera umusaruro agaciro, Kubika Umusaruro igihe kirekire .</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abitabiriye ikiganiro batangiye bagaruka cyane ku buryo umusaruro uboneka igihe gito ukaba uhagije yemwe ugasanga bimwe byabuze abaguzi, ariko hashira igihe gito ugasanga byashize, ibiciro bikazamuka cyane ku masoko. Aha ubwo twakoraga ikiganiro umuhinzi yavuzeko inkebo y&rsquo;inyanya igeze ku mafaranga 5000rwf kandi hari igihe ijya igura amafaranga 60,000rwf.uyu n&rsquo;abo bafatanyije umwuga wo guhinga inyanya I Matimba ati &rdquo;IGICIRO NI AMAHIRWE &ldquo; . Haganiriwe byinshi kuri iyi ngingo kandi buri wese yagiye atanga ingero mu buhinzi bwe .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aha tugiye kubikubira mu ngingo z&rsquo;ingenzi zigaragaza imirongo migari yaganiriweho .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ubwiza n&rsquo;ubwinshi bw&rsquo;umusaruro.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Muri make ubwiza bw&rsquo;umusaruro buracyari hasi ,mu gihe utanatunganyijwe bugira ingaruka mbi ku musaruro mwinshi cyangwa uboneye uba wabonetse .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hari imbogamizi zigaragara zituma umusaruro utaboneka nk&rsquo;uko bikwiye&nbsp; :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; &ldquo;Ibikorwaremezo bidahagije cyangwa bitaboneye, nk&rsquo;ubuhunikiro bw&rsquo; umusaruro&nbsp; igihe&nbsp; hategerejwe kugurishwa&rdquo;,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; &ldquo;gutunganya umusaruro&nbsp; bigabanya ubuziranenge, aha twavuga nk&rsquo; Urugero rw&rsquo; umuhinzi uhuje ikibando&nbsp; ubwiza n&rsquo;ubuziranenge bwawo butandukanye n&rsquo;umuceri wasarujwe imashini zimwe bakoresha ibirenge&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&ldquo; Ubwanikiro&nbsp; budafite ubuziranenge. Urugero hari aho ugera ugasanga banitse ibigori kuri sheeting cyangwa hasi. Ni cyo cyagihe umuhinzi nagurisha hazaba harimo amabuye cyangwa itaka. Niba rwiyemezamirimo&nbsp; ashaka kunguka bizamuhombera birumvikana nawe ahagarike kugurira abo bahinzi&rdquo;. Uyu ati : &ldquo;Ni gute umuhinzi ahinga ibigori akabura isoko kandi uzahagarare k&rsquo;umupaka wa Gatuna ubare amakamyo ahinjira buri saha azanye ibigori munganda zikora processing! Wabisobanura ute?&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; &ldquo;Kumutsa&nbsp; no kubika umusaruro neza. Ibi bikomereye umuhinzi dufite&nbsp; uyu munsi&nbsp; kuko kwanika, kumutsa no kubika&nbsp; umusaruro&nbsp; ku mbuto zibikeneye usanga bitamworoheye kuko bakoresha ingufu z&rsquo;izuba aho udashobora kumenya&nbsp; urugero rw&rsquo;ubushyuhe cyangwa ububobere imbuto zawe zifite. Uru ni urwego rwagombye gushyirwamo ingufu na leta kuko birenze ubushobozi bw&rsquo; umuhinzi. Gusa twibuke ko byakemuka mu gihe abahinzi bibumbiye hamwe kandi hari amategeko n&rsquo;amabwiriza agenga imicungire yabo&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&ldquo; Imitwarire y&rsquo;umusaruro ku mahunikiro no ku masoko. Aha harimo ikibazo kuko nta bikoresho biha umutekano umusaruro ngo udata ubuziranenge bwawo. Urugero umuhinzi mukubitana ajyanye inyanya mu ntebo ari bukore kilometero eshatu ugasanga zimwe zamenetse umutobe urajojoba bityo ingano n&rsquo; ubwiza bikagabanuka kuko&nbsp; n&rsquo;izisigaye usanga zabaye imineke&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; &ldquo;Ibikorwaremezo: imihanda idatunganyije amasoko atajyanye n&rsquo;ubwoko bw&rsquo; umusaruro. Nk&rsquo;urugero ngo niba ari isoko ry&rsquo;inyanya rigire uburyo ryubakwa ndetse&nbsp; n&rsquo;ibihabitswe bigire ubuziranenge. Niba ari imboka uko zibikwa uko zitwarwa ntibitume zinamba ngo umuhinzi ahahombere&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubwinshi bw&rsquo;umusaruro nabwo bwagarutsweho &ldquo;Ubundi mu Rwanda ntitwagakwiye kuvuga ngo umusaruro wabuze isoko kuko ibyo duhinga ubwacu ntibihagije rwose! Urebye umusaruro w&rsquo;imbere mugihugu uko ungana na population (consomateurs) rwose turacyari kure cyane kandi rwose kwihuza kw&rsquo;abahinzi byo byagorana nta rwego rwa leta rubahagarariye ngo rubareberere!&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&ldquo; Erega processing ntabwo yashingira kubuhinzi buri seasonal (bushingiye ku bihe)&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; &ldquo;Hakorwa ubukangurambaga cyane mu itangira ry&rsquo;igihembwe cy&rsquo;ubuhinzi, Ariko iyo abahinzi bamaze gutera imbuto imbaraga zakoreshwaga mu iyamamazabuhinzi zigabanukaho nka 50% (my personal observation ), atari ibyo abahinzi umusaruro wifuzwa mu bwiza no mu bwinshi waboneka dore ko nta muhinzi utifuza inyungu&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kongerera umusaruro agaciro</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aha dusangamo&nbsp; uburyo umusaruro utunganywa kuva mu murima kugeza mu buhunikiro. Gusa twibuke ko mu gihe&nbsp; ibi by&rsquo; ibanze bidatunganye kuwongerera agaciro&nbsp; bigorana. Kugeza ubu uko abahinzi babibona ni uku:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Abaguzi benshi ku bahinzi batatanyije&nbsp;</strong> ;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Usanga abahinzi batibumbiye hamwe buri wese&nbsp; ashaka kwivanaho ibyo yahinze bityo bagahendwa ndetse abenshi ntibagaruze ayo bashoye, banayagaruza akaba ari ku rugero rwo hasi cyane.&nbsp; mugihe bafite umurongo bagenderaho bashobora kugira ijambo ku musaruro wabo. Urugero nta muhinzi ufite ubushobozi bwo guhunika inyanya mu minsi irenze itatu kuko zaba zangiritse. Nyamara baramutse bari hamwe byatanga ingufu zo kubaka nka chambre froide babikamo umusaruro noneho bagafata umwanya wo kumvikana n&rsquo;umuguzi kuko ntacyaba kibirukansa&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Nta nganda ziciriritse cyangwa ubucuruzi&nbsp; bwongerera agaciro umusaruro. </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iki cyagarutsweho cyane aho bagize bati &ldquo;Isoko kujyanayo ibigori urahomba. Jyanayo kawunga!!!&rdquo; ariko hakagaraga ikibazo nanone cy&rsquo;uko &ldquo;dufite ikibazo cya postharvest,Urebye condition zisabwa ku bigori bijya muri Minimex ziragoye kuburyo utabasha kuzigeraho udafite ubwanikiro bwiza.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Gusa twibuke ko imyumvire y&rsquo;abaguzi aha naho ari ikibazo ahitamo kugura ibihendutse atitaye ku isuku n&rsquo;ingaruka. Bigatuma rero n&rsquo;ufite gahunda yo kongerera ibye agaciro ahitamo gukora nk&rsquo;abandi basanzwe.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uburyo umusaruro&nbsp; ukoreshwa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ukurikije amabarura yatambutse y&rsquo;ubuhinzi (Seasonal Agriculture Survey) usanga Abahinzi benshi bahingira kurya kuko umusaruro wo basagurira amasoko ukiri hasi. Ibi bifite impamvu zitandukanye zirimo&nbsp; umusaruro muke uturutse ku bihe by&rsquo;ikirere, guhinga twinshi&nbsp; no kutitabira guhinga igihingwa kimwe ngo babone umusaruro uhagije ku buso bahinga, bitewe n&rsquo;uko ubukungu bwabo buba bukeneye&nbsp; kwitabwaho usanga na duke batumarira ku masoko banahenzwe. Muri make mbona umusaruro wabo ugishingiye ku &ldquo;maramuko&rdquo; kurusha &ldquo;ku kwihaza no gusagurira isoko&rdquo; . Uyu yagize ati &ldquo;Guhunika nibyiza ariko habonetse uburyo bwo kohereza umusaruro hanze byaba byiza .bikaba byatuma umuhinzi ahinga afite isoko&rdquo; ariko biza kugaragara ko &ldquo;Mbere yo kubyohereza hanze twareba niba twihagije.Turacyakenera kawunga iva hanze. Ndumva hashirwaho inganda nyinshi na gahunda y&rsquo;uko izo nganda zajya zigezwaho umusaruro for possessing(wo gutunganya)&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kubika umusaruro igihe kirekire</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Muri rusange aha haracyari ikibazo. Hubatswe amakusanyirizo hirya no hino nubwo nayo adahagije ariko nayo&nbsp; ntabona&nbsp; umusaruro. Aho bikorwa bigaragara ko bitanga&nbsp; ihumure ku muhinzi ko atazabura imbuto kandi bituma umusaruro uhurizwa hamwe n&rsquo;abaguzi bakawusanga uhujwe . Gusa hagaragaramo imbogamizi:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; &ldquo;Aho ari umuhinzi ntazi neza inyungu avanamo uretse kumva ko ihinga nirigera atazabura imbuto&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&ldquo; Ubwumvikane buke ku ngano y&rsquo; umusaruro ugemurwa n&rsquo;uwo umuhinzi&nbsp; asigaragana cyane ko&nbsp; umuhinzi usanga kubera gushaka guhinga twinshi nta n&rsquo; umusaruro uhagije abona ugasanga ntibashaka kubyitabira&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; &ldquo;Kugeza ubu amakusanyirizo aboneka&nbsp; ni ay&rsquo;ibihingwa nk&rsquo;ibigori, ibishyimbo n&rsquo;ibirayi. Usanga ibindi bihingwa nk&rsquo;ibitoki n&rsquo;ibindi nta buryo buhari bwo kubihunika igihe kirekire&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Muri make uru rwego ruracyacyeneye ingufu no kwaguka kandi Leta ikabigiramo uruhare&nbsp; kuko nta muhinzi wabasha kwiyubakira ubu buhunikiro bugezweho&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hari ibihingwa byamaze kubonerwa umuti w&rsquo;iherezo ry&rsquo;umusaruro wabyo</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ku byagiye bigarukwaho hatinzwe cyane ku kuba hari ibihingwa byiganjemo ngengabukungu bifite isoko rihoraho nk&rsquo;ikawa,icyayi, ibireti,&hellip; ndetse n&rsquo;ibindi ngandura rugo birimo ibirayi, ibigori . Abahinzi babyo bemezako nubwo hataburamo utubazo duto duto ariko ntago bajya babura isoko burundu. Abahinzi kandi basabye ko hagakwiye kwigwa uburyo hashyirwaho ikurikiranwa n&rsquo;igeno ry&rsquo;iherezo ry&rsquo;umusaruro wa buri gihingwa (Value chain). Uyu yagize ati &ldquo;Hagakwiye no gukorwa inyigo ku isoko rya buri gihingwa cyangwa ibikomoka kubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi value chain yose ikajya ahagaragara kandi ababishinzwe bose bakamenyekana ibibazo bafite bikamenyekana&rdquo; &ldquo;Icyo gukora value chain ya buri gihingwa ni cyo gisubizo cyonyine njye mbona kuko aho ikibazo kiri hazagaragazwa ibisubizo bishakwe!&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bimwe mu byakorwa </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Kubaka ibikorwa remezo&nbsp; bikozwe na Leta ifatanyije n&rsquo;abikorera&nbsp; mu rwego rwo kongera&nbsp; ubwiza bw&rsquo;umusaruro byanaba intango yo kuzamura agaciro kawo&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Gukomeza ubukangurambaga ku bahinzi mu guhinga&nbsp; ibihingwa hakurikijwe uko byagenwe no kubabumbira hamwe mu rwego rwo guhesha agaciro&nbsp; umusaruro wabo&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Guteza imbere ikoranabuhanga mu bakora ubuhinzi&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Ndumva nkumusanzu wacu Abagronome, mugihe twigisha abahinzi twajya dutinda kukintu cya market targeting (guhingira isoko uzi neza)&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Guhunika umusaruro bikwiriye kurebwa mu bice bibiri:Ibihingwa byangirika vuba (Imboga, ibijumba, ibitoki, n&rsquo;Imbuto); n&rsquo;Ibihingwa bitangirika vuba (ibigori, ibishyimbo,&hellip;)&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Gushyira imbaraga mu kwigisha uko babika umusaruro muburyo bwiza kurwego rw&rsquo;umuhinzi&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;gushiramo imbaraga agri value chain ya buri gihingwa , aho ikibazo kiri hagaragazwe ibisubizo bishakwe&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Abahinzi twagombye guhinga dufite amasezerano yanditse kubijyanye nabazafata umusaruro wacu&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Gukangurira abahinzi guhinga ibihe byose bivuze kuhira mugihe cy&rsquo;impeshyi&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Uko minisiteri ibishinzwe ishyiramo imbaraga ikangurira abahinzi guhinga niko na minisiteri ishinzwe ubucuruzi yakabaye ifata ingamba zizatuma ibyo umuhinzi yejeje &lsquo;bitamusubiza ku isuka&rsquo; ahubwo bikamusunikira&nbsp; mu buhinzi bw&rsquo;umwuga, imufasha kugurisha neza (naho ubundi condition zisabwa ku bwiza zagashobotse ariko zongera agaciro n&rsquo;igishoro kandi azabona Frw make ku&nbsp; kilo )&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Ni hubakwe &lsquo;filiaire&rsquo; ya buri gihingwa, abahinzi bihuze kugira ngo bakore bimwe kandi bashakire isoko hamwe ari nako biyubakira ubushobizi&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byose ntago byagarajwe hano bitewe n&rsquo;uko ari ikiganiro kirekire cyane hagiye hatoranywamo imirongo migari ikavugwa muri make.</li>\r\no<li>Amazina yabatanze ibitekerezo ntago yagaragajwe muri iyi nkuru gusa amagambo yose ari mu utwuguruzo n&rsquo;utwugarizo (&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;) yose yandikuwe uko yanditse mu kiganiro.</li>\r\no<li>Ikiganiro nk&rsquo;iki kiba buri ku Cyumweru.</li>\r\no<li>Ushaka gukurikira ibi biganiro ukaba uri umuhinzi/umworozi cyangwa umugoronome/veterineri ku rwego urwo arirwo rwose nawe wasaba kujya k&rsquo;urubuga rwa YEAN Whatsapp unyuze kuri nimero ikurikira: +250 788 845 727 ,wakurikira YEAN kuri facebook cyangwa kuri twitter #UbuhinziBwacu @YEAN_Rwanda</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n','3',2886,40,'2016-09-28 18:23:52','Ubuhinzi Bwacu',0,'online','no','no'),(146,'Ubuhinzi Bwacu : Ibitekerezo ku ngingo igira iti: KUHIRA IMYAKA','Kuhira imyaka.png','<div>\r\n<p>Kuri iki cyumweru taliki ya 18/09/2016 mu kiganiro <strong>Ubuhinzi Bwacu</strong> gisanzwe kibageraho buri ku cyumweru, mutegurirwa na YEAN Rwanda , habaye ikiganiro ku nsanganyamatsiko igira iti &rdquo; KUHIRA IMYAKA&rdquo;. Bijyanye n&rsquo;ihinduka ry&rsquo;ikirere Kuhira imyaka ni igikorwa kigaragara ko aricyo cyafasha gukomeza kugira ibiribwa kw&rsquo;isoko. Hagarutswe cyane kuri ibi bikurikira ; Ese abahinzi basobanukiwe n&rsquo;uko bikorwa, Ubushobozi bw&rsquo;umuhinzi, Ibikorwa remezo ,&nbsp; Kuhira ku buryo burambye.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bitewe n&rsquo;ubutumwa bwagiye bugaragara mu kiganiro , abahinzi bagaragaje ko basobanukiwe neza ko ubuhinzi bushingiye ku gutegereza imvura gusa budahagije , bemeza ko Kuhira imyaka ari umusingi washobora guhangana n&rsquo;igabanuka ridasanzwe ry&rsquo;ibiribwa ku masoko ndeste hamwe na hamwe hakagaragara amapfa . Uyu yagize ati &ldquo;<em>Murakoze Ku ngingo nziza ijyanye n&rsquo;ikibazo dufite murikigihe mugihugu cyacu cyane mubuhinzi bw&rsquo;imusozi aho nubu tugitegereje imvura kandi mubona aho season yakabaye igeze, kuhira rero niwo muti mubyukuri kuko dukomeje gukora dutegereje imvura twazikanga turi munzara tutabasha kwikuram</em>o&rdquo; . Muri iki kiganiro hagaragayemo ibitekerezo byinshi mu ngeri zose kuko hakiriwe ubutumwa 1023 buvuga kuri iyi ngingo .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kuhira ni gahunda ya vuba mu buhinzi bwacu</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyi gahunda yo kuhira abahinzi n&rsquo;abakora mu buhinzi bemezako itaramara igihe kinini imenyekanye mu bahinzi ku buryo bw&rsquo;umwuga uretse ahari hasanzwe hakoreshwa ibikoresho byo hambere nk&rsquo;indobo , arozwari,&hellip;. Uyu ati &ldquo;Nkekako kubijyanye no kuhira byo murwanda turacyatangira pe! Kuko usibye no kuhira igasozi n&rsquo;ahari amazi ahoraho naho turacyategereza imvura ntiturashobora gukoresha amazi dufite neza! Turacyari Ku rwego rwo hasi pe! Ariko turakataje muri mobilisation yo kuhira kubuso buto kandi hari n&rsquo;imishinga yisumbuyeho minagri ifite yo gushyiraho irrigation schemes kubuso busa n&rsquo;aho ari bunini nka za Nasho, Gashora mubugesera za Kagitumba na matimba ho bimaze igihe!&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Haracyarimo Imbogamizi ku ruhande rw&rsquo;umuhinzi. </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><strong>Ubumenyi mu buhinzi</strong> no kuhira imyaka biri mubyagarutsweho aho uyu yagize ati:&ldquo;Kuruhande rwanjye rero nsaga uburyo bwo kuhira imyaka abahinzi batarabyitabira ahanini. Bitewe nu bumenyi buke ndetse na mikoro kuko usanga ahanini bisaba uburyo bwo gufata amazi!&rdquo; Uyu nawe yunganiye agira ati &ldquo;Muri Rusange irrigation ningenzi mukongera umusaruro, gusa abahinzi ntibasobanukiwe neza uburyo bikorwa kandi ntanubushobozi bafite mukubikora bagura nkibikoresho bicyenerwa nubwo batanga nkunganire biracyahenze Cyane&rdquo; . Abahinzi&nbsp; ntibarasobanukirwa neza na gahunda y&rsquo;Ubuhinzi Leta ifite &ldquo;Ikindi mbona kikigoranye nuko mu Rwanda usanga irrigation ikorwa na Leta bityo ikajyana na Politike y&rsquo;Ubuhinzi ya Leta kandi rimwe na rimwe ugasanga Abahinzi batayiyumvamo neza ,kuko usanga aho umuhinzi akeneye guhinga urutoki hagenewe guhinga Soya bityo kubyaza umusaruro ya irrigation scheme bikagenda biguruntege&rdquo;. Hagaragajwe kandi ko uburyo bukoreshwa mukuhira abahinzi batabusobanukiwe aho &nbsp;hagaragaye ko hari uburyo bwo kuhira buhenda abahinzi kandi bukabahombya uyu ,yagize ati : &ldquo;Ni ngombwa ko tubwira abahinzi bacu baba baragize amahirwe yo kubona ibyo bikoresho kubikoresha neza kuko n&rsquo;amazi ubwayo tunafite agenda aba ikibazo gikomeye&rdquo;</li>\r\no<li><strong>Amikoro y&rsquo;umuhinzi, </strong>uyu ati &ldquo;Mwaramutse, kuhira biracyari ingorabahizi Ku bahinzi mu Rwanda gusa abenshi bajyenda babimenya, ariko nanone usanga ibikoresho bigihenze Nubwo leta yagerageje kubunganira&hellip;. Mbahe urugero : Matimba twishyura 30.000frw per ha per month aho hari big irrigation Naho Kigali aho dukoresha small scale twishyura 10. 000frw kuhira 1 ha per day. Ibaze muri 30days tuvuge wuhiyemo 12 times Wenda ubwo ni 120.000frw per ha per month.&rdquo; Undi ati &ldquo;turiya tumachine twuhira dukoresha essence turanywa Cyane ! Urugero nkuko per week kuhira 3ha nkoresha 50.000frw Rero si umuhinzi wese wapfa kubishobora!&rdquo;&nbsp; &hellip;., &ldquo;Kuhira ntamuntu utazi uburyo Ari byiza ariko ntanumuntu utazi uburyo bihenze cyane nko kuri level ya economy abahinzi bariho iri hasi&rdquo; uyu nawe ati :&rdquo; Yes ntabwo umuhinzi wacu yashobora kugura mazutu yaburi 3times a week , ahubwo kumufasha kuhira hanyuma akishyura yejeje niyo channel yagakoreshejwe kuko yabonye umusaruro ntabwo yakwanga kwishyura&rdquo;.&nbsp; Imashini zizamura amazi ngo zifite igiciro cyo kuzitunga kikiri hejuru aho uyu yagize ati : &ldquo;Erega cost ya fuel iri Hejuru hari abahinzi twaziguriye barazibika, ubu Buhiza imipira Kuko moteur zikoresha mazutu&rdquo; uyu nawe ati: &ldquo;Njye nakoresheke iriya machine ya essence ariko cost iranga ijya hejuru. Ubu natekerezaga kujya kuri solar kuko yo nta kindi kiguzi.&rdquo;</li>\r\no<li><strong>Inyungu biragoye kuyizera, &ldquo;</strong>Usanga cost ya irrigation na market yacu Itari stable udashobora kubona na return on investment, Jye small scale irrigation muyimbaze ndayizi neza&rdquo;. Bitewe n&rsquo;ubumenyi buke abahinzi biragorana kumenya ikizabyara inyungu n&rsquo;ikitazayibyara bitewe n&rsquo;ibigenda igiciro cy&rsquo;umusaruro wabonetse aho uyu agira ati : &ldquo;abahinzi nabo bagomba guhindura imyumvire pe! Kandi ntiwakuhira amasaka cg ubunyobwa ngo uzunguke! Ariko ibigori nzi ababyuhira bakunguka! Imboga zo zose zirunguka&rdquo; Uyu nawe ati isoko naryo rihindagurika rica intege abahinzi ati &ldquo;Nkubu umuntu dukorana yahinze inyanya aruhira intebo Igura amafaranga 40000 abona azunguka none iri kugura amafaranga 12000</li>\r\no<li><strong>Kutabasha Gufata amazi aturuka ku mvura , </strong>aya mazi iyo afashwe mu gihe cy&rsquo;imvura ashobora gukoreshwa mu gihe imvura icitse hanyuma imyaka ntigire ikibazo cy&rsquo;izuba vuba. Gusa bigaragara ko abahinzi bagifite imbogamizi mugufata aya mazi . Aho uyu yagize ati :&rdquo; Ikibazo nyamukuru nukumenya uko dufata amazi yayandi atera isuri n&rsquo; ayo kumazu , imigezi nibindi hagashyirwamo inkunga yo gufasha abaturage kubanza kubisobanukirwa ahasigaye twagira Imana imvura ikagwa tukayabika tukaba twahora duhinga aho gutegereza imvura&rdquo;. Uyu nawe ati : &ldquo;Urebye amazi areka ahantu hatandukanye mugihe cyimvura wanareba iyo izuba ryacanye ibibazo by&rsquo;amazi biba bihari wibaza impamvu ayo mazi atabikwa&rdquo; , gusa aya mazi leta yashyizeho uburyo bwo kuyafata nubwo bitaragera kuri buri wese uyu ati: &ldquo;uyumunsi dukoresha dam sheet (damushiti) kuko niyo Leta yunganira ariko Njyewe mbona hakwiye kwifashishwa ibigega kuko nibyo bifata amazi neza kandi bigatwara umwanya muto&rdquo;,</li>\r\no<li><strong>Isoko ry&rsquo;umusaruro ,</strong>Abahinzi ndetse n&rsquo;abafasha abahinzi bagaragaje ko umusaruro iyo wabonetse ku bantu bitabiriye kuhira akenshi ubura isoko rifatika ribaha inyungu urebye n&rsquo;ibyo baba barashoyemo , uyu ati &ldquo;Aho niho hagomba kugororwa hajyanye na market stability noneho umuhinzi agashora yiteguye kunguka bitewe nigihingwa yashoyemo , ibyo ndibaza Ko nayo ari topic twagateguye tukayikoraho ikiganiro&rdquo;. Uyu nawe yungamo ati &ldquo;Ariko byo muri small scale irrigation technology success stories zirimo cyane kandi barunguka pe iyo bahuye n&rsquo;isoko ryiza kuko bareza neza! Wenda ikibazo kibera Ku isoko ariko production iba yagenze neza pe!&rdquo;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibikorwa remezo mu kuhira imyaka ni bike</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kugeza ubu hari ibikorwa remezo byagiye bishyirwa ahantu hatandukanye ngo bifashe abahinzi guhangana n&rsquo;ikibazo cy&rsquo;imvura nke . Abahanzi bagaragaje ko nko mu duce twa Nasho, Gashora, Kagitumba, na Matimba bimaze kumenyerwa kuhira ku buso bunini gusa bemeza ko &nbsp;&ldquo;ibizihutisha kongera ubuso bwuhirwa mu Rwanda ni small scale irrigation technology (Kuhira ku buso buto)kuko byibuze abenshi mubahinzi bashobora kubigeraho doreko harimo na nkunganire!&rdquo; kandi&nbsp; nonone &ldquo;Ubukangurambaga RAB irabukora muri department ya LIM mugashami ka SSIT kandi abahinzi baguze ibyo bikoresho barunganirwa kugera kuri 50% bahabwa amahugurwa kandi bagakurikiranwa ikindi gishya abari muri iyi gahunda batangiye gukusanya amakuru bareba niba koko abakoresha ibi bikoresho bunguka&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Abahinzi bafite ubushobozi bwo kuhira babona inyungu</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nubwo hejuru twagarutse kuburyo abahinzi badafite ubushobozi bwo kuhira , Abashoboye kubona ubwo bushozi bavuga ko babona inyungu bitewe n&rsquo;ibyo bahinga ,uyu ati &ldquo;Icyo mbona irrigation iri gufasha abahinzi cyane muri kano gace ka Nyagatare cyane nkunda kuganira n abahinzi baho iyo ugeze kunkengero z&rsquo;umuvumba ukareba inyanya zihari ,ukagera Rwangingo ubuhamya buratangwa kandi ni inyungu barayibona hari n&rsquo; uwanyibwiriye ati njye nguze moteur nkayikoresha umwaka umwe niyo nayitanga ayange mba nayakuyeho.gusa nanone isoko rira cyagoye cyane&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyakorwa ngo kuhira imyaka byigerweho vuba </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>&ldquo;leta Yari ikwiye kubaka ibikorwa remezo Wenda hagashakishwa uburyo abaturage Bajya Bishyura amafaranga mbese igasa Naho ibakodesheje!&rdquo;</li>\r\no<li>Urebye imihindagurikire y&rsquo;ikirere kuhira nicyo twategaho ahazaza ku buhinzi. Leta, abafatanyabikorwa, abahinzi n&rsquo;undi wese bireba nibongere ingufu. Biramutse bikunze ibice bishoboka kuhira byose bikabona ibikorwa remezo uburasirazuba n&rsquo;amajyepfo byadutunga.&rdquo;</li>\r\no<li>&ldquo;Gukomeza gukangurira abahinzi babishoboye kuhira ku buso buto kuko nubwo bihenze ariko nibyo dufite bihendutse mu bindi byose&rdquo; &ldquo;Ndemeranya nuwavuze ko small scale irrigation technology ishobora kugira impinduka nkeya itanga, Kuko urugero, abahinzi bacu&nbsp; twabaguriye moteur inywa 2litres za essence ikuhira amasaha ane&rdquo;</li>\r\no<li>&ldquo;Hashakwe utumachine tutanywa Cyane cyangwa se hashakwe uburyo isoko ryaba stable umuntu ashore mu kuhira azi ko azagaruza aye akanunguka&rdquo;</li>\r\no<li>&ldquo;Hakwiye gukorwa inyigo zirambye ku buryo bwo kuhira ku buso bunini, haba mu bishanga cyangwa I musozi murwego rwo kugira uburyo bwo kuhira buhoraho kandi burambye.&rdquo;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byose ntago byagarajwe hano bitewe n&rsquo;uko ari ikiganiro kirekire cyane hagiye hatoranywamo imirongo migari ikavugwa muri make.</li>\r\no<li>Amazina yabatanze ibitekerezo ntago yagaragajwe muri iyi nkuru gusa amagambo yose ari mu utwuguruzo n&rsquo;utwugarizo (&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;) yose yandikuwe uko yanditse mu kiganiro.</li>\r\no<li>Ikiganiro nk&rsquo;iki kiba buri ku Cyumweru.</li>\r\no<li>Ushaka gukurikira ibi biganiro ukaba uri umuhinzi/umworozi cyangwa umugoronome/veterineri ku rwego urwo arirwo rwose nawe wasaba kujya k&rsquo;urubuga rwa YEAN Whatsapp unyuze kuri nimero ikurikira: +250 788 845 727 ,wakurikira YEAN kuri facebook cyangwa kuri twitter #UbuhinziBwacu @YEAN_Rwanda</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n','3',1961,40,'2016-09-21 18:45:12','Ubuhinzi Bwacu ',0,'online','no','no'),(156,'No matter what it will cost me, I know what is behind growing Papaya KWIZERA Christophe','Kwizera Christophe .jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\">Horticulturist by profession Kwizera Christophe member of YEAN-Rwanda and University graduate in Rural Development and Agribusiness, after completion of my studies I didn&rsquo;t find any job and decided to start my project. By that I realized that my first richness is my mind, skills and knowledge; plus land as opportunities with my commitment and engagement as my passion. My farming activities are located in Eastern Province, Bugesera District, Musenyi Sector: Musenyi, Musenyi and Gicaca Cell.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\">I, then started a short survey and finally found that many people don&rsquo;t value papaya. Finally I decide to make progressive researches in youth, women and neighborhoods (especially in Uganda). I started by 5 local seeds in my plot, with approximately 10 fruits per tree, with investment of 5000 Rwandan francs and with 30,000 Rwandan francs as my income per month</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\">By now am working with potential local farmers to develop nurseries and seedlings of improved varieties from Brazil and Indonesia to be distributed in my community and I am expecting to use 500,000 Rwandan francs as investment and expecting to have an income of around 720,000 Rwandan francs per month.In short that is how my journey to agribusiness farming activities started.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\">In the near future, I wish to have more than 1 hectare covered by papaya trees and increase my income from 1000 trees to 5000 trees and I wish to start diversifying my products from Papaya by making juices and other papaya made products.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\">I decided to grow Papaya because not only being a very quick generating money fruit it can also be used as medicine, making juices and other derivatives; papaya give quick money to farmer ; environmentally, this is a good tree that fights against erosion, wind breaking and soil fertilization.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\">Though papaya has a wide market, its producers in Rwanda are still few so I grow this trees in a very suitable ecological conditions of Eastern, Bugesera Bugesera District in Musenyi Sector. For me to improve my farming activities am attending entrepreneurial trainings in different institutions and organizations, farm visits, contract signing with some farmers and sponsorship from BDF.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\">As a young agricultural entrepreneur I face some challenges: Like other businesses, agriculture also requires a capital which is a very high discouraging factor that I am also facing. Promotion of production also is a big problem which requires a high connection and involvement of different institutions .</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\">I can Suggest that the government through banks and microfinance institutions, should facilitate Agriculture business start- up and find a possible way to solve market problem by linking farmers to markets according to the production.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\">My message to fellow youth is that Agriculture is a profession, When it is well done it helps get quick with high income. So my dear fellows, don&rsquo;t hesitate to get engaged and invest in agriculture because all of us will not be working in Office.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\"><em>A story by NIYIGABA Etienne (email: niyigabat@gmail.com)</em></span></p>\r\n','4',4662,3,'2016-07-27 15:08:22','Papaya',1,'online','yes','images/Kwizerachristophe.jpg'),(158,'I Call him Mr. TWEZE , Meet Hubert HIRWA and his TWEZE organic liquidÂ fertilizer','Tweze .jpg','<p>&lsquo;&rsquo;Organic farming is holistic system everything we do is connected and carefully planned so we remain sustainable economically and environmentally.&rsquo;&rsquo; Hirwa Hubert</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My name is Hubert HIRWA. I am 26 years old. I was born in a family that lives from agricultural income in Rwanda and my mother is an Irish potatoes farmer. I was inspired by her as she is very courageous. I have graduated in University of Rwanda, College of Agriculture, Animal Sciences and Veterinary Medicine. I hold a Bachelor&rsquo;s Degree with Honors in Soil Sciences and Environment Management. I am District Environment Facilitator in Rwanda Environment Management Authority (REMA). I am student in Masters of Environment and Development Studies (MEDS) with specialization in Environmental Economics and Natural Resources Management in University of Lay Adventists of Kigali (UNILAK).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How did the TWEZE Idea come out &hellip;.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>After participating in many trainings like Rwanda Entrepreneurial Mindset by Rwanda Development Board (RDB) in collaboration with Grow Movement; I started thinking out of box where I find many opportunities in my mind. With purpose of valorize what I have studied in Agriculture with innovational spirit; I discovered TWEZE liquid organic fertilizer where I use compost materials by diluting them and get black liquid which is used as fertilizer and it has the ability to suppress several foliar diseases as well as seed and root rot. It influences the increase of tomato trees (<em>Solanum betaceum</em>) seed quality and yield. I want to implement the project called <strong>&rsquo;&rsquo;<em>Integrated farming system of Tomato trees and banana with Tweze liquid</em></strong><em> <strong>organic fertilizer to maximize the profit</strong>.</em>&rsquo;&rsquo; in our village of Kinoni/Ntaruka.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In Africa especially in Rwanda, the accessibility of compost to farmers and on agricultural markets is low compared to chemical fertilizers. The idea of our project refers to the fact that <strong>Tweze</strong> (<em>liquid organic compost</em>) is a form of compost which is easy to be accessible to the market and therefore can reduce the environmental destruction by agricultural inputs, as well as improving the soil fertility.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As my knowledge in organic agriculture increases the yield increases, the safer the product. The situation is good where I use to teach small kids nursery preparation and care activities in order to transform their mind with the spirit of initiating the Green Economy concepts using organic matter. I effort to be very conscious of my role as a good agricultural advisor by promoting the use of organic fertilizer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Care, however, has been also given in creation of job for the people around the project where I use daily sixteen (16) women, one agronomist and other smallholder farmers. Many hardworking women and men come to me to buy tomato trees seedlings, to get advisor, to learn how to use organic fertilizer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am very motivated and excited in doing agriculture. My target is to promote sustainable agriculture by mitigating climate change effects. Previously, I taught and trained one of the young farmer who cultivates the tomato tree. The yield increases at 86% of the normal. One tree rises the yield of 14 to 20kg/tree.&rsquo;&rsquo; <em>Tweze is very productive and it improves my livelihood; now there is no malnutrition disease in my house</em>&rsquo;&rsquo; said Gahungu Theoneste.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Once I get more funds &hellip;&hellip;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I will use the direct sales to customers, inventory and transportation. The target customers for this product are smallholder farmers, cooperatives, agricultural enterprises, shop owners and Agrotechs. The product will be selled using negotiation methods, Mobile money, e-commerce using the under creation website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I submitted this Project In a worldwide competition Of young Agripreneurs organized by at <a href=\"http://g/\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">GFAR</span></a> and <a href=\"http://cgiar.org/\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">CGIAR</span></a> and if your admire my idea you can vote for me here <a href=\"http://blog.gfar.net/2016/02/25/yap-proposal-32-integrated-farming-tomato-trees-banana-hubert-hirwa-rwanda/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">YAP Proposal #32: &ldquo;Integrated Farming of Tomato Trees and Banana&rdquo; (Hubert Hirwa, Rwanda)</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Some Picture from his project </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"198179358706204958\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-691\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2016/03/198179358706204958.jpg\" style=\"height:917px; width:516px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tomato tree under TWEZE Application .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"458799769409635859\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-692\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2016/03/458799769409635859.jpg\" style=\"height:917px; width:516px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nursery of Tomato Tree using TWEZE</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"503564755156356264\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-693\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2016/03/503564755156356264.jpg?w=863\" style=\"height:387px; width:516px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tweze Liquid organic fertilizer</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>A story by NIYIGABA Etienne , email : niyigabat@gmail.com</em></p>\r\n','4',3747,3,'2016-03-08 05:50:23','Ifumbire',1,'online','no','no'),(159,'Ubuhinzi ndabukunda kandi nishimira gufasha abahinzi aho nkora Aimable Ibanga','Aimable Ibanga.png','<p>Mu Buhinzi bw&rsquo;umwuga hari byinshi bikorwa , ushobora kuba wajya mu buhinzi nyirizina nk&rsquo;umuhinzi cyangwa ukaba waba Umugoronome ufasha abahinzi mu mirimo yabo ya buri munsi . Aimable Ibanga we akora ubuhinzi afasha abahinzi mu mirimo yabo ya buri munsi nka agoronome mu mushinga GFI w&rsquo;ikigo cy&rsquo;igihugu gishinzwe iterambere ry&rsquo;ubuhinzi RAB . Twagiranye ikiganiro nawe atubwira byinshi ku buryo akora ubuhinzi kandi ari cyo kintu yishimira mu buzima bwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Nkorera hano muri Nyagatare aho mfatanya n&rsquo;abandi batekinisiye gufasha abahinzi gukora ubuhinzi bw&rsquo;umwuga twifashishije uburyo bwo kuhira bugezweho&hellip;. Uyu ni umushinga wa RAB muri Gahunda yayo yo&nbsp; Kuhira imyaka . Maze hano imyaka igeze kuri itatu kandi ndabona ubuhinzi turi kugenda dufasha abahinzi kubugira bwiza kurushaho twifashishije iyi tekinoroji yo kuhira&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ese ubona akazi kawe nk&rsquo;urubyiruko hari icyo kamariye abahinzi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umurimo nkora na bagenzi banjye wafashije abahinzi haba mu mibereho ndetse no mu myumvire no nese iyo ubona umuntu agura imodoka cyangwa akubaka inzu mu mafaranga yakuye muri ubu buhinzi dukorera hano urumva wowe hataba harimo impinduka ifatika. Urwo ni urugero rworoshye ariko no ku rundi ruhande abahinzi bakorera mu mashyirahamwe,barabizi ko imirima atari iya leta ni iyabo niyo mpamvu bakora cyane.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tuvuye ku mibereho tukajya ku musaruro, ubona ubu buryo bwo kuhira bwarahinduye iki k&rsquo;umusaruro?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibyo byo birigaragaza dukora uko dushoboye mu masomo twize ndetse no mu bikoresho tuba dufite (byo kuhira) umusaruro ukaba mwinshi ushoboka nawe urabyumva ko tutarira ngo twabuze imvura!!. Umusaruro wo rwose warirongereye nk&rsquo;ubu ahantu havaga toni 2 z&rsquo;ibigori turi kuhasarura toni 7&nbsp; urumvako hari impinduka ifatika.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ikibazo cy&rsquo;amasoko y&rsquo;umusaruro w&rsquo;ubuhinzi ko giteye inkeke mwe mubigenza mute?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Twe nk&rsquo;uko nabikubwiye hano dukora ubuhinzi bw&rsquo;umwuga , Amasoko ntitujya tuyabura tuba dufitanye amasezerano n&rsquo;abaguzi mbere y&rsquo;uko dusarura cyangwa mbere y&rsquo;uko duhinga nyine nawe urabyumva hakorwa ibishoboka byose ngo baboneke . Nta musaruro wa hano ujya upfa ubusa .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aimable ese waba ufite ubuhinzi bwawe ku giti cyawe ?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubuhinzi ndabufite ntago watoza abandi guhinga wowe ngo ubure kubikora , ntago narebera abandi basarura ngo ntahire kubafasha gusa, najye ndahinga Ibigori n&rsquo;inyanya.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ni iyihe nama wagira urubyiruko ku ijyanye no gukora ubuhinzi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubuhinzi ni umwuga ubereye urubyiruko iyo ubikoze ubikunze kandi ukitanga uko ushoboye kose . Ufite aho yabona yahinga rwose namushishikariza guhinda kuko umusaruro uraboneka kandi washoye make , ikibazo kiza iyo wabikoze nabi utabanje kubitegura. Ikindi mpora mbona abantu tuvuga muri YEAN ngo nta gishoro dufite, nje nabagira inama yo gutangira ku bintu bito buhoro buhoro birakura kandi bikagera kuri wa musaruro wifuzaga .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Nonese ubona YEAN hari icyo yaba yaragufashije mu mwuga wawe?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kirahari kini cyane , byonyine kuganira nabandi bahinzi mu mpande zose zigihugu ni kintu gifahsa mukwaguka mu bumenyi najye nkatanga ibyo nzi tugafatanya twese. Ibitekerezo bivugirwa ku mbuga zose bituma abantu bahungukira byinshi kandi tugafatanya buri munsi mu buhinzi bwacu.&nbsp; Nasaba ahubwo ko habaho kwegera urubyiruko rukiri mu mashuri y&rsquo;ubuhinzi nabo bagatangira guhinga hakiri kare kandi bakanaguka mu bitekerezo bataregera mu kazi .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aimable akora mu Mushinga (Government Funded Irrigation (GFI) wa RAB ugamije guteza imbere ubuhinzi butagendera ku mvura mu bice bikunda kubura imvura Uyu mushinga kugeza ubu umaze kugira ibikorwa bifata hegitari 900 kandi ukaba uteganya kuzakorerwa kuri hegitari 5000 mu turere twa Nyagatare na Kirehe hisfashishijwe amazi y&rsquo; umugezi w&rsquo;Umuvumba na y&rsquo;ibiyaga bya&nbsp; Cyambwe na Rwampanga</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"864876374315553357\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-604\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/864876374315553357.jpg\" style=\"height:688px; width:516px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aimable Ibanga mu kazi mu Mirima</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"146616805789101868\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-606\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/1466168057891018681.jpg?w=863\" style=\"height:290px; width:516px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aha ni mu bwanikiro bw&rsquo;umusaruro w&rsquo;ibigori&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"303577722424340318\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-605\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/3035777224243403181.jpg\" style=\"height:917px; width:516px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iki kigori ni kimwe mu byeze mu mirima Aimable akoramo&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Inkuru yateguwe na NIYIGABA Etienne, email: niyigabat@gmail.com</em></p>\r\n','4',3487,3,'2016-02-25 23:02:26','Ibigori ',0,'online','no','no'),(164,'Ubworozi bw\'Umwuga : Hakwiye amasezerano ahuza abafatanyabikorwa, by\'umwihariko mubworozi bw\'inka z\'umukamo','IMG00680-20150505-1521.jpg','<p>Ubworozi ni umwuga abanyarwanda benshi bafatanya n&rsquo;ubuhinzi , kimwe cyuzuza ikindi ngo babibyaze umusaruro. Kuva kera umubare w&rsquo;amatungo wagaragazaga ingufu z&rsquo;umworozi n&rsquo;ubwo byabaga bitajyanye n&rsquo;inyungu abikuramo.Uwo muco uracyagaragara hamwe na hamwe ku borozi bagitsimbaraye k&rsquo;ubwinshi bw&rsquo;amatungo kandi badashobora kuyabyaza umusaruro ukwiye .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>M&rsquo;urwego rwo gukangurira urubyiruko kwitabira ubworozi bw&rsquo;umwuga,&nbsp;twasuye&nbsp; <strong>VETOPROX LTD,</strong> serivisi y&rsquo;ubuvuzi n&rsquo;ubworozi bw&rsquo;amatungo yikorera mu Ntara y&rsquo;Amajyepfo, ifite icyicaro mu Karere ka Huye, ihagarariwe na Dr Nsekanyarenze Jean Pierre, umuganga w&rsquo;amatungo kuva muri 1988.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/05/img00680-20150505-1521.jpg\"><img alt=\"IMG00680-20150505-1521\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-120\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/05/img00680-20150505-1521.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225\" style=\"height:225px; width:300px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Dr.Jean Pierre mu ruganda rwe rutunganya ibiryo by&rsquo;amatungo ku buryo bugezweho</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyi serivisi yatangiye muri 2008 ifasha aborozi gukumira indwara z&rsquo;amatungo. Guhera muri 2013, yatangiye kwibanda ku bikorwa byo kuboneza imirire y&rsquo;amatungo&nbsp;; ikaba igeze ku cyiciro cyo kubaka uruganda ruciriritse rwo gukora ibiryo by&rsquo;amatungo. Ku nkunga y&rsquo;umushinga <strong>RDCP II</strong> ushyirwa mu bikorwa na <strong>Lande O&rsquo; Lakes, </strong>VETOPROX imaze kubona imashini zishobora gukora byibura toni enye z&rsquo;ibiryo by&rsquo;amatungo k&rsquo;umunsi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Inzitizi m&rsquo;ukuboneza imirire y&rsquo;amatungo&nbsp;:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Amaze kutwibwira no kuduha incamake kuri serivisi ahagarariye, yakomeje atubwira inzitizi ahura nazo muri iki gokorwa cyo kuboneza imirire y&rsquo;amatungo. Aragira ati&nbsp;: Igikorwa cyo kuboneza imirire y&rsquo;amatungo gihura n&rsquo;inzitizi nyinshi, ariko iz&rsquo;ingenzi zaba izi zikurikira&nbsp;:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><strong>Ubumenyi buke bw&rsquo;aborozi</strong>: kimwe n&rsquo;indi myuga, ubworozi bwagakozwe n&rsquo;abantu bakwije ubumenyi ku mibereho y&rsquo;amatungo yabo, bagashobora gukurikiza amabwiriza ngenderwaho y&rsquo;ubworozi, bagateganya inyongeramukamo zikwiye ari nako babara inyungu bateze kuri ubwo bworozi. Ku borozi benshi rero si ko bimeze, inka zahariwe abashumba batazi gusoma no kwandika, basabwa gukama, kwahira no gukuka rimwe na rimwe. Usanga rero ubworozi burangwa n&rsquo;isuku nke idatana n&rsquo;ifumbi, indyo nkene mu bwinshi no mu bwiza bidatana n&rsquo;umukamo muke.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Kwegera aborozi n&rsquo;ubumenyingiro bw&rsquo;abatekinisiye bidahagije</strong>: umubare muto w&rsquo;abatekinisiye ba Leta m&rsquo;uby&rsquo;ubworozi n&rsquo;ubuvuzi bw&rsquo;amatungo ntutuma aborozi benshi <strong>basurwa</strong> ngo bagirwe inama uko byakagombye. Byongeye kandi, no mu bikorera, bemshi baracyahuzagurika. Usanga rero rimwe na rimwe serivise zitangwa zitanyura aborozi ; bagahitamo kwirwariza mu bikorwa binyuranye byagasabye ubumenyi bukwiye nko <strong><em>kwivurira, kwikorera ibiryo by&rsquo;amatungo.</em></strong> Iyo mikorere rero ntibura ingaruka.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Amikoro make y&rsquo;aborozi&nbsp;: </strong>ikiraro n&rsquo;inka ntabwo bihagije ngo umuntu abe abaye umworozi. Agomba no kongeraho ubwatsi n&rsquo;amazi bihagije kandi byiza, biboneka uko inka ibikeneye&nbsp;: ibi ngibi aborozi benshi babikennyeho cyane n&rsquo;ubwo muri rusange bisaba gusa umurimo w&rsquo;ingufu. Hejuru y&rsquo;ibi kandi, hiyongeraho inyongeramukamo zikubiyemo byibuze imiti ikumira indwara, imyunyu n&rsquo;indyo y&rsquo;inyongera (concentr&eacute;)&nbsp;; zo zisaba amafaranga , umworozi atagira kandi agomba kwishyura kashi. <strong><em>Icyo gihe rero, inka ikamwa ayo itahanye</em></strong>. Bivuga ko amikoro make ya benshi mu borozi atuma amatungo yabo atanga umusaruro muke k&rsquo;uwo ashobora gutanga. Nyamara kandi, m&rsquo;ubuke bwawo, n&rsquo;uwo musaruro utangwa ku ideni mu gihe umworozi we nta deni <strong>rikwiye</strong> yahawe ngo byibuze yongere umusaruro w&rsquo;inka ye. Uko ibihe biha ibindi, amatungo arasaza&nbsp;; akagenda nta musaruro ukwiye asigiye aborozi.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Isoko ry&rsquo;umusaruro ritizewe&nbsp;: </strong>kuva aho amakusanyirizo y&rsquo;amata yubakiwe, menshi yatangiye gukora. Ariko mu mikorere yayo, amwe ntiyizeza umworozi ko igihe cyose azanye amata meza azakirwa, uko yaba angana kose. Ibi bigaragara cyane igihe cy&rsquo;imvura, aho amata menshi abura isoko ntiyakirwe, cyangwa se akagabanyirizwa igiciro. Ibi rero bituma aborozi badashishikarira gukoresha inyongeramukamo zatuma inka itanga amata yose ishobora gukamwa.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Arashyigikira igitekerezo gishobora gufasha mu gukuraho izo nzitizi zose&nbsp;:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kunoza umurongo ngenderwaho w&rsquo;amasezerano ahamye ahuza abafatanyabikorwa bahuriye k&rsquo;ubworozi bw&rsquo;inka z&rsquo;umukamo&nbsp;ku nyungu za buri wese: <strong><em>aborozi &ndash; abakusanya amata (MCC) &ndash; abagurisha inyongeramukamo. </em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><strong>Aborozi</strong> bakamenya kwita ku isuku, bagashaka ubwatsi n&rsquo;amazi byiza kandi bikwiye kugirango inka zabo zitange umusaruro mwinshi ushoboka kandi bakabigirwamo inama.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Abagurisha inyongeramusaruro</strong> bakazegereza aborozi mu gihe, ku gipimo no k&rsquo;ubwiza bikwiye kandi bakishyurwa k&rsquo;umusaruro.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Abakusanya amata (MCC)</strong> bakakira amata yose meza bagemuriwe n&rsquo;aborozi bagiranye amasezerano.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibi byaba bigamije korohereza umworozi kubonera igihe inyongeramukamo zikwiye kandi zishyurwa k&rsquo;umusaruro&nbsp;: rikaba n&rsquo;isoko rihoraho ry&rsquo;abacuruza inyongeramukamo. N&rsquo;izindi nzitizi zose zakumirirwa muri iyi mikoranire.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/05/img00677-20150505-1510.jpg\"><img alt=\"IMG00677-20150505-1510\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-121\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/05/img00677-20150505-1510.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225\" style=\"float:left; height:225px; width:300px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Bimwe mu byuma yifashisha mu gutunganya ibiryo by&rsquo;amatungo</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uruhare rw&rsquo;urubyiruko mu guteza imbere ubworozi bw&rsquo;inka z&rsquo;umukamo&nbsp;:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aragira ati&nbsp;: urubyiruko ni u Rwanda rw&rsquo;ejo&nbsp;; ni aborozi b&rsquo;ejo. Bagomba kubitora hakiri kare, kandi bamwe babifitiye ubushobozi bw&rsquo;ibanze&nbsp;; kuko babyize.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Abize</strong>, bakeneye inkunga yo gukarishya ubumenyi ngiro bwabo (<strong><em>cyane cyane mu gukora no gukoresha ibiryo by&rsquo;amatungo)</em></strong>, kugirango ab&rsquo;inyangamugayo bafatanye n&rsquo;abandi kubyaza umusaruro ibyiza Imana yaduhaye, ndetse ku bibumbiye mu matsinda, bakagenerwa gahunda zihariye z&rsquo;ubworozi. Ku babitangiye, bakomereze aho abandi babarebereho.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Abataragiye mu mashuri</strong>, bakwiye amahugurwa ahoraho, bakiga gusoma no kwandika, kandi bagahabwa ubumenyi mu by&rsquo;ubworozi n&rsquo;ibibukomokaho, bagahinduka abanyamwuga b&rsquo;ukuri, maze imibereho yabo igahinduka.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uyu mworozi ndetse akaba n&rsquo;umuvuzi w&rsquo;amatungu by&rsquo;umwuga yasoje</strong> aha ikaze abafatanyabikorwa bakorana m&rsquo;uburyo bw&rsquo;amasezerano&nbsp;kandi ko yiteguye gutanga n&rsquo;izindi serivisi zinyuranye zijyanye n&rsquo;ubworozi n&rsquo;ubuvuzi bw&rsquo;amatungo zirimo no kwigisha uko bakora ibiryo by&rsquo;amatungo uwamukenera wese yamubona .</p>\r\n','2',2699,3,'2015-04-09 05:25:12','Inka ',1,'online','no','no'),(167,'Ubuhinzi Bwacu: Ibitekerezo ku ngingo igira iti:IBYONNYI N\'INDWARA M\'UBUHINZI ','ibyonnyi.jpg','<p>Bimaze kumenyerwa ko&nbsp; kucyumweru ku mbuga nkoranyambaga zitandukanye za YEAN tuba turi mu kiganiro UBUHINZI BWACU. Ku cyumweru tariki 6 Ugushyingo 2016 twaganiriye&nbsp; ku nsanganyamatsiko igira iti&nbsp;&nbsp;&rdquo; <strong>IBYONNYI N&rsquo;INDWARA M&rsquo;UBUHINZI</strong> &ldquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iki kiganiro abahinzi bagaragaje ingaruka nyinshi bahura nazo kubera ibyonnyi ndetse n&rsquo;indwara zitandukanye maze bigatera kutagera ku musaruro wari witezwe ndetse&nbsp; n&rsquo;igishoro cyakoreshejwe ntikibashe kugaruka hamwe&nbsp; maze umuhinzi bikarushaho kumuca intege mu buhinzi bwe. Izi ndwara ndetse n&rsquo;ibyonnyi ukwiyongera kwabyo kandi nabyo biri muri zimwe mu ingaruka z&rsquo;imihindagurikire y&rsquo;ikirerere. Umuhinzi ati &ldquo;<em>Benshi mu bahinzi bahura n&rsquo;ibyonnyi rimwe na rimwe ibihingwa byabo bigashira kubera kutamenya kubirwanya bakagwa mu gihombo</em>. Undi &nbsp;ati&rdquo; <em>Uko bigaragara umuhinzi aracyacyeneye ubufasha mu guhangana n&rsquo;izi mbogamizi ahura nazo mu buhinzi&rdquo;</em>. Muri iki kiganiro havuzwe byinshi bitandukanye ariko byose bigendeye&nbsp; kuri iyi mirongo nyamukuru:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko umuhinzi azi igitera ibyonnyi n&rsquo;indwara n&rsquo;uko yabyirinda.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abahinzi bamwe na bamwe bagiye bazi bimwe mu bimenyetso bigaragaza uburwayi ndetse n&rsquo;ibyonnyi bimwe na bimwe bitewe n&rsquo; uko hari amwe mu mahugurwa bakorewe ndetse n&rsquo;uburambe umuhinzi aba afite mu mwuga w&rsquo;ubuhinzi. Uyu muhinzi ati &rdquo; <em>Abahinzi baba abato n&rsquo;abanini, abakora kinyamwuga n&rsquo; abandi, ibitera indwara mu murima n&rsquo;imyaka barakizi cyangwa bagifiteho Ubumenyi. Hari n&rsquo;abazi uburyo bwo kuzimenya ibimenyetso no kuzirinda.Imfashanyigisho zirahari ubukangurambaga nibwo bukenewe&rdquo;</em>. Undi muhinzi ati&rdquo; <em>Iyo nitegereje nsanga abahinzi benshi baba bazi ibyonnyi ahubwo haba ikibazo cyo kwegera aba agronomes(aguronome) ngo babafashe&rdquo;.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>N&rsquo;ubwo umuhinzi yaba asobanukiwe ubuhinzi ariko abahinzi bavugaga ko akeneye ubufasha bw&rsquo;umutu wabyigiye ubisobanukiwe maze akamufasha guhangana n&rsquo;izo ndwara ndetse n&rsquo;ibyoryi. Aha ubukangurambaga burakenewe ku bahizi ikindi abafite ubuhinzi mu inshingano bakegera abahinzi bakabafasha. Gusa ariko abahinzi bagarutse no kuburyo bwo kumenya indwara ku buryo bwa gakondo abahinzi bakoresha bitewe no kumenyera ibiba mu murima ndetse no kuzirwanya nabyo bigakorwa gakondo ariko ugasanga nta kintu kinini bifasha umuhinzi nko gukoresha uburyo bwa gihanga bugezweho.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2) Imbogamizi zihari mu kurwanya ibyonnyi n&rsquo; indwara m&rsquo;ubuhinzi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibyonnyi bigaragara muri season A2017</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Nkongwa y&rsquo;ibigori;</li>\r\no<li>Agasurira karya kawa;</li>\r\no<li>Umugese mu muceri;</li>\r\no<li>Kabore mu myumbati;</li>\r\no<li>Inda mu nturusu;</li>\r\no<li>Igifuruto (lamp skin) ku nka;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Izi ndwara zose rero siko abahinzi bazisobanukiwe&nbsp; ndetse n&rsquo;abacuruza imiti nabo ntago ari bose bazisobanukiwe . Uyu yagize ati &ldquo;<em>Akenshi usanga bihutira mu ma pharmacie agro-vet kugura imiti kandi abakora muri izo pharmacie&nbsp; ntibaba babisobanukiwe akamuha umuti ubonetse wose bigatuma n&rsquo;icyo yarengeraga cyangirika umusaruro ukabura&rdquo;.</em> Uyu nawe yunga murye ati <em>&ldquo;ndemeranya nawe,aho agrovet zibereye nyinshi abahinzi ntibakita kukwegera agronome cyangwa veterinaire. Bahita bajya kugura imiti ,Bivuze&nbsp; ko umuhinzi ariwe wikoreye Isuzuma ry&rsquo;ibihingwa bye,yiyandikira umuti akaza no kuwiterera!&rdquo;. </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu by&rsquo;ukuri abahinzi benshi bakunda kugwa murujijo bigatuma bakoresha imiti nabi nabyo bikabyara izindi ngaruka . Uyu yagize ati <em>&ldquo;Niko bimeze aho ntuye ndabibona cyane umuhinzi aza abaza umuti ntaza avuga ibyonnyi byafashe ibihingwa bye cg yanabivuga ukumva umucuruzi ngo uwaguha uyu muti nabonye benshi ariwo basigaye bagura. Ubu buhinzi bwacu ni gati ki koko?&ldquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3) Ingaruka ziva kuri izi ndwara n&rsquo; ibyonnyi k&rsquo;ubuhinzi ndetse no k&rsquo;umusaruro </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Izi ndwara tuvuga aha zigira ingaruka nyinshi ku buhinzi ndetse n&rsquo;umusaruro , uretse ibyo twagarutseho haruguru byo kugabanya umusaruro ndetse bikanatera igihombo , bishobora no kugira ingaruka ku bidukikije ndetse n&rsquo;ubuzima bw&rsquo;umuntu . Uyu ati &ldquo;<em>Mubyukuri ibyo muvuze ndemezanya nawe, maze iminsi mbona abantu bahinga inyanya hafi yaho nkorera&nbsp;&nbsp; batera dethane nyinshi cyane barangiza bakazironga bagahekenya namubaza nti kuki utera umuti mwinshi kugera naho na photosynthesis ushobora kuyihagarika akambwira Ngo bibafasha gutuma zihisha vuba&hellip;. Urumva rero abahinzi bakeneye amahugurwa ku ndwara ndetse n&rsquo;imiti&rdquo; </em>Mu bihugu byateye imbere mu buhinzi bimaze kumenyerwako gukoresha cyane imiti yica udukoko mu mirima bigira ingaruka ku buzima bw&rsquo;ibidukikije , hakaba hagenda hashakishwa uburyo bwo kugabanya iyo miti ndetse n&rsquo;imwe n&rsquo;imwe itera ingaruka zihambaye ikagenda isimbuzwa ibasha gukora neza nta ngaruka . Imiti nubwo igabanya ibyonnyi ariko hari n&rsquo;ibyo ibangamira mu bidukikikije . Ubushakashatsi bukwiye kugenda bugaragaza ibyo abahinzi bagakwiye kugenderaho kandi abahinzi nabo bakihutira kubaza agoronome mu gihe bahuye n&rsquo;indwara batazi mu murima wabo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4) Ibisubizo birambye bihari kugira hazaboneke umusaruro mwiza.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Muri iki kiganiro abahinzi bunguranye&nbsp; banagaragaza icyakorwa ngo imbogamizi zikigaragara zigende zikemuka. Uyu yagize ati &ldquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;<em>Muri rusange usanga abahinzi batazi igitera ibyonnyi cyangwa indwara, kuko usanga nta n&rsquo;uburyo bwihariye bateganya igihe cy&rsquo;ihinga, gusa ubu usanga bitewe nigihingwa runaka basigaye bitabira kugura insecticide cyangwa indi miti runaka igakoreshwa nubwo ikoreshwa nabi nko ku bipimo birenze &nbsp;, kubisubizo birambye mbona leta ifite project yitwa plant wise, banahugura aba agronome b&rsquo;imirenge bakaba abavuzi b&rsquo;ibihingwa, usanga bishimishije iyo umuhinzi afite urugero rw&rsquo;igihingwa kirwaye akazana kuvuza&rsquo;&rsquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&ldquo;Abahinzi aha bashishikarizwa kwihutira kugisha aba agronomes mu mirenge yose barahari cyangwa amaduka acuruza imiti ndetse n&rsquo;ibindi bigo bizobereye mu buhinzi bakabagira inama y&rsquo;ama pesticides(imiti irwanya udukoko)bakoresha cyangwa&nbsp; se izindi ngamba za ngombwa kugirango bace ibyonnyi kandi umusaruro wiyongere&rdquo;.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&ldquo;Nakwisabira inzego zishinzwe ubuhinzi gushaka ukuntu hajya hapimwa ubushobozi bw&rsquo;ubutaka mu kwirinda indwara, tugakumira kuko kwirinda biruta kwivuza, Urugero: Mu gihugu cya Kenya inzego z&rsquo;ubuhinzi zikoresha utwuma twitwa &ldquo;soil care&rdquo; kagapima ikigero cy&rsquo;uburumbuke bw&rsquo;ubutaka ndetse n&rsquo;ubushobozi bwifitemo mu kurwanya indwara (Soil Resistance to Diseases). Naho mu Rwanda dupfa kurunda ifumbire mu butaka nta makuru ufite kuri ubwo butaka.&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&ldquo;Kongerera ubumenyi buhagije mubashinzwe ubuhinzi (Agronome) kuko kenshi usanga baraguza umutwe cyangwa bakajya mubitabo/internet </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&ldquo;Guhugura abakangurambaga b&rsquo;ubuhinzi mu midugudu nabo bagahugura abahinzi bagenzi babo&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&ldquo;Gukangurira abahinzi uburyo bwa kamere cyangwa kurinda ibihingwa dukoresheje ibinyabuzima: lutte bioligique&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&ldquo;Kwikorera mu Rwanda imiti ishingiye kubimera byacu ikajya yifashishwa mugihe umuhinzi adafite ubushobozi.&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&ldquo;Narimo nganira n&rsquo;abahinzi bambwirako&nbsp; imbaraga zikoreshwa mu gushakira umuhinzi amafumbire ndeste n&rsquo;imbuto zagakwiye gukomeza, kugira habeho kubungabunga zambaraga zakoreshejwe zikabyara umusaruro. Abahinzi bagira bati. Ducyeneye ubufasha ngiro buhoraho mu kubungabunga ubuhinzi tuba turi gukora bwa buri munsi ntibirangirire mu kutuzanira ifumbire n&rsquo;imbuto.&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byose ntago byagarajwe hano bitewe n&rsquo;uko ari ikiganiro kirekire cyane hagiye hatoranywamo imirongo migari ikavugwa muri make. Amazina yabatanze ibitekerezo ntago yagaragajwe muri iyi nkuru gusa amagambo yose ari mu utwuguruzo n&rsquo;utwugarizo (&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;) yose yandikuwe uko yanditse mu kiganiro.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikiganiro nk&rsquo;iki kiba buri ku Cyumweru.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ushaka gukurikira ibi biganiro ukaba uri umuhinzi/umworozi cyangwa umugoronome/veterineri ku rwego urwo arirwo rwose nawe wasaba kujya k&rsquo;urubuga rwa YEAN Whatsapp unyuze kuri nimero ikurikira: +250 788 845 727 ,wakurikira YEAN kuri facebook cyangwa kuri twitter #UbuhinziBwacu @YEAN_Rwanda</p>\r\n','3',4106,3,'2016-11-30 05:02:45','Ubuhinzi Bwacu',1,'online','no','no'),(168,'Ubuhinzi bwacu : Ibitekerezo ku ngingo igira iti: GUFUMBIRA UBUTAKA , TWONGERA UMUSARURO.','Gufumbira  ifumbire .jpg','<p>Mwaramutseho neza Bahinzi Borozi namwe mukunda ubuhinzi!! Nk&rsquo;uko bisanzwe ku Cyumweru, Saa mbiri za mugitondo ku mbuga za YEAN Rwanda tuba turi mu Kiganiro UBUHINZI BWACU , uyu munsi taliki ya 2/10/2016 &nbsp;turaganira ku nsanganyamatsiko igira iti &rdquo; GUFUMBIRA UBUTAKA , TWONGERA UMUSARURO&rdquo; . Ubutaka bwacu bukenera kongerwamo ifumbire yaba imborera cyangwa mvaruganda kugirango ibihingwa bibone intungagihingwa bikeneye maze bitange umusaruro mwiza. Turibanda cyane kuri ibi: Ifumbire iboneka ite? Ubushobozi bw&rsquo;umuhinzi mu kubona ifumbire, Ubumenyi bw&rsquo;umuhinzi mu gukoresha ifumbire, Icyakorwa muri rusange.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abitabiriye ikiganiro bagaragaje ko ifumbire ari ikintu cy&rsquo;ingenzi mu buhinzi bwacu cyane cyane ko ubutaka bwacu bwagize ihinduka rikomeye cyane ritewe no kubuhinga cyane , isuri y&rsquo;ubwoko butandukanye n&rsquo;ibindi bikorwa bibukorerwabo, ni ngombwa rero kongeramo ifumbire ibyara intungagihingwa igihingwa gikenera mu mikurire yacyo ngo kibe cyabasha gutanga umusaruro wifuzwa. Iyi fumbire igabanyijemo ibice bibiri ; hari ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera n&rsquo;ifumbire mvaruganda. Ibi byose bishobora gutanga intungagihingwa ariko kugeza ubu mu Rwanda nk&rsquo;uko bigaragazwa n&rsquo;ibarura-bushashats rikorwa n&rsquo;ikigo cy&rsquo;igihugu cy&rsquo;ibarurishamibare gifatanyije na minisiteri y&rsquo;ubuhinzi rigaragaza ko abahinzi benshi bakoresha ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera ku kigero cya 71.3% (igihebwe 2016A) .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nubwo ariko ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera ikoreshwa ikoreshwa n&rsquo;abahinzi benshi ntibivuzeko ariyo yongera umusaruro cyane ahubwo nk&rsquo;uko byagaragaje n&rsquo;abahinzi niyo yorohera umuhinzi kuyibona kuko umuhinzi ahobora kuyikorera mu rugo iwe cyangwa akayigura mubaturanyi ku giciro gito ugereranyije n&rsquo;imvaruganda iba yakorewe mu nganda ikagera ku muhinzi ihenze n&rsquo;ubwo itanga intungagihingwa nyishi&nbsp; kandi vuba kurusha imborera. Gusa abahinzi bazi neza ko iyi fumbire mvaruganda iyo ikoreshejwe nabi yangiza ubutaka ,bikaba bisaba kuyikoresha ugendeye kubipimo byagenwe hakurikije uko ubutaka bwawe bwifashe ku bijyanye n&rsquo;imyunyungugu dusanga mu butaka .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ifumbire iboneka ite?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kugeza ubu ifumbire Mvaruganda ikoreshwa iboneka ku bufatanye bw&rsquo;abikorera na Leta aho umuhinzi ayibona ku giciro gito hifashishijwe gahunda ya Leta ya &ldquo;Nkunganire&rdquo; aho reta iba yaragiranye amasezerano n&rsquo;abikorera mukugeza ifumbire ku bahinzi nabo bakayifata ku giciro gito leta ikishyura asigaye . Iyo igihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga kigiye gutangira hakorwa ubukangurambaga mu bahinzi bwo kugana abacuruzi b&rsquo;inyongeramusaruro bakagura ifumbire binyuze mu matsinda mato ya Twigire Muhinzi . Ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera yo itunganyirizwa mu ngo n&rsquo;abahinzi ubwabo ikomotse ku bisigazwa ry&rsquo;ibyagaburiwe amatungo no mu biraro byayo ndetse no ku bisigazwa by&rsquo;ibyasaruwe mu murima hagakoreshwa uburyo bw&rsquo;ibimoteri butuma ibyo bisigazwa bibora vuba bigatanga ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera . Iyi fumbire y&rsquo;imborera hari abahinzi bayigura ku bandi bahinzi baba bayitunganyije .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ubushobozi bw&rsquo;umuhinzi mu kubona ifumbire</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kugeza ubu nk&rsquo;uko twabigarutseho haruguru abahinzi bakoresha cyane ifumbire ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera kuko ariyo ihendutse , abahinzi bayibona ku buryo bworoshye bitewe n&rsquo;uko abenshi ari abahinzi-borozi. Iyo urebye mu myaka ine ishize usanga ikigero cyo gukoresha iyi fumbire y&rsquo;imborera mu bihembwe byose by&rsquo;ibinga bya uri mwaka kiri hagati ya 65-75%. &nbsp;N&rsquo;ubwo twagarutse kuri gahunda ya Nkuganire yo guha umuhinzi inyongeramusaruro &nbsp;ku giciro gito yunganiwe na leta , abagoronome n&rsquo;abahinzi bavugako abahinzi bato iyo uganiriye nabo bakubwirako bataragera kuri rwego rwo gukoresha ifumbire ihagije bitewe n&rsquo;igiciro nubundi kikibagora&nbsp; . Uyu yagize ati : &ldquo;Kugeza ubu iyo wegereye abahinzi bato bamwe bahabwa nkunganire (subsidies) ku ifumbire bakubwira yuko ntacyo bibamariye kuko n&rsquo;ayo basabwa hariho nkunganire ntibayabona&rdquo;. Aho ubutaka busharira , hari gahunda yo gukoresha ishwagara kugirango ifashe mukugabanya ubusharire bukabije , Abahinzi bayigezwaho nanone hakoreshejwe gahunda y&rsquo;imiryango yigenga cyangwa se abikorera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ubumenyi bw&rsquo;umuhinzi mu gukoresha ifumbire</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abahinzi bamaze kwibumbira muma koperative bagaragaza kugira imyumvire igimbutse mu gukoresha ifumbire kurusha abahinzi nyakamwe. Ibi biterwa n&rsquo;uko abahinzi bakorera mumakoperative babona amahugurwa ndetse abagoronome bakabageraho kenshi kuruta wa muhinzi nyakamwe. Ariko nanone abahinzi nyakamwe nibo biganje cyane ibi bituma imyumvire n&rsquo;ubumenyi by&rsquo;abahinzi muri rusange ku gukoresha ifumbire usanga ikiri hasi. Uyu mugoronome ati &ldquo;Ikindi kandi imyumvire y&rsquo;abahinzi iracyari hasi aho urugero nko mu turere dufite ubutaka busharira baba bagomba gukoresha travertin (ishwagara)iyo bayibahaye baragenda bakayimena mu nzira bagacyura umufuka yarimo( bivuze ko umufuka ufite agaciro kurusha travertin)!! Ni ikibazo kuko iyo ubajije umuhinzi impamvu adashaka gukoresha travertin akubwira ko yangiza ubutaka&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikindi kandi Abacuruza inyongeramusaruro nabo usanga badasibanukiwe cyane nazo ,bishobora guterwa n&rsquo;impamvu zinyuranye , aho uyu yagize ati: &ldquo;Nigeze kubabwirako nagiriye umuntu inama yo gutera urea akajya kuyigura bakamuba DAP. Nkasanga ari kuyitera aziko ari gutera urea! Iki nacyo ni ikibazo kuri agrodealers(abacuruza inyongeramusaruro) ndetse n&rsquo;abahinzi badafite ubumenyi kuri products z&rsquo;ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ifumbire irimo&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingorane</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu buryo bw&rsquo;ubumenyi nyesi (natural science) ni ngobwa gusobanukirwa n&rsquo;ibyo uri gukora cyane cyane iyo uri kubikorera ku mutungo kamere (Ubutaka, amazi, umwuka,&hellip;) niyo mpamvua abahinzi badasobaukiwe n&rsquo;ibi bagihura n&rsquo;ingorane mukazi kabo ka buri munsi . Muri izo ngorane twavuga</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Kudasobanukirwa n&rsquo;imikoreshereze y&rsquo;ifumbire</li>\r\no<li>Kudasobanurirwa neza impamvu yo gukoresha ifumbire n&rsquo;izindi nyongeramusaruro zikenerwa mu buhinzi</li>\r\no<li>Kutamenya imiterere y&rsquo;ubutaka mu bijyanye n&rsquo;uburumbuke, ubusharire, ubuhanane, ubwoko, ibikenewe mu butaka,&hellip;</li>\r\no<li>Kutamenya byimbitse ibyo igihingwa gikeneye ngo abe aribyo byongerwa mu butaka.</li>\r\no<li>Ubushobozi bw&rsquo;umuhinzi muto buracyari hasi y&rsquo;ubukenewe ngo anashe kugura ifumbire ihagije mu buhinzi bwe</li>\r\no<li>Gukoresha ifumbire idahagije ku rugero rw&rsquo;ubuso bituma umusaruro wagakwiye kuboneka kuri urwo rugero utagerwaho.</li>\r\no<li>Kuba serivisi yo gupima ubutaka itaboneka naho ibonetse ikaba ihenze cyane ngo abahinzi babibashije babigane basobanukirwe n&rsquo;imiterere y&rsquo;ubutaka bwabo.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyakorwa muri rusange</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bitabirirye ikiganiro bagarutse kukureba icyakorwa ngo gukoresha ifumbire ihagije bibe umuco mubahinzi.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Gufasha abahinzi kugera kuri serivisi yo gupima ubutaka byaba na ngombwa igashyirirwaho nkunganire nk&rsquo;uko ku zindi nyongeramusaruro bimeze.</li>\r\no<li>Gusobanurira byimbitse abahinzi impamvu yo gukoresha ifumbire n&rsquo;ishwagara nyayo ku kigero cyagenwe.</li>\r\no<li>Gufasha abahinzi kumva ko gufumbira ubutaka ari ugufumbira igihingwa mu gihe kitabonye ibigitunga kitatanga umusaruro wifuzwa.</li>\r\no<li>Gufasha abacuruza inyongeramusaruro kongera ubumenyi kumikoreshereze y&rsquo;ifumbire.</li>\r\no<li>Gukoresha ifumbire twibuka kubungabunga ibidukikije twirinda n&rsquo;ingaruka ziva mumikoreshereze mibi y&rsquo;ifumbire .</li>\r\no<li>Kongera ubukangurambaga mugukoresha ifumbire mvaruganda n&rsquo;igiciro kigakomeza gushyirwa kucyo umuhinzi muto ashobora kugeraho.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byose ntago byagarajwe hano bitewe n&rsquo;uko ari ikiganiro kirekire cyane hagiye hatoranywamo imirongo migari ikavugwa muri make.</li>\r\no<li>Amazina yabatanze ibitekerezo ntago yagaragajwe muri iyi nkuru gusa amagambo yose ari mu utwuguruzo n&rsquo;utwugarizo (&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;) yose yandikuwe uko yanditse mu kiganiro.</li>\r\no<li>Ikiganiro nk&rsquo;iki kiba buri ku Cyumweru.</li>\r\no<li>Ushaka gukurikira ibi biganiro ukaba uri umuhinzi/umworozi cyangwa umugoronome/veterineri ku rwego urwo arirwo rwose nawe wasaba kujya k&rsquo;urubuga rwa YEAN Whatsapp unyuze kuri nimero ikurikira: +250 788 845 727 ,wakurikira YEAN kuri facebook cyangwa kuri twitter #UbuhinziBwacu @YEAN_Rwanda</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n','3',1782,3,'2016-10-09 05:10:23','Ubuhinzi Bwacu, Ifumbire',0,'online','no','no'),(169,'Ubuhinzi Bwacu: Ibitekerezo ku ngingo igira iti:UBUHINZI N\'ITEGANYAGIHE','ubuhinzi iteganyagihe.jpg','<p>Ikiganiro Ubuhinzi bwacu cyo kuri uyu wa 11/09/2016 twaganiriye ku nsanganyamatsiko igira iti UBUHINZI N&rsquo;ITEGANYAGIHE &rdquo; Iteganyagihe rihurira he n&rsquo;ubuhinzi? rimariye iki umuhinzi? Amakuru agera ku muhinzi ate? Ese umuhinzi ayakoresha ate? .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikiganiro cyitabiriwe cyane n&rsquo;abahinzi bari banyotewe no kuganira kuri iyi ngingo kandi bari bayifiteho abitekerezo byinshi byose bigamije guteza imbere ubuhinzi. Hakiriwe ubutumwa 1015 muri iki kiganiro bunyujijwe ku mirongo yose yakoreshwaga (Twitter, whatsapp, facebook). Turabanyuriramo muri make mu mirongo migari yagarutsweho . Abatanze ibitekerezo bose bagarukaga ku kuba iteganyagihe ari ikintu gikomeye mu buhinzi kuko gifasha kumenya uko ikirere gihagaze bigatuma umuhinzi afata ingamba z&rsquo;uburyo azahinga.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amakuru y&rsquo;iteganyagihe arahari </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abatanze ibitekerezo bagaragaje ko amakuru kugeza ubu ahari agaragazwa n&rsquo;ikigo cy&rsquo;igihugu gishinzwe iteganyagihe ari menshi kandi ubwayo ahagije ndetse buri wese akaba yemerewe guhamagara iki kigo abaza amakuru akeneye yose ariko ngo kuyakoresha babona aribyo birimo ikibazo. uyu ati: &ldquo;<em>Amakuru Meteo irayatanga ariko hakenewe abayasesengura bijyanye na domaine bakoramo</em>&rdquo;. &ldquo;<em>Gusa nkeka ko kugira amakuru no gukoresha amakuru ufite ni ibintu bitandukanye cyane. Harabura rero abafasha abahinzi gukoresha amakuru bafite kuko nabyo bisaba ubumenyi buhambaye</em>&rdquo; Undi ati &ldquo;<em>Niba amakuru aba ahari ndumva ikibazo gikomeye kikiri mu iyamamazamakuru. Njye nkumva hagakwiye kubaho ubufatanye hagati y&rsquo;imishinga mukuba yasakaza amakuru kubagenerwabikorwa aribo bahinzi&rdquo;</em> . Hashyizweho ikigo gishinzwe iby&rsquo;iteganyagihe mu buhinzi (Rwanda Climate service for Agriculture) kikaba kimaze amezi gitangijwe na minisiteri y&rsquo;ubuhinzi bati <em>&ldquo;Ese abahinzi barakimenye? Bakorana nacyo? Bavandi njye mbona ikibazo dufite si Ubumenyi bucye kubintu; si Technology nke; Ahubwo ni Strategy bikorwamo!&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amakuru y&rsquo;itenyagihe ntago agera ku bahinzi uko bikwiye </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abahinzi batanze ibitekerezo bagaragaje ko amakuru atabagera neza aho uyu yagize ati: &rdquo;<em>Gusa mbona uburyo rigera kumuhinzi bitari byagerwaho neza kuko la majorite(abenshi) ntibabimenya ndetse bitewe nuko ibyavuzwe bijya bihindagurika hari abahinzi bamwe batajya bariha agaciro so icyo numva nuko strategy zikoreshwa kugirango umuhinzi abe updated (amenye amakuru) Ku iteganyagihe zahindurwa cyangwa zikaba improved&rdquo; &ldquo;Icyafasha ni nko kuyacisha aho abaturage bose bagera : Umuganda; mubashinzwe Iyamamaza buhinzi mu midugudu &ldquo; bongeraho ko n&rsquo;amakuru aboneka yagakwiye kujya asobanurwa ingaruka mbi n&rsquo;inziza afite &ldquo;Iteganyagihe duhabwa rigomba kujya rijyana n&rsquo;ibisobanuro bihagije ku ngaruka nziza cg mbi bigira ku buhinzi&rdquo;</em>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko amakuru agera ku muhinzi </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Kugeza ubu uburyo buhari ni radio. Mu ibarura ry&rsquo;imiturire ryo 2012 byagaragaye ko 63% by&rsquo;ingo zari zitunze radio. Ubu byariyongereye kuko abatunze telefone zifite radio. Ariko abo 63% ni abanyarwanda bose kandi abakora ubuhinzi babarirwa muri 90% kdi abenshi batuye mu byaro. bisobanuye ko ukuyemo abatunze radiyo ushobora gusanga ababona amakuru ari bake cyane. Ikindi abahinga kinyamwuga ni mbarwa ubwo urumva ingorane zibamo zirimo guhinga mu kajagari&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Muri make amakuru ku iteganyagihe abageraho nabi kuburyo bitabafasha cyane iteganya buhinzi. Ikindi kibazo ni guhuza amakuru n&rsquo;ubumenyi bw&rsquo;umuhinzi ku iteganyagihe navuga ko buciriritse ( convertir et simplifier le message de meteo). Umuhinzi ntakeneye kumva imibare ahubwo akeneye inama zimufasha kumenya uko yakwifata&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko Umuhinzi Ayakoresha</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Navuga ko umuhinzi ayakoresha uko ayumva kdi abyumva. Icyiza nuko iyo bavuze bati muzahinge kare kuko imvura ari nke babikora. Ariko uru ni urunaana. Musubire <a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.org/2016/09/07/ubuhinzi-bwacu-ibitekerezo-byabahinzi-ku-nsanganyamatsiko-irira-iti-imbuto-nziza-umusaruro-mwiza/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">ku kiganiro cy&rsquo;ubushize cyavugaga Imbuto nziza n&rsquo;umusaruro mwiza</span></a>. Mwibuke imbogamizi twabonye zirimo gutanga imbuto kugihe , imyumvire y&rsquo;umuhinzi nibindi bidindiza umusaruro. Muri make iteganyagihe ubuhinzi n&rsquo;umusaruro ntibisigana kdi bigaragara ko hakirimo ikibazo ku guhuza kw&rsquo;inzego&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibitekerezo kucyakorwa </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Igikenewe ni ukwiga uburyo amakuru yagezwa k&rsquo;ubahinzi n&rsquo;abagenimigambi y&rsquo;ubuhinzi kuko data zo ziba zihari rwose! Nk&rsquo;ubu hakorwa inyandiko ntoya zigasakazwa hose mumirenge ibigo by&rsquo;ubuhinzi nka RAB, NAEB amacooperative n&rsquo;ahandi biriho iteganyagihe&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Inama kurwego rw&rsquo;imidugudu igihe ayo makuru yasohotse : niba dukora inama itegura season hose abajyanama n&rsquo;ubuhinzi n&rsquo;abafashamyumvire n&rsquo;ubuhinzi bakagira ayo makuru binyuze munama bajya bagirana ubwo nibwo buryo n&rsquo;umuhinzi wa mazane mukirwa yamenya ayo makuru kandi agaherekezwa n&rsquo;inama n&rsquo;ingamba zavuye muri minagri z&rsquo;uko abahinzi bakwiye kwitwara according(agendeye) y&rsquo;iryo iteganyagihe&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Hakenewe ubufatanye bw&rsquo;inzego MINIRENA ,MININFRA( Meteo) MINAGRI&hellip;mu gufasha umuhinzi uciriritse kumva neza aya makuru. Ubufatanye bw&rsquo;izi nzego bwabaye mu bihe bya EL NIN&Otilde; bukwiye kugumaho kdi bwasize abaturage bumvise iki kiza bari bumvise bwa mbere&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Hakwiye gushyirwa imbaraga mu itangazamakuru cyane Radio z&rsquo;abaturage nka HUGUKA, ISANGANO, ISHINGIRO, IZUBA, MARIA ,RBA/RC( Rusizi, Musanze, Rubavu, Huye na Nyagatare) bagakora icyo bita &ldquo;agenda setting&rdquo; kuko uko usubiramo kenshi niko abantu bibajyamo</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Bitewe no kugongana mu nshingano cyangwa kurebana mbona hakwiye gusinyana amasezerano y&rsquo;imikoranire hagati y&rsquo;inzego zirebwa n&rsquo;ubuhinzi. Urugero nk&rsquo;uburyo Police yasinye MoU na MVK mu bijyanye n&rsquo;umutekano. Kuki RNRA METEO, MINAGRI, POLICE, MEDIA, CSOs, PSF&hellip; Bitasinyana MoUs mu kunoza imikorere? Mbona byagira icyo byongera&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Hari ikintu MINAGRI yigeze kugira bita ishuri ry&rsquo;abahinzi mu murima (IAMU). Ibi mbona byaguwe byagira uruhare rukomeye kuko begereye abahinzi nyakamwe (individual)&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Hakenewe amahugurwa kuguhuza ibipimo bya Meteo n&rsquo;ibikorwa by&rsquo;ubuhinzi. Birakorwa ariko nibyagurwe kdi inzego z&rsquo;ibanze zibigiremo uruhare kuko zibana n&rsquo;abaturage umunsi kuwundi kurusha&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Meteo ntiwavuga ko ntabikoresho bihari kuko nubwo ikikibazo gihari Meteo ikusanya ayo makuru kdi ikanifashisha iteganyagihe ry&rsquo;akarere nka IGAD n&rsquo;iteraganyagihe mpuzamahanga mu gusesengura amakuru kdi ntibinyuranya rwose. Urugero ni uko Meteo Uganda ibyo yatangaje bidatandukanye na meteo Rwanda kdi nubundi turi mu cyoko kimwe&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Hakwiye kubaho kunganirana abahinzi ntibategereze ko igihe cyose inyandiko zizaza zanditseho MINAGRI cyangwa Akarere runaka , ahubwo hakabaho n&rsquo;abikorera mu kumenyekanisha amakuru y&rsquo;ubuhinzi&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Abantu nibakangukire cyane gukoresha &lsquo;prevention measures&rsquo; harimo no guteganya kuhira aho bishoboka hose, hanashyirwe imbaraga muri &lsquo;ecosystems rehabilitation and management hongerwa ibiti (ahantu hose harimo no mu nzuri) n&rsquo;amashyamba mu rwego rwo kugira &lsquo;Smart and green agriculture&#39;&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byose ntago byagarajwe hano bitewe n&rsquo;uko ari ikiganiro kirekire cyane hagiye hatoranywamo imirongo migari ikavugwa muri make.</li>\r\no<li>Amazina yabatanze ibitekerezo ntago yagaragajwe muri iyi nkuru gusa amagambo yose ari mu utwuguruzo n&rsquo;utwugarizo (&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;) yose yandikuwe uko yanditse mu kiganiro.</li>\r\no<li>Ikiganiro nk&rsquo;iki kiba buri ku Cyumweru.</li>\r\no<li>Ushaka gukurikira ibi biganiro ukaba uri umuhinzi/umworozi cyangwa umugoronome/veterineri ku rwego urwo arirwo rwose nawe wasaba kujya k&rsquo;urubuga rwa YEAN Whatsapp unyuze kuri nimero ikurikira: +250 788 845 727 ,wakurikira YEAN kuri facebook cyangwa kuri twitter #UbuhinziBwacu @YEAN_Rwanda</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n','3',1589,40,'2016-09-14 05:05:10','Ubuhinzi Bwacu, Iteganyagihe',0,'online','no','no'),(170,'Ubuhinzi Bwacu: Ibitekerezo ku ngingo igira iti IMBUTO NZIZA , UMUSARURO MWIZA','Ubuhinzi Bwacu  Banner1.jpg','<p>Mu kiganiro UBUHINZI BWACU cyo kuya 4/08/2016 twagarutse ku buhinzi nanone nk&rsquo;uko bisanzwe ariko noneho turaza kwibanda ku nsanganyamatsiko igira iti &ldquo; IMBUTO NZIZA , UMUSARURO MWIZA&rdquo; .Turaganira ku ngorane, imbogamizi , n&rsquo;amahirwe ari mu kubona IMBUTO .&nbsp; Abahinzi bagira uburyo butandukanye bwo gutegura imbuto bazatera hari abayigura , hari abayibika bahereye kubyo bejeje hakaba n&rsquo;abayikura kubandi bahinzi , Imbuto umuntu ateye igira ingaruka ku musaruro. Buri wese watanze ibitekerezo bijyanye n&rsquo;uko abyumva dushingiye kubyo tubamo mubuhinzi bwacu buri munsi ndetse tunashingiye k&rsquo;uburyo imbuto zimeze cyangwa ziboneka mu Rwanda. Twaganiriye kandi kuri ibi dutekereza ko turi kwitegura Gutangira igihembwe cy&rsquo;Ihinga cya 2017A.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibyagarutsweho byagiye byibanda cyane cyane ku kuba umuhinzi afite imbuto nziza bituma umusaruro we uzarushaho kuba mwiza&nbsp; uyu ati :&rdquo; iyo ufite imbuto nziza uba ufite 1/2 cy&rsquo;umusaruro aho uba usigaje kurwana no kuyitaho haba kuhira kubagara ndetse n&rsquo;ibindi &hellip; Imbuto rero n&rsquo;ikintu gikomeye cyane iyo tugendeye kuri target y&rsquo;umusaruro (umusaruro ugambiriwe)&rdquo;. Ibi abahinzi barabizi n&rsquo;ubwo usanga nta buryo bwa siyansi(Science) bukoreshwa ariko usanga bategura imbuto bahereye ku buryo basanzwe bayizi, umusaruro itanga n&rsquo;uburyo ibikwa bakabumenya . Abahinzi benshi kugeza ubu ni abakoresha imbuto gakondo aho mu gihembwe cya 2016A 74.6% bakoresheje imbuto za gakondo naho 25.4% bagakoresha imbuto zitari iza gakondo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubu buryo bwo gukoresha imbuto za gakondo zizwiho kutagira umusaruro mwinshi ugereranyije n&rsquo;imbuto za kijyambere ngo usanga biterwa n&rsquo;imyumvire ikiri hasi ku gukoresha izi mbuto zibyara umusaruro mwinshi . Umwe ati :&rdquo; <em>Hari abahinzi cyane cyane bato usanga baratsimbaraye kumbuto yabo yakera badashaka kuyivaho. Sinzi niba muyizi ariko hari imbuto yakera y&rsquo;ibigori bita &ldquo;kanjegeri&rdquo; ibaze kuba ikibaho! Ese biterwa no kubura iyisimbura cg nuko umuhinzi yashimishijwe n&rsquo;umusaruro wayo cg quality atabona kuzitangwa ubu?</em>&rdquo; Uyu nawe ati: <em>&ldquo;Ikibazo gituma batsimbarara cyane babiterwa n&rsquo;imyumvire micye iterwa no kutabona ubushobozi bwo kubaha amahugurwa naho abaturage iyo ubegereye ukabakorera barumva kuko sibo bishimiye kuvunikira ubusa ahubwo extension ntambaraga ifite kandi umuntu ntabwo ahindurwa n&rsquo;ijambo gusa ahubwo wongeraho urugero&rdquo;. &ldquo;FFS irakenewe apana utu tuntu tuba kutugari twa demos usanga baheruka bashyiramo imbuto ariko ukibaza uwazihinze ukamubura&rdquo;</em>Ikindi kandi ngo imbuto zitangwa ntago ushobora kuzikuraho imbuto uzatera mu gihembwe gitaha igihe usaruye , bisaba kugura indi , ibi bikagora umuhinzi uciriritse. Abahinzi kandi bagaragaza ko ngo imbuto cyane iy&rsquo;ibigori bahabwa itaryoha bagahitamo guhinga n&rsquo;iya gakondo aho uyu yagize ati : &ldquo;<em>ibi bigori batuzanira ntibiryoha niyo mpamvu nubwo tubihinga tubihingira isoko ariko ibi nibyo kwirira</em>&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingorane zitambamira umusaruro mwiza</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Imyumvire y&rsquo;abahinzi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Abahinzi bamwe na bamwe uracyasanga bafite imyumvire&nbsp; ihabanye. Aho usanga babika imbuto ngo iraryoha nko ku bishyimbo cg se irera cyane ariko ntibarebe igihe iyo mbuto imara mu murima n&rsquo;ibibazo by&rsquo;imvura nke bisigaye byigaragaza. Urundi rugero hari nkaho usanga bagikomeye kumbuto y&rsquo;imyumbati, iyo bitaga ngunda cyangwa gitaminsi. Iyi mbuto nkurikije uko nayibonaga imara nibura amezi 48 mu butaka ukaba watangira gusarura mu gihe hari imara amezi 18 ikaba yaramira nyirayo. Hari abitwaza ngo imituburano irabiha n&rsquo;ibindi. Ibyo ubwabyo bihoza umuhinzi mu nzara n&rsquo;igihombo kubera imyumvire idahwitse mu mbuto y&rsquo;indobanure aba yagejejweho&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kudahingira Intego</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;ibi ni kwa kundi umuhinzi ahinga kuko imvura yaguye ntiyibaze ati nkeneye guhinga iki? Kubera iki? Mu buhe buryo? Ibi bituma akenshi iyo yejeje umusaruro we uba muke cg ubonetse ukaba udafite igenamicungire rihamye&rdquo; .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Izi ngorane zigira ingaruka mu gutera imbogamizi zikurikira</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Haboneka imbogamizi k&rsquo; uruhande rw&rsquo;ubuyobozi .Uyu yagize at: &ldquo;<em>Leta itanga imbuto nziza&nbsp; ku bahinzi ariko hakab</em>a ubwo idakorana n&rsquo;ubutaka bikadindiza umusaruro. Urugero ni imbuto y&rsquo; ibigori yigeze gutangwa mu majyaruguru abahinzi bakavuga ko ari mbi nyamara Leta yagiye kugira icyo ikora igihe cyaragiye. Ni byiza ko hafashwe ingamba.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imbogamizi ku ihanamakuru ritanoze, Aho uyu yagize ati: &ldquo;Iyo habayeho impinduka mu buhinzi bisaba ko imenyeshwa ababukora ku gihe kugirango bumve kandi bacengerwe n&rsquo;impamvu yazo. Muri communication twemera ko ubutumwa bugera ku ntego iyo bukoresheje umuyoboro n&rsquo;uburyo nyabwo ngo bugere kuwo bugenewe. Iyo bitagenze bityo habaho kumva bitandukanye intego yabwo &rdquo; Dissonance cognitive&rdquo;. Igikunze kubaho henshi izi mpinduka zitangwa na ba ES b&rsquo;utugari baba batanasobanukiwe n&rsquo;ubuhinzi. Bituma bazitangaza nk&rsquo;itangazo rihita rihinduka itegeko mbere yo kumva ibyo umuturage yifuza kuzisobanukirwaho. Uko mbyumva ES ntafite ubunararibonye ahubwo agronome niwe wakifashishwa. Ibi bitera resistance (kwinangira) ikomeye bagakoresha zambuto zabo ngirango mujya mwumva abitwikira ijoro bakabiba imbuto itarateganyijwe&rdquo;. Izi ngorane n&rsquo;izi mbogamizi ariko ahanini usanga zugarije abahinzi bato batabarizwa mumakoperative cyangwa amatsinda.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Abahinzi batanze ibitekerezo ku cyakorwa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>&ldquo;Gukoresha abanyamwuga n&rsquo;abavuga bakumvwa mu ihanamakuru no gukusanya ibitekerezo bya rubanda&rdquo;</li>\r\no<li>&ldquo;Kurushaho gushishikariza abatari mu makoperative kwibumbira mu matsinda yegeranye kuko byagaragaye ko abayarimo ari bo bumva akamaro k&rsquo;imbuto nziza nuko wabona umusaruro mwiza. Ikindi byorohera abafite aho bahurira n&rsquo;ubuhinzi gutanga ubutumwa kandi bukumvwa vuba&rdquo;.</li>\r\no<li>&ldquo;Guhora hafi y&rsquo;abahinzi cyane abatari mu makoperative kugirango hamenywe imbogamizi bahura nazo. Nka Minisiteri y&rsquo;Ubuhinzi n&rsquo;Ubworozi yari ikwiye kugena OUTREACH ROGRAM ikagera ku muhinzi wo hasi bakagira icyo nakwita &lsquo;Friendly Exchange and problems solving&rsquo; ibi sinshidikanya ko byazana impinduka&rdquo;.</li>\r\no<li>&rdquo;Abatubuzi b&rsquo;imbuto n&rsquo;amakompanyi acuruza imbuto bemewe mu Rwanda bajye bagenzurwa cyane n&rsquo;ababishinzwe bityo imbuto itangwa ikaba ari nzima .</li>\r\no<li>Abanyarwanda babishoboye bakwiye, bahabwa uburenganzira bwo gutangira gutunganya imbuto z&rsquo;imboga zitandukanye ntizikomeze kuva mu mahanga aho ziza zidahuje n&rsquo;ubutaka bwo mu Rwanda .</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byose ntago byagarajwe hano bitewe n&rsquo;uko ari ikiganiro kirekire cyane hagiye hatoranywamo imirongo migari ikavugwa muri make.</li>\r\no<li>Amazina yabatanze ibitekerezo ntago yagaragajwe muri iyi nkuru gusa amagambo yose ari mu utwuguruzo n&rsquo;utwugarizo (&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;) yose yandikuwe uko yanditse mu kiganiro.</li>\r\no<li>Ikiganiro nk&rsquo;iki kiba buri ku Cyumweru.</li>\r\no<li>Ushaka gukurikira ibi biganiro ukaba uri umuhinzi/umworozi cyangwa umugoronome/veterineri ku rwego urwo arirwo rwose nawe wasaba kujya k&rsquo;urubuga rwa YEAN Whatsapp unyuze kuri nimero ikurikira: +250 788 845 727.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n','3',1506,3,'2016-09-08 06:12:32','Ubuhinzi Bwacu, Imbuto',0,'online','no','no'),(171,'Ubuhinzi Bwacu: Ibitekerezo ku ngingo igira iti :ITERAMBERE RY\'UBWOROZI BW\'INKOKO','inkoko.jpg','<p>Nkuko bisanzwe&nbsp; ku cyumweru saa mbiri ku mbuga zose za YEAN haba hacaho ikiganiro ku insanganyamatsiko iba yateguwe maze akaganirirwaho mu kungurana ibitekerezo ndetse no gusobanukirwa neza ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi bwacu&nbsp; maze tukarushaho kubuteza imbere.Kuri iki cyumweru taliki 9/10/2016 haganiriwe&nbsp; ku insanganyamatsiko igira iti &ldquo;<strong>ITERAMBERE RY&rsquo;UBWOROZI BW&rsquo;INKOKO&rdquo; .</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubu bworozi ni ubworozi bwamye mu muco w&rsquo;abanyarwanda kandi bugaragaza gutanga inyungu vuba iyo bukozwe neza. Nkuyu yagize ati &ldquo;<em>ubworozi bw&rsquo;inkoko!!! Ni ubworozi bigaragara ko buri gutera imbere cyane kubera ko amasoko hirya no hino mu karere ahari cyane cyane muri Congo, ikindi Kandi na gahunda zo kurushaho kuzana za hatcheries(</em>amaturagiro<em>) iri kugenda neza ngo aborozi babone imishwi myiza kandi ku giciro cyiza&rdquo;</em> Muri iki kiganiro hagiye hatangwa ibitekerezo ku mirongo ngenderwaho yari yateganyijwe kuganiraho ari nazo zikubiye muri iyi nshamacye yateguwe kubyavugiwe muri iki kiganiro</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gutangira ubworozi bw&rsquo;inkoko</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uyu yagize ati &ldquo;<em>Ubundi iyo umuntu avuze ubworozi bw&rsquo;inkoko/ poultry farming, humvikana ibi : &ndash; inkoko z&rsquo;itera amagi / layer chicken. inkoko z&rsquo;inyama / broiler chicken. Usibyeko iyo bikomatanye n&rsquo;ibiguruka byose bizamo ( imbata , dendon, geese etc )&rdquo;.</em>&nbsp; Ubworozi bw&rsquo;inkoko kubutangira bisaba kuba ufite ibitunga inkoko ndetse n&rsquo;ahantu ho kororera /ubutaka/inyubako zikoze kuburyo inkoko zibasha kwisanzura ndetse no kubaho&nbsp;&nbsp;neza zitabyigana ndetse ngo hazemo ubushyuhe/ubukonje butera ikibazo inkoko zawe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amahirwe mu gukora ubu bworozi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Inkoko ni itungo ryororoka vuba kandi rigatanga umusaruro wihuse, kandi uhoraho iyo zitawe honeza zigakurikiranwa neza , uyu ati&rdquo; <em>ubu bworozi bukorwa ku buso buto kandi ku buso buto hashobora kororerwaho inkoko nyinshi , abanyarwanda bagenda babuyoboka kandi buratanga icyizere</em> arakomeza ati&rdquo;<em>Inkoko ziraribwa cyane kandi amagi yo araribwa birenze, buri boutique, alimentation, supermarket, amasoko manini n&rsquo;amato amagi aragurwa cyane</em>&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Muri iki gihe leta mu kuzana abashoramari, amaturagiro arimo kwiyongera bikorohereza umworozi kubona imishwi ihendutse .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko isoko rimeze kugeza ubu</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kuri iyi ngingo icyagarutsweho cyane ni uko aborozi batarabasha guhaza isoko kuko haracyaboneka amagi aturuka hanze ava mu bihugu by&rsquo;abaturanyi. uyu ati&rdquo; <em>isoko ntirirabasha guhazwa&nbsp;&nbsp;kuko umusaruro utarabasha guhaza abanyagihugu hiyambazwa umusaruro urutse hanze(Uganda)&rdquo;.&nbsp; </em>Aborozi bakomeje bavugako kugeza&nbsp; ubu ibikomoka ku inkoko bihenze . uyu yagize ati&rdquo; <em>Igiciro ku bikomoka ku bworozi biri hejuru(birahenze) ku magi ndetse no ku inyama&rdquo; </em>&nbsp;Bakomeje bavuga ko ibikoresho nkenerwa mu bworozi bw&rsquo;inkoko&nbsp; nabyo bihenze&nbsp; maze bigatera ingaruka k&rsquo;umusaruro uboneka ugasanga&nbsp; qualite(ubwiza) buragenda bugabanuka ugereranyije na n&rsquo;ubigenderwaho ku rwego mpuzamahanga.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Imbogamizi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aborozi ikintu bagarutseho cyane nk&rsquo;imbogamizi ni ibiryo byo kugaburira inkoko aho bagira bati&rdquo;&nbsp; <em>Ibiryo birimo ikibazo, Urebye muri iki gihe ibiryo nibyo bituma products(umusaruro</em><em>) zibukomokaho zihenda cyane&rdquo;</em>&nbsp; Ibiryo by&rsquo;inkoko biboneka ntabwo ari byiza (qualite) ni nkeya bigatuma inkoko zidatanga umusaruro mwiza umworozi yari yiteze undi nawe ati&rdquo; <em>naganiriye n&rsquo;umworozi wazo ambwirako iyo ugiye kugura,ikiro cy&rsquo;ibiryo biva hanze y&rsquo;igihugu usanga bihenze cyane,kuburyo,utarebye neza wasanga wahombye , ambwirako we ahitamo kubyikorera ariko nabyo ngo ntago bimworohera&nbsp; kubera kubura matiere premier(ibyo gukoresha) zo kubikoramo&rdquo;.&nbsp; </em>&nbsp;Aha hagiye havugwako bimwe mu biryo by&rsquo;ibanze bisabwa mu gukora ibiryo by&rsquo; inkoko bihenda ndeste bikaboneka ari bikeya ku masoko aho bavugagako ibigori n&rsquo; indagagara biri muri bimwe bitaboneka neza ndetse nk&rsquo; ibigori bimwe biva hanze(ugunda) mu kunganira ibiri mu gihigu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uyu ati&rdquo;<em>Ubworozi bw&rsquo;inkoko nibyo buri gukura cyane. Ariko imbogamuzi nyinshi zirimo:-busaba ishoramari ridasuzuguritse. -raw materials(ibikoresho) zikora ibiryo byazo ziri competitive(zibasha guhangana n&rsquo;izindi) kuburyo ibiryo byazo bihenda ugereranyije na quality isabwa. &ndash; bukorwa n&rsquo;abantu batabigira umwuga (second alternative) kuburyo hari abatabasha gukurikirana umunsi k&rsquo;umunsi imishinga yabo bityo ntibamenye ibibazo birimo</em>&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Undi ati&rdquo;<em>aborozi bahora barwana no kubona igi ridashobora kurenza 100, ku muguzi wa nyuma, bati riramutse riyarengeje ntiryagurwa kandi birashoboka(gusa nanone inganda zitunganya ibi biryo nibyo ngo zirahenda akaba aribyo bituma aborozi bafata,umwanzuro wo kubyikorera,mu bumenyi,bagenda bahererekanya</em>&rdquo; aha aborozi bakomeje bavugako usanga hari aborozi bakora ubworozi ndetse bagakora n&rsquo; ibiryo ugasanga izi sectors(ibindi bice) zitandukaye nazo zigira uruhare mu kutagera ku musaruro wari witezwe kuko&nbsp; hari kimwe kititabwaho neza. Kuko si aborozi benshi babasha kubikorera icyarimwe kuko biba binasaba igishoro kinini, bityo hakifuzwako&nbsp; habaho inganda zizwi ndetse n&rsquo;ababikora by&rsquo;umwuga bityo hakaboneka ibiryo byiza byujuje ibisabwa maze umusaruro w&rsquo;inkoko ukiyongera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abandi bagiye bavugako Igishoro nacyo ari gicye gutyo hakifuzwa amabanki yumva imishinga maze agatanga &nbsp;inkunga. Ibindi byagarutsweho ni inganda zitunganya/zikora ibiryo by&rsquo;inkoko biri ku giciro gihenze, Ubwoko bw&rsquo;inkoko qualite(ubwiza) itari nziza zitujuje ubuzirange rimwe na rimwe&nbsp; bigateza&nbsp; gutanga umusaruro utari mwiza ndetse zikarwaragurika, Inkingo ndetse n&rsquo;imiti y&rsquo;inkoko ibura kandi icyenewe ku isoko, ubufasha bukeya bw&rsquo;abaveterineri.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyakorwa ngo ubu bworozi bugende neza </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Murwe rwo guteza imbere ubworozi bw&rsquo; inkoko aborozi bagiye bagaruka kuri ibi:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Kubona race(ubwoko) nziza z&rsquo;inkoko zitanga umusaruro mwiza kandi zororoka neza</li>\r\no<li>Inganda zikora ibiryo byiza byujuje qualite(ubuziranenge)</li>\r\no<li>Ibiryo bikaboneka ku giciro gito</li>\r\no<li>Igiciro gito kuri supplements(inyunganizi) zigaburirwa inkoko</li>\r\no<li>Inkingo ndetse&nbsp;&nbsp;n&rsquo;imiti ibonekerera kugihe</li>\r\no<li>Gukorera muma cooperative murwego rwo kongerera agaciro umusaruro uyu ati <em>aborozi baretse inganda zizewe zigakora nabo bakazigurira, bakarwanya abatubuzi ngo basigaye banashiramo uburozi ubu bworozi bwaba bwiza</em>&rdquo;.</li>\r\no<li>Abavuzi bakurikirana ndetse bakita k&rsquo;ubworozi bw&rsquo;inkoko by&rsquo;umwihariko</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byose ntago byagarajwe hano bitewe n&rsquo;uko ari ikiganiro kirekire cyane hagiye hatoranywamo imirongo migari ikavugwa muri make.</li>\r\no<li>Amazina yabatanze ibitekerezo ntago yagaragajwe muri iyi nkuru gusa amagambo yose ari mu utwuguruzo n&rsquo;utwugarizo (&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;) yose yandikuwe uko yanditse mu kiganiro.</li>\r\no<li>Ikiganiro nk&rsquo;iki kiba buri ku Cyumweru.</li>\r\no<li>Ushaka gukurikira ibi biganiro ukaba uri umuhinzi/umworozi cyangwa umugoronome/veterineri ku rwego urwo arirwo rwose nawe wasaba kujya k&rsquo;urubuga rwa YEAN Whatsapp unyuze kuri nimero ikurikira: +250 788 845 727 ,wakurikira YEAN kuri facebook cyangwa kuri twitter #UbuhinziBwacu @YEAN_Rwanda</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n','3',3941,40,'2016-10-13 21:50:21','Ubuhinzi Bwacu, Inkoko',0,'online','no','no'),(172,'Ubuhinzi Bwacu :Ibitekerezo ku ngingo igira iti : GUHINGA IBISHANGA TWONGERA UMUSARURO UBIKOMOKAHO','ibishanga.jpg','<p>Nk&rsquo;uko bisanzwe buri ku cyumweru saa mbiri dukora ikiganiro <strong>UBUHINZI BWACU</strong>, kuri icyu cyumweru twaganiriye ku insanganyamatsiko igira iti: &ldquo;<strong>GUHINGA IBISHANGA TWONGERA UMUSARURO UBIKOMOKAHO&rdquo;</strong> Igishanga ni hamwe mu hantu hatanga umusaruro mwinshi kandi hitabazwa mu guhinga ndetse no mu bihe ahandi haba hatabasha guhingwa . abatanze ibitekerezo bagarakuaka kuburyo ibishanga ubusanzwe dusanzwe tumenyereyeko ariho haboneka umusaruro mugihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga cya C. Muri iki gihe cy ihindagurika ry ikirere gukoresha ibishanga ni bumwe muburyo bwadufasha kubona no kongera umusaruro ku isoko. Uyu ati&rdquo; <em>Nkuko mubizi ibishanga ni ahantu hadufasha gukora ubuhinzi buhoraho&nbsp; kuko ahahantu imvura yagwa itagwa ubuhinzi bwakomeza gukorwa, Niyo mpamvu ibishanga bigomba kwitabwaho bigafatwa neza nabahinzi&rdquo;.</em> Undi ati&rdquo;<em>Urebye ukuntu imihindagurikire y&rsquo;ibihe irushaho kuba mibi kandi ugasanga iryo hindagurika ryerekeza ku zuba rihoraho, Ibishanga ni byo bigega byizewe&rdquo;.</em> Muri iki kiganiro hibanzwe kuri izi ngingo zikurikira:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Imikoreshereze y&rsquo;ibishanga byacu</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hafi 10. 6% by&rsquo;ubuso bw&rsquo;u Rwanda bwihariwe n&rsquo;ibishanga. Ibarura ry&rsquo;ibishanga ryakozwe na REMA mu mwaka wa 2008 ryagaragaje ko u Rwanda rufite ibishanga 860 biri ku buso bwa hegitari 278,536 . Muribyo 53% y&rsquo;ubuso bwabyo ni bwo buhingwamo. ibishanga bitandukanye byarabungabunzwe harimo nk&rsquo;icya Rugezi cyashyizwe ku rutonde rw&rsquo;ahantu hahehereye hafite akamaro ku rwego mpuzamahanga (Wetlands of International Importance) nyuma yo gusubiranywa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubu leta y&rsquo;u Rwanda&nbsp;iri mu nzira zo gusaba ko n&rsquo;ibindi bishanga bitatu, birimo igishanga cy&rsquo;Akagera, Kamiranzovu na Rweru-Mugesera, na byo byashyirwa muri uru rwego.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Umusaruro uturuka ku bishanga</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uyu ati&rdquo;<em>Ibishanga rero nkurikije uko mbizi niho hantu hahingwa Igihembwe cy&rsquo;Ihinga C kimaze kumenyerwa . Kugeza ubu gitanga umusaruro ushimishije mu bijyanye n&rsquo;imboga</em>&rdquo; ndetse ibishanga byeramo n indi myaka myinshi: ibijumba, ibigori, soya, ibishyimbo,,,. Undi ati&rdquo;<em>Tugarutse nanone ku musaruro uva mu bishanga , aho byatunganyijwe biragagerageza ariko nanone umusaruro wagakwiye kuba uva ku rugero rw&rsquo;ubuso uracyari mucye haba ku bigori ndetse no ku muceri , za ngamba zose dukunda kuvugira aha zo guhinga neza n&rsquo;inyongeramusaruro nziza kandi zihagije nicyo gikenewe kuko uburyo bwo,guhinga bwo ni bumwe nta gihinduka&rdquo;.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abahinzi bavuzeko hari impinduka ku musaruro uturuka mu bishanga, aho bagize bati&rdquo; <em>Yego hari ikinyuranyo pe! Kubera politique&nbsp; yagerageje kubiha agaciro&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyakorwa ngo ibishanga bibyazwe umusaruro mwinshi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tugarutse nanone kuburyo bwo kugira ibishanga bikoreshwa neza , ni ngombwa ko ibishanga birindwa isuri ituruka ku misozi ibikikije , aha abahinzi bashishikarizwa guhinga bakoresha gahunda yo kurwanya isuri harimo,gukora amaterasi, gucukura imiringoti ifata amazi, gutera ibiti n&rsquo;ibindi, ikindi kandi amazi yo mu bishanga ndetse n&rsquo;inkombe z&rsquo;imigezi zihaterwaho ibyatsi bituma ubutaka budatwarwa n&rsquo;amazi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uyu ati &ldquo; <em>ikibazo gikunze kugaragara ni imitunganyirize rimwe na rimwe ikorwa badahereye kuri Bassin versant bigatera flooding Mu gihe cy&rsquo;imvura.&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Undi ati &ldquo;<em>Ikindi ni Valorization yabyo ikorwa n&rsquo;amakoperative ugusanga idatanga umusaruro cyane nkuko bikwiye!, kuko buriya Leta igiye iha technical Support ariya makoperative&nbsp; byaba byiza kurushaho. Impamvu ni uko Koperative yishakira Agronome kandi ikanamuhemba&nbsp; bityo rero ntabwo yashyira igitsure kubamuhaye akazi. Ikindi harigihe bamuhemba makeya maze nawe agakora gakeya bitewe nuko Ibyo akenera byamufasha mu kazi atabihabwa maze Umusaruro twifuzaga ntugerweho&rdquo;</em>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Undi muhinzi nawe ati&rdquo;<em>Ibishanga biri mu hantu hake mu Rwanda haberanye no gukoresha imashini,zunganira abahinzi mu mirima , mbona rero dukurikije uburyo Agri Mechanization iri guhabwa umwanya munini muri,iyi minsi, ibishanga byaza mubyamvere bishyira mu bikorwa iyi,gahunda&rdquo;.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>iki kiganiro cyagiye kigaruka no kbindi bitekerezo byafasha kugira turusheho kubyaza umusaruro ubutaka bwegereye amazi;uyu ati&rdquo;<em>Si ibishanga gusa erega!&nbsp; </em><em>N&rsquo; ibyitwa inkuka! Inkuka ni igasozi ariko hasengurutse amazi ukuyemo buffer zones naho. Hakwitabwaho huhizwa ayo mazi y, inzuzi, ibiyaga, n, imigezi&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byose ntago byagarajwe hano bitewe n&rsquo;uko ari ikiganiro kirekire cyane hagiye hatoranywamo imirongo migari ikavugwa muri make.</li>\r\no<li>Amazina yabatanze ibitekerezo ntago yagaragajwe muri iyi nkuru gusa amagambo yose ari mu utwuguruzo n&rsquo;utwugarizo (&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;) yose yandikuwe uko yanditse mu kiganiro.</li>\r\no<li>Ikiganiro nk&rsquo;iki kiba buri ku Cyumweru.</li>\r\no<li>Ushaka gukurikira ibi biganiro ukaba uri umuhinzi/umworozi cyangwa umugoronome/veterineri ku rwego urwo arirwo rwose nawe wasaba kujya k&rsquo;urubuga rwa YEAN Whatsapp unyuze kuri nimero ikurikira: +250 788 845 727 ,wakurikira YEAN kuri facebook cyangwa kuri twitter #UbuhinziBwacu @YEAN_Rwanda</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n','3',2023,40,'2016-10-22 14:40:21','Ubuhinzi Bwacu, Ibishanga',0,'online','no','no'),(173,'Ubuhinzi Bwacu: Ibitekerezo  ku ngingo igira iti: AMAHIRWE Y\'URUBYIRUKO MU GUKORA UBUHINZI','IMG-20161108-WA0022.jpg','<p>Kuri uyu Gatanu taliki ya 13 Nyakanga 2015 hatanzwe umwanya ku mbuga zose YEAN ikoresha mu gusakaza amakuru facebook, twitter, Whatsapp,Linkedin ndetse na Google+ mu kiganiro &ldquo;UBUHINZI BWACU&rdquo; wo kuganira ku ngingo yagiraga iti &ldquo;Iyo urebye hirya no hino kw&rsquo;isi usanga havugwa ko hari amahirwe menshi mu buhinzi (Opportunity), iyo bigeze ku mugabane wacu wa Afurika ho biravugwa cyane rwose abayobozi ndetse n&rsquo;abashinzwe Ibijyanye n&rsquo;ubuhinzi bagashishikariza urubyiruko kujya mu buhinzi no kubukunda kuko burimo amahirwe menshi , Byagera no mu Rwanda Urubyiruko rugashishikarizwa kugana ubuhinzi mu rwego rwo kubyaza umusaruro amahirwe menshi abuvugwamo ndetse no mu nama nyinshi ugasanga bivugwa ko urubyiruko rukwiye kugana ubuhinzi rugakora rukiteza imbere. Ku rundi Ruhande iyo uganiriye n&rsquo;urubyiruko rwamaze kugera muri ubwo buhinzi rubukora buri munsi usanga bagaragaza imbogamizi nyinshi zishobora guca intege undi wakwifuza kubujyamo, ndetse hari na bamwe bakubwira bati bya bindi tubwirwa biri he? Ese wowe ubibona ute?&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urubyiruko Rukora ubuhinzi mu Rwanda Rwatanze ibitekerezo byarwo ku buryo babibona tukaba twabakusanyirije bimwe mu byavugiwe Ku Rubuga rwa Whatsapp aha akaba ari naho aba bahinzi basangirira amakuru y&rsquo;ubuhinzi ya buri munsi ku buryo bwihuse.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Icyitonderwa:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1) Aba batanze ibitekerezo ni urubyiruko Rukora ubuhinzi mu byiciro itandukanye harimo abikorera, abakorera ibigo bitandukanye, abakorera imishinga ya leta ndetse ndetse n&rsquo;abanyeshuli.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2) Ibitekerezo byandikuwe uko byatanzwe nta gihinduwemo kugirango bigumane umwimerere wa nyirukubitanga gusa hahiswemo kugaragazwa ibitekerezo gusa ngo abatakurikiye ikiganiro babashe kubona icyo urubyiruko rutekereza ku buhinzi bwacu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3) Ibi bitekerezo ni iby&rsquo;abahinzi YEAN icyo yakoze ni ugutanga umwanya mu kiganiro.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikiganiro cyatangiye Umwe agira ati&hellip;..</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/11/yean-2.jpg\"><img alt=\"yean  2\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-278\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/11/yean-2.jpg?w=300&amp;h=160\" style=\"height:160px; width:300px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yego hari abaguca integer kubera inzitizi bahuye Nazi ariko hari nabaguyera imbaraga kubera ibyo bagezeho; ex: bamwe mu bitabiruye Youth in Agribusiness festival yari yateguwe ba RDI na Agriprofocus kubufatanye na CAVM ndetse na YEAN yafashije mukubimebyesha benshi, batangiye gupanga uko bashora mubuhinzi bitewe na role models bahabinye.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Akenshi usanga facilities zikiri nke cyane, urugero nzi umuhinzi witwa Diego ahinga inyanya mu bugesera ariko umusaruro we kubera utubutse, akenshi umupfana ubusa kubera kubura isoko ryagutse!!! Njye nkumva leta yatworohereza mukudushakira amasoko yo hanze kko twe kuyabona biratugora!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Amahirwe arahari mubyukuri</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wenda ikibazo cyaba uburyo bukoreshwa kugira ngo ayo mahirwe amenyeshwe kandi agere kubo yagenewe ndavuga urubyiruko.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urugero mukwezi kwa Kane uyu mwaka, MYICT na SNV twabyumviseho aya amakuru:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu rwego rwo kongerera urubyiruko ubushobozi mu kwihangira imirimo hashingiwe ku buhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi ndetse n&rsquo;ibidukikije n&rsquo;ingufu zivuguruye, uyu munsi Minisiteri y&rsquo;Urubyiruko n&rsquo;Ikoranabuhanga (MYICT) yasinye amasezerano y&rsquo;ubufatanye n&rsquo;umuryango w&rsquo;Abaholandi wita ku iterambere (SNV). Ibi bikaba bizaha akazi urubyiruko rubarirwa ku bihumbi bine mu gihe cy&rsquo;imyaka ibiri n&rsquo;itatu</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikigamijwe gikuru ngo ni ukwereka urubyiruko amahirwe arwegereye ndetse no kuba rwabyazwa umusaruro cyane cyane mu buhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi ndetse no kurengera ibidukikije.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu mwaka w&rsquo; 2015 Minisiteri y&rsquo;Urubyiruko n&rsquo;ikoranabuhanga ivuga ko abanyarwanda 65% bakora ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi ari urubyiruko, benshi muri aba akaba ari abatarabashije kugera mu mashuri.Minisitiri w&rsquo;Urubyiruko n&rsquo;Ikoranabuhanga, Jean Philbert Nsengimana yavuze ko aya masezerano agiye gufasha mu kongera amahirwe urubyiruko rufite mu kwihangira imirimo mu bice bitandukanye, kandi ko mu buhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi ahakenewe kongerwa umusaruro ariho bagiye kwibanda mu gukoresha ikoranabuhanga aho ngo urubyiruko rugera ku 4 000 ruzabonamo imirimo.Yanavuze ko bagiye gushyira imbaraga mu kwifashisha ikoranabuhanga mu buvumvu (ubworozi bw&rsquo;inzuki) aho urubyiruko rugera kuri 500 ruzahugurwa rukaba rwayibyaza umusaruro .Phomolo Maphosa, umuyobozi mukuru wa SNV Rwanda, yavuze ko bishimiye gukorana na Minisiteri y&rsquo;Urubyiruko n&rsquo;Ikoranabuhanga mu gutanga umusanzu mu iterambere bagabanya ubukene baha urubyiruko ubushobozi bwo guhanga imirimo mu bijyanye n&rsquo;ingufu z&rsquo;ivugurura.Ati &ldquo;Ibi bijyanye n&rsquo;intego y&rsquo;u Rwanda mu gutanga akazi ku rubyiruko rugera ku bihumbi 200 kandi ndabyizeye ko abo iyi gahunda ireba bazahabwa akazi kandi bazaba bari mu bantu bazatanga umusanzu mu iterambere rirambye ry&rsquo;igihugu.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mbese nibangahe bamaze kugerwaho cg bamenye iyi gahunda?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uburyo bwo gusakaza aya makuru buracyari ikibazo</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mbese nibangahe bamaze kugerwaho cg bamenye iyi gahunda? Uburyo bwo gusakaza aya makuru buracyari ikibazo</p>\r\n\r\n<p>nonese ziriya opportunities zivugwa , abantu ntibazibona biturutse kutamenya amakuru? NE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mwaramutse iki kiganiro Nikiza gusa igitekerezo naranga nuko buri wese ubifuteye ububasha cyangwa ubumenyi akwiye kuba umukangurambaga warundi rubyiruko nkubu murwanda murabuzi barabivuga natwe turabivuga ko urubyiruko naba gore bafite amahirwe aruta ayabandi nukuvuga tutabaye abakangurambaga ayamahirwe azashira ntacyo tugezeho</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Amahirwe muri agriculture uretse no ku rubyiruko n&rsquo;abagore arahari.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gusa ikibazo gihari kdi mbona kizabonerwa umuti bitinze ni uburyo bwo kubungabunga umusaruro w&rsquo;ibikomoka ku buhinzi. &ldquo;Post harvest technology&rdquo;.Kuko ntibyumvikana ukuntu umuntu ahinga ndetse akeza yarangiza akabura aho aganisha umusaruro we. Za NAEB n&rsquo;ibindi bigo bya leta bikorana n&rsquo;ubuhinzi byakagize department ishinzwe guhuza abanyarwanda bafite umusaruro mwinshi n&rsquo;amasoko yo hanze mu gihe uburyo bwo guhunika bukigaragara nk&rsquo;imbogamizi mu buhinzi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nzaramba nanjye nicyo navuze haruguru</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nabisomye ariko nanjye mbona ariho ruzingiye kuko ubundi ubuhinzi bwakabaye bwaradukijije.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ariko jyewe ndabona ibyo muvuga ataribyo kuko miniteri y&rsquo; inganda hamwe n&rsquo;iyimari imibare iracyari micye cyane kuburyo ntahamanya namwe</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urebye inyanya zipfa ubusa ku mwero wazo, ukareba igiciro cy&rsquo;ibigori ku mwero wabyo,&hellip;twahita twemeranya.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Njye numva leta yashyira ingufu zisumbuye kuzo ishyira mu buhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi kdi hagafatwa n&rsquo;ingamba zihariye Ku Bantu babangamira iterambere ry&rsquo;umuhinzi mworozi.Amasoko nayo agashakishwa kuko iyo umuntu abonye umusaruro akabura isoko bimuca intege zogukomeza gukora!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mwaramutse Nubwo ikiganiro amasaha yacyo ameze nkayarangiye ariko nubundi ndizera ko dukomeje tukaganira kuri iyi nsanganya matsiko byaba ByizaUbuhinzi mu rwanda mu rusange harimo ikibazo</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>ubutaka bwo guhingaho ugeraranyije nuko tungana ni buke</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>2.nubwo bucye buhari bwakagombye kwera nibwo bwororerwaho.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.tutirenfagije ko urubyiruko rwinshi ntanubushobozi ruba rufite kandi nuburyo bwo kubona igishoro bitaba byoroshye rimwe na rimwe ntibinakunde.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4.ngirango niba nta na 1%ryurubyiruko rukora ubuhinzi tukaba tuvuga ko isoko ntaryo kubera post harvest technologies nke cg zisa zisa nkaho ntanizihari kandi wenda ntanubwo abanyarwanda ubwabo baba bahaze kuburyo twatangira gusagurira amahanga.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikigaraga nuko ubuhinzi mu rwanda butarimo amahirwe yo kuba abantu bakiteza imbere nkuko mu bivuga kuko simpakanye ko hari abi buteza imbere ariko se nibangahe%</p>\r\n\r\n<p>@Kayitana imibare igaragaza ko benshi mubakora ubuhinzi ari abatarize bivuzeko n&rsquo;amshirwe yo kumenya amasoko ari ari limited.Mbese nibategerwa bizagenda bite?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ninyanya abashaka isoko bagakwiye gutunganya umusaruro</p>\r\n\r\n<p>@Ernest amahirwe yo gutera imbere bivuye kubuhinzi arahari kandi koko ubuhinzi buteza imbere uwabukoranye ubuhanga akabigira umwuga</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Naho ujya guhinga kugira ngo ataraza gusa ntazigera atera imbere</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jackson ndakumva ariko se bisaba urumva uri urubyiruko uyu munsi urangije kaminuza wabyuka ugahita ujya guhinga cyangwa wabanza ukajya gushaka igishoro mu zindi domaine?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kuko ubuhinzi akenshi ntago uba wizeye neza the yield u will gain according to the input used. Jyewe mbona bitoroshye p!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cyakora nk&rsquo;ibirayi buriya byafatiwe ingamba kuko ruriya tuganda rwa Musanze rukora chips hari icyo rwongereye kigaragara.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mwe sinzi niba mutabona ko gukora ubuhinzi bigoye ahubwo njye mbona leta yashushikariza urubyiruko kugana izindi domain kuko uko buri muntu wese wurubyiruko azashyira imbaraga mu buhinzi agakura yumva ko agomba kuba umuhinzi nicyo cyizatuma tudatera imbere nkurubyiruko</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Njye icyo mbona ahubwo twe urubyiruko tuganira hano tujye twita kuri post harvest ndetse research and development insteady yo kurwanira kuba aba Growers</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nkuko indi mishinga yose itegurwa no kijya mubuhinzi bisaba gutegurwa-gushaka ibishoro n&rsquo;ibindi Ntabwo nyine warangiza kaminuza udafite igishoro ngo uhite utangura ubuhinzi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kujya muhuhinzi ntibivuze gusa kujya gutera seeds no gusarura</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ndabyumva ariko mba mbona tuba aribyo twibanzeho kandi ibyo bindi byi ni big issue isaba imbaraga urubyiruko rwinshi rudafite</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Izo ni big issues ndabyemera-aho niho duhita dusabwa guhuza imbaraga</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubuhinzi ni bwiza bwadukiza gusa hasabwa ingamba zo kuba hakongerwa ubutaka bwo gukingaho hakaganywa umubare wabahinzi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uretse ko nubuhari nabwo budakoreshwa neza rimwe na rimwe kandi ukabona bumaze igihe kinini ntacyo bukora</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Erega sinzi haribyinshi bituma urubyiruko rucika intege mu byubuhinzi ariko nka Yean nicyo ibereyeho nubukangurambaga.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gusa tuzave mu guhora tuvuga niba koko ayo mahirwe ahari twagakwiye kubanza kuba beneficial yayo nkabagenerwa bikorwa</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ariko niba biza bamwe ntibanabimenye ngo wenda ntibabibyaze umusaruro ariko babimenye harimo ikibazo pee.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mwaramutse bahinzi bavandimwe, hano ibintu turimo kuganira ni ingirakamaro pe. Gusa ikibazo gikomeye, ubutaka buhingwaho bukera ahantu henshi bubangamiwe n&rsquo;imiturire. Ikindi ni uko ubuhinzi bukorwa akenshi n&rsquo;abatabuzi; iyo ugiye guhinga kuko wabonye kanaka ahinga gusa utabanje kwiga neza umushinga wawe ngo umenye neza byanze bikunze aho uzagurisha ibyo wejeje, nta kabuza urahomba. Amasoko arahari menshi y&rsquo;umusaruro ahubwo dukwiriye kumenya kuyashaka. Usanga iyi isoko ribonetse, tubura umusaruro uhagije cg wujuje ubuziranenge. Uwejeje nawe usanga ari utuntu duke utashobora gushakira isoko. So, icyo dukoneye ni abahinzi bazi icyo bakora kandi bari consistent kandi bakora uyu mwuga professionally. Naho ubundi leta ntacyo yageraho idafite abahinzi bameze batyo kuko opportunities zo irazitanga zihagije. Gusa leta nayo igomba kugira system 2 zikomeye kandi zinganya imbaraga; Extension na Marketing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mwiriwe neza nshuti bakunzi biterambere ryu buhinzi. Kurwanjye ruhande mbona kugirango ubuhinzi hano iwacu butere imbere kurwego twwifuza kandi nurubyiruko rugere kuri ayo mahirwe hari byinshi bikwiye gukorwa harimo icyambere gushyiraho uburyo bwiza bwo kugeza umusaruro kwissoko kuri ki hari byinshi bimaze gukorwa nkogushyiraho ibigega bihunika umusaruro ariko kandi haracyabura flow of information mperutse kubona ku makuru hari ahantu muri Rubavu bavuga ko umusaruro wa karoti bawugaburira amatungo ariko ugiye kureba hari ahantu henshi hano mugihugu bafite ikibazzo cyo kutabona karoti! Ikindi nekereza ni ukongera ikorana buhanga mubuhinzi haba muri production ndetse na value chain technology kuko ubutaka bwo ni buto ibi nkabona uruhare runini rwaba urwa leta mugukangurira financial institution korohereza abashora imari mubikorwa nkibyo ibi binshobora no gufasha mukongera ibyo twohereza mu mahanga nkasanga rero challenges kurubyiruko cyane cyane urwize ibijyanye nu buhinzi ari 1. Amikoro yokuba batangiza ibikorwa nibyo kuko usanga ahanini nta nubutaka baba bafite 2. Imyumvire itaba myiza kurwego rwurubyiruko 3. Lack of information</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mwakoze cyane ku bitekerezo byiza.Nanjye ndemeranya namwe ko kutabona amakuru y&rsquo;aho ibintu bikeneweke no kuba tudafite technology yo guhunika cyane cyane imboga n&rsquo;imbuto biri mu bihombya abahinzi (umusaruro waba mwinshi abaguzi bakamuha frs make agapfa kuyafata kuko atabashije kubibika ngo ashake isoko ryiza yitonze).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Birakwiye ko umuhinzi atangira umushinga yabanje kwiga neza isoko. Sinzi niba natwe mu Rda tuzagera aho umuhinzi yajya agirana contrat n&rsquo;abo azajya aha umusaruro, byibuze ku bigo binini. Numvise ko n&rsquo;abatubuzi b&rsquo;imbuto bakoranaga na RAB yabatengushye</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Leta ifashe abikorera gushyiraho inganda mu byaro zitunganya umusaruro ukaba wahunikwa cyangwa transport ikoraha. Bongere post harvest technology</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nk&rsquo;ubu inanasi n&rsquo;amatunda ntibishobora kubura isoko kuko bikorwamo jus.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nunze murya Daniel, kuki inganda zose yewe n&rsquo;izitunganya ibikomoka k&rsquo;ubuhinzi zigomba kuba mumigi mugihe raw materials bakoresha ziba mubyaro?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nizegerezwe abahinzi ubwikorezi buborohere,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abashinzwe innovations mubuhinzi (niba bahari) nibatwigire uburyo bwo guhunika by&rsquo;igihe gito umusaruro cyane cyane w&rsquo;imboga n&rsquo;imbuto( 60% muri afrika utagera Ku isoko)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibi nigeze mbibaza nyakubahwa minister kuri Twitter session ansubizako hari ba rwiyemezamirimo benda kubishoramo imari.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikindi umubare w&rsquo;abahinzi ukwiye kugabanuka bakareka kuba bwa buro bwinshi..</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urubyiruko rukwiye gufashwa kubona imirima yo guhingaho</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mwiriwe, ikintu mbona kigoye abahinzi burubyiriko si amikoro, ahubwo tubura amakuru ahagije. Urugero nko kumenya ese ni neza tones runaka zinyo mpinga mfite isoko rohoraho kuburyo nagira sustainable production ifite sustainable market?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ese mfite dufite ubumenyi buhagije mugutegura umushinga uzaba successful(forecasting)? Iyo ibibintu ubifite ugomba kuba enterpreneur mwiza kandi nta Bank nimwe yakwima amafaranga kuko Opportunities zirahari ahubwo habuze aba exploiting. Tugerageze twegere BDF institution zizadufasha bifatika. Thx</p>\r\n\r\n<p>amakuru aratanga ahubwo wenda,ntago agera,ku bantu ku buryo bushimishije akenshi agera,ku bantu bitabira inama gusa</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ikindi wenda n&rsquo;abahinzi ubwabo ntibabasha kubona,uwo babaza,ayo makuru</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mwaramutse! Ababishinzwe nibegere abahinzi bo mu cyaro kugirango berekwe ayo mahirwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ni byiza koko natwe urubyiruku ko dushyira imbaraga zacu mu buhinzi bworozi naho imbogamizi nubundi ntakintu nakimwe wakora ngo uzasange solutions (ibisubizo ) ari 100% kandi ntihakemurwa ibitabonetse, gusa nanjye nungutse bimwe ntakururaga turi kumwe&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nishimiye iyi gahunda yo kuganira kuri topic yatanzwe, nshimiye abateguye iyi gahunda n&rsquo;abatanga ibitekerezo bose.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hari ikibazo mbona kibaho mu bihugu byacu, abantu benshi ni aba theoristes. Usanga rwose abantu benshi bakubwira ko ibintu ibi nibi bishoboka (urugero:kwihangira umurimo) kdi bo nta n&rsquo;umwe bigeze bahanga. Burya ukuri kw&rsquo;ikintu ukumenya neza iyo ukirimo cg wacyibayemo. Actions speak louder than words</p>\r\n\r\n<p>OK ikiganiro cyaryoshye ariko sinagize amahirwe ko nari class ari ndibuze gusubiramo.muri dute mbonye hari some relevant knowledge I have gained.thx</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Improvement irakenewe ku buhinzi borozi twese kuva kuwo mu murima cyane ndetse ababufite mu nshingano</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikindi aba partener in agriculture twareba uburyo dukora kuburyo nta butaka bwasigara butabyajwe umusaruro, twakoresha irrigation, drip irrigation, dams, naho twe nkurubyiruko iyo turi kuri terrain haba hato ugasanga ni competition on scars land,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibi ugasanga aribyo biyuma bamwe ba dropping out in agriculture</p>\r\n\r\n<p>OK ikindi ntabwo turasobanukirwa kuri implementation of mechanical power in agriculture mbivuze student mechaniser in year five.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>OK ikindi ntabwo turasobanukirwa kuri implementation of mechanical power in agriculture mbivuze nka student mechaniser in year five.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikindi abafite aho bahurira na fertilizers importation in our country they should take care where this nitrogen is synthisised from, kko iyo iri from acidic we pollute our land indirect, this should known by RBS, And da mission of RAB and RBS, sametime they giving us loss in case of SEEDS IMPORTATION, they supply empty seeds, infected seeds,&hellip;., in case of imbuto yibigori, imyumbati in ruhango, bagerageze kbs kugira amakenga kubyo binjiza, bitazajya bituma capital nke dufite igendera mubihombo. Murakoze.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Selfish ni ikibazo bavandimwe</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Buri wese aratekinika noneho bikarangira haje bad seed.what would u do for them?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikindi turashimira YEAN RWANDA yateguye uru rubuga tubasabe abateguye baze gukora summary and conlusion and highlite imyanzuro and send it in agriculture boad to the concern. Thank you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nta myanzuro tafatwa aha kuko sitwe dushyiraho agri policies kdi n&rsquo;izihari ubwazo ziba ari nziza ku izina kuko imbere usanga zuzuyemo selfish gusa without much considering farmer&rsquo;s interests</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urugero ni Agasozi ndatwa. Njye nakoraga internship ahantu mpasanga agasozi ndatwa ngomba gukurikirana ko abahinzi bahingaho ingano zavamo bagahinga ibigori kdi bakoresheje DAP na urea. Ko mwize ubuhinzi iyo rotation muyizi he? Gukoresha DAP 2yrs nta lime byo ubwo what is it?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, it was my wonts if it so,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ni uko nyine hari ibyo ubona ukabura uko ubigenza</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hari aba technicien nabo batu desouva rwose, ugasanga baravuga igunduka ryimirina batitaye kuri crop ratation, batigeze bamenya disease host plant even same they do not think about season and update on climate,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kdi bose bahabwa amahugurwa ukibaza niba baba babyumvise?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubundi ngo abatechniciens benshi tubona ibyo bakora ntabwo ari scientific ni political from their own politics basanga muri institutions bakoramo. Uko usanze system yubatse niko ukora. urugero buriy umutechnicien agronome ukora muri RAB atandukanye na agronome w&rsquo;umurenge mu karere runaka</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abakorera leta hamwe na hamwe usanga icyo bagiye gukora babanza kureba inyungu zabo bwite kurusha icyo umugenerwabikorwa(farmer) abazunguka. Aha urugero bareba ordre de mission uko ingana.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Land use management iracyari nke mu Rda rwose aho usanga abantu batura hatarebwe kuri soil productivity or fertility bakibanda ahera ahatera hagasigara. Njye mbyibazaho cyane nkasanga food security ari ikibazo kitazatworohera muri futur</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nkumu technician utazana chenges, wakwibaza icyo akora, mumwanya arimo, ark kdi abonye adashoboye yareka abaturage bagakoresha indigenous technics</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Njye buriya mbabazwa cyane n&rsquo;imikorere mbona mu rwego rw&rsquo;ubuhinzi kuko mbona food security izaba ikibazo gikomeye mu myaka iza.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Naho c opportunities bavuga ni izihe? Theorists gusa</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngewe abantu bashinze imiturire nabagira inama bakajya kureba uburyo muri korea or bakaganira nabo kubijyanye nimiturire, umundi MINIREMA,MINAGRI,MIDIMAR,MINALOC,&hellip;. nizindi zifite aho zihuriye nubuhinzi murwanda bicare hamwe bahuze imirongo ngenderwaho kko hari ibikorwa bya ministeri imwi bibangamira ibyiyindi, bagatekereza SUSTAINABLE AGRICULTURE AND FOOD SECURITY</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Naphtali Urakoze cyane</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Njyewe icyo mbona nkikibazo cyane nuko ubuhinzi buri gukorwa nabantu benshi kdi batabifitiye ubushobozi, nkabona tubonye abashoramari mubyubuhinzi byaba byiza bagafata ubutaka bunini buri gukoreshwa nabi ntibutange umusaruro,bagakora ishoramari ry&rsquo;igihe kirambye nibwo twabona umusaruro uhagije!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nunze murya Daniel, kuki inganda zose yewe n&rsquo;izitunganya ibikomoka k&rsquo;ubuhinzi zigomba kuba mumigi mugihe raw materials bakoresha ziba mubyaro?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abashinzwe innovations mubuhinzi (niba bahari) nibatwigire uburyo bwo guhunika by&rsquo;igihe gito umusaruro cyane cyane w&rsquo;imboga n&rsquo;imbuto( 60% muri afrika utagera Ku isoko) Igihe umuntu agishakisha isoko umusaruro we ntupfe ubusa</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibi nigeze mbibaza nyakubahwa minister kuri Twitter session ansubizako hari ba rwiyemezamirimo benda kubishoramo imari. Ikindi umubare w&rsquo;abahinzi ukwiye kugabanuka bakareka kuba bwa buro bwinshi..</p>\r\n\r\n<p>mukanya saa kumi ni mwe turasoza ikiganiro hanyuma dukoeze kufanira bisanzwe , ubwo turaba dusoje ibijyanye n,ingingo twari twageneye uyu munsi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nizegerezwe abahinzi ubwikorezi buborohere,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ushobora kandi gukurikirana <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1564341857121351/\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">uko ikiganiro cyagenze kuri facebook ya YEAN </span></a>ndetse ukanakurikirana <a href=\"https://twitter.com/YEAN_Rwanda\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">YEAN kuri Twitter</span></a></p>\r\n','3',2498,40,'2015-07-15 01:04:02','Ubuhinzi Bwacu',0,'online','no','no'),(175,'Ubuhinzi Bwacu: Urubyiruko rukora ubuhinzi rusaba koroherezwa ngo rutange umusanzu muri uyu mwuga','IMG-20161214-WA0007.jpg','<p>Mukiganiro cyahuje urubyiruko rukora umwuga w&rsquo;ubuhinzi mu Rwanda, cyari gifite insanganyamatsiko igira iti &ldquo;Iyo urebye hirya no hino kw&rsquo;isi usanga havugwa ko hari amahirwe menshi mu buhinzi (Opportunity), iyo bigeze ku mugabane wacu wa Afurika ho biravugwa cyane rwose abayobozi ndetse n&rsquo;abashinzwe Ibijyanye n&rsquo;ubuhinzi bagashishikariza urubyiruko kujya mu buhinzi no kubukunda kuko burimo amahirwe menshi , Byagera no mu Rwanda Urubyiruko rugashishikarizwa kugana ubuhinzi mu rwego rwo kubyaza umusaruro amahirwe menshi abuvugwamo ndetse no mu nama nyinshi ugasanga bivugwa ko urubyiruko rukwiye kugana ubuhinzi rugakora rukiteza imbere. Ku rundi Ruhande iyo uganiriye n&rsquo;urubyiruko rwamaze kugera muri ubwo buhinzi rubukora buri munsi usanga bagaragaza imbogamizi nyinshi zishobora guca intege undi wakwifuza kubujyamo, ndetse hari na bamwe bakubwira bati bya bindi tubwirwa biri he? Ese wowe ubibona ute .&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urubyiruko rwaganiriye byinshi, ahatanzwe ingero zitandukanye z&rsquo;amahirwe aboneka mubinzi yafasha urubyiruko mukwinjira mu buhinzi: amasezerano atandukanye hagati y&rsquo;inzego za leta n&rsquo;abaterankunga uregero <a href=\"http://www.myict.gov.rw/home/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">MYICT</span></a> na <a href=\"http://www.snvworld.org/en/countries/rwanda\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">SNV </span></a>mukongera ikoranabuhanga mubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi bw&rsquo;inzuki kurubyiruko rusaga 3000 yasinywe mu kwezi kwa Mata 2015, ibigega nka BDF nibindi bigo by&rsquo;imari byorohereza urubyiruko kubona ubushobozi bwo gukora ubuhinzi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu bindi bitekerezo byatanzwe harimo:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kuba urubyiruko rutumva neza ngo runasobanukirwe n&rsquo;amahirwe atandukanye ruba rufite cyangwa ngo runamenye aho rubariza amakuru ajyanye nabyo, gusa ngo amahirwe yo arahari nkuko byagaragajwe n&rsquo;umwe murubyiruko rwitabiriye ihuriro ryiswe &ldquo;Youth in Agribusiness Festival&rdquo; yateguwe na <a href=\"http://agriprofocus.com/rwanda\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">AgriProfocus</span></a> kubufatanye na Kaminuza y&rsquo;u Rwanda ishami ry&rsquo;ubuhinzi (CAVM), RDI na YEAN aho yagaragaje ko hari ingero nyinshi z&rsquo;urubyiruko rwamenye rukanabyaza umusaruro ayo mahirwe kuburyo ubu bageze ku bikorwa bifatika.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urubyiruko kandi Rwavuze ko rutamenya amakuru kugihe cyangwa ntanamenyekane bitewe n&rsquo;inzira zakoreshejwe mukuyatangaza.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikibazo kindi cyagaragajwe nka kimwe mu by&rsquo;ingutu bibangamira urubyiruko ni ikibazo cyo kutabona ubutaka cyangwa bukaboneka buhenzwe kugira ngo batangire bashyire mungiro ubumenyi butandukanye baba baravanye mumashuli. Iki kibazo cyiyongeraho ikindi kibazo cyo kuba ubuhinzi bukorwa n&rsquo;abantu benshi badafite ubumenyi buhagije bwo gukora ubuhinzi kinyamwuga ndetse baba bataniteguye kumva no gushyira mubikorwa gahunda nshya z&rsquo;ubuhinzi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imiturire itizwe neza kandi y&rsquo;akajagari ikomeje gutwara ubutaka aho usanga inashyirwa kubutaka bigaragara ko aribwo bwagakoreshejwe mubuhinzi bukanatanga umusaruro.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikibazo cyuko n&rsquo;abagerageje gukora ubuhinzi rimwe na rimwe umusaruro wabo cyane cyane imboga n&rsquo;imbuto bibapfana ubusa bitewe no kubura amasoko ndetse nubumenyi budahagije muguhunika.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu myanzuro n&rsquo;ibyifuzo byatanzwe harimo kuba</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MINAGRI n&rsquo;izindi nzego bireba zashyira imbaraga mukumenyekanisha amahirwe aba ahari hagakoreshwa uburyo bushoboka guhuriza hamwe abantu benshi nk&rsquo;imbuga nkoranya-mbaga.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gufasha urubyiruko kubona ubutaka bwo guhingaho</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gutangira gushaka ingamba zituma umubare w&rsquo;abakora ubuhinzi ugabanuka ubuhinzi bugakorwa n&rsquo;ababifitiye ubushobozi n&rsquo;ubumenyi bihereye mumasambu ya leta n&rsquo;ibyanya bitandukanye nko mubishanga n&rsquo;ahandi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imiturire n&rsquo;ahagenerwa imidugudu n&rsquo;imigi byakwiye kujya bibanza bikigwaho hagakorwa ubushakashatsi na no guhuza ubutaka kuko hagaragaye ko hamwe imijyi igenda ijya ahagakwiye gukorerwa ubuhinzi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hakwiye gukomezwa uburyo bwo gufasha abahinzi mumihingire yabo n&rsquo;ikoreshwa ry&rsquo;amafumbire rikaba habanje kwiga ibyo akozemo hato bitazangiza ubutaka bwacu muminsi iri imbere. Abashinzwe gufasha abahinzi bakwiye kuba abantu babifitiye ubumenyi kuko mu nzego z&rsquo;ibanze usanga harimo abakora ako kazi bataranize ubuhinzi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hakwiye Kubaho kandi ubufasha mukongera ubumenyi bw&rsquo;umuhinzi muguhunika cyane cyane imboga n&rsquo;imbuto kandi n&rsquo;inganda zitunganya umusaruro zikegerezwa abaturage mubyaro aho kuba gusa mumigi kuko ibi usanga binagora abahinzi kuzigezaho umusaruro.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abahinzi bakwiye gufashwa kumenya no kugeza umusaruro wabo kumasoko byaba byiza bakanagirana amasezerano naba rwiyemeza mirimo bazagura umusaruro wabo mbere yo guhinga bigafasha umuhinzi gushora imari mu buhinzi azi ko afite isoko.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MINAGRI n&rsquo;izindi nzego bireba bakwiye kongera imbaraga mugushyiraho uburyo urubyiruko ruhura rugasangira amakuru n&rsquo;ubuhamya ku mahirwe n&rsquo;ibikorwa byagezweho, ibi bikaba byafasha rumwe murubyiruko mukongera ubushake bwo kwitabira ubuhinzi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urubyiruko kandi rwifuje ko Amahuriro nka YEAN n&rsquo;ayandi yahabwa agaciro n&rsquo;inzego zishinzwe ubuhinzi kuko ariyo miyoboro bashobora kunyuzamo ibitekerezo n&rsquo;inama zitandukanye ndetse no kumenya amahirwe atandukanye aba ahari.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibi ni bimwe mu bitekerezo bitangwa mu kiganiro UBUHINZI BWACU kinyura ku mbuga nkoranyambaga zose YEAN yifashisha mu gusakaza amakuru y&rsquo;Ubuhinzi. Aho hategurwa ingingo runaka iganirwaho hanyuma Umuhinzi wese aho aherereye agatanga igitekerezo bishingiye ku ngingo yo kuganiraho iba yatanzwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Byateguwe na Ndera Jackson</em></p>\r\n','3',13710,3,'2015-11-26 00:25:26','Urubyiruko, Ubuhinzi Bwacu',0,'online','no','no'),(176,'Tumenye ifumbire ya DI Grow ihabwa ibihingwa n\'amatungo','DIGROW.jpg','<p>Iyini ifumbire y&rsquo;umwimerere isukika nziza cyane ikungahaye ku myunyu ngugu ikenerwa n&rsquo;igihingwa ku bwinshi (macronutrients), mu buke (micronutrients), imisemburo ituma igihingwa gikura neza ,indabyo zacyo ntizihunguke (Plant grow hormones) aribyo byongera umusaruro ku bihingwa byerera hejuru y&rsquo;ubutaka no ku byerera mu butaka bigashora imizi myinsi kandi minini.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyi fumbire kandi ifite Humic acid ituma ubutaka bugenda burushaho kuba bwiza bugasubirana umwimerere bwahoranye uko ugenda uyikorresha ku rugerp rugeze kuri 30% bityo ukaba ubungabunze ibidukikije bivuzengo umusaruro ugenda wiyongera kuva kuri 30% kugeza kuri 300% by&rsquo;umusaruro wabonaga, ikindi kandi itwarika neza.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyo itewe ku mababi n&rsquo;uruti ihita yinjira mu gihingwa bityo igahita yunganira indi myunyu ngugu igihingwa cyakuraga mu butaka bityo igihingwa kikaba kibonye ibigitunga ku buryo buhagije ku rugero rwuzuye kigashobora kwihanganira indwara (Kongerera igihingwa ubudahangarwa).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/04/digrow.jpg\"><img alt=\"Y\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-41\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/04/digrow.jpg?w=464&amp;h=232\" style=\"height:232px; width:464px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ubwoko bwa D.I.Grow.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hari ubwoko bubiri: D.I. Grow y&rsquo;Icyatsi ndetse na D.I. Grow y&rsquo;Umutuku</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>D.I. Grow y&rsquo;Icyatsi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ifite umwihariko kuko ikoreshwa ku bihingwa byose n&rsquo;amatungo yose yongera umusaruro w&rsquo;ibibikomokaho. Iyo winitsee imbuto y&rsquo;indobanure uba ugirango wongere ubudahangarwa imbuto wateye., Biturutse ku myunyungugu ndetse na humic acid ndetse n&rsquo;imisemburo iboneka muri D.I.Grow igatuma zimera vuba kandi zishishe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/04/di-grow.jpg\"><img alt=\"Di grow\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-43\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/04/di-grow.jpg\" style=\"height:345px; width:345px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>D.I.Grow y&rsquo;Icyatsi ku gihingwa .</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikoreshwa kuva binika imbuto z&rsquo;indobanure ikanaterwa ku bihingwa bimaze kuzana amababi kugeza bizanye uruyange ku byerera hejuru y&rsquo;ubutaka no ku binyabijumba bitera gushora imizi. Ikoreshwa kandi ku biti byera imbuto no ku bitera imbuto.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Akamaro ka D.I.Grow y&rsquo;Icyatsi ku bihingwa muri Rusange</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Iyo uyinikishije imbuto z&rsquo;indobanure ugahita uzitera nyuma y&rsquo;igihe kigenwe ku mbuto ugiye gutera byihutisha kumera kwimbuto wateye, byongerera ubudahangarwa imbuto wateye ntipfe gufatwa n&rsquo;indwara iyo ariyo yose bityo zikamera ari nyinshi.</li>\r\no<li>Iyo uyiteye cyangwa uyuhiye igihingwa kuva bimeze kugeza bizanye uruyange bituma habaho gukura vuba kw&rsquo;ibyo wateye, bigashora neza imizi, bikazana amashami menshi n&rsquo;amababi atoshye .</li>\r\no<li>Yongera ubushobozi bwo kurwanya indwara, bityo ikongera ubushobozi bw&rsquo;imizi mu gukurura imyunyu ngugu itunga igihingwa .</li>\r\no<li>Ituma igihingwa gikura neza kandi vuba kuko ikungahaye ku myunyu ngugu yose n&rsquo;imisemburo ndetse na Humic acid utasanga mu yindi fumbire iyo ariyo yose.</li>\r\no<li>Ituma igihingwa gishora imizi kure kandi ntibore</li>\r\no<li>Ituma amababi y&rsquo;igihongwa adahunguka akiri mato</li>\r\no<li>Yihutisha igihingwa mu gukura bityo kikera vuba .</li>\r\no<li>Yongerera ubushobozi ubutaka bwagundutse bukongera bukagarura umwimerere wabwo kuri 30%uko usaruye iyo ifatanijwe n&rsquo;imborera</li>\r\no<li>Igabanya ikoreshwa n&rsquo;ifumbire mvaruganda ku kigero cya 30% ku bantu bifuza kubifatanya.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>D.I.Grow y&rsquo;umutuku</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikoreshwa ku bihingwa gusa iyo bomaze kuzana uruyange cyangwa indabyo ku byerera hejuru yubutaka no ku binyabijumba bimaze gushora imizi ariwo musaruro wabyo kugeza bimaze kugaragaza ko byeze.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/04/di-grow-itukura.jpg\"><img alt=\"di grow itukura\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-42\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/04/di-grow-itukura.jpg\" style=\"height:323px; width:323px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>NB: D.I. Grow y&rsquo;umutuku wibuke ko idakoreshwa ku matungo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Akamaro ka D.I. Itukura ku Bihingwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Ituma indabyo zidahunguka kandi amatunda ntagwe ateze</li>\r\no<li>Ituma imbuto ziba nziza kandi zikaryoha</li>\r\no<li>Yongera igihe cyo guhunika imbuto n&rsquo;indabyo</li>\r\no<li>Ituma indabo zidahunguka vuba</li>\r\no<li>Yongera kwigabanyamo uturemangingo bityo bikongera umusaruro</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Uburyo Bayishyira ku bihingwa</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Gufuhera: D.I. Grow yicyatsi ifuherwa ku bihingwa byose dushyikira mu burebure uretse ku nsina naho yaba ikiri nto kubera imitere y&rsquo;amakoma yayo. Iyo ufuhera ufuhera ku mababi ndetse no ku giti nkuko bikorwa ku miti yica udukoko twonona ibihingwa. Ahangaha igomba gufungurwa mu mazi ku bipimo byagenwe.</li>\r\no<li>Gucukura: Ibi bikorwa ku bihingwa bidashobora gushikirwa cyangwa ibiti nk&rsquo;amatunda n&rsquo;ibindi&hellip; aho ducukura utwobo tune ku mbade enye z&rsquo;igiti muri cm25 uvuye ku giti, umwobo ukaba ufite cm15 cyangwa ugakubita isuka imwe. Uvanga ml 25 za D.I. Grow muri litiro imwe y&rsquo;amazi. Muri urwo ruvange rwa D.I.grow ugabanyamo ibice bine bingana maze ushyire muri buri mwobo.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gukoresha urushinge:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibi bikorwa ku nsina aho D.I.Grow idafungura ahubwo ufata sesi 5 cyangwa ml 5 zayo idafunguye ukayitera mu nsina ku nguni ya 45<sup><span style=\"font-size:small\">0 </span></sup>. Ku nsina ikiri ntoya utera kuri kimwe cya kabiri cyayo naho inkuru ukayitera muri metero imwe uvuye hasi, bigakorwa rimwe mu kwezi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/04/di-grow-banana.jpg\"><img alt=\"di grow banana\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-44\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/04/di-grow-banana.jpg\" style=\"height:330px; width:425px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>D.I. Grow yicyatsi ku matungo</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyi yo ifite umwihariko kuko ihabwa amatungo yose yaba amaremare , ibiguruka ndetse n&rsquo;amafi aho igira umumaro ukurikira iyo ukoreshejwe neza, wibukeko ikungahaye ku myunyu ngugu ikamurwa mu cyatsi kikiri gito gikungahaye ku runyuranyurane rw&rsquo;imyunyu ngugu itungo ryajyaga gushaka mu byatsi yari burishe cyangwa yari bukenere mubyo kurya byaryo bitandukanye .</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Yongerera itungo apeti</li>\r\no<li>Ituma rikura vuba kandi rikabyibuha</li>\r\no<li>Yunganira itungo yongera imyunyu ngugu rikenera</li>\r\no<li>Ituma ritanga umusaruro mwiza kandi mwinshi</li>\r\no<li>Ituma ritarwaragurika</li>\r\no<li>Yongera ubwiza n&rsquo;agaciro k&rsquo;ibirikomokaho</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Byateguwe hifashishijwe imfashanyigisho yateguwe na DYNAPHAM</em></p>\r\n','1',4157,3,'2015-04-04 05:12:44','Ifumbire, DI Grow',2,'online','no','no'),(177,'FAO launches the #soils4life Instagram photo contest','FAO-soils4life.jpg','<p><strong><em>Post a photo, raise awareness on the importance of soils, win a prize! </em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p>This year, soils are at the centre of global attention. As part of the International Year of Soils, we are turning to you to help FAO highlight the importance of sustainable soil management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are launching the <strong>#soils4life </strong>contest on Instagram to share photos related to soils, their potential, their functions, but also instances of exploitation or abuse to help draw attention to the myriad of issues concerning this valuable resource.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How to participate: </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.Take a photo of something you want to draw attention to regarding soils and share it on Instagram. The photo must be original, which means you should take it yourself. Your photos are governed under the Instagram terms of use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.Tell in the posting where the photo was taken, and why you think soils are important for a healthy life. Include the hashtag #soils4life. Don&rsquo;t forget to set your account to &ldquo;public&rdquo; to have your likes counted!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.In the first round of the contest, the 20 photos with the most likes on their Instagram account will be selected for a second round of voting. Other social media channels do not matter for this contest!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4.The final 20 photos will be featured on the <a href=\"https://instagram.com/unfao/\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">@UNFAO Instagram</span></a> account and a photo album will be shared on the FAO webpage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.During the second round, people will vote on the FAO Instagram account the three out of twenty best soil photos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dates: </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The first stage</strong> of the contest will run from 2 April until 17 May. All photos posted during this time with #soils4life hashtag will be eligible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The final counting for likes will take place on 17 May and the 20 finalists will be selected and their pictures posted on the FAO Instagram account the following week. The finalists will be contacted by the FAO social media team for more information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The second stage</strong> of the contest will start on 25 May.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The three most voted photos out of the twenty on our Instagram account will be announced on 15 June.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prizes for the three winners will include an International Year of Soils goody bag to be delivered directly to the winners*.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Spread the word:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even if you don&rsquo;t participate in the contest, you can spread the word across your network and help us raise awareness of the contest and the International Year of Soils. We are looking for photos related to soils from around the world, which can cover any aspect that you deem important and want to share. If you want to share more than one photo, please do! There is no limit to how many pictures you can post!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>* The social media team in FAO will contact all winners for their high resolution photos as well as for information on where to deliver prizes. </em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n','1',1281,3,'2015-04-04 05:12:44','Competition',0,'online','no','no'),(182,'Ibipimo by\'ifumbire ya D.I.Grow Bikoreshwa ku Bihingwa no ku Matungo','Di grow.jpg','<p>Mu Minsi ishize twabagejejeho ifumbire yitwa D.I. Grow ikoreshwa ku Bihingwa no ku matungo kandi igatuma umusaruro ubivaho usumba uw&rsquo;izindi fumbire wakoresha, abantu bakomeje kudusaba ibijyanye n&rsquo;ibipimo bikoreshwa kuri buri bwoko bw&rsquo;ibihingwa ndetse no ku matungo,twarabibakusanyirije.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p><strong>IBIPIMO BYA D.I.GROW BIKORESHWA MU BIHINGWA </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Buri bwoko bw&rsquo;ibihingwa bugira ingano y&rsquo;ifumbire bukenera niyo mpamvu hano muri iyi nkuru twabakoreye ibipimo bikoreshwa kuri buri bwoko bw&rsquo;ibihingwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibinyamisogwe:</strong> Muri litiro 1 yamazi hajyamo ml 5 za D.I.Grow, igaterwa nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 14 hagati y&rsquo;itera n&rsquo;irindi. Kwinika imbuto z&rsquo;indobanure bikorwa iminota 30.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urugero: Ibishyimbo , amashaza ubunyobwa , soya,&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibinyampeke:</strong> Muli litiro y&rsquo;amazi hajyamo ml 5 za D.I.Grow , igaterwa nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 10-14. Kwinika imbuto byo bimara iminota 30 uretse ingano n&rsquo;umuceri bimara amasaha 24.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urugero: amasaka, ingano , umuceri , ibigori,&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Imboga:</strong> <strong>:</strong> Muri litiro 1 yamazi hajyamo ml 5 za D.I.Grow, igaterwa nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 14 hagati y&rsquo;itera n&rsquo;irindi. Kwinika umurama ufatika bikorwa iminota 30.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urugero: Amashu ,inyanya ,karoti, ibihaza ,&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibinyabijumba </strong>: Muri litiro 1 yamazi hajyamo ml 5 za D.I.Grow, igaterwa nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 21 hagati y&rsquo;itera n&rsquo;irindi. Kwinika bikorwa iminota 15 ku migozi y&rsquo;ibijumba no ku ngeri z&rsquo;imyumbati.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urugero: Ibirayi , ibijumba, ibikoro, imyumbati,&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibiti byera imbuto:</strong> Muri litiro 1 yamazi hajyamo ml 7 za D.I.Grow, igaterwa nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 30 hagati y&rsquo;itera n&rsquo;irindi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urugero:Avoka ibipapayi , ibinyomoro</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Umuceri</strong>: Muri litiro 1 yamazi hajyamo ml 5 za D.I.Grow, igaterwa nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 14 hagati y&rsquo;itera n&rsquo;irindi. Ibi bikorwa ku bwoko bwose bw&rsquo;umuceri.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibihumyo:</strong> Muri litiro 1 yamazi hajyamo ml 5 za D.I.Grow, igaterwa nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 7 hagati y&rsquo;itera n&rsquo;irindi. Ibi bikorwa ku bwoko bwose bw&rsquo;ibihumyo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Imbuto ziri muri pipiniyeri:</strong> Muri litiro 1 yamazi hajyamo ml 5 za D.I.Grow, igaterwa nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 14 hagati y&rsquo;itera n&rsquo;irindi. Bikorwa ku bwoko bwose buri pipiniyeri.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyayi:</strong> Muri litiro 1 yamazi hajyamo ml 5 za D.I.Grow, igaterwa nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 14 hagati y&rsquo;itera n&rsquo;irindi. BIkorw ku bwoko bwose.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibiskeke:</strong> Muri litiro 1 yamazi hajyamo ml 5 za D.I.Grow, igaterwa nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 14 hagati y&rsquo;itera n&rsquo;irindi. Kwinika bikorwa iminota 15 . Ku bwoko bwose bw&rsquo;ibisheke.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Itabi: </strong> Muri litiro 1 yamazi hajyamo ml 5 za D.I.Grow, igaterwa nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 14 hagati y&rsquo;itera n&rsquo;irindi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Inanasi:</strong> Muri litiro 1 yamazi hajyamo ml 5 za D.I.Grow, igaterwa nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 14 hagati y&rsquo;itera n&rsquo;irindi. Kwinika bikorwa iminota 15 .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Insina:</strong> Muri litiro 1 yamazi hajyamo ml 5 za D.I.Grow, igaterwa nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 30 hagati y&rsquo;itera n&rsquo;irindi. Kwinika bikorwa iminota 15 . Aha twabibutsa ko iyo ari ku nsina idafungurwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikitonderwa: Ibi bipimo bikoreshwa kuri D.I Grow itukura kimwe n&rsquo;Iy&rsquo;icyatsi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>IBIPIMO BYA D.I.GROW BIKORESHWA KU MATUNGO</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Inka iri hejuru y&rsquo;amezi 18</strong> bayiha ml15 cyangwa sesi 15 muri litiro 5 z&rsquo;amazi bigakorwa 3 mu cyumweru . Uhagarika kuyiha isigaje 1/3 cy&rsquo;amezi imara kugirango ibyare.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Inka iri munsi y&rsquo;amezi 18</strong> bayiha ml15 cyangwa sesi 15 muri litiro 10 z&rsquo;amazi bigakorwa 3 mu cyumweru . Ntago umuntu ashobora guha inyana yonka kandi wirinda ko ibyibuha cyane kugirango itazanga kwima.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amatungo magufi</strong> bayaha ml15 cyangwa sesi 15 muri litiro 10 .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibiguruka</strong> babiha ml15 cyangwa sesi 15 muri litiro 10 z&rsquo;amazi .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amafi</strong> bayaha litiro 3mu cyuzi cya Hegitari imwe bigakorwa rimwe kugera uhinduye amazi.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n','1',4763,3,'2015-04-27 21:45:02','Ifumbire, DI Grow',0,'online','no','no'),(185,'Plant-for-the-planet irahamagarira abakuru b\'Ibihugu bibarizwa mu muryango w\'ibihugu bikize kwisi G7 gushyigikira umushinga wo Gutera ibiti munini wa mbere mu mateka y\'isi.','Plant for the planetb.jpg','<p>Ihindagurika ry&rsquo;ikirere ni kimwe mu bibazo bihangayikishije isi yose kandi kikaba kirimo no kwangiza umusaruro ukomoka ku buhinzi. twifuje kubagezaho uburyo urubyiruko rurimo guhangana n&rsquo;iki kibazo kw&rsquo;isi yose aho rwibumbiye mu muryango Plant-for-the-planet.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p>&ldquo;Kubaho kwacu Urubyiruko ndetse n&rsquo;abana bato bikwiye guhabwa agaciro&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Plant-for-the planet umuryango w&rsquo;abana n&rsquo;urubyiruko wahamagariye abakuru b&rsquo;ibihugu bigize umuryango w&rsquo;ibihugu 7 bya mbere bikize kw&rsquo;isi G7 gushyigikira umushinga wo gutera ibiti munini wa mbere mu mateka y&rsquo;isi.Yugratna Srivastava afite imyaka 19 ni umunyeshuli ukomoka mu Buhinde ndetse akaba n&rsquo;umwe mu bagize inama y&rsquo;ubuyobozi y&rsquo;umunyamuryango Plant-for-the-planet ati &ldquo; Mu myaka umunani ishize, twe abana n&rsquo;urubyiruko twateye ibiti miliyari 14 dufashijwe n&rsquo;abandi bantu bakuru. &ldquo;Igihe kirageze ngo Abakuru ba za Guverinoma batange umusanzu wabo mu kubungabunga ejo hazaza hacu&rdquo;. Ubu butumwa ndetse n&rsquo;indi myanzuro yose ni umusaruro wavuye mu nama y&rsquo;Urubyiruko, yari yitabiriwe n&rsquo;abageze kuri 88 baturutse mu bihugu 23, U Rwanda Rukaba Rwari Ruhagarariwe .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Inyandiko yateguwe ku bufatanye n&rsquo;inzobere mu by&rsquo;ubukungu ,imihindagurikire y&rsquo;ikirere ndetse n&rsquo;inzobere mu bya politiki. Ivuga ko intego yabo ya mbere ari ugutera ibiti miliyari 1000. Ibi biti bizabasha gufata umwuka wa CO<sub><span style=\"font-size:small\">2</span></sub> (uyu mwuka niwo utuma isi ikomeza gushyuha ikierere kigahinduka) ungana na &frac14; cy&rsquo;umwuka wa CO<sub><span style=\"font-size:small\">2</span></sub> wose ushyirwa mu kirere n&rsquo;abantu bityo bibe biri gufasha kugera ku ntego yabo ya kabiri yo guhindura ingufu zikoreshwa kw&rsquo;isi wo uzaba wagezweho mu mwaka 2050.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya YALE bwerekana ko hari ahantu hahagije kw&rsquo;isi ho gukorera uyu mushinga wa mbere mugari mu mateka y&rsquo;isi mu bijyanye no Gutera ibiti. Ubu bushakashatsi buzashyirwa ahagaragara mu mezi ari imbere. Felix Finkbeiner, arangije amashuri yisumbuye akaba ari nawe washinze uyu muryango ashingiye ku byavuye mu nama yahuje abakuru b&rsquo;ibihugu bose nyuma y&rsquo;ihungabana ry&rsquo;ubukungu muri 2008 yagize ati: &ldquo; Kubaho kwa milliyari 3 z&rsquo;urubyiruko ruri kw&rsquo;isi bigomba guhabwa agaciro kuruta gushora amafaranga mu mabanki make ari kw&rsquo;isi&rdquo; .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Felix Finkbeiner arongera ati &ldquo;Ibigo byose ndetse n&rsquo;imiryango yose bibashije gutera miliyari 1 y&rsquo;ibiti, twagera kuri iyi ntego y&rsquo;ibiti milliyari 1000 mu mwaka w&rsquo;2020&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iri huriro ry&rsquo;urubyiruko rwateguwe ku bufatanye hagati y&rsquo;umuryango w&rsquo;abana ndetse n&rsquo;urubyiruko Plant-for-the-plant, Ishami ry&rsquo;umuryango w&rsquo;abibumbye rishinzwe Ibidukikije (UNEP), ndetse n&rsquo;ikigo Evangelische Akademie Tutzing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abayobozi ku rwego rw&rsquo;isi ubutaha bazaba bari muri iri huriro rizaba kuwa 11 Mata- 16 Mata 2016 , kugirango bafatanye mu kureba uburyo habaho guhindura ingufu zikoreshwa ku isi. Uru rwandiko rero Rurashyikirizwa abahagarariye ibihugu byabo mu Budage mu murwa mukuru Berlin uyu munsi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hateguwe uburyo bw&rsquo;amafoto ndetse na filimi bizafasha uru rubyiruko kugeza ubutumwa kuri aba bayobozi b&rsquo;ibihugu bikize cyane kwisi G7, ubu butumwa bwose bwanditse ku mibumbe minini yafatiwe mu kirere na n&rsquo;indege . ushobora nawe kubibona hano : <a href=\"http://pftp2014-prod.plant-for-the-planet.org/de/informieren/neuigkeiten/ba06252b-02cb-11e5-a0ac-902b34544d94\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">http://pftp2014-prod.plant-for-the-planet.org/de/informieren/neuigkeiten/ba06252b-02cb-11e5-a0ac-902b34544d94</span></a> ushobora kandi kubona hano inyandiko yagenewe abo bakuru b&rsquo;ibihugu ikubiyemo ibyifuzo by&rsquo;urubyiruko.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ushobora kandi no kureba uko byari bimeze mu mafoto hano <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/plant-for-the-planet/sets/72157651159450043\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">https://www.flickr.com/photos/plant-for-the-planet/sets/72157651159450043</span></a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n','1',1271,3,'2015-06-03 01:12:30','Amashyamba ',0,'online','no','no'),(192,'Dusobanukirwe n\'igihembwe cy\'Ihinga C','IMG-20160721-WA0053.jpg','<p>Iyo bigeze mu gihe cy&rsquo;impeshyi abahinzi hakangurirwa gukora ubuhinzi bwibanda mu guhinga mu bishanga cyangwa ahandi hantu hashobora kugera amazi . Iki gihe ubutaka bwinshi buba bumaze gusarurwamo ibihingwa byahinzwe mu itumba ndetse ugasanga harakomeye cyane ku buryo kuhahinga biba bitoroshye hifashishwa amapiki kugirango barimire aho bazatera ibihingwa byo ku muhindo.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p>Iki gihembwe cya C rero gitangira muri Gicurasi kikagera muri Kanama aho abahinzi bashishikarizwa guhinga imibande n&rsquo;ahandi ku musozi habasha kugera amazi. Kugeza ubu ubuso bwuhirwa ubu bugeze kuri 33,000 ha mu gihe ubuso bushobora kuhirwa mu Rwanda hose ari 600,000ha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abahinzi b&rsquo;inkwakuzi bahinga mu gihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga C kuko aribyo ngo Bizana amafaranga menshi kandi ibihingwa ntibihure n&rsquo;indwara nyinshi nko mu gihe cy&rsquo;imvura. Ikindi kintu gituma mu mibande hakunda guhingwa cyane ni uko burya ngo mu Mibande haba hari ubutaka bwiza kuko bwa bundi bwose isuri itwara ku misozi bugenda bukaruhukira mu Mibande.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubu huhinzi bwo muri iki gihembwe busaba kuhira . Habaho rero uburyo bubiri bwo kuhira mu Rwanda Harimo uburyo bwo kuhira ku buso buto n&rsquo;uburyo bwo kuhira ku buso bunini.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gahunda yo kuhira ku Buso buto yatangiye vuba mu mwaka wa 2014. Mbere habagaho uburyo bugari mu bishanga no ku misozi ariko bigakorwa ku buryo bugoranye. Ubu buryo bwo kuhira ku buso buto buroroshye kandi ntago buhenze . Busaba ibikoresho bitari byinshi cyane aho dusangamo imipira yo kuhiza, utumoteri duto, ibyuma bifasha mu kuhira,&hellip; Ishami rishinzwe ibyo kuhira muri RAB rivuga ko iyi gahunda igira nkunganire ya 50% by&rsquo;igiciro usabwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kugirango ubone iyi mfashanyo ya nkunganire kandi ukoreshe n&rsquo;ubu buryo bworoshye mu kuhira hari icyo bisaba ku muhinzi ushaka kubikora mu buhinzi bwe . Iyo ukeneye aya makuru wegera ishami rikwegereye rya RAB cyangwa ukabaza Agoronome w&rsquo;akarere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibihingwa byinshi bishobora kuhirwa ariko muri iki gihembwe hakunda guhingwa ibihingwa bidatinda kwera nk&rsquo; indabo, dodo, inyanya, amashu, caroti, ndetse n&rsquo;ibindi bijyanye n&rsquo;imboga byose.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu guhangana n&rsquo;ikibazo cy&rsquo;ibura ry&rsquo;ibiribwa haba mu ngo no ku masoko, ni ngombwa ko abantu bakorana umwete bakitabira guhinga muri iki gihembwe C kuko bizatuma ibiciro ku masoko bigabanuka.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Byateguwe na Niyigaba Etienne.</em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n','1',1700,3,'2015-07-24 01:01:12','Igihembwe cy\'Ihinga',0,'online','no','no'),(195,'Twigire Muhinzi: Dusobanukirwe n\'ubu buryo bushya bw\'Iyamamazabuhinzi','IMG-20160615-WA0041.jpg','<p>Munshamake TWIGIRE-MUHINZI&nbsp; ni&nbsp; uburyo&nbsp; bushya&nbsp; bw&rsquo;iyamamazabuhinzi&nbsp; bufite&nbsp; intego&nbsp; yo&nbsp; kunoza&nbsp; no gusakaza amakuru y&rsquo;ubuhinzi umuhinzi abigizemo uruhare. Ubu&nbsp; buryo bushingiye kw&rsquo;iyamamazabuhinzi rikorwa n&rsquo;abahinzi &nbsp;ubwabo&nbsp; no gushyiraho ingamba zigena imikorere&nbsp; yabo bikabafasha kunoza&nbsp; imikorere no gutanga raporo&nbsp; zifututse ku bashinzwe iyi gahunda&nbsp; n&rsquo;ibikorwa&nbsp; byayo&nbsp; mu&nbsp; gihugu.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p>TWIGIRE-MUHINZI&nbsp; ihuza&nbsp; uburyo&nbsp; bubiri&nbsp; bw&rsquo;iyamamazabuhinzi&nbsp; bw&rsquo;abafashamyumvire&nbsp; bakoresha imirima-shuri&nbsp; (FFS)&nbsp; hamwe&nbsp; n&rsquo;iyabajyanama&nbsp; b&rsquo;ubuhinzi&nbsp; baba &nbsp;muri&nbsp; buri&nbsp; mudugudu&nbsp; (farmer promoters).&nbsp; Mu&nbsp; mirima-shuri&nbsp; (FFS),&nbsp; igihingwa&nbsp; ni&nbsp; cyo&nbsp; mwarimu&nbsp; naho&nbsp; umurima&nbsp; ukaba&nbsp; ishuri.&nbsp; Ubu buryo bwa FFS bwubaka ubushobozi bw&rsquo;abahinzi, bukabafasha kwisesengurira ibibazo no kwikorera ubushakashatsi&nbsp; bubafasha&nbsp; kubona&nbsp; vuba&nbsp; ibisubizo&nbsp; nyabyo&nbsp; by&rsquo;ibibazo&nbsp; byabo. Binyuze mu mirimo yabo yo mu murima-shuri abahinzi&nbsp; biyubakira&nbsp; ubushobozi mu&nbsp; gufata&nbsp; ibyemezo&nbsp; bibafasha&nbsp; gucyemura&nbsp; ibibazo&nbsp; baba&nbsp; bafite&nbsp; ndetse&nbsp; n&rsquo;ibindi&nbsp; bishobora&nbsp; kuvuka nyuma,&nbsp; ku&nbsp; buryo&nbsp; bavamo&nbsp; abacungamutungo&nbsp; bakomeye&nbsp; mu&nbsp; bikorwa&nbsp; byabo&nbsp; byose.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibi&nbsp; bituma bongera umusaruro ku buryo bugaragara ari nako binjiza amafaranga mu ngo zabo.&nbsp; Buri tsinda rya FFS&nbsp; rikeneye umufashamyumvire w&rsquo;inzobere&nbsp; ufasha&nbsp; abarigize,&nbsp; akabigisha imikorere yimbitse.&nbsp; Ubu abafashamyumvire&nbsp; 2500&nbsp; (FFS&nbsp; facilitators)&nbsp; bamaze&nbsp; guhugurwa&nbsp; mu&nbsp; gihugu&nbsp; hise&nbsp; mu&nbsp; bihe&nbsp; by&rsquo;ihinga kandi&nbsp; bakaba&nbsp; biteguye&nbsp; gukorana&nbsp; n&rsquo;amatsinda&nbsp; mashya&nbsp; ya&nbsp; FFS&nbsp; agizwe&nbsp; n&rsquo;amatsinda&nbsp; yo&nbsp; ku&nbsp; rwego rw&rsquo;imidugudu.&nbsp; Abahinzi bibumbiye mu matsinda kugirango abe urwinjiriro rw&rsquo;iyamamaza-buhinzirya&nbsp; TWIGIRE&nbsp; MUHINZI.&nbsp; Gukora&nbsp; amatsinda&nbsp; y&rsquo;abahinzi&nbsp; afite&nbsp; Ubushobozi&nbsp; byoroshya&nbsp; gusangira ubumenyi ku buhinzi hagati y&rsquo;abanyamuryango b&rsquo;ayo matsinda, bigatuma abahinzi bagira uruhare runini&nbsp; mu&nbsp; kongera&nbsp; umussaruro&nbsp; w&rsquo;ubuhinzi&nbsp; bakorera&nbsp; hamwe.&nbsp; Buri&nbsp; mudugudu&nbsp; utora&nbsp; umujyanama w&rsquo;ubuhinzi&nbsp; umwe,&nbsp; bigakorwa&nbsp; n&rsquo;abaturage&nbsp; b&rsquo;uwo&nbsp; mudugudu&nbsp; hashingiwe&nbsp; ku&nbsp; ngingo zumvikanyweho.&nbsp; Iyamamaza-buhinzi&nbsp; ryongerera&nbsp; ubumenyi&nbsp; umujyanama&nbsp; w&rsquo;ubuhinzi&nbsp; ku&nbsp; makuru mashya agezweho y&rsquo;ubuhinzi, n&rsquo;uburyo iyamaza-buhinzi rikorwa. Abo bajyanama b&rsquo;ubuhinzi bahita baba&nbsp; abamamaza-buhinzi&nbsp; mu&nbsp; midugudu&nbsp; yabo&nbsp; bakagira&nbsp; ishingano&nbsp; yo&nbsp; guhugura&nbsp; abahinzi&nbsp; bagenzi babo&nbsp; baba&nbsp; mu&nbsp; matstinda&nbsp; kubyo&nbsp; baba&nbsp; bahuguweho.&nbsp; Abajyanama&nbsp; b&rsquo;ubuhinzi&nbsp; bangana&nbsp; na&nbsp; 14.837 bazahugurwa kugirango bahure abandi bahinzi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Umudugudu = Umutima wa Twigire-Muhinzi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ku rwego rw&rsquo;akagal haba hari umufashamyumvure (FFS Facilitator) ushinzwe guhugura itsinda rya FFS naho ku rwego rw&rsquo;umudugudu haba hari umujyanama w&rsquo;ubuhinzi (Farmer promoter) ushinzwe guhugura amatsinda y&rsquo;abahinzi aho muri buri tsinda havamo abahinzi 3-5 bakajya mu itsinda rya FFS.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TWIGIRE-MUHINZI Ishingiye ku buryo bw&rsquo;abahinzi bahugurana hagati yabo bashigikiwe n&rsquo;inzego za Leta niz&rsquo;abikorera ku giti cyabo zose zifite ishingano zitandukanye. Abikorera ku gi ti cyabo bagira uruhare mu kubaka ubushobozi n&rsquo;ubumenyi by&rsquo;abahinzi n&rsquo;abakozi bashinzwe iyamamaza-buhinzi, ibyo&nbsp; bigakorwa&nbsp; hakurikijwe&nbsp; ubushobozi,&nbsp; intego&nbsp; ndetse&nbsp; na&nbsp; gahunda&nbsp; ya&nbsp; Leta &nbsp;yo&nbsp; guteza&nbsp; Imbere ubuhinzi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hari&nbsp; uburyo&nbsp; bwinshi&nbsp; buriho&nbsp; bukoreshwa&nbsp; mu&nbsp; gusakaza&nbsp; amakuru&nbsp; n&rsquo;ubutumwa&nbsp; ku&nbsp; byerekeye ikoranabuhanga&nbsp; mu&nbsp; by&rsquo;ubuhinzi,&nbsp; bikagera &nbsp;ku&nbsp; matsinda&nbsp; y&rsquo;abahinzi.&nbsp; Ubu&nbsp; buryo&nbsp; ni&nbsp; bwiza&nbsp; kuko bwuzuzanya,&nbsp; aha&nbsp; twavuga&nbsp; nk&rsquo;amanama&nbsp; y&rsquo;imidugudu,&nbsp; kwigira&nbsp; ku &nbsp;mirima-shuli,&nbsp; ingendo-shuli, amanama&nbsp; nkangurambaga,&nbsp; Radio,&nbsp; Televisiyo,&nbsp; Ubutumwa-bugufi&nbsp; kuri&nbsp; telephone,&nbsp; Imfashanyigisho z&rsquo;ubuhinzi,&nbsp; n&rsquo;ibindi.&nbsp; Abahinzi&nbsp; bazagira&nbsp; ubumenyi&nbsp; bwinshi&nbsp; kandi&nbsp; butandukanye&nbsp; ku&nbsp; buhinzi&nbsp; bwa kijyambere biciye mu mirima-shuli.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu&nbsp; gukorera&nbsp; mu&nbsp; nzego&nbsp; zegerejwe&nbsp; abaturage,&nbsp; komite&nbsp; zishinzwe&nbsp; ubuhinzi&nbsp; ku&nbsp; rwego&nbsp; rwa&nbsp; site,&nbsp; mu Mudugudu,&nbsp; mu&nbsp; Kagari,&nbsp; mu&nbsp; Murenge,&nbsp; mu&nbsp; Karere,&nbsp; mu&nbsp; Ntara&nbsp; ndetse&nbsp; no&nbsp; ku&nbsp; rwego&nbsp; rw&rsquo;Igihugu&nbsp; nizo zizita&nbsp; cyane kw&rsquo;ishyirwa mu bikorwa bya gahunda y&rsquo;iterambere ry&rsquo;ubuhinzi mw&rsquo;iterambere rusange ry&rsquo;igihugu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Twigire-Muhinzi ifite ingingo zirindwi igenderaho</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>(I)&nbsp; Kwegerereza&nbsp; abahinzi&nbsp; ku&nbsp; gihe&nbsp; ubutumwa&nbsp; bw&rsquo;iyamamaza-buhinzi&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; hashyirwaho&nbsp; abamamazabuhinzi hafi yabo (farmer promoters na FFS Facilitators)&nbsp; kugirango babashe kwongera umusaruro no kuwubyaza inyungu bawugurisha ku masoko.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(II) Guha abahinzi uburyo bwo kwigishanya neza hakoreshejwe imirima-shuri (FFS).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(III)&nbsp; Guhugura&nbsp; abamamaza-buhinzi&nbsp; (Abashinzwe&nbsp; ubuhinzi&nbsp; ku&nbsp; rwego &nbsp;rw&rsquo;utagi,&nbsp; imirenge&nbsp; n&rsquo;uturereabafashamyumvire&nbsp; (FFS&nbsp; Facilitators)&nbsp; n&rsquo;abajyanama&nbsp; b&rsquo;ubuhinzi&nbsp; (farmer&nbsp; promoters)&nbsp; bongererwa ubumenyi mw&rsquo;ikoranabuhanga rishamikiye ku buhinzi .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(IV) Gushyiraho komite nyobozi z&rsquo;ubuhinzi zikazakora nk&rsquo;ihuriro ry&rsquo;abafat anyabikorwa barimo MINAGRI&nbsp; na&nbsp; MINALOC,&nbsp; inzego&nbsp; z&rsquo;umutekano,&nbsp; abikorera&nbsp; ku&nbsp; giti&nbsp; cyabo&nbsp; (ba&nbsp; Rwiyemeza-mirimo), abahinzi,&nbsp; amakoperative&nbsp; n&rsquo;amashyirahamwe&nbsp; y&rsquo;abahinzi,&nbsp; abashakashatsi,&nbsp; bigakorwa&nbsp; bitangiriye&nbsp; ku rwego rw&rsquo;imidugudu, utugari, umurenge, akarere, intara ndeste no ku rwego rw&rsquo;igihugu hagamijwe kunoza ishyirwa mu bikorwa rya TWIGIRE-MUHINZI.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(V)&nbsp; Kwongerera&nbsp; imbaraga&nbsp; abahinzi&nbsp; bibumbiye&nbsp; mu&nbsp; matsinda&nbsp; mato&nbsp; mato&nbsp; ari&nbsp; mu&nbsp; midugudu, akazavukamo koperative ku rwego rw&rsquo;umurenge</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(VI)&nbsp; Kongera&nbsp; ubushobozi&nbsp; bw&rsquo;abahinzi&nbsp; gushaka&nbsp; no&nbsp; kubona&nbsp; ubushobozi&nbsp; bwo&nbsp; kugura inyongeramusaruro&nbsp; no&nbsp; kubahuza&nbsp; n&rsquo;ibigo&nbsp; by&rsquo;imari&nbsp; iciriritse&nbsp; bitanga&nbsp; inguzanyo&nbsp; nka Microfinance,(MFIs), Imirenge-SACCOS n&rsquo;andi ma banki asanzwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(VII)&nbsp; Gukurikira no gusuzumira hamwe ibikorwa bya TWIGIRE-MUHINZI.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AMAHAME-SHINGIRO YA TWIGIRE-MUHINZI</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>TWIGIRE-MUHINZI ifasha&nbsp; abahinzi&nbsp; guhinga&nbsp; neza&nbsp; bakoresha &nbsp;Imbaraga &nbsp;n&rsquo;ubushobozi&nbsp; byabo hashingiwe ku mahame akurikira</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li><strong><em>Gukorana n&rsquo;amatsinda&nbsp; y&rsquo;abahinzi&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; bifite&nbsp; inyungu&nbsp; nyinshi.</em></strong></li>\r\no<li><strong><em>Abahinzi bakwiye&nbsp; kugira uruhare mu&nbsp; bikorwa byose bigamije &nbsp;kuzamura imibereho yabo akaba ariyo&nbsp; mpamvu&nbsp; aribo&nbsp; berekana&nbsp; ibyo&nbsp; bacyeneye&nbsp; ku&nbsp; iyamamaza-bunzi .</em></strong></li>\r\no<li><strong><em>Abahinzi bakwiye gushishikarizwa&nbsp; kwigira&nbsp; udushya&nbsp; mu&nbsp; buhinzi&nbsp; mu&nbsp; mirima-shuli</em></strong>&nbsp; kandi&nbsp; ubwo buryo&nbsp; bukwiye&nbsp; gukorwa&nbsp; mu&nbsp; buryo&nbsp; bwihuse&nbsp; bugaragaza&nbsp; udushya&nbsp; kugirango&nbsp; bifashe&nbsp; abahinzi kubyigana.</li>\r\no<li><strong><em>Iyamamaza-buhinzi rifatanyishe&nbsp; n&rsquo;ibgo&nbsp; by&rsquo;ubushakahsatsi&nbsp; rikwiye&nbsp; guhanga&nbsp; udushya&nbsp; dukenewe, ibi&nbsp; bigafasha&nbsp; gusakaza&nbsp; ibisubizo&nbsp; hagati&nbsp; y&rsquo;abahinzi&nbsp; ubwabo&nbsp; kandi&nbsp; imamaza-buhinzi&nbsp; igomba gukoresha udushya tudahenze, kandi tuboneka hafi y&rsquo;abahinzi n&rsquo;aho batuye.</em></strong></li>\r\no<li><strong><em>Iyamamaza-buhinzi rigomba&nbsp; gukorana&nbsp; n&rsquo;abandi&nbsp; bafatanyabikorwa&nbsp; mu&nbsp; kugeza&nbsp; ibikenewe&nbsp; ku bahinzi&nbsp; no&nbsp; kubakorera&nbsp; umurimo&nbsp; unoze.</em></strong></li>\r\no<li><strong><em>Iyamamaza-buhinzi rikwiye&nbsp;&nbsp; gukora&nbsp; no&nbsp; gukoresha&nbsp; n&rsquo;ubuyobozi&nbsp; bw&rsquo;ibanze</em></strong>,&nbsp; kandi&nbsp; rikubakira&nbsp; ku bikorwa byari bisanzwe biriho mu Karere.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>GUSHYIRA GAHUNDA YA TWIGIRE-MUHINZI MU BIKORWA </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>i.Abahinzi bibumbira mu matsinda y&rsquo;abantu bari hagati ya 15 kugeza kuri 20.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ii.Buri tsinda ryitorera&nbsp; umuyobozi&nbsp; ushinzwe&nbsp; ahanini&nbsp; gufasha&nbsp; no&nbsp; kugenzura&nbsp; imikorere&nbsp; y&rsquo;abagize itsinda mu kwitabira ubuhinzi bwa kijyambere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>iii. Abajyanama&nbsp; b&rsquo;ubuhinzi&nbsp; (farmer&nbsp; promoters),&nbsp; umwe muri&nbsp; buri&nbsp; mudugudu&nbsp; baratorwa bakigishwa&nbsp; ibyerekeranye&nbsp; n&rsquo;ubuhinzi&nbsp; bwa&nbsp; kijyambere,&nbsp; uburyo&nbsp; bunoze&nbsp; bwo&nbsp; gukora&nbsp; gahunda (planning) n&rsquo;ubukangurambaga maze bakaba abamamaza-buhinzi b&rsquo;umwuga mu midugudu yabo.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Abafashamyumvire mu buhinzi&nbsp; (FFS&nbsp; facilitators)&nbsp; bahuguwe&nbsp; mu&nbsp; mikorere&nbsp; y&rsquo;imirima-shuri&nbsp; (FFS)barabarurwa mu tugari bagiye babonekamo (ariko hagombye kuba umwe muri buri kagari) bagomba gufasha&nbsp; amatsinda&nbsp; ya&nbsp; FFS&nbsp; ku&nbsp; bihingwa&nbsp; bitandukanye&nbsp; noneho&nbsp; abahinzi &nbsp;3-5&nbsp; batoranyijwe&nbsp; muri&nbsp; buri tsinda&nbsp; ry&rsquo;abahinzi&nbsp; bagashyirwa&nbsp; mu&nbsp; itsinda&nbsp; rya&nbsp; FFS&nbsp; yo&nbsp; mumidugudu.</li>\r\no<li>Itsinda ry&rsquo;abahinzi bari muri FFS rizahabwa ingufu kugirango ribashe gufata ibyemezo bizamura umusaruro binyuze mu kubyigira hamwe babifashijwemo n&rsquo;umufasha-myumvire (FFS facilitator).</li>\r\no<li>Komite z&rsquo;Ubuhinzi ku nzego zose zishyirwaho kugirango zijye zifata ibyemezo kandi zishingwe imirimo ikurikira: kuyobora, gukurikirana ibikorwa, gutanga amaraporo, ubukangurambaga ndetse n&rsquo;ubuvugizi.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>vii. Komite ihoraho&nbsp; (igizwe n&rsquo;abantu&nbsp; 2-3)&nbsp; ba&nbsp; MINAGRI na&nbsp; MINALOC ishyirwaho mu&nbsp; Turere no ku rwego rw&rsquo;Igihugu igakurikirana ibikorwa bya TWIGIRE-MUHINZI&nbsp; umunsi ku wundi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>vii.&nbsp; Komite&nbsp; tekiniki&nbsp; ku&nbsp; rwego&nbsp; rw&rsquo;Igihugu&nbsp; izakurikirana&nbsp; ishyirwa&nbsp; mu&nbsp; bikorwa&nbsp; kandi&nbsp; ijye&nbsp; itanga imirongo ngenderwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>INSHINGANO Z&rsquo;INZEGO ZISHINZWE GUSHIRA MU BIKORWA GAHUNDA YA TWIGIREMUHINZI </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Inshingano zihariye z&rsquo;Uturere :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Gukora amatsinda y&rsquo;abahinzi no kuyaha ubushobozi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Gukoresha ama komitey&rsquo;ubuhinzi yo ku rwego rw&rsquo;umudugudu, akagarai, umurenge, n&rsquo;akarereKugaragaza ibyo abahinzi bakeneye, Gutegura igihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga, Gukangurira abahinzi kubona inyongeramusaruro, inguzanyo, Kurema amashyirahamwe y&rsquo;abahinzi (amatsinda, ama koperative), Gukurikirana no kworohereza abahinzi kubona inyongeramusaruro, Gukurikirana uko igihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga kiri kugenda, Gutanga raporo y&rsquo;uko igihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga kiri kugenda-abashinzwe ubuhinzi ku rwego rw&rsquo;utugari bakora ikurikirana ry&rsquo;ibikorwa bibera ku rwego rw&rsquo;imidugudu. Izindi nzego zigasuzuma ama raporo yaturutse ku nzego zo hasi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ishingano zihariye za MINAGRI</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>MINAGRI&nbsp; izaba&nbsp; ifite&nbsp; ishingano&nbsp; yo&nbsp; gutegura&nbsp; gahunda&nbsp; y&rsquo;ibizakorwa&nbsp; n&rsquo;uburyo&nbsp; bizakorwa,&nbsp; kureba nimba&nbsp; bishyirwa&nbsp; mu&nbsp; bikorwa,&nbsp; gushyiraho&nbsp; gahunda&nbsp; n&rsquo;amahame&nbsp; ngenderwaho&nbsp; n&rsquo;uburyo&nbsp; isuzuma bikorwa by&rsquo;imihigo y&rsquo;ubuhinzi izakorwa. Izaba inashinzwe kugena uburyo amafaranga azakoreshwa mu mishinga izaba yatoranyijwe</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Byateguwe na Mugiraneza Jean Luc hifashishijwe inyandiko yategiwe na Minagri.</em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n','1',2627,3,'2015-08-12 00:56:01','Twigire Muhinzi',0,'online','no','no'),(196,'Ibintu 5 byagufasha kwitegura Igihimbwe cy\'ihinga A neza','IMG-20161019-WA0044.jpg','<p>Ubuhinzi ni umwuga ukorwa n&rsquo;abasaga 90% mu Rwanda kandi bo mu byiciro byose baba abakuru ndetse n&rsquo;urubyiruko. Uyu mwuga bikomeza kuvugwa ko abanyarwanda bawukora ariko bikiri mu buryo bwa Gakondo , Minisiteri y&rsquo;ubuhinzi nayo ikaba irimo gukora ibishoboka byose ngo abawukora babashe kuwukor a by&rsquo;umwuga . Ibi ariko bigendana no guhugura abahinzi buri gihe ndetse bakanahabwa amakuru ku gihe y&rsquo;ibyo bakeneye guhinga n&rsquo;uburyo bwo kubihinga .</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p>Iyo dusoje igihe cy&rsquo;impeshyi hakurikiraho igihe cy&rsquo;imvura aricyo twita Umuhindo gitangira muri Nzeri kikagera muri Mutarama. Iki gihembwe kirangwa no guhinga ibihingwa Ngandurarugo ndetse no kwita kubihingwa Ngengabukungu. Buri muhinzi rero aba agombwa kwitegura neza iki gihembwe kuko aricyo gitangira umwaka w&rsquo;ubuhinzi , iyo utabashije kukitwaramo neza mu buhinzi bwawe uba usatira kutazagira umusaruro mwiza umwaka wose.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hari ibyo umuhinzi akwiye kubanza gutegura mbere y&rsquo;uko iki gihembwe gitangira:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li><strong>Gutegura umurima uzahingwa</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Umurima uzahingwa muri iki gihembwe ugomba gutegurwa mbere ndetse bikaba muri iki gihe cy&rsquo;izuba kugirango imvura niyikubita hasi umuhinzi azahite ayifatirana ku gihe. Aha hakorwa imirimo nko kurima amasinde mu bisigati ndetse n&rsquo;ahandi hazahingwa ndetse no gusukura aho hantu uzahinga.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\no<li><strong>Gutegura Imbuto uzatera</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Imbuto ni ikintu gikomeye kiguha ishusho y&rsquo;umusaruro uzagira , iyo wateye imbuto mbi usarura umusaruro muke , iyo wateye imbuto nziza witegura umusaruro mwiza. Iyo tuvuze imbuto nziza ni za mbuto wakuye ahantu hizewe nko mu bigo bishinzwe gutanga imbuto, mu bacuruza imbuto ndetse no ku bashinzwe Ubuhinzi cyangwa iyo wowe wizeye yakomotse kuri za mbuto wakuye ahizewe. Iyo rero uteye imbuto yabitswe nabi nabyo bigira ingaruka ku musaruro ugira kuko ishobora kuba yarangiritse mu kuyibika. Abahinzi barashishikarizwa kugana ibigo bishinzwe gutanga imbuto bikabafasha.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\no<li><strong>Gutegura ifumbire</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Kugirango ubone umusaruro mwiza ni ngombwa gukoresha ifumbire yaba imvaruganda cyangwa imborera, ibi biterwa n&rsquo;ubwoko bw&rsquo;ubutaka uhingaho hanwe n&rsquo;igihingwa uzahinga . Ni byiza kuvanga izi fumbire zombi ukurikije amabwiriza yo kuzivanga kuko si byiza gukoresha ifumbire mvaruganda gusa ubutaka bukenera n&rsquo;imborera ifasha mu gukura kw&rsquo;igihingwa. Ibi kandi bijyana no gukoresh bya byatsi bigira imyunyu ngugu ibihingwa bikenera nabyo bigakora mu gukora ya fumbire y&rsquo;imborera.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\no<li><strong>Gutegura isoko ry&rsquo;umusaruro wawe</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Ntago ibi ari ibintu bimenyerewe ariko ni ngombwa ku muntu ukora ubuhinzi bw&rsquo;umwuga . Ibihingwa ni ibintu bidatinda mu murima iyo bimaze kwera kandi nta buryo buhagije bwo kubibika igihe kirekire ubu twari twagira buhagije mu Rwanda niyo mpamvu ugomba guhinga ufite igitekerezo cy&rsquo;aho uzagurisha umusaruro wawe. Aha hazamo kumenyana n&rsquo;abacuruza umusaruro w&rsquo;ibikomoka ku buhinzi ndetse n&rsquo;abandi bose bashobora kugufasha mu kugeza umusaruro wawe kw&rsquo;isoko.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"5\">\r\no<li><strong>Gutegura amafaranga bizagutwara</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Buri gikorwa kugirango gitange umusaruro wakitezemo hari ibyo ugomba kugitangaho byanga bikunda niyo mpamvu ugomba guteganya mbere amafaranga ibikorwa byawe by&rsquo;ubuhinzi bizagutwara . Kugirango uhingire ku gihe nta bukererwe bujemo . Aya mafaranga rero ni ngombwa kugirango ibikorwa byawe bizagende neza kandi bijyane n&rsquo;ihinga igihe umuhindo uzaba uhinduye.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nubwo Ubuhinzi bwacu bukiri mu buryo bwa Gakondo hari uburyo bwo kugenda tugerageza kubigira umwuga kandi abahinzi benshi bari kugenda babona ingaruka nziza bibaha. Nawe rero itegure neza mbere y&rsquo;uko Imvura igera hasi kugirango uzahin gire igihe kandi nta mbogamizi ugize.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Byateguwe na NIYIGABA Etienne , email: niyigabat@gmail.com</em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n','1',2009,3,'2015-09-01 19:12:35','Igihembwe cy\'Ihinga',0,'online','no','no'),(197,'Ibigo byemerewe gutumiza no gukwirakwiza inyongeramusaruro mu gihembwe cy\'ihinga 2016A na B','Gufumbira  ifumbire .png','<p>Dukurikije ibyo dusanga mu mabwiriza ya Minisitiri ushinzwe ubuhinzi n&rsquo;Ubworozi yerekeye itangwa ry&rsquo;inyongeramusaruro z&rsquo;ubuhinzi (Ifumbire mvaruganda n&rsquo;imbuto z&rsquo;indobanure) harimo nkunganire ya leta mu gihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga cya 2016A &amp;B , Hari urutonde rw&rsquo;ibigo by&rsquo;abikorera birindwi (7) bifitanye amasezerano na MINAGRI muri uyu mwaka w&rsquo;ubuhinzi 2016A na B ko aribyo byonyine byemerewe gutumiza no kugeza ifumbire mvaruganda ku gihe munturere twose tw&rsquo;igihugu muri gahunda ya Nkunganire ya Leta . Bakaba bemerewe gucuruza mu bice byose by&rsquo;igihugu binyuze mu bacuruzi b&rsquo;inyongeramusaruro n&rsquo;amakoperative my&rsquo;abahinzi bemewe na MINAGRI babarizwa mu mirenge itandukanye y&rsquo;igihugu.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p>Urutonde rw&rsquo;ibigo n&rsquo;aho mwabasanga</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li><strong>BALTON</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>PO Box: 2972 Kigali _Rwanda</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: +250788307483/+250252570053</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: <span style=\"color:#1ab106\">balton@balton.co.rw</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\no<li><strong>YARA LIMITED</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Po: Box: 3390Kigali Rwanda</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: +250788303702/735518740</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: <span style=\"color:#1ab106\">peter.ngugi@yara.com</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\no<li><strong>TOP SERVICES ENTERPRISE LTD</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Po Box: 4955 Kigali Rwanda</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: +250788385900/788304063</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: <span style=\"color:#1ab106\">topservicee@yahoo.fr</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\no<li><strong>One Acre Fund</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Po Box: 6640 Kigali Rwanda</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: +250788741343</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: <span style=\"color:#1ab106\">inforwanda@oneacrefund.org</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"5\">\r\no<li><strong>NYIOMBO INVESTMENT (R) LTD</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>PO box: 7522Kigali Rwanda</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: +250788307421</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: <span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Gerad.nyiombo@gmail.com</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"6\">\r\no<li><strong>ETS BIRAHAGWA JANVIER</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>PO Box: 2626 Kigali Rwanda</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: +250788302399</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: <span style=\"color:#1ab106\">barajana@yahoo.fr</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"7\">\r\no<li><strong>ETS NKUBILI ALFRED </strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>PO Box: 2690 Kigali Rwanda</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: +250788300760/788301967</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: <span style=\"color:#1ab106\">alfrednkubili@yahoo.fr</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n','1',1568,3,'2015-09-03 21:13:56','Ifumbire',0,'online','no','no'),(199,'Sobanukirwa na gahunda  yo kongera umusaruro w\'igihingwa cyatoranyijwe (crop intensification program)','IMG-20161205-WA0035.jpg','<p><em>Sobanukirwa na gahunda&nbsp; yo kongera umusaruro w&rsquo;igihingwa cyatoranyijwe (crop intensification program)</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bitewe n&rsquo;ubwiyongere bwinshi bw&rsquo;abaturage mu mijyi ndetse no mu byaro mu Rwanda, bitewe kandi &nbsp;nikibazo cy&rsquo;ubutaka bucye igihugu cyacu gifite, leta yashyize imbaraga mu kongera umusaruro w&rsquo;ibihingwa ngandurarugo (food crops) nk&rsquo;igisubizo ku bibazo twavuze haruguru.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umusaruro mwiza kandi uhagije ugendana no gukoresha uburyo bwiza bugezweho mu buhinzi twavuga nk&rsquo;imbuto zindobanure, gukoresha amafumbire, amazi (irrigation) ndetse n&rsquo;amamashini ahinga, MINAGRI rero yashyize imbaraga nyinshi mu guteza imbere iyi gahunda kandi byagaragayeko ari igisubizo mu kwihaza mu biribwa, ubu u Rwanda ni igihugu gihagaze neza mu kwihaza (food security country).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyi gahunda rero yatangiye muri Kanama 2007, iyi gahunda yibanda ku bihingwa bitandatu aribyo: ibigori, umuceri, ibirayi, ibishyimbo, imyumbati na soya. Binyuze muri iyi gahunda abahinzi bose icyarimwe barayumvishe kandi bahinga kubutaka bwahujwe n&rsquo;ubwegeranyijwe mu rwego rwo kugira aho guhinga hahagije, ntago ari ibi gusa kuko imbuto z&rsquo;indobanure n&rsquo;amafumbire byegerejwe abaturage binyujijwe mu bufatanye hagati ya leta n&rsquo;inzego zikorera ku giti cyazo no muri serivise zo kwamamaza ubuhinzi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nkuko twabivuze haruguru iyi gahunda yatanze igisubizo kiza ndetse umusaruro wariyongereye bigaragara, umusaruro w&rsquo;ibigori na soya&nbsp; wiyongereye, uw&rsquo;ibirayi n&rsquo;imyumbati wikubye gatatu naho uw&rsquo;umuceri n&rsquo;ibishyimbo wiyongera 30%&nbsp; mu myaka 4 ishize. Uyu musaruro watumye u Rwanda ruba igihugu gitekanye kubiribwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nshuti dusangiye gukunda ubuhinzi ndetse no kubuteza imbere mureke dufatanye na leta yacu gushishikariza abahinzi kwitabira gahunda za leta zijyanye n&rsquo;ubuhinzi kuko byagaragayeko zitanga ibisubizo ku bibazo ubuhinzi bwacu buhura nabyo.</p>\r\n','1',1312,3,'2015-09-23 22:45:20','CIP',0,'online','no','no'),(204,'Hasabwa iki ngo ube umutubuzi w\'imbuto z\'indobanure wemewe','IMG-20160921-WA0030.jpg','<p>Uburyo bwiza bwo kwongera umusaruro mu by&rsquo;ubuhinzi ni ugukoresha imbuto zisumbije ubwiza izo abahinzi bisanganiwe cyangwa se iziturutse hirya no hino ku masoko. Imbuto nziza niyo nyongeramusaruro iruta izindi zose kubera ko ariyo izindi nyongeramusaruro zishingiraho, idahari, zikaba ntacyo zamara. Ubushobozi bwo gutanga umusaruro mwiza bw&rsquo; igihingwa cyose buba mu mbuto. Kugirango ubuhinzi bw&rsquo; igihugu bushobore gutera imbere, abahinzi bagomba kugezwaho imbuto nziza zihagije kandi zibonekera ku gihe. Abashakashatsi n&rsquo;abatubuzi b&rsquo; imbuto bafite uruhare runini mu guteza imbere ubuhinzi muri rusange no mu gutuma imbuto ziboneka by&rsquo;umwihariko.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Imbuto ni iki</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imbuto ni Intete, umurama,igihingwa cyangwa se igice cy&rsquo;igihimgwa, ingeri ,ikibabi, umuzi bikoreshwa mu ituburwa ry&rsquo;ibihingwa muri rusange. Imbuto y&rsquo; indobanure ni imbuto yatunganyijwe imaze gukorerwa ubushakashatsi, imbuto yagenzuwe, ifite ibisobanuro bya ngombwa ku cyo ipfunyitsemo kiyiranga.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko imbuto nziza ishobora kongera umusaruro kugeza kuri 25 ndetse na 30%, iyo iherekejwe n&rsquo;izindi nyongeramusaruro, ishobora gukuba umusaruro kabili ndetse na gatatu. Imbuto rero zitandukanywa n&rsquo;amoko yazo, imiterere n&rsquo;imimerere. Kugeza ubu, imbuto z&rsquo;indobanure zigera ku bahinzi ni nkeya cyane ugereranyije nizikenewe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dore zimwe mu nzitizi zituma imbuto z&lsquo;indobanure zitagera ku bahinzi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Ubuke bw&lsquo;imbuto, kuko imbuto zituburwa ari nke cyane ugereranije n&lsquo;izikenewe,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Kutamenya akamaro k&lsquo;imbuto z&lsquo;indobanure birenze ubushobozi bw&lsquo;abahinzi,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; kuzitubura birahenze.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Kutagira imyumvire imwe ku mbuto n&rsquo;uburyo yagezwa ku bahinzi, hagati ya Leta, abashakashatsi n&rsquo;abahinzi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Igiciro cy&rsquo;imbuto z&rsquo;indobanure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>GUTUBURA IMBUTO</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:decimal\" type=\"1\">\r\no<li><strong>Intambwe zo gutubura imbuto.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Kugira ngo imbuto igere ku muhinzi ica mu nzira zinyuranye zigamije ko imbuto igumana umwimerere n&rsquo; ubwiza byayo kandi ikabonekera igihe no mu bwinshi. Kubera ibyo, hashyizweho umubare ntarengwa buri rwego rushobora gutuburwamo:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; urwego rw&rsquo;imbuto bita &laquo; Remezo/icyororo&raquo; ituburwa rimwe cyangwa kabiri gusa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; urwegorw&rsquo;imbuto bita &laquo;ibanze &raquo; ishobora gutuburwa kugeza kuri gatatu mu gihe imbuto idata umwimerere wayo. Ibi bikorwa cyane ku bihingwa bisaba imbuto nyinshi nk&rsquo;ibirayi cyangwa bigira umusaruro muto kuri hegitari nk&rsquo; ibishyimbo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; urwego rw&rsquo;imbuto bita &laquo;Icuruzwa ifite icyemezo&raquo; ituburwa rimwe cyangwa kabiri bitewe n&rsquo; ubwinshi bw&rsquo; imbuto ikenewe.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\" style=\"list-style-type:decimal\" type=\"1\">\r\no<li><strong>Amabwiriza y&rsquo;itubura</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Kwitarura indi mirima ngo bitabangurirana, bikanduzanya indwara</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hakoreshejwe : Inkuta cyimeza (igihingwa bisa gikikije, ikindi gihingwa metero z&rsquo;ubwitarure ziba nyinshi ku bihingwa bibangurirana (metero 400 ku bigori na metero 5-10 kuri soya)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hasabwa iki ngo ube umutubuzi?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Kwandikira RAB uyisaba kuba umutubuzi</li>\r\no<li>Kuzuza ifishi yo gusaba kuba umutubuzi</li>\r\no<li>Kuba ari ku rutonde rwemewe n&rsquo;ikigo kibifitiye ububasha rw&rsquo;abatubuzi.</li>\r\no<li>Kuba ufite imirima ihagije itari munsi ya Ha 5</li>\r\no<li>Kugira imbuga yo gusaruriraho no gutunganyirizaho umusaruro.</li>\r\no<li>Kugira amangazini yo kubikamo imbuto (umusaruro).</li>\r\no<li>Kuba ufite ibikoresho byo gupima (iminzani) no gupfunyikamo imbuto.</li>\r\no<li>Kuba ufite amapompo yo guteresha imiti.</li>\r\no<li>Kugira umutekinisiye wo gukurikirana imirimo (bishobotse)</li>\r\no<li>Gutunga itegeko ry&rsquo;imbuto ( rigenga imituburire y&rsquo; imbuto)</li>\r\no<li>Kuzuza ifishi yo kumenyekanisha ihinga (D&eacute;claration de culture)</li>\r\no<li>Kuzuza ifishi yo kumenyekanisha umusaruro (D&eacute;claration de r&eacute;colte)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\" style=\"list-style-type:decimal\" type=\"1\">\r\no<li><strong>Ibigomba kwitabwaho mw&rsquo; itubura ry&rsquo; imbuto.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.1. Guhitamo ahazatuburirwa imbuto.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Buri bwoko bw&rsquo; imbuto bugomba gutuburirwa mu karere (ahantu) iyo mbuto ibereyemo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.2. Kwirinda ko imbuto zihumanyana &laquo;isolement &raquo;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kugirango amoko y&rsquo; imbuto adahumanyana biciye mw&rsquo; ibangurirana cyangwa ivangwa ry&rsquo; imbuto, umurima w&rsquo;ubwoko bw&rsquo; imbuto ituburwa ugomba gutandukanywa n&rsquo;umurima w&rsquo; iyindi mbuto cyangwa ubundi bwoko bw&rsquo; imbuto y&rsquo; icyo gihingwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibyo bikorwa hasigwa umwanya uhagije hagati y&rsquo; imirima ituburirwamo, ubwoko bunyuranye cyangwa imbuto zinyuranye cyangwa hashyirwa uruzitiro hagati y&rsquo; imirima yombi ; Ubundi buryo bukoreshwa ni uguterera igihe gitandukanye kugirango izo mbuto zombi zitazarabiriza rimwe bityo zikaba zabangurirana.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.3. Ubuso bw&rsquo; umurima utuburirwaho imbuto</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubusanzwe umurima muto wemewe gutuburiraho imbuto ni Ha eshanu ku bigori. Ku bindi bihingwa, imirima mito yegeranye ishobora kwemerwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.4. Guhinga umurima</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umurima w&rsquo; imbuto ugomba guhingwa neza kugera kubujya hasi bwa cm 25 cyangwa 30 byibura, ukwezi kumwe mbere y&rsquo; itera kugirango ibyatsi biri mu murima bishobore kubora kandi kugirango imbuto itazacikanwa n&rsquo; imvura zambere. Akenshi guhinga utinze bituma utera utinze bikaba byakuviramo kuteza neza igihe imvura icitse kare.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.5. Gufumbira umurima</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mbere yo gutera ushyira mu murima ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera ingana na Kg 200 kuri are ( ni ukuvuga nibura toni 20 kuri hegitari) mu turere dufite ubusharire bw&rsquo; ubutaka, hongerwamo ishwagara ingana na kg 25 kuri are imwe (ni ukuvuga toni 2,5 kuri hegitari). Nyuma y&rsquo; ifumbire y&rsquo; imborera, umurima ushyirwamo ifumbire mvaruganda ikubiyemo imyunyu ya N, P, K. mu bipimo binyuranye bitewe n&rsquo; ibihingwa ndetse n&rsquo; imiterere y&rsquo; ubutaka.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Muri rusange, ibinyamisogwe bikenera cyane imyunyu ya Phosiphore (P), Ibinyampeke bigakenera cyane umyunyu wa Azote (N) naho ibinyabijumba imyunyu ya potasiyumu (K).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.6. Imirimo yo gutera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kugirango haboneke imbuto nziza, umutubuzi agomba kwubahiriza inama zijyanye n&rsquo;igihe cyiza cyo gutera, guhungira imbuto mbere yo kuzitera, imbuto ziterwa kuri hegitari n&rsquo; ubucucike (densit&eacute;)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.7 Gukura imbuto mbi n&rsquo; izirwaye mu murima.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kugirango imbuto ituburwa igumane umwimerere wayo, umutubuzi akomeza akuramo imbuto mbi cyangwa irwaye mu murima agasiga izifite umwimerere w&rsquo;iyo atubura.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.8 Indwara n&rsquo; uko zivurwa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Indwara n&rsquo; ibyonnyi by&rsquo; imyaka bigabanya ubwiza bw&rsquo; imbuto bikagabanya n&rsquo; umusaruro.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umutubuzi w&rsquo; imbuto agomba kumenya neza indwara z&rsquo; ibihingwa n&rsquo;ibyonnyi byabyo akamenya n&rsquo; uburyo birwanywa</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.9. Gusarura</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Igihe cy&rsquo;isarura umutubuzi agomba kwita kuri ibi bikurikira:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Kwirinda gusarura imbuto zigifite ubuhehere bwinshi. Ubuhehere bugomba kuba hasi ya 20%.</li>\r\no<li>Kudatinza imbuto mu murima iyo igeze igihe cy&rsquo;isarura.</li>\r\no<li>Gukomeza kurobanura imbuto zitari nziza cyangwa zirwaye zigakurwamo.</li>\r\no<li>Kwirinda guta umusaruro mu murima.</li>\r\no<li>Kwirinda kuvanga ubwoko bunyuranye bw&rsquo;imbuto buri mbuto isaruwe ihabwa ikimenyetso kiyiranga.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.10. Gutunganya imbuto</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><strong><em>Kwumisha imbuto.</em></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Akenshi iyo imbuto igisarurwa iba ifite ubuhehere buri hejuru. Nibyiza kubanza kuyanika mbere yo kuyitunganya ( kuyihungura cyangwa kuyihura) Nyuma yo kuyihura, irasubira ikanikwa kugirango igere ku buhehere butuma ishobora guhunikwa neza. Ku bihingwa byinshi nk&rsquo;ibinyampeke n&rsquo;ibinyamisogwe, ubuhehere bugomba kujya munsi ya 13%.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.11. Guhura /Kugosora/ Guhungira no guhunika </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyo imbuto z&rsquo;ibinyampeke cyangwa ibinyamisogwe zimaze kwuma, zirahurwa. Mu gihe cy&rsquo;ihura umutubuzi agomba kwirinda kumena cyangwa gukomeretsa impeke z&rsquo;imbuto. Guhura bikorwa n&rsquo;amaboko cyangwa se n&rsquo;imashini kubazifite. Nyuma y&rsquo;ihura, imbuto iragosorwa kugirango batandukanye imbuto n&rsquo;ibishogoshogo, umukungugu n&rsquo;amabuye. Kugosora bituma kandi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>imbuto ziteze cyangwa zinyuranye n&rsquo;imbuto yatubuwe zitandukanywa n&rsquo;imbuto nziza. Ubusanzwe hakoreshwa intaro mu kugosora imbuto ariko habaho n&rsquo;imashini z&rsquo;ubwoko bunyuranye zigosora imbuto.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Izo mashini zifite ubushobozi bunyuranye, hari n&rsquo;izikora akazi ko guhungira no gushyira mu mifuka. Mu gihe hakoreshejwe imashini mu kugosora, hagomba kwirindwa ko imbuto z&rsquo;amoko anyuranye zivanga bitewe ko hari izaheze mu mashini. Imashini igomba gusukurwa neza igihe igosoye imbuto inyuranye n&rsquo;ikurikira.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.12. Guhunika</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imbuto iyo zimaze kugosorwa, zirahungirwa, zigashyirwa mu mifuka , zigahunikwa ahantu humutse kandi hanyura umuyaga. Imifuka ihunikwamo igomba gusukurwa kugirango itanduza imbuto igiye guhunikwamo. Ahantu hahunikwa imbuto, hagomba kuba hafite isuku, hakingiye ibyonnyi n&rsquo;imvura. Umutubuzi agomba kumenya ko ubushyuhe n&rsquo;ubuhehere byinshi bituma imbutso zihunitse zononekara. Umutubuzi agomba guhora asura ahahunitse imbuto kugirango yirinde icyakonona imbuto cyose.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Guhinga, gusarura, gutunganya imbuto no kuzihunika bigomba kwitabwaho kugirango haboneke imbuto nziza. Ntibihagije kugirango uhinge, weze, ugomba no gukomeza kwita ku musaruro kugeza igihe imbuto ziviriye mu mangazini/ubuhunikiro. Koko rero, imbuto uyizera ari uko uyihunitse, ariko kandi ntibicira aho, ugomba kuyirinda imungu, imbeba n&rsquo;ibindi bisimba. Ubushobozi bwo kumera bushingiye ku mibikire myiza. Iyo bugabanutse ntabwo ari ikintu upima ku jisho gusa: Ni ngombwa gusuzumisha imbuto muri laboratwari ndetse no mu turima duto. Gukoresha imbuto nziza ni bumwe mu buryo buzatuma dushobora kongera umusaruro kandi ibyo bigakorwa n&rsquo;inzego zose zibishinzwe kugera ku muhinzi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Iyi nkuru tuyikesha imfashanyigisho watanzwe na <a href=\"http://www.duhamic.org.rw/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">DUHAMIC-ADRI.</span></a> </em></p>\r\n','1',2209,3,'2015-10-24 08:02:12','Imbuto ',1,'online','no','no'),(207,'Itangazo USAID/ PSDAG :Gushishikariza abashoramari n\'abafatanyabikorwa mu buhinzi gufatanya ibikorwa n\'umushinga','usaid logo.jpeg','<p><em><strong>Itangazo USAID/</strong><strong> PSDAG :Gushishikariza abashoramari n&rsquo;abafatanyabikorwa mu buhinzi gufatanya ibikorwa n&rsquo;umushinga</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>Uko umushinga uteye </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Private Sector Driven Agricultural Growth (PSDAG) ni umushinga w&rsquo;imyaka itanu wa USAID watangiye ibikorwa muri Kanama 2014. Inshingano z&rsquo;uyu mushinga ni guteza imbere abahinzi baciriritse, binyujijwe mu ishoramari ry&rsquo;abikorera mu buhinzi. Umushinga PSDAG ufite intego ebyiri zibanze: a) gukorana na Leta y&rsquo;u Rwanda mu gushishikariza abikorera gushora imari mu buhinzi b) korohereza abashoramari mu ruhererekane rw&rsquo;ibikorwa nyongeragaciro ku bihingwa binyuranye</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko itangazo riteye</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umushinga PSDAG urifuza kubaka ubufatanye n&rsquo; abikorera ku giti cyabo mu ntego yo kuzamura ishoramari mu buhinzi no kongera ubukungu bw&rsquo; abahinzi baciriritse binyuze mu bikorwa byongerera umusaruro agaciro ku isoko. Muri gahunda z&rsquo;umwaka wa 2016 &ndash;<strong>Ukwakira 2015 kugeza muri Nzeli 2016</strong>&ndash; PSDAG izibanda ku bikorwa nyongeragaciro ku bihingwa bikurikira: Ibirayi, Ibishyimbo, Ibigori, Imbuto n&rsquo; imboga.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iri tangazo rigamije kugaragaza intego PSDAG ifite mu mwaka wa 2016, ikanakangurira amashyirahamwe n&rsquo;abikorera ku giti cyabo bafite ibikorwa byongera agaciro k&rsquo;ibihingwa byavuzwe haruguru, gusaba ubufatanyabikorwa n&rsquo;umushinga binyuze mu <strong>nyandiko zisobanura imishinga bafite</strong>. PSDAG izatanga ubufasha ibinyujije mu ipiganwa ry&rsquo;inkunga mu bikorwa nyongeragaciro (Value Chain Competitiveness Grants-VCCG), izajya yunganira igishoro cy&rsquo;umushoramari. PSDAG irashishikariza abafite ibikorwa:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Bifite isoko rifatika, cyangwa umuguzi wizewe;</li>\r\no<li>Biteza imbere ubufatanye hagati y&rsquo;abafatanyabikorwa mu ruhererekane rw&rsquo;ibikorwa nyongeragaciro (abatanga inyongeramusaruro, abahinzi, abakusanya umusaruro/abacuruzi, abaguzi bacuruza ndetse n&rsquo;amasosiyete y&rsquo;ubwikorezi;</li>\r\no<li>Bishora imari mu koranabuhanga ryorohereza abafatanyabikorwa kubona serivise zinoze kandi zitanzwe neza, cyangwa byongera umusaruro;</li>\r\no<li>Bitanga uburyo bwo guhuza abahinzi baciriritse ku bwinshi;</li>\r\no<li>Byongera inyungu y&rsquo;ingano y&rsquo;ibigurishirizwa ku murima ndetse n&rsquo;umutungo w&rsquo;abahinzi</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyo bisaba</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibizakurikizwa mu guhitamo abunganirwa n&rsquo;umushinga, ni ibi bikurikira:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Gutanga <strong>inyandiko isobanura umushinga </strong>n&rsquo;ibiyiherekeza byose;</li>\r\no<li>Kuba ari umuryango utegamiye kuri leta wo muri Amerika cyangwa mu Rwanda, wahawe ubuzima gatozi, wemewe n&rsquo;amategeko yo mu gihugu;</li>\r\no<li>Indi miryango yigenga yemewe n&rsquo;amategeko, harimo:</li>\r\no<li>Ibigo/ imiryango yikorera ku giti cyayo</li>\r\no<li>Amashyirahamwe n&rsquo;ibigo by ubuhinzi</li>\r\no<li>Imiryango itegamiye kuri Leta (iharanira inyungu n&rsquo;idaharanira inyungu);</li>\r\no<li>Ibigo by&rsquo;ubushakashatsi/ Kaminuza,</li>\r\no<li>N&rsquo;ingaga/impuzamashyirahamwe zemewe n&rsquo;amategeko z&rsquo;iyo miryango yavuzwe;</li>\r\no<li>Kwerekana ko umushinga uzaza wuzuza <strong>intego ya 1 na 2 za PSDAG n&rsquo;intego zihariye z&rsquo;ingengamikorere ya 2016 </strong></li>\r\no<li>Kwerekana ubushobozi bwo gufatanya gushora imari ihagije mu mushinga wawe</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amabwiriza y&rsquo;Ubusabe</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umushinga PSDAG uzajya wakira inyandiko zigendanye n&rsquo;ingengamikorere yayo uko zije, izisuzume kugeza igihe itariki iri tangazo rizarangiriraho izamenyekanishwa. Abafatanyabikorwa bujuje ibisabwa bazatoranywa mu buryo bw&rsquo;ipiganwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abujuje ibyangombwa bakohereza ubutumwa bwabo kuri grants@psdag.rw bagahabwa amabwiriza arambuye ajyanye nuko basaba ubufasha muri PSDAG. Aya mabwiriza kandi bayasanga ku biro by&rsquo;umushinga biherereye kuri KG 684 St, No.19, Kacyiru, Kigali.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Itangazo turicyesha&nbsp;Christelle Kamaliza ushinzwe itangazamukuru mu mushinga&nbsp;PSDAG</em></p>\r\n','1',1287,3,'2015-11-18 08:23:42','Amatangazo',0,'online','',''),(209,'Technology solution promises to improve potato farmer\'s incomes','usaid ibirayi.png','<p>The Ministry of Trade and Commerce&rsquo;s new strategy for marketing Irish potatoes in Rwanda through potato collection centers seeks to increase smallholder farmers&rsquo; incomes by addressing challenges in selling the crop. To facilitate the implementation of these collection centers, the United States Agency for Development (USAID), through its project, Private Sector Driven Agricultural Growth (PSDAG Project), is piloting a technology solution called Farmbook, a data collection program and web app that is designed to help increase farmers&rsquo; productivity and competitiveness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some of the constraints faced by potato farmers include a lack of easy access to the market information needed to be competitive in selling Irish potatoes. In response, the potato collection centers have been designed to organize potato business transactions and build formal contracts between farmers, traders, and wholesalers. Farmbook will further allow for professional management of the collection centers, better business planning, and improved trading conditions, which will ultimately lead to the increase of farmers&rsquo; income.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ibirayi USAID\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-360\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/ibirayi-usaid.jpg?w=863\" style=\"height:347px; width:516px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><em>Representatives of 6 Potato Cooperatives at the partnership agreement signing event with USAID Private Sector Driven Agricultural Growth Project on &nbsp; December 10, 2015</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To pilot Farmbook, USAID&rsquo;s PSDAG Project will partner with six potato cooperatives supporting 10 potato collection centers located in Musanze, Burera, and Nyabihu Districts and supporting 2,347 farmers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mugorozi Fabien, president of the CVMB Cooperative in Burera District, relayed the members&rsquo; expectation of the new system and stated, &ldquo;The members are already excited that aggregation centers will help keep potato prices stable and with Farmbook, we will be able to gather a lot of information to make smart decisions.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rwanda Private Sector Driven Agricultural Growth (PSDAG) is a five-year (2014-2019) project funded by the United States Agency for International Development. The goal of PSDAG is to increase smallholder farmers&rsquo; incomes by promoting private sector investments and to facilitate the transformation of agriculture into a market-oriented, competitive, and high-value sector.</p>\r\n','4',1695,3,'2015-12-16 01:54:23','Ibirayi ',1,'online','',''),(211,'How To Achieve Your Agribusiness Dream','IMG-20160721-WA0048.jpg','<p><strong>THE DREAM:</strong> Your dream is the most important thing in agribusiness success. The dream shows where you are going and how you want your agribusiness to be in future. Write down the dream in details in order to remain clear and focused as you work on your agribusiness idea.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BE ORIGINAL:</strong> Your agribusiness must be a solution to an existing human problem or need for it to succeed, and not a mere imitation . Take care and identify gaps&nbsp;to address and you will not desperately ask for market the last minute for your goods and services, common with starters in Agribusiness. Every human problem is a business opportunity. Business opportunities are as many as human problems. Be unique.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>EXPECT TOUGH TIMES:</strong> There are times when things get tough in every business and agribusiness is no exception. Focusing on the dream will keep you going when things get tough as you wait for better times. The dream will drive your passion and motivate you to act to achieve it. Remain clear about your agribusiness idea and stay focused on achieving your dreams.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BREAK DOWN THE DREAM</strong> into manageable portions. Being overambitious will lead to frustration and discouragement. Write down 5-10 things you need to do in order to realize your dream, and they must be simple, measurable (Quantify to enable monitoring of progress) achievable within your resources and abilities, setting a time deadline for each.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>TARGET CUSTOMERS:</strong> Find out who&rsquo;ll be your target customers (e.g. households, hotels, processors, Schools, hospitals etc) what product/ service they need and of what quality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>COMPETITORS:</strong> Find out who&rsquo;ll be your competitors their strengths and weaknesses. Take advantage of their weaknesses by offering what they are not offering the customer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PREPARE EXPECTED INCOME AND EXPENDITURE BUDGET</strong> for your agribusiness, and determine how long it will take to recover the capital invested.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>FINANCE:</strong> Lastly decide where money will come from and how much you will need.</p>\r\n','1',1434,3,'2015-12-02 21:02:13','Agribusiness',0,'online','',''),(214,'Kigali-Rwanda to host the 7th Africa Agriculture Science Week and FARA General Assembly','fara.png','<p>The AASW and FARA General Assembly is the principal forum for all stakeholders in African agriculture science, technology and innovation to take stock of their collective achievements over the past three years and craft a common agenda along with modalities for achieving their collective targets over the next three years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You are invited to the 7<sup>th</sup> AASW and FARA General Assembly which will take place in Kigali, Rwanda, 13-16 June 2016.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>FARA is co-organizing this event jointly with:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:decimal\" type=\"1\">\r\no<li><strong>Sub-regional Agricultural Research Organisations: (ASARECA, CCARDESA &amp; CORAF/WECARD)</strong><br />\r\no<strong>2. African Union Commission and NEPAD Planning and Coordinating Agency</strong><br />\r\no<strong>3. CGIAR centres (AfricaRice, IITA, ILRI, IFPRI, ICRISAT, ICRAF, CIAT)</strong><br />\r\no<strong>4. Education networks (ANAFE, RUFORUM, AAU)</strong><br />\r\no<strong>5. Continental AR&amp;D organisations (AFAAS, AGRA, PAFO, AAIN and AATF)</strong><br />\r\no<strong>6. The Technical Centre for Agriculture and Rural Cooperation (CTA), FAO, the Global Forum on Agricultural Research (GFAR) and the Global Forum for Innovations in Agriculture.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>The event will focus on the operationalization of the Science Agenda for Agriculture in Africa at country level. Thus its overall theme is &ldquo;Apply Science, Impact Livelihoods&rdquo;. The content will be organized around the following five sub-themes:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:decimal\" type=\"1\">\r\no<li><strong>Institutional systems and policies for making science work for African agriculture</strong><br />\r\no<strong>2. Sustainable productivity growth, value chains and profitable agribusinesses</strong><br />\r\no<strong>3. Human capital development and the Youth</strong><br />\r\no<strong>4. Sustainable financing of Science, Technology and Innovation for African agriculture</strong><br />\r\no<strong>5. Megatrends in African Agriculture</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>The event will feature distinguished keynote speakers, plenary sessions, an exhibition / trade fair, parallel side meetings, the Rwanda day (when the host country will showcase its achievements in agricultural research and innovation) and a business session of the FARA General Assembly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will shortly receive an announcement with detailed information about the programme and registration plus a link to the event&rsquo;s website.</p>\r\n','1',13928,3,'2016-01-26 22:54:23','News Amakuru',0,'online','',''),(215,'Ikiganiro hagati y\'umuhinzi n\'igihingwa','Kwizera olivier .png','<p>Ikiganiro hagati y&rsquo;umuhinzi n&rsquo;igihingwa tugikesha Kwizera Olivier ,umuhinzi w&rsquo;urutoki mu karere ka Ngoma , ubu akaba ari gukorera mu karere ka Rwamagana afasha abahinzi muri Ubwo buhinzi .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umuhinzi mwiza arabyuka buri gitondo akajya gusuhuza ibyo yahinze akabirebana ubwuzu, akabikorakora, akabibaza amakuru, akabibaza niba byaraye neza bigasubiza biti: &ldquo;ibyonnyi byatumye tudasinzira neza&rdquo;<br />\r\nUmuhinzi (U): Muhumure ejo ndabashakira pesticides<br />\r\nIbihingwa(I): Reba amababi yacu yarabye andi yabaye umuhondo kandi tuberewe no gusa n&rsquo;icyatsi<br />\r\nU: mwihangayika ndabashakira amazi mbuhire muhore mutoshye.<br />\r\nI: none se ko ubona turi kugwingira mu mikurire, ubwo umusaruro twagusezeranije uzavahe Nyakubahwa muhinzi?<br />\r\nU: Mwihangayika nimwe ba databuja nduhira. Ejo mugitondo ndabazanira ifumbire yuzuye intungagihingwa nka Nitorojeni, fosifori na potasiyumu muzakura neza bityo nange mbonereho umusaruro<br />\r\nI: Nubundi turabizi ko udukunda ariko ntiwibagirwe ko hari ibindi byatsi mudafitanye gahunda byaje bidusanga hano kandi bikanaducura amazi n&rsquo;intungagihingwa uba watwihereye<br />\r\nU: eh! Sinabyihanganira nzazinduka numuryango wange nibikoresho bihagije byo kubirimbura, ntibizanangora cyane kuko nzazana n&rsquo;imiti ya herbicide, aho ntababangamiye nzayikoresha.<br />\r\nI: Nyakubahwa turumva uko udukunda biturenze. Gusa ntuzatwarwe no kutwitaho ngo wirengagize kurengera ibindi bidukikije kuko birimbutse mugihe kizaza ntitwakongera kubaho, bigatuma nabana bawe badahorana natwe.<br />\r\nU: ibyo ndabizirikana kandi nzabahora hafi. Reka nzamuke nge kureba naya matungo yange nayo nyabaze uko yaramutse.<br />\r\nI: umunsi mwiza<br />\r\nU: murakoze namwe photosynthesis nziza!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iki kiganiro tugikesha Kwizera Olivier , Umuhinzi w&rsquo;urutoki mu karere ka Ngoma</p>\r\n','1',1355,3,'2015-02-05 21:54:21','Ubuhinzi Bwacu',0,'online','',''),(217,'How was Rwandan Agriculture in 2015Â (figures)','rwanda agri 2015.png','<blockquote>\r\n<p><em><strong>This is the summary of how was Agriculture in Rwanda in 2015, looking at Farm Characteristics (Production ,Yield, Area). All figures presented are from the Seasonal Agriculture Survey that &nbsp;covered three agricultural seasons (A, B and C) for the year 2015 in/Rwanda with two categories of respondents : Agricultural Operators(or Small Scale Farmers) and Large Scale Farmers (LSF). </strong></em></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p>According to NISR the main crops grown in 2015 Season A were Banana followed by Cassava, beans, Sorghum and maize. In Season B, the main crops grown were banana followed by cassava, beans, sorghum and maize. Season C was quite different as the main crops were Irish potatoes followed by Sweet Potatoes, vegetables and Beans.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>Crop Areas. </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In Rwanda, in terms of land area under crops the main crops grown in Season A&nbsp;were Banana (22.9%), Cassava (21.5%), Beans (19.8%), and Maize (12.4%)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season B were Banana (23.1%), Cassava (22.8%), Beans (16.6%), Sorghum (8.8%) and Maize (5.2%)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season C were Irish potatoes (34.5%), Sweet potatoes (20.5%), vegetables (19.7%)&nbsp;and Beans (17.19%).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Crop production</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong>The share of crop production by groups of crops was significantly high for&nbsp;Tubers and Roots (37.4%) followed by Banana (27.9%). Other crop groups&nbsp;contributed as follows: Cereals (10.5%), Legumes and Pulses (7.8%), and&nbsp;Vegetables and Fruits (4.7%). The share of crop production for individual crop was&nbsp;highest for Banana for Beer (14.4%), followed by Sweet Potatoes (14.3%), Cassavas(11.4%), Cooking Banana (10.7%) and Irish Potatoes (9.5).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season B : The share of crop production by groups of crops was significantly high for Tubers and Roots (41.4%) followed by Banana (27.2%) and Cereals (7.5%). Other crop&nbsp;groups contributed as follows: Legumes and Pulses (6.4%) and Vegetables and&nbsp;Fruits (4.4%).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season C: The results showed that the share of crop production was significantly high for Irish Potatoes (55.7%) followed by Vegetables (34.0%), Sweet Potatoes (8.0%) and Beans (2.2%).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Use of Organic Fertilizer</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season A , 51.3% of all Agricultural Operators in Rwanda reported that they used organic fertilizer . For Large Scale Farmers, 66.8% of LSF reported that they used organic fertilizers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season B: 43.1% of all Agricultural Operators in Rwanda reported that they used&nbsp;organic fertilizer. For LSF, 42.3 percent used organic fertilizer</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season C: 65.2% of all Agricultural Operators in Rwanda reported that they used&nbsp;organic fertilizer</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Use of Inorganic Fertilizer by Agricultural Operators and Large Scale&nbsp;</strong><strong>Farmers</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season A: 21.1 %of Agricultural Operators used inorganic&nbsp;fertilizers while 54.8 % of LSF used inorganic fertilizers during 2015 Season A&nbsp;This shows that a larger proportion of LSF used inorganic fertilizer than Agricultural Operators during this agricultural season.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season B: 14.6 percent of Agricultural Operators used inorganic&nbsp;fertilizers while 51.5 percent of LSF used inorganic fertilizers .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season C: The survey results showed that 46.0 percent of Agricultural Operators used inorganic fertilizers</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Use of Seeds</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In 2015, Agricultural Operators used traditional seeds more than improved ones&nbsp;(84.5 % and 15.5% respectively). For LSF, on country level, traditional seeds are&nbsp;used at (79.8 %). Traditional seeds were used for almost all crops by Agricultural operators as well as by LSF. Agricultural operators used improved seeds mostly to grow Maize (23.9%) and Vegetables (23.6%). Among LSF, the highest use of improved seeds has been to grow Vegetables (76.9%) followed by Wheat and Climbing beans as their percentages are (66.7% and 52.4% respectively).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season B: &nbsp;Agricultural Operators used more traditional seeds (88.4%) than&nbsp;improved seeds (11.6%). The same to LSF, the use of traditional seeds was more&nbsp;than the use of improved seeds 60.2 and 39.8 respectively.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season C : Agricultural Operators used more traditional seeds (87.6%) than&nbsp;improved seeds (12.4%)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Irrigation Practices</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>SeasonA: &nbsp;results showed that about 1.1% of agricultural operators and 24.6 %&nbsp;of LSF practiced irrigation . On the type of irrigation used by Agricultural Operators, the survey results showed that the majority of Agricultural Operators used Water channels for irrigation (71.5%), followed by those that used Watering can (22.0%)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season B: 1.5% of Agricultural Operators practiced irrigation in 2015 Season B&nbsp;while for LSF 28.4 practiced irrigation during their farming activities</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season C: The survey results showed that about 20.5% of agricultural operators practised irrigation</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Use of Pesticides</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season A: &nbsp;9.1% of Agricultural Operators used pesticides in their farming activities against 46.7% of LSF Countrywide, for Agricultural Operators, Dithane is the&nbsp;most used pesticide (35.4% of all Agricultural operators)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season B: 7.9 percent of Agricultural Operators used pesticides in their farming activities while 32.9% of LSF used pesticides in the farming activities</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Season C : 53.3 percent of Agricultural Operators used pesticides in their farming activities</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Small Agricultural Equipment</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Expenditure on small agricultural equipment by agricultural operators was mainly on&nbsp;the Hoe (28.3%) followed by Bike and Sacks for agricultural operators (12.2% and&nbsp;7.5% respectively) while LSF spent mainly on Sheeting, Sacks and Hoe (36.8%,&nbsp;31.6% and 16.2%respectively).</p>\r\n','1',1510,3,'2016-02-29 21:54:46','News Amakuru',0,'online','',''),(218,'Imyumbati : Igihingwa kiri kw\'isonga mu mirire y\'abanyarwanda','imyumbati .png','<p>Imyumbati : Igihingwa kiri kw&rsquo;isonga mu mirire y&rsquo;abanyarwanda</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imyumbati ni igihingwa ni igihingwa gikunda ubutaka buseseka, gihingwa hafi mu Gihugu hose ariko cyane cyane mu ntara y&rsquo;amajyepfo mdetse n&rsquo;iburasirazuba.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu Mu mwaka wa 2014 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe n&rsquo;ikigo cy&rsquo;igihugu cy&rsquo;ibarurirsha mibare ku bufatanye na minisiteri y&rsquo;Ubuhinzi n&rsquo;Ubworozi bwagaragaje ko imyumbati ari yo yatanze umusaruro kuruta ibindi bihingwa byose ahoyo n&rsquo;ibindi binyabijumba byihariye 35.9% mu gihembe A ndetse no mu gihembwe B bikiharira 39.2%. Bigaragara kandi ko ubutaka byahizweho ari bwo bunini mu butaka bwahinzwe bwose muri uyu mwaka wa 2014 aho imyumbati yihariye 22.6% by&rsquo;ubutaka byahinzwe bwose mu gihembwe A ndetse no mihembwe ikiharira 23.3% by&rsquo;ubutaka bwahinzwe bwose .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tugiye kureba mu mwaka ushize wa 2015 dusanga imyumbati nanone ikomeje kuza mu myanya ya mbere mu bihingwa bifitiye akamaro abahinzi mu gihugu hose urebye ku musaruro ndetse no ku bwitabire mu kubihinga haba abahinzi bato cyangwa abahinzi bakora ubuhinzi bwagutse . &nbsp;Tugendeye ku butaka byahinzweho mu gihembwe A usanga urutoki (22.9%) rwarahinzwe ahantu hanini kurusha imyumbati (21.5%), ariko nubundi umusaruro w&rsquo;imyumbati n&rsquo;ibinyabijumba &nbsp;ukomeza kuba munini &nbsp;aho ibinyabijumba bifite (31%),mu urutoki rufite &nbsp;(22.5%), naho mu gihembwe B umusaruro w&rsquo;ibinyabijumba wari (33 %), kandi ubuso bwahinzweho imyumbati bukaba ari (22.8%), by&rsquo;ubuso bwahinzwe bwose.Twibanze ku bihembwe A na B kuko mu Gihembwe C ahanini nta myumbati ihingwa ahubwo iki gihembwe kigaragaza umwero w&rsquo;ibirayi mwinshi kurusha ibindi bihingwa .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nubwo ariko imyumbati ifitiye akamaro kanini abahinzi , ikomeje kugaragaza indwara zituma umusaruro ugabanyuka nk&rsquo;uko abahinzi babivuga hirya no hino mu gihugu izo ndwa ariko ubushakashatsi bukaba bugenda bukorwa n&rsquo;ibigo bibishinzwe mugushaka imbuto yahangana nabwo .</p>\r\n','1',1478,3,'2015-02-13 22:21:56','Imyumbati',0,'online','',''),(222,'GMOs ibihingwa biri kwamaganwa n\'amahanga mu Rwanda byifashe gute?','GMO.png','<p>Ntibyoroshye kubibonera izina ry&rsquo;Ikinyarwanda reta tubyite &ldquo;Jimo&rdquo;.Abahinzi benshi mu Rwanda bibaza ibibazo bitandukanye&nbsp; ku bihingwa bizwi ku izina rya &ldquo;Genetically modified plants/organisms( GMOs)&rdquo;tugenekereje mu Kinyarwanda twakwita (ibihingwa byahinduwe mu miterere yabyo karemano na bantu).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Si abahinzi gusa kuko usanga nabantu&nbsp; baha agaciro kubungabunga ubuzima bwabo mu mirire bibaza niba bene ibi&nbsp; bihingwa&nbsp; byaba byarageze ku &nbsp;masoko yo mu Rwanda. Ibibazo&nbsp; byinshi bigarukwaho ni nki ngaruka byaba bigira kubuzima &nbsp;bw&rsquo;uwabiriye, ingaruka &nbsp;bigira ku b&rsquo;inyanubuzima ni b&rsquo;idukubidukikije,&nbsp; ndetse n&rsquo;umusaruro wabyo ugereranyije n&rsquo;umusaruro w&rsquo; imbuto dusanzwe duhinga.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mubyukuri, ubushakashatsi kuri ubu bwoko bushya bw&rsquo;ibiribwa buravuguruzanya kubyerekeye ingaruka mbi byaba bifite ku bidukikije ndetse no kubuzima bwa b&rsquo;abifungura. Ibi bikaba biterwa ahanini ni nyungu abavumbuye iri koranabuhanga ( Ikigo cyo muri Leta z&rsquo;Unze Ubumwe za America) baba babona mw&rsquo;icuruzwa z&rsquo;imbuto n&rsquo;ikorabuhanga ryabo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abo bashakashatsi bemeza ko imbuto zabo ziberanye n&rsquo;imihindagurikire y&rsquo;ikirere kuko zigaragaza uguhangana n&rsquo;izuba kudasanzwe, zihangana n&rsquo;ibyonnyi hamwe n&rsquo;utundi dusimba twonona umusaruro w&rsquo;umuhinzi kurenza kure izindi mbuto zisanzwe ku isoko</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ku rundi ruhande abashakashatsi bo mu bihugu byunze ubumwe by&rsquo; iburayi bagaragaje ko ibi bihingwa (GMOs) bidakwiye kwiye kuribwa, kuko bigira ingaruka mbi ku buzima bwababiriye ndetse no k&rsquo;urusobe rw&rsquo;ibinyabuzima. Mu bushakashatsi bwabo bemeza ko byateye ibibyimba (aribyo bishobora kuvamo kanseri) ku mwijima w&rsquo;imbeba bakoreshaga mu bushakashatsi bwabo. Ibi byatumye ibihugu by&rsquo;Uburayi bifata icyemezo cyo guca ziriya mbuto no kwamagana ririya koranabuhanga. Nyuma ama sosiyete sivile yo muri America nayo yahagurukiye kwamagana izo mbuto nubwo rwose ba nyir&rsquo;iri koranabuhanga banenze ibya vuye mu bushakashatsi bw&rsquo;abanyaburayi bavuga ko butubahirije amabwiriza akurikizwa mubushakashatsi; bityo bakaba barakomeje kwagura amasoko yabo, nko mu Buhinde, Burikinafaso, n&rsquo; Afurika y&rsquo;Epfo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kuru ndi ruhande ibihugu nka Zambia na Kenya byamaganiye kure ibi biribwa, ndetse nko muri Zambiya bubatse ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura iyinjizwa ry&rsquo;izo mbuto no kuzikumira; Kenya yo yashyizweho igitutu isabwa kwemera guha abahinzi izo mbuto, ariko Inteko y&rsquo;aba Depite yumvira ibyifuzo by&rsquo;abahinzi ikomeza gukumira iyinjizwa ryizo mbuto nshya.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Muri Kenya Ntibari bishimye mbere y&rsquo;Inteko yari igiye guterana kugirango ifate Umwanzuro kuri ibi bihingwa.Ikizwi mu mikorere y&rsquo;ibi bihingwa bishya, nuko koko birinda ibyonnyi kandi bikihanganira Izuba n&rsquo;amazi make. Udusimba twibasira imyaka twa hato na hato; agasimba akariko kose&nbsp; (ndetse n&rsquo;udusimba dufite akamaro nki nzuki n&rsquo;utundi) kaje kuri bene icyo gihingwa gahita gapfa nta wundi muti urinze guteraho, ibi rero bikaba bigira ingaruka kurusobe rw&rsquo;ibinyabuzima, ndetse bamwe bemeza ko uko umuti uba uri mugihingwa wica utwo dusimba, ninako ugira ingaruka ku muburi w&rsquo;umuntu uriye ibyasaruwe kuri bene ibyo bihingwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uko ibintu bihagaze mu buhinzi bwo mu Rwanda nk&rsquo;uko tubikesha Umunyamabanga Wa Leta muri Minisiteri y&rsquo; Ubuhinzi n&rsquo; Ubworozi Tony Nsanganira mu ganiro yatanze kuri Radio KFM taliki 24 Gashyantare 2016 avugako&nbsp;Ibi bihingwa bitari byagera ku masoko yo mu Rwanda. &nbsp;Yongeyeho ko bari gufatanya n&rsquo;inzego mpuza mahanga kugirango bashyireho ambwiriza agenga imikoreshereze yabyo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ugendeye kuri aya makuru twahawe mu Rwanda ntazihari, ariko kandi ntago zigezwe zikumirwa ndetse ntago turamenya neza aho Minisiteri ihagaze kuri Iki kibazo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ese dufite ubushobozi bwo gukumira iyinjizwa zibyo bihingwa, cyane ko bisaba ikoranabuhanga, ndetse ni nzobere mu binyabuzima? Aba kurikiranira hafi amakuru yu buhinzi ntibashidikanya ko&nbsp; isaha ni saha , ibi bihingwa byakwinjizwa magendu. Guhana amakuru y&rsquo;ubuhunzi cyane cyane ku mbuto zinjizwa ziturutse hanze bikaba bigomba gushyirwamo ingufu, cyane ko bifasha no mu gukumira ikwirakwizwa ry&rsquo;indwara zitandukanye z&rsquo;ibihingwa ndetse niz&rsquo;abantu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Inkuru yateguwe na Muvunyi Blaise Pascal</em></p>\r\n','1',16011,3,'2016-03-20 01:54:06','Ubuhinzi Bwacu',0,'online','',''),(224,'U Rwanda rwatangije umushinga wo guteza imbere ubuhinzi bushingiye kw\'iteganyagihe','Iteganyagihe .jpg','<p>Ku girango hubakwe Ubuhinzi bushingiye kw&rsquo;iteganyagihe, Leta y&rsquo;u Rwanda ifatanyije n&rsquo;abafatanyabikorwa, batangije umushinga wiswe &ldquo;&ldquo;Rwanda Climate Services for Agriculture&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uyu mushinga wagenewe imyaka 3 watangijwe ku mugaragaro taliki ya 23 Werurwe 2016, ukazafasha cyane cyane mu guhindura ubuhinzi bwo mu cyaro ndetse n&rsquo;ubukungu bw&rsquo;igihugu binyuze mu kwirinda ingorane zituruka ku iteganyagihe .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Innocent Bisangwa ushinzwe Ibidukikije n&rsquo;imihindagurikire y&rsquo;ibihe muri Minisiteri y&rsquo;Ubuhinzi n&rsquo;Ubworozi aragira ati:&ldquo;Ni ngombwa ko &nbsp;umuhinzi abona amakuru y&rsquo;ihinduka ry&rsquo;ibihe cyangwa iteganyagihe, binyuze muri iyi gahunda tuzabafasha mu gufata imyanzuro myiza y&rsquo;igihe cyo guhinga , ingano y&rsquo;ifumbire yo gukoresha ndetse n&rsquo;igihe cyo gusarura&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uyu mushinga ufite umwihariko kuko uzakemura ibibazo bikomeye bibiri aribyo gutanga amakuru yuzuye y&rsquo;iteganyagihe ndetse no gutanga amakuru y&rsquo;iteganyagihe hashingiye ku byifuzo by&rsquo;umuhinzi ndetse n&rsquo;abandi bakenera ayo makuru.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uyu mushinga ni igikorwa cya Minisiteri y&rsquo;ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi ifatanyije n&rsquo;ikigo cy&rsquo;igihugu gishinzwe iteganyagihe (Meteo Rwanda) ku bufatanye n&rsquo;ibigo nka CGIAR, CCAFS, International Research Institute for Climate and Society (IRI), Columbia University, the International Center for Tropical Agriculture (CIAT), International Livestock Research Institute (ILRI), ku nkunga ya USAID.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyi nkuru yashyizwe mu Kinyarwanda ishingiye ku nkuru dukesha Ishami rya MINAGRI rishinzwe itangazamakuru.</p>\r\n','1',1184,3,'2016-03-29 21:23:32','Iteganyagihe',0,'online','',''),(226,'Uburyo bwo guhinga Uvanga Ibihingwa, uko bikorwa n\'ibyiza byabyo','Kuvanga ibihingwa.png','<p><em><strong>Uburyo bwo guhinga Uvanga Ibihingwa</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Guhinga uvanga ibihingwa ni uburyo bwo guhinga ibihingwa bibiri cyangwa byinshi icyarimwe mu murima umwe. Ubu ni uburyo ukoresha igihe gito kandi ku butaka buto ukeza ibihingwa bitandukanye. Muri ubu buhinzi ibihingwa bisangira ubutaka ariko bihingwa kuburyo bubyorohereza gusangira intunga gihingwa ziba mu butaka bitabangamiranye ukurikije ibyo buri gihingwa gikenera ndetse bigafashanya muri ubwo buzima . Ubu buhinzi bushobora gukorwa uvanga bihingwa bidatinda mumurima hagati yabyo(annual plants intercrop) , ibihingwa bitinda mumurima n&rsquo;ibidatinda mumurima (annual plants with perennial plants), ibitinda mumurima hagati yabyo (perennial plants intercrop).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uburyo butandukanye bwo gukoramo ubu buhinzi:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><strong>Kuvanga ibihingwa uko wishakiye (Mixed or multiple cropping) :</strong> Ubu ni uburyo ibihingwa bibiri cyangwa byinshi bishobora kuvangwa kubutaka bumwe ariko bidahinze bikurikije imirongo runaka y&rsquo;igihingwa ukwacyo bigahingwa bikurikije amabwiriza yo kuvanga ibihingwa ndetse n&rsquo;ubwoko bw&rsquo;ibihingwa bishobora kuvangwa.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Guhinga igihingwa nyuma y&rsquo;ikindi (Relay cropping):</strong> Ubu ni uburyo ibihingwa bibiri cyangwa byinshi bishobora kuvangwa ariko kuri ubu buryo ho urareka igihingwa wateye mbere kikabanza kigakura cyarangiza gukura ugatera ikindi wifuza kukivanga nacyo.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Guhinga ku mirongo (Row intercropping):</strong> Ubu ni uburo igihingwa kimwe cyangwa byinshi bivangwa bigasangira ubutaka n&rsquo;igihe cy&rsquo;ihinga ariko bihinze ku buryo buri gihingwa gihinze ku murongo wacyo.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Guhinga mu dutsiko tw&rsquo;ibihingwa cyangwa mu bipande(Strip cropping) :</strong> Ubu ni uburyo ibihingwa bivangwa ariko buri gihingwa kigahingwa mu dutsiko dutandukanye mu murima ; umurima ugabanywamo ibice kuburyo buri gihingwa gihingwa kugace kamwe hanyuma uduce tugahingwa dukurikiranye ariko hagaterwamo ibihingwa bitandukanye mu duce dukurikirana. Ni ukuvugako buri gihingwa kigenda gihingwa mu gace kacyo mumurima .</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibyiza byo Kuvanga ibihingwa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abanditsi benshi n&rsquo;abashakashatsi bagiye bagaruka ku byiza byo kuvanga imyaka hano tugiye kubagezaho bimwe muri ibyo byiza byabyo</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Byongera umusaruro no Gukoresha ubutaka neza kurusha uwabihinze bitandukanye</li>\r\no<li>Bituma ubutaka butagunduka vuba kandi bikongera imyunyugugu ya Nitrogen mubutaka</li>\r\no<li>Bigabanya ukurwara kw&rsquo;ibihingwa guturutse ku dusimba cyangwa ibindi byonnyi .</li>\r\no<li>Bigabanya udusimba tuza mu murima dutera indwara ku</li>\r\no<li>Bigabanya isuri yo kumisozi kandi bikarinda ubutaka buhingwa gutwarwa n&rsquo;isuri.</li>\r\no<li>Bigabanya kumera kw&rsquo;ibyatsi bidakenewe mu murima cyane ko ibi byatsi bituma ibihingwa bidakura neza.</li>\r\no<li>Gukoresha abakora mu murima bake ugereranije n&rsquo;iyo wari guhinga utandukanyije ibihingwa .</li>\r\no<li>Gutanga umusaruro uturutse ku bihingwa bibiri cyangwa byinshi aho gusarura kimwe.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Buyateguwe na <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/etienne-niyigaba-b75b6142\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">NIYIGABA Etienne</span></a></em>&nbsp;<em>Hifashishijwe imfashanyigisho za FAO.</em></p>\r\n','1',2574,3,'2016-05-20 00:36:02','Ubuhinzi Bwacu',0,'online','',''),(227,'Gusasira ibihingwa, uko bikorwa n\'impamvu ukwiye kubikora','gusasira .png','<p>Gusasira ni uburyo byo gutwikira ubutaka buhinze cyangwa buhingwa ukoresheje ibintu binyuranye harimo ibibabi by&rsquo;ibiti, ibyatsi, ibisigazwa by&rsquo;ibyasaruwe n&rsquo;ibindi. Isaso yongera imikorere y&rsquo;ibinyabuzima biba mu butaka nk&rsquo;iminyorogoto. Isaso kandi ituma ubutaka bumera neza kuburyo bugira imiterere myiza ituma imvura yinjira neza mu butaka, bikanagabanya amazi atemba mu murima. Iyo isaso itangiye kubora byongera ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera iri mu butaka. Imborera kandi niyo ituma ubutaka bugira ya miterere myiza ituma igihingwa kibona ibigitunga mu butaka. Gusasira rero ni ingenza mu guhinga kuko binagira uruhare runini mukurwanya isuri.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu bice bimwe by&rsquo;isi hari aho bakoresha isaso ikoze mu mashashi yabugenewe atangiza ikirere cyangwa bagakoresha amabuye ariko aha tugiye kubagezaho gusasira ukoresheje ibyatsi n&rsquo;ibindi bisigazwa by&rsquo;ibyasaruwe bibora.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ni iyihe mpamvu dusasira?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Kugirango turinde ubutaka isuri itewe n&rsquo;amazi cyangwa n&rsquo;umuyaga ni ukuvuga ko iyo wasasiye ubutaka bwawe buguma hamwe .</li>\r\n	<li>Kongera uburyo amazi y&rsquo;imvura yinjira mu butaka ; nta bidendezi bigaragara mu murima kuko ubutaka bwinjirwa n&rsquo;amazi neza .</li>\r\n	<li>Gutuma ubutaka bugumana ubuhehere kandi bikagabanya amazi asubira mu kirere bitewe n&rsquo;ubushyuhe; ntago ubutaka bwumagana vuba no mu gihe cy&rsquo;impeshyi bushobora gukomeza kuba buhehereye .</li>\r\n	<li>Kugaburira no kwita ku binyabuzima biba mu butaka ; isaso dusasiza ni ibiryo ku binyabuzima biba mu butaka ituma bigira aho kuba habibereye kugirango bikore akazi kabyo mu butaka.</li>\r\n	<li>Kugabanya ibyatsi bimera bidakenewe mu murima; iyo wakoresheje isaso ihagije mu murima ibyatsi bidakenewe mu murima ntago bibona uko bimera bityo ntibibe bicyanjije imyaka wateye.</li>\r\n	<li>Gutanga intungagihingwa n&rsquo;imyunyungugu ku gihingwa; iyo isaso iri kubora itanga mu butaka ibyari biyigize bikaba ibiryo ku gihingwa bigatuma ubutaka bugira intungagihingwa n&rsquo;imyunyungugu bihangije.</li>\r\n	<li>Isaso yongera imborera mu butaka</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Guhitamo isaso</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubwoko bw&rsquo;isaso wakoresheje bugira akamaro kanini mu buryo iyo saso izagirira akamaro ibihingwa ndetse n&rsquo;ubutaka. Isaso ibora vuba izarinda ubutaka mu gihe gito ariko izatanga intungagihingwa nyinshi mu butaka igihe izaba irimo kubora. Isaso itabora vuba izatwikira ubutaka bwawe mu gihe kinini ariko izabora bigoranye kandi itange intungagihingwa nke mu butaka mu gihe iri kubora. Ushaka kongera uburyo bwo kubora kw&rsquo;isaso yawe unyanyagiza amase y&rsquo;inka, ifumbire ivuye mu kiraro cy&rsquo;ingurube itarimo ibyatsi n&rsquo;indi myanda y&rsquo;amatungo hejuru y&rsquo;isaso ibi kandi byongera ingano ya Nitrogen iri mu butaka.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyo ubutaka bwawe ubufite ikibazo cy&rsquo;isuri iri hejuru, isaso itabora vuba ni igisubizo ku kurinda ubutaka bwawe ugereranije n&rsquo;isaso ibora vuba .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Isaso ivahe ?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ibyatsi byameze mu murima bidakenewe</li>\r\n	<li>Ibisigazwa by&rsquo;ibihingwa yasaruwe</li>\r\n	<li>Ibyatsi wakuye ahandi hantu</li>\r\n	<li>Ibisigazwa byo mu buhinzi cyangwa mu nganda zitunganya umusaruro w&rsquo;ubuhinzi</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Inama mugusasira ibihingwa byawe.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nubwo gusasira bifite ibyiza byinshi bishobora no kugira ingaruka mbi rimwe na rimwe</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hari ibinyabuzima bishobora kuza mu murima wawe kubera isaso nyinshi wakoresheje aha twavuga nk&rsquo;imiswa , inshishi n&rsquo;ibimonyo.</li>\r\n	<li>Hari indwara zishobora guhererekanywa bitewe n&rsquo;isaso yakoreshewje yaturutse ku bihingwa birwaye . Iyo ibihingwa byarwaye indwara yandura cyangwa ishobora gukwirakwizwa nicyo gihingwa ntago iyo saso uba ukiyikoresheje . Aha ariko gusimburanya ibihingwa nibyo bituma izi ndwara zidakwirakwizwa cyane kuko udukoko dutera indwara dushobora kuba twaba mu gihingwa runaka ariko ntidushobore kuba mu kindi gihingwa usimbuje icyo wari wahinze.</li>\r\n	<li>Iyo isaso yakoreshejwe ifite Nitrogen nyinshi ibinyabuzima biba mu butaka bishobora gukoresha Nitrogen isanzwe mu butaka kugirango bitume habaho kubora kw&rsquo;isaso , icyo gihe igihingwa wateye gishobora kubura igihe gito Nitrogen gikoresha mu gukura .</li>\r\n	<li>Isaso kandi ikibazo gikomeye nuko kuyibina nabyo bitoroshye , bisaba rimwe na rimwe amafaranga n&rsquo;abakozi benshi bishobora gutuma igiciro cyo guhinga kiba kinini cyane .</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko basasira</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bibaye ibishoboka ugomba gusasira mbere y&rsquo;uko igihe cyo kugwa kw&rsquo;imvura kigera kugirango ubutaka butazangizwa n&rsquo;imvura .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyo isaso ishyizweho mbere yo gutera, ugomba gukora kuburyo ibihingwa kizabasha gushora imizi ikagera mu butaka. Ushobora kandi gusasira nyuma yo guhinga cyangwa kubagara mugihe ibihingwa byawe bisanzwe bihinze. Ugomba gushyira isaso uyizengurutsa ku gihingwa cyane cyane ku bihingwa bizana uruti cyangwa ugasasira umurima wose .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Byateguwe na<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/etienne-niyigaba-b75b6142\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\"> NIYIGABA Etienne</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hifashishijwe imfashanyigisho za FAO</p>\r\n\r\n<p>teca.fao.org</p>\r\n','1',2331,3,'2016-05-15 01:54:23','Gusasira ',0,'online','',''),(228,'Rwanda hosted the biggest event for African Agriculture -Click once , get all stories fromÂ AASW7','aasw7.png','<p>On 13<sup><span style=\"font-size:small\"><sup>th</sup> </span></sup>&ndash; 16<sup>th</sup> June 2016 in Kigali Rwanda held the 7<sup><span style=\"font-size:small\">th</span></sup> Africa Agriculture Science Week (AASW7) and FARA (Forum for Agriculture Research in Africa) general assembly. It was the first time for Rwanda to host a so important agriculture event like this.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The AASW and FARA General Assembly is the principal forum for all stakeholders in African agriculture science, technology and innovation to take stock of their collective achievements over the past three years and craft a common agenda along with modalities for achieving their collective targets over the next three years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The event was focused on the operationalization of the Science Agenda for Agriculture in Africa at country level. Thus its overall theme was &ldquo;Apply Science, Impact Livelihoods&rdquo;. The content was being organized around the following five sub-themes:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Institutional systems and policies for making science work for African agriculture</li>\r\no<li>Sustainable productivity growth, value chains and profitable agribusinesses</li>\r\no<li>Human capital development and the Youth</li>\r\no<li>Sustainable financing of Science, Technology and Innovation for African agriculture</li>\r\no<li>Megatrends in African Agriculture</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>The event was featuring distinguished keynote speakers, plenary sessions, an exhibition /trade fair, parallel side meetings, the Rwanda day (when the host country was showcasing its achievements in agricultural research and innovation) and a business session of the FARA General Assembly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>AASW serves as a forum for stakeholders and partners in Agriculture sector to refresh and re-affirm a shared vision for Agriculture research for development (AR4D), take stock of their collective achievements on the commitments undertaken; is an all-encompassing planning session providing a unique opportunity for collegial assemblage of all stakeholders with interests in Africa&rsquo;s AR4D. Almost all major stakeholders in Africa and beyond have been represented in AASW7</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There was more than 1000 participants in this event most of them were researchers, agriculturist, farmers, business people that invest in agribusiness and other different partners in agriculture sector in Africa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In his remarks opening this 7<sup><span style=\"font-size:small\">th</span></sup> agriculture science week President Akinwumi Adesina of the African Development Bank appreciated what FARA is doing by mobilizing research, technology and innovation for the agriculture development in Africa. He argue AASW7 participants to look on how Africa should transform its agriculture sector into a wealth creating and economy improvement sector</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Forum for Agricultural Research in Africa (FARA) has honored Dr. Akinwumi Adesina, President of the African Development Bank (AfDB) with a leadership prize for advancing agriculture, science, technology and innovation in Africa .The award was presented to him on behalf of FARA by His Excellency Anastase Murekezi, Rwandan Prime Minister at the opening ceremony. The FARA leadership prize is the organization&rsquo;s highest award presented to deserving individuals who have demonstrated outstanding contributions to the advancement of agricultural research for the development of Africa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As young farmers matters for African Agriculture , during the week was organized an African Agribusiness Incubator Network (AAIN) side event. AAIN is an initiative supported by FARA under the universities, businesses and research in agribusiness innovation program with the core mandate of &ldquo;strengthening agribusiness incubation capacity as well as commercializing agricultural technologies and innovation in Africa. The theme was &ldquo;youth engagement in agribusiness, trade and investment in Africa&rdquo;. We had different discussions with different speakers. The amazing one was testimonial from two young from youth representatives; one from Uganda who runs a small industry of juice and another young ladies from Rwanda who with a company of peanut butter and honey production. The Rwandan lady with a very good presentation called attention of every participant and The AAIN representative fund them with 5000 USD.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The AASW7 was attended by Social media reporters mainly from YPARD Rwanda and YEAN Rwanda where they were reporting the whole event on social media like twitter, facebook and blog. The social reporting team was trained on social media and live reporting by a professional mentor form CGAIR and member of YPARD that led them to publish</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On twitter: 16,801 #AASW7 tweets, sent by 1,517 contributors, delivered to 3.2 million Twitter users</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>On facebook:</strong> 87,918 people mentioned #AASW7 on Facebook. Also this is very high and shows an excellent engagement. You can get more and lead about #AASW7 here: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/search/latest/?q=%23aasw7\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">https://www.facebook.com/search/latest/?q=%23aasw7</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>On the blog:</strong> More have 31 AASW7 blogposts have been created and posted online: <a href=\"https://faraafrica.wordpress.com/\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">https://faraafrica.wordpress.com</span></a>/ . In the past week, these blogs have been read by 1,200 different people</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>VLogs:</strong> Video blogs are online on the FARA Youtube channel: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCEJQGxNwCCFuEHCTDOljeqg\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCEJQGxNwCCFuEHCTDOljeqg</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>All these figures are from the FARA online social platform admin and social media reporters mentor Peter Casier</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Participants had time to attended different pre-plenary session in various side events and come up with different recommendation some of them highlighted here below:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The African agriculture concept should seek to gainfully involve youth and change attitude of youth to agriculture to take it as punishment but considering it as a source of income</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Through different sessions on youth and Agribusiness and value chain they have realized challenges and barriers that face youth in agriculture value chain and agribusiness which are:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Access to land</li>\r\no<li>Markets</li>\r\no<li>Policy involvement</li>\r\no<li>Inadequate to finance and poor infrastructure</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Article prepared by <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/etienne-niyigaba\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Niyigaba Etienne</span></a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/nirosine\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Nishimwe Rosine</span></a> , <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ShemaFred4\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Shema Fred</span></a> , <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BeninkaG\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Beninka Gerardine</span></a></p>\r\n','1',1480,3,'2016-06-25 21:34:26','News Amakuru',0,'online','',''),(229,'Uburyo bwo guhinga usimburanya ibihingwa , akamaro kabyo, impamvu tubikora ','gusimburanya ibihingwa rotation.gif','<p>Ubu buryo ni uburyo bw&rsquo;ibanze mu buhinzi bufasha kubungabunga ubutaka . Guhinga usimburanya ibihingwa ni uburyo bwo gusimburanya ibihingwa bitandukanye ku butaka bumwe mu bihimbwe by&rsquo;ibihinga bikurikirana, hakurikizwa ibyo umuhinzi yifuza kugeraho mu gukurikiranya ibihingwa mu murima we. Ubu buryo bufasha mu kugabanya isuri mu mirima, kongera uburumbuke w&rsquo;ubutaka no kongera umusaruro.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Guhinga igihingwa kimwe mu murima umwe mu gihe kirerekire bituma ubutaga bugunduka kuberako igihingwa gikenera ibintu bimwe mu butaka iyo bishizemo ntabwo igihingwa gikomeza kwihanganira kwera kitabonamo ibigitunga , ariko iyo uhinduye ugahinga kuri ubwo butaga ikindi gihingwa , bitewe nuko ibihingwa bikenera itungagihingwa zitandukanye , iki uhateye gifata za ntungagihingwa icyambere kitakoresheje kuko arizo gikeneye gusa hanyuma ugasanga igihingwa gishishe rwose. Ubu buryo kandi butuma ibisigazwa by&rsquo;igihingwa gisaruwe bisigara mu murima bivamo imborera ibyara intungagihingwa z&rsquo;igihingwa kigiye kuhingwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hari amahame y&rsquo;ingenzi atatu agenga gusimburanya ibihingwa (Cook and Ellis, 1987):</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Gusimburanya ibihingwa ni byiza cyane kurusha guhinga igihingwa kimwe buri gihe nubwo igihingwa waba usimburanyije nacyo cyaba kiba mu muryango umwe w&rsquo;ibihingwa n&rsquo;icyo gisimbuye .</li>\r\no<li>Uburyo bwiza bwo gusimburanya ibihingwa n&rsquo;uburyo buzanamo Ibihingwa bijyanye n&rsquo;ibinyamisogwe.</li>\r\no<li>Gusimburanya ibihingwa ubwabyo ntibihagije kugirango bitange umusaruro mwiza mu gihe kirekire. Bivuzeko kongeramo ifumbire mu murima nabyo bikenerwa.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibyo kwitaho mugutegura uburyo bwo gusimburanya ibihingwa .</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Buri gihe tekereza ku buryo bwo kongera imborera y&rsquo;ibisigazwa by&rsquo;ibihingwa mu murima wawe . Aha ibihingwa bibyara ibisigazwa byinshi byitabwaho kugirango byongere nyine iyo mborera mu butaka bukomeze bugire intungagihingwa zihagije n&rsquo;ubuhehere bwinshi.</li>\r\no<li>Igihingwa kimwe ntago kijya gihingwa ku butaka bumwe mu bihembwe by&rsquo;ihinga bikurikirana.</li>\r\no<li>Ibihingwa uteye bigomba kuba byihanganira ikirere cy&rsquo;aho uri kubitera , byaba yemwe n&rsquo;ibyatsi bizana ifumbire mu murima .</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hagomba kwitwa ku ngaruka igihingwa kigira ku kindi kizagikurikira:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Kureba niba ibihingwa byishimirana hagati yabyo</li>\r\no<li>Uburyo igihingwa kihanganira indwara n&rsquo;ibyonnyi bituruka kucyakibanjirije</li>\r\no<li>Uburyo igihingwa kibyara ibisigazwa bisigara mu murima.</li>\r\no<li>Kureba ibijyanye n&rsquo;ubwoko bw&rsquo;imizi y&rsquo;ibihingwa</li>\r\no<li>Kureba intungagihingwa zikenerwa na buri bwokobw&rsquo;igihingwa</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibyiza byo guhinga ukurikiranya ibihingwa </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Iyo hakoreshejwe ubu buryo , Ibihingwa byinshi bigaragaza gutanga umusaruro mwiza</li>\r\no<li>Ubu buryo butuma habaho kugabanya indwara n&rsquo;ibyonnyi by&rsquo;ibihingwa ndetse no kugabanya ibyatsi bimera mu murima bidakenewe kubera bya bisigazwa by&rsquo;igihingwa cyasaruwe bikora nk&rsquo;isaso mu murima.</li>\r\no<li>Ubu buryo kandi butanga ingaruka nziza ku kubungabunga ubwiza bw&rsquo;ubutaka (imizi y&rsquo;igihingwa ikaba myinshi kandi ikinjira mu butaka kure), bikanongera ibikorwa by&rsquo;utunyabuzima tuba mu butaka.</li>\r\no<li>Muri ubu buryo birashoboka ko wagabanya amafaranga ukoresha mu gutunganya imirima yawe kandi ukagira uburyo bufatika bw&rsquo;ingengabihe y&rsquo;ubuhinzi bwawe.</li>\r\no<li>Ubu buryo kandi bushobora kugabanya Ibiza bikomoka ku mihindukire y&rsquo;ikirere n&rsquo;ibihe kuko ibihingwa bibyihanganira ku buryo butandukanye.</li>\r\no<li>Ubu buryo butuma umuhinzi ahorana umusaruro wiyongera bitewe n&rsquo;uburyo ubutaka buhora bufite intungagihingwa zikenewe.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Uburyo bwo gusimburanya ibihingwa ni buryo bwizewe kandi buhendutse bwo kugabanya indwara n&rsquo;ibyonnyi by&rsquo;ibihingwa. Ubu buryo kandi butuma ubutaka buhorana intungagihingwa zikenewe kuko buhorana ibisigazwa by&rsquo;ibihingwa byasaruwe .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Guhitamo uburyo ibihingwa bikurikirana</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubundi ibi biterwa n&rsquo;intego umuhinzi afite ishora kuba kurwanya ibyatsi bimera bidakenewe, kongera intungagihingwa zikenewe mu butaka n&rsquo;imyunyungugu nka Nitrogen (N), Kurwanya isuri, kongera imborera mu butaka, kurwanya indwara runaka n&rsquo;ibindi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Byateguwe na <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/etienne-niyigaba\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">NIYIGABA Etienne </span></a>&nbsp;. Hifashishijwe imfashanyigisho za FAO/TECA</p>\r\n','1',2494,3,'2016-07-31 05:12:32','Ubuhinzi Bwacu',0,'online','',''),(232,'Amabwiriza ya Minisitiri w\'ubuhinzi n\'ubworozi ku bihembwe by\'ihinga bya 2017 A na B','amabwiriza ya Minisitiri 2017AB.JPG','<p>Muri gahunda y&rsquo;imbaturabukungu mu buhinzi ishingira ahanini mu guhinga ibihingwa byatoranyijwe hakurikijwe aho bihingwa , abahinzi bagezwaho ifumbire n&rsquo;imbuto ku giciro gito aho leta ibishingira mu kwishyura igice kimwe cy&rsquo;ifumbire n&rsquo;imbuto.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mbere yo gutangira buri gihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga abahinzi ndetse n&rsquo;abacuruza izi nyongeramusaruro bakurikiza amabwiriza atangwa na Minisitiri ku bubyerekeranye na gahunda ya Nkunganire muri icyo gihembwe , Ibigo bizaba bishinzwe iby&rsquo;amafumbire, ibizaba bishinzwe iby&rsquo;imbuto ndetse n&rsquo;uburyo bizatangwa .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ku bijyanye n&rsquo;amabwiriza ya Minisitiri y&rsquo;umwaka wa 2017 kanda aha <a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/amabwiriza-ya-seasons-2017-ab_july_-2016.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Amabwiriza ya seasons 2017 A&amp;amp;B_JULY_  2016\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Amabwiriza ya minisitiri igihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga cya 2017A na B</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Muri aya mabwiriza hagaragaramo ko ibigo umunani aribyo byemerewe gutumuza no kugeza ifumbire mvaruganda mu gihungu ku gihe muri Gahunda ya Nkunganire. Hagaragaraho ibiciro byizo fumbire kuburyo nta muhinzi wahendwa. Aya mabwiriza kandi agaragaza ibigo bitatu byemerewe gutumiza hanze y&rsquo;igihugu imbuto y&rsquo;ibihingwa ndetse n&rsquo;ibiciro byazo.</p>\r\n','1',2476,3,'2016-07-16 21:24:43','Amabwiriza',0,'online','',''),(233,'Ni iki urubyiruko rw\'abagoronome n\'abahinzi rutekereza ku guteza imbere ubuhinzi binyuze mu bushakashatsi','IMG-20160921-WA0037.jpg','<p>Urubyiruko ni imbaraga zikomeye z&rsquo;igihugu kandi rumaze kugaragaza ko koko rushoboye aho mu nzego zinyuranye z&rsquo;ubuyobozi ndetse no mu bigo byigenga usanga muri iyi minsi higanjemo urubyiruko , ibi bamwe bavugako biterwa no kuba igihugu cy&rsquo;u Rwanda umubare munini ari urubyiruko abandi bakavugako bitewe n&rsquo;impinduramatwara igihugu kirimo gukora mu nzego zitandukanye ari ngombwa kwifashisha urubyiruko dore ko ari narwo rumenyereye cyane ikoranabuhanga ririmo kugenda ritera imbere mu Rwanda.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubuhinzi nabwo ntibwatanzwe muri uru rugendo aho Igihugu gishaka kuva mu buhinzi bwa Gakondo kikagana mu buhinzi Buganisha k&rsquo;ubucuruzi. YEAN nk&rsquo;umuryango uhuza urubyiruko rukora ibikorwa by&rsquo;ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi mu Rwanda washyizeho imbuga zinyuzwaho amakuru ndetse n&rsquo;ibiganiro byihuse (Chat) muri izo mbuga hari Urukorera ku rubuga nkoranyambaga rwa Whatsapp rukaba ruhuza abagoronome n&rsquo;abahinzi 213 baba ari abanyamuryango ba YEAN cyangwa atari bo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kuri icyi cyumweru taliki ya 17 Kanama 2016 wari umunsi mwiza kuri uru rubuga aho hateruwe ikiganiro kibanda kubushakashatsi bukorwa mu buhinzi mu Rwanda n&rsquo;ingaruka bigira ku buzima bw&rsquo;Abahinzi n&rsquo;umusaruro wabo. Ibi byakomotse cyane cyane ku ijambo ryavuzwe na Minisitiri w&rsquo;Ubuhinzi n&rsquo;Ubworozi agira ati: &ldquo;Abashakashatsi dufite mu buhinzi bisa nk&rsquo;aho ntacyo bamaze&rdquo; nkuko tubisanga mu nkuru yanditswe n&rsquo;igitangazamakuru Imvaho Nshya ku mu nama yo kwinenga mu buhinzi, yabereye i Rwamagana.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aba bagoronome ndetse harimo n&rsquo;ababa muri ibi bigo by&rsquo;ubushakashatsi bamwe ntibemeranya na Minisitiri aho bagira bati: &ldquo;Murebe Ku mpande zose, Ese minisiteri itanga byose bikenewe Ku mushakashatsi&hellip;&hellip;.cg ikigo uwo mushakashatsi akorera tutirengagije&hellip;&hellip;..hano hari ababizi cyane badufasha. Abaheruka mw&rsquo; itorero ry&rsquo; ingamburuzabukene batubwira kurushaho&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo; ubushize yiyamye abagronome badashaka kwikoza itaka none ati RAB abashakashatsi. Ikibazo si ukudasoma njye mbona ari imprematation ibura n&rsquo;ubushobozi bwo gushyira finding mubikorwa Niyo wasoma ugahuza ibitabo byose kugirango habe imprematation ni ikibazo, ikindi nta facilities ziboneka kubashakashatsi&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abandi bagahamya ko Ibi byari ugukebura abo ashinzwe mu nshingano ze aho umwe yagize ati:&ldquo;Yabivuze nka nyir&rsquo;urugo ngo bikosorwe ntabwo cyangwa hakorwe impinduka. Nanjye aho kugirango umbaze ikosa narigaragaza mbere y&rsquo;uko urimbaza&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bati byose bipfira mu mashuli yigisha iby&rsquo;Ubuhinzi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngo Hari imishinga ihabwa amafaranga menshi &nbsp;ariko ntigaragaze umusaruro . &hellip;. &ldquo;Image ya research muyihere muri kaminuza zacu. Muby&rsquo;ukuri nta gahunda ihamye dufite&hellip; research projects zirapfa zashowemo menshi. Inzego bireba ariko cyane cyane MINEDUC bazikubite agashyi&rdquo; . Ku rundi ruhande abarangije muri Kaminuza zigisha iby&rsquo;Ubuhinzi n&rsquo;Ubworozi bemezako ubundi Kaminuza yagakwiye kuba izingiro ry&rsquo;ubushakshatsi kuko haba hari intiti zihagije ndetse n&rsquo;abanyeshuli babisobanukiwe, aho bagaragaza ko Abarimu ndetse n&rsquo;abanyeshuli bagakwiye kujya bashyira hanze ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwabo, gusa ngo birakomeye kuko mu gihe cyo gukora ubushakashatsi busoza amashuli ya Kaminuza nta mafaranga mafaranga ahabwa umunyeshuli ndetse n&rsquo;ibikoresho ngo abukore bikarangira akoze mubyo abashije Kugirango mwalimu abone aho ahera amuha manota iyi akaba ari nayo mpamvu ngo nta bushakashatsi bw&rsquo;umunyeshuli wa Kaminuza buhabwa agaciro.Uyu aragira ati: &ldquo; Wakora research ntamafaranga, ko utanga research proposal !! Bakayibona ariko kubikora nikibazo,Urabona umunyeshuli kwikura 300000frw ari gukora research biragoye nta mafaranga rwose!!&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibigo bishinzwe ubushakashatsi n&rsquo;abashinzwe iyamamazabuhinzi nibo kibazo.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aha bamwe bagaragaza ko abashakasatsi badakora neza akazi bashinzwe ngo ndetse bamwe usanga nta bushobozi bafite abandi ugasanga bafite ubushobozi ndetse n&rsquo;ibyangombwa bisabwa ariko ugasanga ngo ibiva muri ubwo bushakashatsi iyo bigeze mu bahinzi usanga byateje ikibazo cy&rsquo;Umusaruro muke cyane bitewe n&rsquo;indwara ahanini aha hatanzwe urugero rw&rsquo;imyumbati ndetse n&rsquo;ibigori bimaze iminsi byibasirwa n&rsquo;indwara zikomeye kandi abahinzi bakagaraza ko imbuto bazihawe n&rsquo;ikigo cy&rsquo;igihugu gishinzwe ubushashatsi mu buhinzi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abandi kandi bemezaga ko abashakashatsi baba bakoze akazi kabo ngo hakurikirao ibikorwa by&rsquo;iyamamazabuhinzi aribyo bisakaza iyi mbuto mu bahinzi gusa aha ntago bose babivugaho rumwe kuko byaba byaturutse kubashakashatsi cyangwa byaturutse ahandi nubundi ngo ingaruka zigaruka k&rsquo;ubahinzi. Uyu yagize ati &ldquo;Njye ubwanjye niyumviye umuturage arira avuga uburyo yatse inguzanyo &nbsp;ya 17 million yose ikaba ihombye yarahinze imbuto yahawe na RAB, icyo RAB yamusubije baramubwiye ngo yihangane bazamubwirira bank imwongerere igihe&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Muri iki kiganiro kandi abagoronome bagaragaje ko ngo hari ibigo bimwe by&rsquo;ubushakashatsi bitagikora neza nka mbere yuko&nbsp; bibumbirwa mu kigo kimwe cya RAB , aha hagarutswe kuri ISAR Ruhande(Arboretum),ISAR Tamira, ISAR Rubona, ISAR Rwerere aho uyu yabivuze agira ati: &rdquo;Murebe ahantu hose hakorerwaga ubushakashatsi, za isar tamira, rwerere, rubona n&rsquo;ahandi ntarondoye harimo za Nyanza kibirizi, nyamagabe na nyaruguru, nta bakozi bakihaba ngo ntibari bashoboye&rdquo; Undi Ati:&rdquo; Yes izo station zimwe zirafunze abakoragamo benshi barirukanwe, abagize amahirwe yo gusigaramo nabo bakorera mu biro, nihe mwabonye umuhinzi ukorera mu biro icyumweru kigashira ukwezi kugataha!!! Ejo bundi twahuraga n&rsquo;abakora muri domaine agricole bose bari kugura bottes bagiye mu ngando, ubwo se agronome CG veto utagira bottes urumva aba akora?&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uyu Nawe ati:&rdquo; Mperuka ka kuri station ya RAB mu kinigi nsanga bahinze amashaza yararengewe n&rsquo;ikigunda k&rsquo;uburyo utari kumenya igihinzemo!!!&nbsp; Unless baba barimo kureba resistance yayo mashaza kuri weeds ubundi byaba arugupfusha ubusa imisoro yacu.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Biyemeje Gukora ibyo bashoboye buhoro buhoro.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nubwo abaganiraga bose ari abagoronome ndetse n&rsquo;abakora mu bigo by&rsquo;ubuhinzi bitandukanye , bagarukaga kubitagenda neza mu Bushakashatsi rwose bananenga cyane ibibuvamo , abenshi nanone bakora muri ibi bigo by&rsquo;ubushakshatsi ndetse birirwa mu mirima bafsha abahinzi mu mirimo ya buri munsi. Bose rero basoje iki kiganiro biyemeje kugira uruhare mu guhindura uburyo ibinengwa bikorwa kuko bavugako hari n&rsquo;ibidasaba ubushobozi buhambaye ariko bigakorwa nabi ndetse nk&rsquo;uko tubikesha ikiganiro Minisitiri&nbsp; yagiranye n&rsquo;abanyamakuru yavuzeko utakwaka umuntu ibitari mu bushobozi bwe, agaragaza ko ibikenewe ngo ubushakashatsi bukore biba byatanzwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Icyo kintu nicyo, kuko research ya RAB nigira ikibazo, ubuhinzi bwurwanda buzahura nikibazo gikomeye, inzara nibindi bitere, kandi bizitirirwa abanyarwanda Bose cyane cyane twe tugaruka mubuhinzi! Buri wese abigiribye, bitabaye ibyo tuzaguma gutyo twitana bamwana&rdquo; Undi ati: &ldquo;Ikindi buri wese hano cyangwa ahandi ngirango twemerewe kugira uruhare rwaba ruziguye cg rutaziguye mu kwerekana aho ibintu bipfira mugihe tubifitiye gihamya .&rdquo; Undi ati: &ldquo;Very true. Igihugu rero ninjye nawe. Let us all say NO and move forward. Uwiga amenye ko ashaka kumenya kandi ko kwiga bihoraho. Aho niho ruzingiye.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hifujweko ibitekerezo byatanzwe byashyirwa ahagaragara</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nyuma yo kuganira , kuberako ibyavugiwe kuri uru rubuga bibonwa n&rsquo;ururiho gusa kandi bakaba bifuzaga ko ibyo bitekerezo byagera no kubo bireba bose, YEAN nka ny&rsquo;ir&rsquo;urubuga yahisemo kuzuza iby&rsquo;ifuzo byabo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aho&nbsp; bagize bati: &ldquo;Hello everyone, Nakomeje gukurikira discussion nziza yabereye hano numva ngize ikibazo :Ese dufitemo abadecision&amp;policy&nbsp; makers hano kuri uru rubuga?abaresearchers ?The idea behind nuko wasanga tuvugira aha bikarangira kandi hari aho bikwiye kugera kugira ngo habeho impinduka.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Juste twasabye Admin ko yajya adushakira umutumirwa umwe cyangwa babiri mu gihe runaka tukajya tugira d&eacute;bat ku kintu runaka then tukabatuma</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Harimo aba Reporters munzego zitandukanye, Gusa nange ndasaba abayobozi Buru rubuga ko bazatumirira abantu bo muri MINAGRI bakaza umunsi umwe tukaganira tuziko bahari<strong>&rdquo;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa: </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byose ntago byagarajwe hano bitewe n&rsquo;uko ari ikiganiro kirekire cyane hagiye hatoranywamo imirongo migari ikavugwa muri make.</li>\r\no<li>Amazina yabatanze ibitekerezo ntago yagaragajwe muri iyi nkuru gusa amagambo yose ari mu utwuguruzo n&rsquo;utwugarizo (&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;) yose yandikuwe uko yanditse mu kiganiro.</li>\r\no<li>Ibiganiro nk&rsquo;ibi hiba buri munsi na buri gihe kuri uru rubuga .</li>\r\no<li>Ushaka gukurikira ibi biganiro ukaba uri umuhinzi cyangwa umugoronome ku rwego urwo ariwro rwose nawe wasaba kujya k&rsquo;urubuga rwa YEAN Whatsapp unyuze kuri nimero ikurikira: +250 788 845 727.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n','1',1993,3,'2016-07-19 06:45:50','Ubuhinzi Bwacu',0,'online','',''),(234,'Itangazo rya MINAGRI rigenewe abahinzi mu gutegura igihembwe cy\'ihinga 2017 A(Umuhindo)','umuhinziw.jpg','<p>Umuhinzi nyawe ni uhingira igihe agakurikiza inama z&rsquo;impuguke mu by&rsquo;ubuhinzi bityo nawe umwero ukazamuhira .Niyo mpamvu rero mu myiteguro y&rsquo;iki gihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga cya 2017A twongeye gushishikarizwa gutegura kare imirima dutunganya neza imirwanyasuri dutegura ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera kuri buri site y&rsquo;ubutaka buhujwe, ndetse n&rsquo;ishwagara ku butaka busharira.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tugomba kandi kwibumbira mumakoperative cyangwa mu matsinda ya twigire y&rsquo;abahinzi hagati ya 15 na 20 hakurikijwe uko imirima yegeranye , tukiyandikisha ntawe ucikanywe kuri lisiti za twigire kugirango tuzabashe kubona inyongeramusaruro bityo binadufashe kugezwaho inama n&rsquo;inyigisho zo guhinga neza.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Inyongeramusaruro turazigurira hafi ku bacuruzi bazo bakorana na APTC Inkeragutabara mu tugari aho buri wese azibona amaze kwishyura uruhare rwe havuyemo nkunganire ya Leta. Ku bijyanye n&rsquo;ifumbire ibihingwa byunganirwa byariyongereye ubu harimo ibigori, <a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.org/2016/02/26/uburyo-bukomatanyije-bwo-kwita-ku-gihingwa-cyibishyimbo-hagamijwe-kongera-umusaruro-ubikomokaho/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">ibishyimbo</span></a>,ingano , <a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.org/2015/04/20/soya-igihingwa-kivamo-ibintu-bitandukanye-tumenye-uko-gihingwa/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">soya</span></a> , <a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.org/2015/03/23/menya-uko-bahinga-umuceri/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">umuceri</span></a> , ibirayi,<a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.org/2015/06/20/imyumbati-dore-uburyo-bwo-kuyihinga-kijyambere/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">imyumbati</span></a>, <a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.org/2015/04/23/urutoki-uyu-munsi-menya-uko-baruhinga/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">urutoki</span></a>, imboga n&rsquo;imbuto zitandukanye. <a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.org/2016/07/22/ibiciro-byimbuto-nifumbire-mu-gihembwe-cyihinga-2017a-na-b/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Ibiciro by&rsquo;amafumbire mvaruganda byarangabanutse</span></a>, ifumbire ya Uree ni amafaranga 355 ku kilo, DAP ni amafaranga 410 ku Kilo naho NPK 17 17 17 ni amafaranga 520. Naho <a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.org/2016/07/22/ibiciro-byimbuto-nifumbire-mu-gihembwe-cyihinga-2017a-na-b/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">ibiciro by&rsquo;imbuto z&rsquo;indobanure</span></a> Ku mbuto z&rsquo;<a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.org/2016/03/15/uburyo-bwo-kubagara-ibigori/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">ibigori</span></a> za hybride zihingwa mu misozi miremire umuhinzi yishyura amafaranga hagati ya 460 na 520 ku kilo naho ku zihingwa mu misozi migufi n&rsquo;ibibaya akishyura amafaranga hagati ya 275 na 310 naho ku mbuto z&rsquo;ibigori bya OPV ho yishyura amafaranga 295. Ku mbuto za <a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.org/2015/04/20/soya-igihingwa-kivamo-ibintu-bitandukanye-tumenye-uko-gihingwa/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">soya</span></a> zose , umubinzi yishyura amafaranga 250 ku kilo , ku mbuto z&rsquo;<a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.org/2015/06/15/ingano-tumenye-uko-zihingwa-ku-buryo-bwa-kijyambere/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">ingano</span></a> zitumizwa mu mahanga akishyura 260 ku kilo , naho izituburirwa mu Rwanda akishyura 300 ku kilo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ku bindi bisobanuro mwakwegera abakozi ba RAB cyangwa abashinzwe ubuhinzi mu Mirenge n&rsquo;uturere kugirango babafashe ,mwanahamagara kandi umurongo wa telefone utishyurwa wa RAB ariwo 4675 cyangwa 4676 . Ngaho rero dukure amaboko mu mifuka dukore , ubutaka bwose bushoboka haba ku misozi, ibishanga bitunganyijwe n&rsquo;amaterasi y&rsquo;indinganire tubibyaze umusaruro twihaze mu biribwa dusagurire n&rsquo;amasoko .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iri tangazo murigejejweho na minisiteri y&rsquo;ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi, ibinyujije mu kigo cy&rsquo;igihugu gishinzwe guteza imbere ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi (RAB)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/amabwiriza-ya-seasons-2017-ab_july_-2016.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Soma amabwiriza ya Minisitiri ajyanye n&rsquo;igihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga 2017A na B</span></a></p>\r\n','1',1689,3,'2016-08-15 21:46:32','Ifumbire, Igihembwe cy\'Ihinga',0,'online','',''),(236,'AGRF2016: Seize the moment: Africa Rising through Agricultural Transformationâ. How was the first day, click once ,get all media coverage about AGRF2016','AGRF 1.png','<blockquote>\r\n<p><strong><em>&ldquo;We have to make agriculture profitable, otherwise farmers will only engage in it for subsistence.&rdquo; Kenya&rsquo;s Cabinet Secretary for Agriculture, Livestock and Fisheries, Willy Bett</em></strong></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p>The AGRF press briefing hosted by the Government of Kenya represented by the Cabinet Secretary for Agriculture, Livestock and Fisheries Willy Bett, Alliance for a Green Revolution Africa (AGRA), The Rockefeller Foundation, International Development Research Centre (IDRC) and Australian Centre for International Agricultural Research (ACIAR) focused on the key objective of this year&rsquo;s forum which is delivering major investments for African agriculture.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The official campaign slogan &ldquo;Seize the moment&rdquo; is expected to bring a world-wide call to action from the United States Agency for International Development (USAID), energized by President Obama&rsquo;s Global Food Security initiative&mdash;the largest development commitment from the administration and one that is aligned closely with the African Union&rsquo;s agriculture agenda.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The conference is very popular so far, there have been<strong> </strong><strong>98</strong><strong> </strong>news stories picked up and over <strong>&shy;1,600</strong><strong> </strong>mentions on social media in the last 24 hours.Using the hashtag &shy; #AGRF2016, <strong>307,502</strong><strong> </strong>accounts were reached within the past 24 hours.Over <strong>645</strong> users tweeted with over <strong>2.7 M</strong> people potentially reached.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TOP NEWS ON PARTNERS</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Business Daily, </strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=2d03b515bf&amp;e=80b13f5918\"><strong><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Sixth AGRA conference to be held at United Nations Complex in Nairobi</span></strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Alliance for a Green Revolution in Africa (AGRA) will host a week-long conference at the United Nations Complex, Nairobi, where African agriculture sector stakeholders will discuss various ways of transforming agriculture into a key driver of socioeconomic development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Star,</strong> <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=f57b40a85e&amp;e=80b13f5918\"><strong><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">North Rift maize diseases: the biggest threat to food security</span></strong></a><strong>, (Written by Stephen Rutto)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Towards the end of each year, jubilation is often palpable among maize farmers in the North Rift, as they prepare for bumper harvests. But this year, the prospects are not looking good. A strange disease outbreak, coupled with doubtful seeds and fertilisers, have hit maize farming in the region hard. As the African Green Revolution (Agra) Forum begins in Nairobi today, many maize farmers are staring at hunger and poverty as a low harvest looms.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Leadership (Nigeria), </strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=9e542af867&amp;e=80b13f5918\"><strong><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">East Meets West: Promoting African Agricultural Integration</span></strong></a><strong>, (Written by Ade Adefeko)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The theme of this year&rsquo;s summit is Seize the Moment: Securing Africa&rsquo;s Rise through Agricultural Transformation is very apt as it delves into the very heart of our Food security conversation on the continent and questions our dependence and long term sustainability of fossils fuels to the detriment of Agriculture. This year the forum is focusing on promoting investments, public/private opportunities and policy support for driving the vision contained in the African Declaration on Agriculture and Food Security.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Capital FM, </strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage2.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=e4c5caeea9&amp;e=80b13f5918\"><strong><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Agriculture contribution to GPD in Africa declining</span></strong></a><strong>, (Written by Kennedy Kangethe)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Agriculture contribution to Gross Domestic Product (GDP) in Africa has continued to deteriorate in the last five years. According to Rockefeller Foundation Africa Managing Director Mamadou Biteye, the agricultural sector in Africa has been diminishing as countries remain adamant in investing in the sector.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bloomberg, </strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=f2171c5b55&amp;e=80b13f5918\"><strong><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Africa may need $400 billion to improve agriculture, AGRA says</span></strong></a><strong>, (Written by Samuel Bebre)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Africa may need as much as $400 billion of investment in food production over the next decade to meet the continent&rsquo;s needs, a report showed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NEWS OF INTEREST</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ventures Africa, </strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=1f7de008c8&amp;e=80b13f5918\"><strong><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">finding the sweet spot of Africa&rsquo;s agriculture</span></strong></a><strong>, (Maria Andrade)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Africa is a continent where, at least outwardly, we like to celebrate our diversity &ndash; the rich variety that can be found in our many cultures, languages, fashion, flora and fauna. That&rsquo;s why it&rsquo;s perplexing to see such a large segment of the African population depending on a very small number of food crops like maize, rice, and wheat. And it&rsquo;s more than just boring to the palate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>News Ghana, </strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=303d39fa30&amp;e=80b13f5918\"><strong><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Africa urged to invest in smallholder food production</span></strong></a><strong>, (Xinhua &amp; News Ghana)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Food security experts on Monday called on Africa to incorporate multisector and interdisciplinary investment approaches in smallholder food production and reduction of post-harvest loss.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TOP BLOGS &amp; URLs &ndash; AFRICA FOCUS</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage2.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=23a3f24e4a&amp;e=80b13f5918\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">4 ways to end hunger in Africa</span></a> &ndash; Written by Kofi Annan, Chair of the Kofi Annan Foundation and Former Secretary-General of the United Nations (5<sup><span style=\"font-size:small\">th</span></sup> September 2016)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=313971c8ea&amp;e=80b13f5918\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">AGRF 2016: African Leaders &lsquo;Seize The Moment&rsquo; to Harness the Potential of Agriculture in Promoting Long-Term Economic Growth</span></a> &ndash; Written by Felicia Omari Ochelle, Ventures Africa (5<sup><span style=\"font-size:small\">th</span></sup> September 2016)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=131a6fc793&amp;e=80b13f5918\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">New investments in support of African agriculture expected at AGRF</span></a> 2016 &ndash; Written by Kofi Adu Domfeh, Development Arena (5<sup><span style=\"font-size:small\">th</span></sup> September 2016)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=ad5d3bcd3f&amp;e=80b13f5918\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Africa Eyes Science and Innovation to Unlocking its Agriculture Potential</span></a> &ndash; Written by David Indeje, Soko Directory (5<sup><span style=\"font-size:small\">th</span></sup> September 2016)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hosted by The Alliance for a Green Revolution in Africa (AGRA) ,the 2016 AGRF is bringing together heads of state and government, farmer organizations, business leaders and captains of industry, eminent thought leaders, development partners, researchers, and finance &amp; investment leads. The delegates will share their insights on how to create, align and leverage financial, technical, policy and market-expanding resources to develop game-changing and inclusive agribusiness models for Africa. This year&rsquo;s event will consist of plenary sessions, break-out sessions, B2B meetings, the Africa Food Prize and informal networking opportunities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Invited speakers include: H.E. Uhuru Kenyatta President of the Republic of Kenya; Dr. Akinwumi Adesina, African Development Bank; Dr. Rob Smith, Vice President, AGCO; Svein Tore Holsether, YARA President and CEO; Mr. Strive Masiyiwa, AGRA Board Chair, and Dr Agnes Kalibata, AGRA President</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Written by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/NiyigabaEtienne\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">NIYIGABA Etienne</span></a> (niyigabat@gmail.com)&nbsp;in collaboration with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jndayambaje\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Jean Claude Ndayambaje</span></a> (jndayambaje@outlook.com)</em></p>\r\n','1',14138,3,'2016-09-06 21:34:46','News Amakuru',0,'online','',''),(237,'AGRF2016:Seize the moment: Africa Rising through Agricultural Transformation Day 3&4 top media coverage and stories','AGRF 2 .png','<div><em>&ldquo;I have seen the power of investments to help individuals and whole communities to change their future&rdquo; </em><strong>Kanayo F. Nwanze, IFAD President and Winner of the 2016 African Food Priz</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div>The 2016 African Green Revolution Forum (AGRF 2016) was officially opened yesterday by H.E. Uhuru Kenyatta, President of the Republic of Kenya. The Grand Ceremony was also graced by H.E. Paul Kagame, President of the Republic of Rwanda, Tanzania&rsquo;s former President Jakaya Kikwete, former Nigeria President Olusegun Obasanjo and African Union Commissioner Rhoda Peace.\r\n<p>&ldquo;Let African governments streamline their national plans and strategies to align them to the Malabo Declaration and have specific timelines to achieve the set goals,&rdquo; President Kenyatta said during his speech&hellip;<a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=23df36b7cc&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Read speech</span></a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>TOP 10 CLIPPINGS IN PRINT &amp; ONLINE MEDIA<br />\r\n<strong>Business Daily, <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=7b23aeab7f&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Africa can improve yields, nutrition by raising investment </span></a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>African countries that took early action in the past decade to invest in agriculture have reaped the rewards, enjoying higher economic growth and a bigger drop in malnutrition, a major farming development organisation said on Tuesday.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Daily Nation, <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=b7dfe1f9e4&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Forum pushes for higher investment in agriculture</span></a>, (Written by Leopold Obi)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>African leaders and think tanks issued a common call to push the region&rsquo;s investments in agriculture to the next level in the next five years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The People Daily, <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=f5a3701837&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Kenya to pump Sh20b in agriculture, says Uhuru</span></a>, (Written by George Kebaso and Fred Aminga</strong>)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Kenyan government will invest Sh20 billion ($200 million) in the agriculture sector over the next five years to enable farmers access finance, farm inputs, technology and machinery in what is expected to spur agro-processing in the country.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Standard, <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=53fd3a8ada&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Uhuru&rsquo;s Sh20b shot in the arm to boost agriculture</span></a>, (Written by Protus Onyango)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Farmers in Kenya will now be able to access Sh51 billion to improve their farming activities after President Uhuru Kenyatta said his government had set aside Sh20 billion ($200 million) to invest in agriculture in the next five years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ventures Africa, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=4921a93979&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">watch live: AGRF 2016 day 3 symposium</span></a>, (Written by </strong><strong>Fumnanya Agbugah</strong><strong>)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The sixth edition of the African Green Revolution Forum (AGRF) is taking place in Nairobi, Kenya, at the United Nations Complex from the 5th to 9th of May 2016. The forum, themed &ldquo;Seize the Moment: Securing Africa&rsquo;s Rise through Agricultural Transformation,&rdquo; is attended by over 1500 delegates, the largest number of AGRF participants ever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Star, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=1c5213d55f&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Focus on smallholder farmers for food security, state told</span></a>, (Written by John Muchangi)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The thousands of small-scale farmers in the villages remain Kenya&rsquo;s hope for food security and sustained economic growth, leaders have said.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Coomod Africa,</strong> <strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=793862c91c&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">A Nairobi, on planche sur la r&eacute;volution agricole en Afrique</span></a>, (Written by Par Commod Africa)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Apr&egrave;s des d&eacute;cennies de stagnation, la plupart de l&rsquo;Afrique a enregistr&eacute; une croissance soutenue de la productivit&eacute; agricole depuis 2005&rdquo;, souligne un rapport de l&rsquo;Alliance pour une r&eacute;volution verte en Afrique (Agra, de son sigle anglais) pr&eacute;sent&eacute; hier, &agrave; Nairobi, &agrave; l&rsquo;ouverture du 6&egrave;me Forum sur la r&eacute;volution verte en Afrique (AGRF), intitul&eacute; &ldquo;Seize the Moment: Securing Africa&rsquo;s Rise Through Agricultural Transformation&rdquo;. Quelque 1500 personnes venues de 40 pays participent &agrave; cet &eacute;v&egrave;nement qui dure toute la semaine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Biz Community,</strong> <strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=e550169c87&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Agriculture contribution to GPD in Africa declining</span></a>, (Written by Kennedy Kangethe)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Agriculture contribution to Gross Domestic Product (GDP) in Africa has continued to deteriorate in the last five years. According to Rockefeller Foundation Africa managing director Mamadou Biteye, the agricultural sector in Africa has been diminishing as countries remain adamant in investing in the sector.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The New Times, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=1ab6f3db9d&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Agriculture can shape Africa&rsquo;s development path, says Kagame</span></a>, (Written by Collins Mwai)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>President Kagame was speaking, yesterday, at the African Green Revolution Forum (AGRF) in Nairobi, Kenya, during a panel session alongside Kenyan President Uhuru Kenyatta and Rhoda Tumusiime, the African Union commissioner for rural development and agriculture.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Anadolu Agency, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=1cffc1b322&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">&lsquo;$60 billion&rsquo; pledged for Africa agriculture</span></a>, (Written by Magdalene Mukami)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Heads of state were among the figures which met at the African Green Revolution Forum (AGRF) at UN headquarters in the Kenyan capital, Nairobi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TOP CLIPPINGS IN ELECTRONIC NEWS<br />\r\n<strong>CNBC Africa, <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=bdd2634604&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">interview: David Ameyaw, Lead Author, African Agriculture Status Report 2016, AGRA</span></a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>David Ameyaw, Lead Author, African Agriculture Status Report 2016, AGRA discusses about the agriculture report.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Citizen TV, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=6c7ca1995e&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Farmer extension slowing down agriculture growth</span></a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lack of Farmer extension services to most farmers in the country has being named as what is slowing down agriculture growth in the country.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NTV, <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=8a6cb282ff&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">live coverage: African Green Revolution Forum</span></a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The feature was focused on the African Green Revolution Forum which was officially opened by President Uhuru Kenyatta in Nairobi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>KTN, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=f43df4a626&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">African government&rsquo;s urged to finance small scale farmers</span></a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>African governments have been challenged to scale up funding&rsquo;s to small holder farmers if the continent is to experience a green revolution and feed its fast growing population</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TOP NEWS ON PARTNERS<br />\r\n<strong>The Post, <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=9739da54ae&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Africa loses $35 billion annually through food imports &ndash; AGRA</span></a>, (Written by Chambwa Moonga)</strong><br />\r\nKenya&rsquo;s ministry of Agriculture, Livestock and Fisheries Cabinet Secretary Willy Bett says realistic industrialisation in African countries will not happen if it is not agro-based.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Africa News,</strong> <strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=4eded05c83&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Nigerian wins $100,000 &lsquo;Africa Food Prize&rsquo; award</span></a>, (Written by </strong><strong>Abdur Rahman Alfa Shaban)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dr Kanayo Nwanze has been adjudged the winner of the inaugural &lsquo;Africa Food Prize&rsquo; award. He was awarded for his courageous leadership in fostering solidarity with Africa&rsquo;s small-scale farmer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Capital FM, <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=1b72738e53&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Africa losing Sh400bn yearly in post-harvest losses</span></a>, (Written by Kennedy Kangethe)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>International Fund for Agriculture Development President Konayo Nwanze attributes this to poor storage facilities on the continent that urgently needs to be addressed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>New Mail, <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=c20f221e1f&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Root Capital, MasterCard Foundation to increase incomes for 300,000 farmers in West Africa</span></a>, (Written by Kayode Ogundele)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Foundation has committed $5.2 million to Root Capital over five years to support early-stage agricultural businesses that generate transformational impact in rural communities in C&ocirc;te d&rsquo;Ivoire, Ghana, and Senegal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aljazeera, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=07819a3e96&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">How can food security in Africa be achieved?</span></a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Alliance for a Green Revolution (AGRA) says that agricultural productivity over the past 10 years has improved lives in Ghana, Rwanda, Ethiopia and Burkina Faso.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Business Day Live, <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=bafe093da2&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Why early investment in farming is vital for Africa</span></a>, (Written by Isaiah Esipisu)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>African countries that took early action in the past decade to invest in agriculture have reaped the rewards, enjoying higher economic growth and a bigger drop in malnutrition, a major farming development organisation said on Tuesday</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NEWS OF INTEREST</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mail &amp;Guardian, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=a03b322208&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Africa urgently needs to be part of the microbial revolution sweeping through farming</span></a>,</strong><br />\r\n<strong>(Written by Dumi Gumbi)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not too many years ago, global health advocates bemoaned the fact that it took decades for lifesaving vaccines to become widely accessible in poorer countries. This resulted in the unnecessary deaths of millions of children every year.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bloomberg, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=e03100af21&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">small is better in Africa&rsquo;s economies as biggest nations stumble</span></a>, (Written by Hellen Nyambura Mwaura)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>East African nations are playing an increasing role in driving growth in the world&rsquo;s poorest continent as they ride a wave of cheap oil, slowing inflation and lower interest rates. Left behind: Former powerhouses Nigeria and South Africa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TOP BLOGS &amp; URLs &ndash; AFRICA FOCUS<br />\r\n<strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage2.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=d475879b55&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"New Report Finds Ten Years On, African Countries that Embraced Agriculture Saw Food Production, GDP and Nutrition All Improve\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">New Report Finds Ten Years On, African Countries that Embraced Agriculture Saw Food Production, GDP and Nutrition All Improve</span></a></strong><strong>, Smart farmer Magazine</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A decade of intense domestic attention to farmers and food production has generated &ldquo;the most successful development effort&rdquo; in African history, with countries that made the biggest investments rewarded with sizeable jumps in both farm productivity and overall economic performance, according to a new report released today by the Alliance for a Green Revolution in Africa (AGRA).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=f48f677eab&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">AfDB shares its long term agenda for continental agriculture and agribusiness development at African revolution forum</span></a>, Kitomari banking and finance blog</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The African Development Bank discusses its bold agenda to transform Africa&rsquo;s agriculture and agribusiness long-term wealth creation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage2.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=787b7a72e7&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">One in five Africans are underfed due to climate impact on farming</span></a>, Anatao picked from the standard</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>According to the report released at the ongoing Africa Green Revolution Forum (AGRF) conference at UN, Gigiri, a projected rise in extreme weather conditions and average temperatures of about two degree Celsius by mid-century could substantially reduce the land suitable for growing the main staple crops, and reduce crop yields by up to 20 per cent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=5d0ee1b7f6&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">New Report Makes a Strong Case for Betting Big on Agriculture in Africa</span></a>, </strong><strong>Med Africa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As the African Green Revolution Forum (AGRF) kicked off this sept. 6 in Nairobi, with the participation of heads of state and high-level officials from around the world, a new report revealed that the countries which invested in agriculture were rewarded with sizeable jumps in both farm productivity and overall economic performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Written by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/NiyigabaEtienne\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">NIYIGABA Etienne</span></a> (niyigabat@gmail.com) in collaboration with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jndayambaje\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Jean Claude Ndayambaje</span></a> (jndayambaje@outlook.com)</em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n','1',1984,3,'2016-09-08 22:05:13','News Amakuru',0,'online','',''),(238,'AGRF2016 : Seize the moment: Africa Rising through Agricultural Transformation Day 5 top media coverage and stories','AGRF 3.png','<blockquote>\r\n<p><em>&ldquo;African countries ought to view the agriculture sector as the backbone of their economies and agent for transformation,&rdquo; </em><strong>H.E Paul Kagame, President of the Republic of Rwanda</strong></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p>Following the official opening of the sixth African Green Revolution Forum (AGRF), it was a great moment for African agriculture as African leaders, businesses, and major development partners pledged more than US $30 billion dollars in investments to increase production, income and employment for smallholder farmers and local African agriculture businesses over the next ten years. The collective pledges at AGRF 2016 are believed to represent the largest package of financial commitments to the African agricultural sector to date, backed by the broadest coalitions ever assembled in support of food production on the continent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TOP 10 CLIPPINGS IN PRINT &amp; ONLINE MEDIA</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ghana Business News, <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=3ab06e4220&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">African countries promised $30b investments in agriculture</span></a>, (Written by Emmanuel K. Dogbevi)</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,\'helvetica neue\',helvetica,sans-serif\">African leaders, businesses and international donors have made promises to contributing a total of $30 billion to the continent&rsquo;s agriculture sector at the ongoing sixth African Green Revolution Forum (AGRF), in Nairobi, Kenya.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>EIN News, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=1f89a83601&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">African Leaders urge to invest more in Agriculture</span></a></strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,\'helvetica neue\',helvetica,sans-serif\">H.E. Tumusiime Rhoda Peace, AUC Commissioner for Rural Economy and Agriculture, yesterday joined Kenyan President H.E. Uhuru Kenyatta and President of Rwanda, H.E. Paul Kagame at a presidential panel on transforming African agriculture, during the official opening ceremony of the Alliance for a Green Revolution Forum 2016, in Nairobi, Republic of Kenya.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Ventures Africa, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=152bcb04c9&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">The role of smallholder farmers in sustaining the progress of agricultural transformation in Africa</span></a>, (Written by </strong><strong>Felicia Omari Ochelle</strong><strong>)</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,\'helvetica neue\',helvetica,sans-serif\">In recent times, stakeholders in Africa&rsquo;s agricultural sector have laid the foundations for a renaissance in agriculture across the continent; one powered by the enormous progress increasingly evident in farmers who are gaining more options in the seeds they plant, in the fertilisers they use, and in the markets available to purchase their produce. Farmers also have better access to markets, farming has also fast become more commercialised and productive.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Capital FM, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=d4127edced&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Kenya investing 6 percent of budget to agriculture</span></a>, (Written by (Kennedy Kangethe)</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,\'helvetica neue\',helvetica,sans-serif\">Agriculture Cabinet Secretary Willy Bett says the country is committed to achieving the 10 percent investment of national budget to agriculture as agreed at the Maputo Declaration on Agriculture and Food Security in 2003.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>The Post, <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=de6899e071&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Zambia&rsquo;s tea industry can grow the economy &ndash; Kenyan farmer</span></a>, (Written by Chambwa Moonga)</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,\'helvetica neue\',helvetica,sans-serif\">Moi Wanyama, in an interview at the ongoing sixth edition of the African Green Revolution Forum (AGRF) on agriculture in Nairobi, explained that if well harnessed, Zambia&rsquo;s tea industry could add significance to the country&rsquo;s economy.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>The Star,</strong> <strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,\'helvetica neue\',helvetica,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=99145429d7&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">African farmers to get Sh 3 trillion pledges, Uhuru to give Sh 20 billion</span></a>, (Written by John Muchangi)</span></strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,\'helvetica neue\',helvetica,sans-serif\">Small-scale Kenyan farmers and local technology entrepreneurs will benefit greatly from the Sh3 trillion ($30 billion) parties have pledged to spend on agriculture in Africa over 10 years.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>The Exchange, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=d5e4924aff&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">President Kagame urges Africa to take agriculture seriously and embrace technology</span></a></strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,\'helvetica neue\',helvetica,sans-serif\">Putting agriculture sector at the centre stage of the continent&rsquo;s development has the power to shape Africa&rsquo;s economic future. This is according to President Paul Kagame.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>The New Times,</strong> <strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=c23f048249&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">African states should step up agriculture transformation efforts</span></a>, (Written by New Times)</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,\'helvetica neue\',helvetica,sans-serif\">Putting the agriculture sector at the centre stage of Africa&rsquo;s development has the power to shape the continent&rsquo;s economic future. The observation was made by President Paul Kagame, on Wednesday, during the African Green Revolution Forum (AGRF) in Nairobi, Kenya.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Daily News, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=277f1234bc&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Africa pledges $30bn support to small-scale farmers\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Africa pledges $30bn support to small-scale farmers</span></a></strong><strong>, (Written by Henry Lyimo)</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,\'helvetica neue\',helvetica,sans-serif\">African leaders, business people and major development partners pledged more than 30billion US dollars in investments to increase production, income and employment for small scale farmers and local African agricultural businesses over the next ten years.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:arial,\'helvetica neue\',helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Daily Nation, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=9cb31d8677&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Forum pushes for higher investment in agriculture</span></a> (Written by Leopold Obi)</strong></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,\'helvetica neue\',helvetica,sans-serif\">African leaders and think tanks issued a common call to push the region&rsquo;s investments in agriculture to the next level in the next five years</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>TOP CLIPPINGS IN ELECTRONIC NEWS</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CCTV Africa, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=053d23f391&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">interview: Boaz Keizire, African Green Revolution Forum</span></a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>CCTV&rsquo;s Uche Okoronkwo hosts Boaz Keizire, Policy Head at the African Green Revolution Forum who expounds more on the forum.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CNBC Africa, <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=094b5f9b7f&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Initiatives to build resilient economies in Africa</span></a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unemployment, food insecurity and exposure to external shocks are among the challenges that the continent of Africa continues to face.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NTV, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=3205f768f2&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">$30B pledged for farming in Africa</span></a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As the African Green Revolution Forum draws to a close, 30B dollars has already been placed on the table to fund different aspects of the agricultural value chain in order to increase production over the next 10 years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>KBC Channel 1, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage2.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=79c309708c&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Africa loses over $69 billion in illicit financial inflows</span></a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Former Nigerien President Olusegun Obasanjo, while speaking at the AGRF conference in Nairobi says Africa is losing over $69 billion in illicit financial outflows through tax evasion and fraud annually.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>KTN News, Interview: <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=45d56f286e&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Dr. James Nyoro, Presidential advisor on agriculture</span></a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dr. James Nyoro, Presidential advisor on agriculture talks about various projects by government like the Galana Kulalu Irrigation Project and SGR that aimed at reduce food prices in the near future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TOP NEWS ON PARTNERS</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Investors Ideas, <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=7c2a4bf539&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Root Capital and the MasterCard Foundation to Increase Incomes for 300,000 Farmers in West Africa</span></a>, (Written by </strong><strong>Lauren Baum)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Impact investing pioneer Root Capital (<a href=\"http://www.rootcapital.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">www.RootCapital.org</span></a>) announced today at the African Green Revolution Forum a new partnership with The MasterCard Foundation (<a href=\"http://www.mastercardfdn.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">www.MastercardFdn.org</span></a>) that will help raise incomes for over 300,000 smallholder farmers in West Africa. The Foundation has committed $5.2 million to Root Capital over five years to support early-stage agricultural businesses that generate transformational impact in rural communities in C&ocirc;te d&rsquo;Ivoire, Ghana, and Senegal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Footprint to Africa, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=087f40966a&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">IFAD President Awarded the Africa Food Prize</span></a>, (Written by Mally W. Maina) </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The $100, 000 prize package from the Alliance for a Green Revolution in Africa (AGRA) was launched by former Nigerian President Olusegun Obasanjo in Accra, Ghana in July 2016 replacing the Yara Prize that was established in 2005.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Eye Witness, <a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage2.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=ed466f42db&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">F</span></a></strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=5959f66b43&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">arm boost of $30b aimed at helping Africa &lsquo;feed itself&rsquo;</span></a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>African farmers are set to benefit from tens of billions of dollars pledged by African leaders, development banks, the private sector and international donors at a conference in Nairobi this week.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Voice of America, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=7c4613052a&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Push for Agricultural renaissance in Africa gets $30 billion boost</span></a>, (Lenny Ruvanga)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The forum is wrapping up with a significant boost toward that goal: a pledge of $30 billion during the next 10 years to support smallholder farmers and local African agribusinesses. The donors include African governments, businesses and development partners, many of whom have been present for the Nairobi forum.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ghana Trade, </strong><strong><a href=\"http://the%20alliance%20for%20a%20green%20revolution%20in%20africa%20%28agra%29%20this%20week%20announced%20a%20us%24867%2c788%20grant%20to%20essoko%20ghana%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20a%20mastercard%20foundation-funded%20project-%20the%20agro%20input%20access%20solution%20project./\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Ess</span></a><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=d74bd044ed&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">oko gets a US$867,788 grant to help smallholder farmers</span></a>, (Written by Correspondent)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Alliance for a Green Revolution in Africa (AGRA) this week announced a US$867,788 grant to Essoko Ghana for the implementation of a MasterCard Foundation-funded project- the Agro Input Access Solution Project.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TOP BLOGS &amp; URLs &ndash; AFRICA FOCUS</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=45bac547cb&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">$60 billion boost for agriculture</span></a>, </strong><strong>Fresh plaza</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>On Wednesday 7 September, political leaders and philanthropists committed themselves to securing investment in Africa for agriculture. Heads of state were among the figures which met at the African Green Revolution Forum (AGRF) at UN headquarters in the Kenyan capital, Nairobi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=f2e3e49abb&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Report by African Green Revolution Forum calls for training of smallholder farmers</span></a>, Farmers Trend</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Status of Agriculture in Africa report said while stakeholders including policy makers, has undergone one or two forms of training, smallholder farmers have always been left on their own mainly relying on obsolete traditional knowledge produce goods.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://agrf.us13.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=18be0fd3e2c47ba4554d061ed&amp;id=9a13fe7160&amp;e=80b13f5918\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Agric investment yields growth and nutrition gains for Africa</span></a>, B&amp;FT Online</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>African countries that took early action in the past decade to invest in agriculture have reaped the rewards, enjoying higher economic growth and a bigger drop in malnutrition, a major farming development organization said on Tuesday.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Written by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/NiyigabaEtienne\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">NIYIGABA Etienne</span></a> (niyigabat@gmail.com)&nbsp;in collaboration with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jndayambaje\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">Jean Claude Ndayambaje</span></a> (jndayambaje@outlook.com)</em></p>\r\n','1',1965,3,'2016-09-10 22:45:56','News Amakuru',0,'online','',''),(243,'The world will need food forever, farmers will always provide food said Eulade Nzayinambaho, meet him and his fruits seedling nursery ','809415557468691971.jpg','<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">A Bachelor degree with Honors holder in Agriculture Mechanization from University of Rwanda College of Agriculture and Veterinary Medicine, Nzayinambaho Eulade a young passionate in Agriculture is producing improved fruits seedling for his community in Western Province, Karongi district, Gishyita Sector. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&ldquo;After graduating from university I went back to my community, I was looking for where and how to start my own farming activities and help my community improving our farming techniques, then I realized that my community has no fruits trees nursery while fruits is of a great meaning in nutrition and generates quick money then I decided to start my trees nursery&rdquo; said Eulade</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">He started the project only with 800 seedlings of orange citrus with an investment of 285,000 RWF but after selling them he got a incredible profit of almost triple of the investment!!! After one year of his business his is now producing 3600 grafted seedlings for mango and orange citrus on a small land of </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"> </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">with an expected income of almost 3.5 Million RWF.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&ldquo;I&rsquo;m planning of producing more 10,000 grafted seedlings of orange, mango and avocado and scale up my business to a big land for me to reach at least a 10 Million RWF income project. I already bought a 0.5 Ha land which is located near a water source that will allow me to reduce the cost of production and increase my production capacity.&rdquo;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">There is huge demand of fruits trees in my district even in the whole country said Eulade, my business is still at startup level with a minimum investment but due to my motivation and love for Agriculture , I have chosen this career to be my job and creates jobs for my fellows young people. I am still starting but there is great hope that I will achieve my goal. For now I can&rsquo;t satisfy the market demand but am finding a way to invest more and get what farmers need.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Being engaged an agripreneur was not common in Rwandan youth but as the government is encouraging youth to be engaged in agriculture to help in Agriculture transformation with new and fresh innovations. Nowadays, it&rsquo;s a great source of job as more young people are being massively engaged in Agriculture as an untapped sustainable source of income. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Eulade said that he is still facing some challenges for his business to grow faster as he is trying to build trust and creates awareness for farmers to buy improved seedlings, small investment and lack of professional training in the field to be more competent. He also mentioned that young farmers need more of study trips for them to be more innovative. Eulade proposed some suggestions to overcome these challenges like organizing some training for a given farming activity or crop value chain, organizing study visits to others farmers with same activities in the country or abroad, connecting farmers to markets and buyers, etc. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&ldquo;Dear friend young farmers, we are sitting on a Golden stone, especially we, who did agriculture in our studies, let&rsquo;s create jobs rather than asking for jobs. We have skills and we are surrounded by a nice study environment to name farmers. Step by step we can achieve more. Welcome to my farming activities, I love and appreciate your spirit of sharing ideas and information; I got more inspirations from our YEAN Platforms online discussions.&rdquo; </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Get connected to </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><a href=\"http://yeanrwanda.org/community.php?id=283\">Eulade Nzayinambaho</a></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Story by NIYIGABA Etienne (email: eniyigaba@yeanrwanda.org)</span></span></span></em></p>\r\n','4',4245,3,'2017-05-01 13:19:25','Urubyiruko, Agribusiness, success story',3,'online','yes','images/profile photo.jpg'),(245,'Tumenye ubutaka duhinga imitere yabwo n\'amafumbire ubutaka bukeneye mu Rwanda','IMG-20161005-WA0009.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Tumenye ubutaka duhinga imitere yabwo n&rsquo;amafumbire ubutaka bukeneye mu Rwanda</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Gusobanukirwa n&rsquo;ibimenyetso biranga ibura ry&rsquo;intungagihingwa bifasha umuhinzi kumenya ubwoko bw&rsquo;ifumbire yakongerwa mu butaka kugira ngo yongere umusaruro w&rsquo;ibihingwa. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Kubera ubutaka buto bw&rsquo;u Rwanda n&rsquo;imirima mito (impuzandengo y&rsquo;igice cya hegitari), abahinzi basabwa kongera umusaruro kugira ngo n&rsquo;inyungu ziva mu buhinzi ziyongere. Byakorwa gute? Kongera no kunoza ikoreshwa ry&rsquo;amafumbire mvaruganda bifite uruhare runini mu gusubiza iki kibazo. Muri iki gihe, abahinzi bo mu Rwanda bakoresha kuri hegitari kimwe cya cumi (1/10) cy&rsquo;ifumbire mvaruganda ugerereranyije n&rsquo;ikoreshwa n&rsquo;abahinzi mu bihugu byo muri Aziya ku butaka buto nk&rsquo;ubw&rsquo;abahinzi bo mu Rwanda. Ariko mu by&rsquo;ukuri kongera ingano y&rsquo;amafumbire asanzwe akoreshwa (Ire, DAP na NPK) ntabwo bihagije. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Ibipimo by&rsquo;ubutaka mu Rwanda byerekana ko ubutaka budakeneye gusa intungagihingwa za Azoti, Fosifori na Potasiyumu (ziboneka muri Ire, DAP na NPK). Kandi na none ibyo bipimo byagaragaje ko akenshi ubutaka bubura imwe cyangwa nyinshi muri izi ntungagihingwa eshanu zikurikira: Sufure (Sulfur), Boroni (Boron), Zenke (Zinc), Umuringa (Copper) na Manyeziyumu (Magnesium). </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Abahinzi bamenya bate intungagihingwa zibura mu mirima yabo kugira ngo umusaruro wiyongere? </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Amakuru mu rwego rw&rsquo;Akarere (region): </span></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Intambwe ya mbere ku bahinzi ni ukureba amakuru rusange ku butaka cyangwa ku mirima yo mu karere baherereyemo: </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Ibipimo by&rsquo;ubutaka: </span></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Muri 2014, IFDC yasuzumishije ibipimo 1000 by&rsquo;ubutaka bivuye hirya no hino mu Rwanda. Ibisubizo by&rsquo;iryo suzuma bikubiye mu rutonde rw&rsquo;amakarita icumi yerekana aho ubutaka bukennye muri imwe muri za ntungagihingwa umunani, bigendanye n&rsquo;indi miterere itandukanye y&rsquo;ubutaka . RAB na IFDC byashyize ahagaragara aya makarita mu mfashanyigisho ku mikoreshereze y&rsquo;amafumbire mu mirima y&rsquo;icyitegererezo. Iyo mfashanyigisho yahawe abacuruzi b&rsquo;inyongeramusaruro bose, abafashamyumvire b&rsquo;ishuri ry&rsquo;abahinzi mu murima n&rsquo;abandi bantu bakorana n&rsquo;abahinzi. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Imirima y&rsquo;igerageza ry&rsquo;amafumbire</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">: Muri 2013-15, RAB na IFDC byashyizeho imirima myinshi y&rsquo;igerageza mu Rwanda hose. Iyo mirima y&rsquo;igerageza yerekana ko imvange zinyuranye z&rsquo;intungagihingwa zishobora kongera umusaruro cyane. Ubu bwiyongere bw&rsquo;umusaruro bukaba bushobora guhinduka bitewe n&rsquo;uturere dutandukanye. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Amakuru yihariye ajyanye n&rsquo;ahantu: </span></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Amakuru yavuye mu isuzuma ry&rsquo;ubutaka mu karere (region) runaka n&rsquo;ayavuye mu mirima y&rsquo;igerageza ry&rsquo;amafumbire ntabwo ahagije kugira ngo umuhinzi amenye intungagihingwa zikenewe ku murima we wihariye. Ubutaka bw&rsquo;u Rwanda ntibutandukanira gusa ku turere ahubwo no mu ntera ntoya usanga bunyuranye. Ubutaka bwo ku mpinga y&rsquo;imisozi muri rusange burera cyane, uburumbuke bugenda bugabanuka uko uva ku mpinga y&rsquo;umusozi umanuka, mu gihe ubutaka bwo mu nkuka no mu gishanga bwo buba bufite uburumbuke burushijeho. Ubutaka burushaho kugunduka uko imyaka ihita ukoresha amafumbire y&rsquo;ubwoko bumwe ku gihingwa kimwe </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">None se agendeye kuri iyi mihindagurikire y&rsquo;ubutaka bw&rsquo;ahantu, umuhinzi yamenya ate intungagihingwa zidahagije bituma umusaruro uba muke mu murima we? </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Arebeye ku mababi, imbuto n&rsquo;ibindi bice by&rsquo;igihingwa: umuhinzi ashobora kumenya ibimenyetso biranga ibura ry&rsquo;intungagihingwa. Ibihingwa bifite ikibazo cy&rsquo;intungagihingwa zidahagije byerekana ibimenyetso byihariye kuri iyo ntungagihingwa idahagije, nk&rsquo;imirongo (ingenge), ku mababi mashya cyangwa ashaje. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Imirima y&rsquo;igerageza no kwigira ku makosa: umuhinzi ashobora kongera ubumenyi bwe binyuze mu mirima y&rsquo;igerageza no kwigira ku makosa, abaturanyi bagahererekanya amakuru ku buryo bwongera umusaruro n&rsquo;ubutawongera. Kubera urusobe rw&rsquo;ibigize ubutaka n&rsquo;ibiberamo, kuzamura umusaruro ntibituruka ku bumenyi gusa ahubwo binajyana n&rsquo;uburyo bw&rsquo;imikorere. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Gupima ubutaka: umuhinzi ashobora kujyana ubutaka bwe muri laboratwari ngo bupimwe. Bimwe mu bipimo by&rsquo;ubutaka birahendutse, nko gupima ubusharire, rero byagombye kugezwa ku bahinzi. Ariko kubera uburyo gupima ubutaka bihenze ku ntungagihingwa zitandukanye, umuhinzi ashobora kubikora gake cyane gashoboka. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia\">Iyo umuhinzi amaze kumenya intungagihingwa zibura, ashobora gutekereza ku buryo yazibona akazikoresha. Ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera (ituruka ku matungo, ku byatsi n&rsquo;ibisigazwa by&rsquo;umusaruro) nayo itanga zimwe mu ntungagihingwa kandi z&rsquo;ingirakamaro ku butaka. Ariko ingano y&rsquo;imborerera yakenerwa kugira ngo itange intungagihingwa zose zikenewe kandi ku rugero ruhagije ntabwo byoroshye kuyibona.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n','1',2706,3,'2017-05-27 14:06:02','Ifumbire, Ubutaka',0,'online','',''),(246,'Nyirabagwiza Magnifique: \"Chicken farming: Quick money, short period with a small house\"','Magnifique 1.jpg','<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Not long ago people used to keep 2 to 4 chicken in their home, most of them were traditional races, for eggs and may be for the sake of having some birds domesticated. Nowadays young people and professionals farmers are harvesting a lot of money from Poultry farming especially Chickens with improved chicken races </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Nyirabagwiza Magnifique , graduated from the University of Rwanda lives in Ruhango District , Byimana Sector, after graduating</span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"> </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">she was looking for jobs to start her career, but things didn&rsquo;t work like expected ; she didn&rsquo;t get any job until she got an idea of starting her own business that can create job even for some people in his community. She thought about staring a chicken farm though she didn&rsquo;t have enough money to run the business, she was hopping for the best to get money provided she had a nice business idea. &ldquo; I heard many times on radio that people are getting money from Chicken farming , then I said why not me?&rdquo; Said Magnifique , &ldquo;I had a nice idea and got fund from a FAO Project that was supporting unemployed young people to start small businesses, I started with 300 chickens but I scaled up to 550 chicken, now I every morning collect about 265-280 eggs from those 300 chicken I stated with .&rdquo;she added . It is not an easy job; to keep them healthy, feed them for better eggs production; I&rsquo;ve got to find 2 people to help me and pay them monthly.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">She got some trainings and study trips to help her increase her skills about this business but still she is facing some challenges; she needs more trainings on chicken farming as she wants to scale up her farming activities, medicines and veterinary services are expensive, chicken food is expensive and most of them are imported, the price of eggs and chickens is almost the same on markets whatever the production cost. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">She is very proud of her business when she talks about it and she is ready to make it more professional. She mentioned that our Country Rwanda is more of young people who needs jobs, that&rsquo;s fine and </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"> </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">good that we have young </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"> </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">but it won&rsquo;t be good if they all need office jobs, worse again if they won&rsquo;t serve Agriculture that host more that 80% of our population . &ldquo;What we got from school must be a great tool to start thinking beyond what worked with our parents that can no longer work with our generation.&rdquo; Said Magnifique.</span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"> </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">She wish to share her farming story with YEAN, to inspire and get inspired as she is enjoying to chat with farmers on YEAN Platform. We wish her all the best in her Poultry farming and wish to see her growing to reach her dreams as a Young agripreneurs .</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><em><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Story by Bucyansenga Kizito (bucyakakizito@gmail.com)</span></span></span></em></p>\r\n','4',5271,3,'2017-06-01 15:59:23','Urubyiruko, Agribusiness, success story',1,'online','yes','images/Nyirabagwiza Magnifique banner 2.jpg'),(248,'Gusasira ibihingwa hakoreshejwe amashashi yabugenewe.','315372302518333701.jpg','<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Gusasira ibihingwa hakoreshejwe amashashi yabugenewe.</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Gusasira ni uburyo bwo gutwikira ubutaka kugirango bumere neza bituma ibihingwa bikura neza, bikanabyara umusaruro mwiza. Muri make ni ugutwikira ubutaka. Mu gihe isaso yakunze gukoreshwa cyane ari amababi y&rsquo;ibihingwa, ibisigazwa by&rsquo;ibyasaruwe, ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera byakoreshejwe kuva mu myaka yo hambere hasigaye hariho ubundi buryo bwo gukoresha isaso ikorewe mu nganda . Ibi byakozweho ubushakashatsi bwinshi bugaragaza ko iyi saso ifite ubushobozi mu gufasha ubutaka kumera neza. Uyigereranyije n&rsquo;indi saso , iyi saso y&rsquo;amashashi yabugenewe izwiho kudahitisha amazi cg ngo amazi ayinjiremo bivuzeko burya uko izuba rivuye hari amazi ava mu butaka ajya mu kirere ku buryo bw&rsquo;umwuka, ubwo bushyuhe butuma ubutaka buta amazi menshi cyane ubutaka bugakakara bukuma. Iyi saso rero ituma amazi yo mu butaka agumamo yose. </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"> </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ibyiza by&rsquo;isaso y&rsquo;amashashi yabugenewe</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ntago ihitisha amazi</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ituma mu gihe hashyushye amazi atajya mu kirere mu buryo bw&rsquo;umwuka avuye mu butaka hanyuma igatuma ubutaka buhora butoshye.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ituma umuhinzi ashyira ifumbire aho ikwiye kujya bikagabanya intungagihingwa zimanuka mu butaka ntizifatwe n&rsquo;igihingwa</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ituma ubutaka butinjirwamo n&rsquo;udukoko twangiza imyaka&nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Isaso itabonerana ituma ibyatsi by&rsquo;ibyonnyi bitamera kuko nta rumuri biba byabonye</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Iyo isaso ibonerana nk&rsquo;indorerwamo ituma udusimba twona imyaka duhunga uwo murima</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Iyi saso ituma ubutama bukomeza gushyuha bigafasha imbuto kumera vuba ndetse n&rsquo;ibihingwa bikagira imizi vuba vuba</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Iyo ubutaka busasiye gutya bituma ubutaka bukomera kugira imiterere imwe mu gihe cyose igihingwa kimara mu murima </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Iyi saso iyo yasasijwe imbuto cg imboga, ituma imbuto zihiye zihunguka zitangirika ngo zise nabi cyangwa zibore vuba , ituma kandi imboga zikomeza gusa neza mu gihe zimara mu murima cyose</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Iyi saso ituma igihingwa gikura neza kuko nta byatsi bikura iruhande rwacyo kandi ubutaka ntibuhingwa ngo hahungabanywe imizi yacyo</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Iyi saso igabanya isuri mu murima&nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ugereranyije n&rsquo;isaso isanzwe, Iyi saso imara igihe kinini.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><em><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ubutaka bugumana ubuhehere</span></span></span></em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Amashashi yabugenewe bitewe n&rsquo;uko adahitisha amazi/ubuhehere ntatuma amazi ava mu butaha ngo ajye mu kirere, iyo hashyushye amashashi atuma amazi ashaka kuzamuka mu buryo bw&rsquo;umwuka abura aho anyura hanyuma akaza kongera kw&rsquo;ikoramo ibitonyanga imbere muri iyo shashi bitewe n&rsquo;ubushyuhe burimo imbere akaza kongera kugwa</span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"> </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">ku butaka nk&rsquo;ibitonyanga</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Iyo wuhira umurima wawe, iyi saso ituma amazi adashira vuba mu butaka hanyuma umuhinzi akuhira gake.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Amazi yuhiwe cyangwa ay&rsquo;imvura yinjira mu butaka binyuze mu myanya yatobowe mu mashashi aho igihingwa kiba cyarazamukiye</span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"> </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">cyangwa akinjirira ahandi hadatwikiriye . </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><em><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Kurwanya ibyatsi bidakenewe mu murima </span></span></span></em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Amashashi yirabura ntago atuma imirasire y&rsquo;izuba yinjira mu butaka bigatuma nta gihingwa kiri munsi y&rsquo;iyo shashi gikura. Ubundi bwoko butari ubw&rsquo;umukara bushobora gutuma hari ibyatsi bimera ariko ntago bikura .</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Imbogamizi muri ubu buryo</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Iyi saso irahenda ugereranyije n&rsquo;isaso isanzwe y&rsquo;ibyatsi n&rsquo;imborera</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ibihingwa bito bishobora gutwikwa n&rsquo;ubushyushe bwinshi buri mu butaka&nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Gushyiraho ifumbire ku gihingwa biragorana nyuma yo gutwikira</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Iyi saso iyo uhinga ahantu hanini bisaba ko wifashisha imashini mu kuyishyiraho ariko ushobora no kukoresha intoki bisanzwe gusa bisaba abantu bagufasha mu kuyishyiraho.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Amazi kuko atinjira mu butaka ashobora gutemba&nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Bishobora kwangiza ibidukikije iyo hakoreshejwe ishashi zitabugenewe .</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Iyo ubuhinzi bukoresha imashini biragorana mu kunyuzamo imashini</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Iyo wakoresheje amashashi yoroshye cyane uyakoresha igihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga kimwe.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Amashashi ashobora kuba imbogamizi ku bwatsi bw&rsquo;amatungo.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ubwoko bw&rsquo;amashashi akoreshwa </span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ubwoko bunyuranye bw&rsquo;amashashi yarageragejwe</span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"> </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">mu myaka ya za 1960. LDPE (</span></span></span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Low-density_polyethylene\" title=\"Low-density polyethylene\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">low-density polyethylene</span></span></span></a><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">) , HDPE (</span></span></span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/High-density_polyethylene\" title=\"High-density polyethylene\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">high-density polyethylene</span></span></span></a><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">) na PVC zose zarageragejwe ariko zigaragaza itandukaniro hagati yazo. Kugeza ubu Amashashi akozwe muri Polyethylene niyo akunzwe cyane kubera uburyo ahitisha urumuri n&rsquo;uburyo afata ubushyuhe .</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Iby&rsquo;ingenzi biranga iyi saso</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ituma umwuka utagenda bityo igatuma nta mazi agenda mu buryo bw&rsquo;umwuka</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ituma ubushyuhe bw&rsquo;ubutaka budahindagurika</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ishobora gukoreshwa ibihembwe by&rsquo;ihingwa birenze kimwe bitewe n&rsquo;iyo ariyo</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Uko iyo saso iteye</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Umubyimba w&rsquo;ishashi: </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">ubusanzwe umubyimba w&rsquo;ishashi nta ngaruka ugira ku bwiza bw&rsquo;isaso kereka iyo iyi yakoreshejwe nk&rsquo;uburyo bwo gushyushya ubutaka. Ariko muri iyi minsi hari ubushashatsi bugenda bwerekana ko umubyimba w&rsquo;isaso hari icyo wongera/ugabanya ku musaruro .</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Ubugari bw&rsquo;ishashi: Ibi ahanini bigenwa n&rsquo;intera iri hagati y&rsquo;imirongo y&rsquo;ibihingwa. Ubusanzwe ubugari bwa metero imwe cyangwa imwe n&rsquo;igice nizo zikunda gukoreshwa ku bihingawa byinshi</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Ibara ry&rsquo;Ishashi yakoreshejwe : Ibara ry&rsquo;ishashi rigira ingaruka:&nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Ubushyuhe bw&rsquo;ubutaka</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ubushyuhe bw&rsquo;umwuka iruhande rw&rsquo;igihingwa</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ikigero cy&rsquo;umunyu w&rsquo; ubutaka</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Uburyo bwo gusasiza Amashashi yabugenewe</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ku biti by&rsquo;imbuto, imboga, n&rsquo;ibindi bihingwa</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ishashi ikenewe uyikata ku kizingo uba waguze</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Banza usukure aho ugiye gutwikira ukuraho amabuye, ibyatsi n&rsquo;ibindi byakwangiza isaso yawe&nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Banza ubinge neza aho ugiye gusasira kandi uhuhire niba humagaye.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ugomba gukora ku buryo aho isaso irangirira ku ruhande uri bubashe kuyitaba agace gahera kugirango itaka ugeretseho ribashe kuyifata</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ushobora gutobora ishashi mu mpanze enye zihera zayo kugirango worohereze amazi kugenda mu butaka</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Uburyo bwo gusasira Imboga&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Amashashi yoroshye cyane adafite umubyimba munini niyo akoreshwa</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ishashi iramburwa ku murongo uri buterweho imbuto bikozwe mu burebure bwawo.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Utobora ishashi rwagati muri yo, ufatiye ku bugari bwayo ukoresheje igikoresho gifite umurambararo munini</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Uhereye ku mutwe umwe w&rsquo;umurongo uterwaho imbuto urambura ishashi uyikura ku kizingo cyayo, iyo nta mashini yo kuyishyiraho hifashishijwe abantu batari munsi ya batatu, umwe afata ishashi akayirambura abandi babiri umwe mu ruhande rumwe rw&rsquo;iyogi undi mu rundi bagenda bataba ku mpera z&rsquo;ishashi.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Banza uhinge ubutaka neza unashyiremo ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera n&rsquo;imvaruganda ikenewe mbere yo gusasira</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Imbuto zishyirwa mu butaka nyuma yo gushyiraho isaso unyujije muri ya myenge watoboye mu ishashi</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Mu gihe ari ingemwe ugiye gutera nazo ziterwa muri iyo myenge uba watoboye twavuze hejuru</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Mu gihe uri gusasira imbuto zatewe mbere, gupfumura ishashi nabyo bikorwa kimwe hanyuma mu kuyishyiraho ukabanza gutaba uruhande rumwe hanyuma ukarambura ishashi/isaso hejuru yazo ukagenda winjiza muri ya myenge wasize ubikoze n&rsquo;intoki warangiza ukaza gutaba urundi ruhande</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ibyitonderwa mu gushyiraho ishashi</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Mu gihe cyo gushyiraho ishashi ntuyikurure cyane byatuma icika cyangwa ikazahura n&rsquo;ikibazo cy&rsquo;ubushyuhe bwinshi igacika cyangwa se bitewe n&rsquo;imikurire y&rsquo;igihingwa bikazayigiraho ingaruka.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ishashi igomba kuramburwa neza kugirango itazizingazinga bitewe n&rsquo;ubushyuhe cyane cyane kw&rsquo;isaso y&rsquo;umukara</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ishashi ntigomba gushyirwaho mu masaha y&rsquo;ubushyuhe bwinshi icyo gihe ishashi iba ishobora gukweduka byoroshye igacika</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Gukuraho ishashi/isaso nyuma yo kuyikoresha </span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Mu gihe ishashi/Isaso ikeneye gukoreshwa mu gihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga gikurikira , ibihingwa bisarurwa bikatirwa hejuru gato y&rsquo;ishashi/isaso hanyuma isaso igakurwaho neza ikongera igakoreshwa (ibi bikunze kuba ku mashashi afite umubyimba munini). </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Hari amashashi akoze ku buryo iyo ahuye n&rsquo;imirasire y&rsquo;izuba atangira guhinduka agacikagurikamo uduce duto cyane bitewe n&rsquo;iminsi uwayikoze yayigeneye , aya mashashi rero arabora agahindukamo ibintu bidateye ikibazo ku butaka, gusa cya gice cyatabwe cyo kuko kidahura n&rsquo;izuba ntikibora , iki rero mu guhinga gukurikiyeho giteza ikibazo, ubushakashatsi buracyakorwa ngo hakorwe amashashi atangiza ubutaka n&rsquo;ibidukikije.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Uburyo bwo kuhira iyo wakoresheje iyi saso</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ku kuhira gukoresheje ibitonyanga (drip irrigation) udutembo dutwara amazi tunyuzwa mundi y&rsquo;ishashi kandi tugashyirwamo mbere yo gusasira.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Mu buryo bwo kuhira ukoresheje amazi menshi atemba ( flooding irrigation) amazi yinjirira muri twa twenge twatobowe mu isaso.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Isaso ikenewe ingana ite?</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Kumenya isaso ukeneye ni ikintu cy&rsquo;ingenzi mu gutegura ubuhinzi bwawe. Mu butaka buringaniye, isaso ikoreshwa iba ugereranyije ingana n&rsquo;ubuso bw&rsquo;umurima ushasha gusasira. Mu butaka bugizwe n&rsquo;amabimba n&rsquo;amayogi isaso ikenerwa izaba iruta ubuso bw&rsquo;umurima ushaka gusasira.</span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"> </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Mu buryo bwo gusasira bugenda busiga umwanya munini hagati y&rsquo;imirongo, isaso iba ingana na 50-60% by&rsquo;ubutaka bushaka gusasirwa.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><em>Byateguwe na NIYIGABA Etienne (eniyigaba@yeanrwanda.org)</em></p>\r\n','1',5272,3,'2017-06-26 19:02:01','Ubutaka, Gusasira',1,'online','',''),(250,'Abanyamuryango ba YEAN Community bafashije umuturage watemewe inka kubona Ubwatsi bw\'izo yashumbushijwe mu gihe kingana n\'umwaka. ','697654991144934535.jpg','<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Abanyamuryango ba YEAN Community bafashije umuturage watemewe inka kubona Ubwatsi bw&rsquo;izo yashumbushijwe mu gihe kingana n&rsquo;umwaka. </span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Bakimara kumva inkuru ibabaje y&rsquo;umuturage wo mu karere ka Kicukiro watemewe inka n&rsquo;abagizi ba nabi mu gihe cyo Kwibuka Jenoside yakorewe abatutsi , abahinzi-borozi n&rsquo;abagoronome babigize umwuga bibumbiye muri YEAN Community, uyu ukaba umuryango mugari w&rsquo;abahinzi n&rsquo;abagoronome basangira amakuru y&rsquo;ubuhinzi/ubworozi binyuze mu mbuga ngari zashyizweho na YEAN, batangiye igikorwa cyo gukusanya ubwabo inkunga yo gushumbusha uyu muturage wahemukiwe. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Mu gihe bari batarashyira mu bikorwa iki gikorwa kiza biyemeje, hari abandi bagiraneza bagiye bamushumbusha maze abasha kongera kubona inka zisimbura iyatemwe. Bitewe n&rsquo;ubushobozi bw&rsquo;uyu muturage, abari bashinzwe igikorwa cyo kumushumbusha muri YEAN Community, mbere yo kumushumbusha baramusuye maze babonana nawe ndetse n&rsquo;ubuyobozi bw&rsquo;inzego zibanze z&rsquo;aho atuye, maze umuryango ushimira icyo igikorwa kiza, umuryango wifuzako ikiza si ukumuha indi nka isanga izo yari amaze guhabwa, ahubwoko umuryango wifuza kumufasha mu kubona ubwatsi bw&rsquo;izo yari yahawe mbere ngo zibeho neza. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Muri iki gikorwa hiyambajwe ubuyobozi bw&rsquo;inzego z&rsquo;ibanze ndetse n&rsquo;ubuyobozi bwa SACCO y&rsquo;umurenge wa Kigarama maze hafungurwa Konti ishyirwaho amafanga angana n&rsquo;ibihumbi magana abiri na mirongo itanu y&rsquo;amanyarwanda (250 000 Frw), azagura ubwatsi buri kwezi mu gihe cy&rsquo;umwaka umwe. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Kuri uyu wa 4 Nyakanga 2017, umunsi u Rwanda rwizihizaho umunsi wo kwibohora nibwo, abahagarariye YEAN Community bifatanyije n&rsquo;abaturage bo mu murenge wa Kigarama akagali ka Nyarurama umudugudu wa Zuba mu kwizihiza uyu munsi baboneraho no Gushyikiriza ku mugaragaro inkunga bageneye umu muturage. Abayobozi banyuranye bari bahari bashimye igikorwa uru Rubyiruko rw&rsquo;abahinzi borozi bakoze bashishikariza abanywanda bose kujya bagira umutima w&rsquo;urukundo n&rsquo;ishyaka ryo gushyigikira,kurwanirira ndetse no gufasha umunyarwanda uwariwe wese wahuye n&rsquo;ikibazo.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Uwari uhagarariye ubuyobozi bwa YEAN Nshimiyimana Arcade, yashimye abantu bose bagize uruhare ngo iki gikorwa kigerweho, yaba abanyamuryango ba YEAN Community n&rsquo;abandi bose bafashije mu gushyira mu bikorwa iki gikorwa . </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">YEAN ni iki</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">YEAN ni Umuryango watangiye muri 2014 ukora ibikorwa by&rsquo;iyamamazabuhinzi hibandwa ku guha umuhinzi-mworozi ubushobozi bwo kumenya neza imihingire n&rsquo;imyororere ya Kijyambere mu buryo bwo guhindura ubuhinzi bukaba ubw&rsquo;umwuga hibandwa k&rsquo;ubukangurambaga mu rubyiruko ngo rwitabire uyu mwuga , ruzanemo amaraso mashya mu kubaka ubuhinzi butunga umuhinzi/umworozi bukanamubera isoko y&rsquo;ubukungu butajegajega.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><a href=\"http://yeanrwanda.org/community.php\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">YEAN Community</span></span></span></a>&nbsp;ni iki</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Mu buryo bw&rsquo;iyamamazabuhinzi YEAN yashyizeho imbuga ngari zikoresha internet zikorera ku mbuga nkoranyambaga zitandukanye , aha rero niho abasangira amakuru bahurira ku buryo bworoshye , bwihuse kandi butuma umuhinzi amenya amakuru byoroshye ari mu buhinzi bwe , bikamuhuza n&rsquo;abandi bahinzi basangiye umwuga mu gihugu hose , bityo umuhinzi akagira amakuru y&rsquo;ibyo akeneye ku gihe . Aba bose rero bahurira kuri izi mbuga ngari bamaze kugera kuri 3500 nibo bagize umuryango mugari wa YEAN Community.</span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"> </span></span></span></p>\r\n','4',22523,40,'2017-07-05 19:23:00','News Amakuru',0,'online','',''),(254,'Ubuhinzi Bwacu: Ibitekerezo by\'abahinzi ku ngingo igira iti: \" Gucika kw\'amoko amwe namwe y\'ibihingwa \"','ibikoro.jpg','<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"display:none\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ubuhinzi Bwacu: Ibitekerezo by&rsquo;abahinzi ku ngingo igira iti: &quot; Gucika kw&#39;amoko amwe namwe y&#39;ibihingwa &quot;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Bahinzi Borozi namwe mukunda ubuhinzi Mwaramutse , Uyu munsi tugarutse mu Kiganiro UBUHINZI BWACU, Turaganira ku nsanganyamatsiko igira iti&quot; Gucika kw&#39;amoko amwe namwe y&#39;ibihingwa &quot;. Bitewe n&#39;ihindagurika ry&#39;ibihe ndetse na gahunda yo kongera agaciro ibihingwa byatoranyijwe, hari amoko y&#39;ibihingwa agenda agabanyuka mu Rwanda.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Turagaruka kuri izi ngingo zikurikira </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ni iki cyakorwa ngo imbuto z&#39;ibihingwa gakondo zigire uruhare mu gutera imbere k&#39;ubuhinzi.</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Hari imbuto iwanyu zaba zarahabaga none zikaba zitakiboneka? </span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ni uruhe ruhare rw&#39;ubushakashatsi mu gusigasira ibihingwa gakondo</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Imbogamizi mu gusigasira ibihingwa gakondo</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ibisubizo kuri izo mbogamizi?????</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Mu gutangira ikiganiro uyu yatangiye agaragaza amoko amwe y&rsquo;ibihingwa agenda acika harimo Imitima y&#39;imfizi/coeur de beuf, inkoli, imikunde, ibikoro, amateke bitaga nshogeye (yararaga kuziko), Imyumbati ya gitaminsi,imiribwa,insina ya gisubi,kamaramasenge nibindi [...] byaracitse kandi byari bifite akamaro gakomeye mumirire y&#39;abanyarwanda </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Mu kumwunganira uyu yagize ati : &ldquo;Uko bigaragara ku masoko atandukanye ibiribwa bimwe biragenda biba bicyeya mu bwinshi ndetse no mu bwiza.</span><span style=\"color:#000000\"> </span><span style=\"color:#000000\">Imbuto ku masoko zifite amusaruro mucye kandi ziranahenze cyane. Imineke imwe twita goromisheri muri iki gihe yarabuze mu masoko cyane cyane mu intara naho ibonetse iba ihenze umwe ugura 100 cyangwa hejuru , bitewe naho uherereye. Wagaruka kuri kamara masenge(imineke mito) nayo nuko umwiza urahenze cyane aho usanga kamwe ukabariye igiciro kiri hagari ya 50 cyangwa hejuru </span><span style=\"color:#000000\"> </span><span style=\"color:#000000\">. Muri rusange ibi biribwa ndindamubiri birimo kugenda bigabanuka kukigero cyihuta. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Uyu nawe ati: &ldquo;RAB ifite Gene Bank aho buri kintu cyose kibitse ku buryo kitazimira burundu igisabwa nukureba umusaruro bitanga hakurikijwe ibikenewe muri iki gihe tugezemo kuko uko abantu biyongera ni nako hakenerwa ibyo kurya byinshi&rdquo;</span><span style=\"color:#000000\"> </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&ldquo;iki kiganiro no cyiza ,imbuto gakondo zanimezaga mu cyaro ntizikihaba ,amapera ,amapapaye,amarongi,imyembe isigaye ituruka Burundi na Tanzania , sinzi niba hari abantu bashinzwe kwita kumbuto muri RAB ? Hakwiye izindi ngufu mu kuzegereza abahinzi no mucyaro kuko nabo barazishaka cyane ahubwo ntamakuru yaho zaboneka !&rdquo;</span><span style=\"color:#000000\"> </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&ldquo;Gucika burundu ntibyazimira kuko bibitswe neza ariko ikibazo nukumenya ngo bizongera guhingwa cyane ryari?&rdquo; </span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&ldquo;Imyumbati ya gitaminsi, bugurubwinkware yamaraga imyaka 2-3 ubu turahinga iyera mu mwaka 1.&rdquo;</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&ldquo;Ibikoro byahingwaga mu mishike none kuraza ubutaka ntibikibaho&rdquo;</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&ldquo;Amateke ya nshogeye yahingwaga nayo mu mushike kandi agashyirwaho amase ahagije none ubu kubona imborera ni ikibazo kitoroheye abahinzi!!!!&rdquo;</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ikiganiro uko cyagiye kigenda abahinzi n&rsquo;abagoronome bakomeje gutanga ibitekerezo byabo ku buryo bunwa iyi ngingo aho uyu yagize ati: &ldquo;Amoko y&#39;ibihingwa bimwe na bimwe agenda azimira bitewe nuko abahinzi baba bamaze kubona andi moko abyara umusaruro mwinshi ariko ku bijyanye no guteza imbere ibihingwa twari dusanganywe , njye mbona tuzageraho tugasigara duhinga imbuto zo hanze gusa kuko, ubucuruzi bw&#39;imbuto zitunganyijwe mu nganda neza buragenda butera imbere cyane bityo uzicuruza ntaba ashaka ko umuhinzi ashobora kwibikira imbuto ye , hari imbuto zimwe za hybrids udashobora gukuraho imbuto ngo uyibike kuko uyiteye itazamera. Bityo rero ndumva hagakwiye kubaho ubushakashatsi bushingiye ku mbuto twahoranye zigakorerwa breeding zigatanga imbuto zishobora gutanga umusaruro uhagije ndetse zikanabasha kwihanganira ubutaka bwacu kuko nubundi ariho zari zisanzwe zihingwa.&rdquo; </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&ldquo;Ikindi nkaho nzi iwacu, heraga ibihaza , ubwoko bw&#39;amasaka bumwe ntiwabubona, imyumbati ya gacyacyari (imiribwa), iya gitaminsi ( y&#39;ubugali) nayo imwe ntikiboneka, amoko y&#39;insina zagiraga imineke iryoshye, ibijumba n&#39;ibindi byinshi.&rdquo;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Mwaramutse , izimira ry&#39;Imbuto za gakondo ririmo guterwa nuko ubu agriculture dufite ari business oriented (ubuhinzi bwerekeza k&rsquo;ubucuruzi) kandi nkuko mubizi zitanga umusaruro mukeya urugero ibigori ariko hakabayeho uburyo bwo gukora conservation yazo kuko kugeza ubu muri za restaurants nizo zikunzwe urugero Idegede muri hotel</span><span style=\"color:#000000\"> </span><span style=\"color:#000000\">rihenda cyane kurusha inyama amashaza iyo wishyiriyeho rushe imwe hiyongeraho 500 kuyo wari kwishyura .</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#1d2129\">Uyu yashatse gutanga igitekerezo cye mu cyongereza aho yagize ati :&ldquo;The role of research in the conservation of indigenous crop species should be: (1) Construction of a digitalized &amp; peer reviewed database with clear morphological characterization and information on origins, (2) Construction of a digitalized and peer reviewed Gene Bank for indigenous crop species, (3) Establishment of Botanical Gardens composed of compatible indigenous crop species in protected &amp; isolated areas such as National Parks</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#1d2129\">Uyu yagerageje kuvuga uko yumva imvano y&rsquo;iri cika ry&rsquo;imbuto zimwe na zimwe ati : &ldquo;Ugucika kw&#39;amoko y&#39;imbuto zimwe na zimwe za gakondo, mbona biterwa n&#39;ingufu nke zigaragara mu bushakashatsi bw&#39;ikigo RAB mu kubungabunga amwe mu moko y&#39;imbuto za gakondo.<br />\r\nUrugero: Mu mwaka wa 2002-2003 , ikigo cy&#39;ubushakashatsi mu by&#39;ubuhinzi cyitwaga, icyo gihe, ISAR, cyari gifite gahunda ihamye yo guteza imbere imbuto za gakondo z&#39;imboga. Aha twavuga nka : imbogeri, dodo, imbwija, inyabutongo, isogi, isogo, inkori,..... Icyo gihe bamwe mu bashakashatsi ba ISAR/RUBONA, bari kumwe na Ruganzu Vicky,baje kudukangurira, aho nakoraga, guhinga ayo moko y&#39;imboga ku buryo wabonaga ari ibintu bifite sustainability. None iyo gahunda mbona yaracumbagiye. Uretse imboga gusa , hari n&#39;ibindi bihingwa bikwiye kwitabwaho.&rdquo;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#1d2129\">Inama n&rsquo;ibisubizo byatanzwe</span></strong></span></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ingamba zikomeye zikwiriye kwita bwaho harimo kuzana imbuto nziza bashishikariza abahinzi gutera imbuto nziza ndetse n&rsquo;abandi muri rusange kugira ibiti mu ngo zabo byeraho imbuto nk&rsquo;izirandaranda ku nzitiro zabo ndetse no mu turima twegereye inzu. Urugero nk&#39;amatunda , ibinyomoro, amarongi mandarine. Nkumva ibi RAB na NAEB</span><span style=\"color:#000000\"> </span><span style=\"color:#000000\">bifatanije mu bukangurambaga hari icyahinduka kandi kiza&rdquo;</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&ldquo;Umuti mbona ni uko hagakwiye kubaho gahunda yo guteza imbere imbuto gakondo zigahabwa ubushakashatsi zigatanga umusaruro nazo mwiza.&rdquo;</span><span style=\"color:#000000\"> </span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&ldquo;RAB yakarebye uburyo zitacika kuko inyinshi nasanze Arizo zifite ubudahangarwa mukurwanya indwara zadutse zirimo cancer , Diabetes n&rsquo;ibindi&rdquo;</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&ldquo;Igisubizo cyabyo kigomba kuva kumbaraga RAB,Minagri nabandi bafatanyabikorwa babo bazashyira mubushakashatsi butuma bicika&rdquo;</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#1d2129\">Icyitonderwa:</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#1d2129\">Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byose ntago byagarajwe hano bitewe n&rsquo;uko ari ikiganiro kirekire cyane hagiye hatoranywamo imirongo migari ikavugwa muri make. Amazina yabatanze ibitekerezo ntago yagaragajwe muri iyi nkuru gusa amagambo yose ari mu utwuguruzo n&rsquo;utwugarizo (&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;) yose yandikuwe uko yanditse mu kiganiro na ba nyirayo.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#1d2129\">Ikiganiro nk&rsquo;iki kiba buri ku Cyumweru.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#1d2129\">Ushaka gukurikira ibi biganiro ukaba uri umuhinzi/umworozi cyangwa umugoronome/veterineri ku rwego urwo arirwo rwose nawe wasaba kujya k&rsquo;urubuga rwa YEAN Whatsapp unyuze kuri nimero ikurikira: +250 788 845 727 ,wakurikira </span><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/YEANRWANDA/\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">YEAN kuri facebook</span></a><span style=\"color:#1d2129\"> cyangwa </span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/YEAN_Rwanda\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">kuri twitter #UbuhinziBwacu @YEAN_Rwanda</span></a></span></span><span style=\"display:none\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n','3',3298,3,'2017-08-11 03:08:23','Ubuhinzi Bwacu',0,'online','',''),(255,'Ibihingwa byera mu turere tw\'u Rwanda , buri Karere n\'ibihingwa bihera','Rwanda agriculture zones.JPG','<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ibihingwa byera mu turere tw&rsquo;u Rwanda , buri Karere n&rsquo;ibihingwa bihera</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Igihugu cy&rsquo;u Rwanda kigizwe n&rsquo;uduce dutandukanyije imiterere yaba mu buhaname, mu miterere y&rsquo;ubutaka n&rsquo;aho ako gace gaherereye , ibi bituma rero ibihingwa bitandukanye bigenda bikunda ahantu hatandukanye kuburyo usanga igihingwa cyera ahantu runaka kitabasha kwera ahandi. Umuhinzi akwiye kubanza kumenya neza ibihingwa byera neza mu gace ashaka guhingamo mbere y&rsquo;uko atangira umushinga we. Muri iyi nyandiko twabakusanyirije uturere twose n&rsquo;ibihingwa byeramo kurusha ibindi. Bipanze ku buryo habanza intara hagakurikiraho akarere , hakazaho akarere k&rsquo;Ubuhinzi (Urugero: Impala) hanyuma hakazaho ibihingwa byera muri ako karere. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Uburengerazuba </span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">1.1.Rusizi</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Imbo</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">: Umuceri, ibigori,Ibishyimbo, Inyanya,Ibitunguru, Imyumbati</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Impala</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">: Ikawa, urutoki, soya,ibishyimbo, marakuja,ibigori.</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ubutakabw&rsquo;imisozi miremire yo mu ishyamba rya kimeza:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Urutoki, icyayi, marakuja, ibigori.</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Inkengero z&rsquo;ikiyaga cya Kivu:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Ikawa, urutoki, soya, ibigori, ibishyimbo, makadamiya</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">1.2.Nyamasheke </span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Impala :</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Ikawa, urutoki, soya, ibishyimbo, imyumbati, imboga, marakuja, makadamiya, ibigori</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ubutaka bw&rsquo;imisozi ya Cyangugu:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Ikawa, icyayi, marakuja, urutoki, ibigori</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Inkengero z&rsquo;ikiyaga cya Kivu:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Ikawa, imbuto, imboga, soya, urutoki, ibigori</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Isunzu rya Kongo Nili:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Urutoki, ibishyimbo bishingirirwa, ibigori</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">1.3.Karongi</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Inkengero z&rsquo;ikiyaga cya Kivu :</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Ikawa, ibigori, imbuto, imboga, soya, urutoki, iboberi, ibishyimbo</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><spa