pan></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">2.8.Muhanga </span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Akarere k&rsquo;urubuye/ Akarere k&lsquo;umugongo:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Ikawa, imyumbati, imbuto, imboga, ibigori, ibishyimbo, Soya.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Amajyaruguru</span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">3.1.Burera</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ubutaka bw&lsquo;amakoro:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Ibirayi, ibigori, ibishyimbo bishingirirwa, ingano, ibireti</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Imisozi y&lsquo;Ububeruka:</strong> Ibirayi, ingano, ibishyimbo bishingirirwa, imboga.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">3.2.Musanze</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ubutaka bw&lsquo;amakoro:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Ibirayi, ingano, ibireti, imboga, ibigori, ibishyimbo bishingirirwa.</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Imisozi y&lsquo;ububeruka:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> ingano, ibishyimbo bishingirirwa, imboga. </span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">3.3.Gakenke</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Imisozi y&rsquo;Ububeruka:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Ingori, ingano, ibishyimbo bishingirirwa.</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Akarere k&rsquo;urubuye/ Akarere k&lsquo;umugongo:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Marakuja, ikawa, makadamiya, inanasi, imyumbati </span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">3.4.Gicumbi</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Imisozi y&lsquo;Ububeruka:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Ibigori ikawa, icyayi, ibirayi, ingano, ibishyimbo bishingirirwa</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Akarere gakikije ibibaya by&lsquo; I burasirazuba:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Icyayi, ibigori, amasaka, marakuja</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">3.5.Rulindo</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ibibaya by&rsquo;I Burasirazuba:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Icyayi, Marakuja, Ibigori</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Akarere k&rsquo;urubuye/ Akarere k&lsquo;umugongo:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Marakuja, ikawa, ibigori </span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Uburasirazuba</span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">4.1.Bugesera: </span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Mayaga/ Ubugesera:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Imyumbati, amasaka, umuceri, ibigori, soya, ibishyimbo</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">4.2.Ngoma</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Akarere gakikije ibibaya by&lsquo; I burasirazuba:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Urutoki, amasaka, inyanya, ibishyimbo, umuceri, inanasi, ikawa, ibigori</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">4.3.Rwamagana</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Akarere Gakikije ibibaya by&lsquo; I burasirazuba:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Urutoki, amasaka, inyanya, ibishyimbo, umuceri, makadamiya, ibigori, ikawa.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">4.4.Gatsibo</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Akarere gakikije ibibaya by&lsquo; I burasirazuba:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Urutoki, amasaka, inyanya, ibishyimbo, ibigori.</span></span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ibibaya by&lsquo;iburasirazuba:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Amasaka, ibishyimbo, ibigori, umuceri</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">4.5.Kirehe</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ibibaya by&lsquo;iburasirazuba :</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Inyanya, amasaka, urutoki, umuceri, ibigori, inanasi, soya, ikawa, ibishyimbo.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">4.6.Kayonza</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ibibaya by&lsquo;iburasirazuba :</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Inyanya, amasaka, umuceri, ibigori, ibishyimbo</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">4.7.Nyagatare: </span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ibibaya by&lsquo;iburasirazuba:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Amasaka, imyumbati, urutoki, ibigori, umuceri, ibishyimbo</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"5\">\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Umujyi wa Kigali</span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">5.1.Gasabo</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Akarere gakikije ibibaya by&lsquo; I burasirazuba:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Amasaka, ibigori, imboga,ibishyimbo, ikawa, indabo, ibobere</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">5.2.Kicukiro</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ibibaya by&lsquo;iburasirazuba:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Imbuto, ibishyimbo, Jeraniyumu, ikawa, indabo, ibigori.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">5.3.Nyarugenge</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Akarere k&rsquo;urubuye/ Akarere k&lsquo;umugongo:</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\"> Imboga, imbuto, ikawa, indabo, ibigori, ibishyimbo</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"color:#000000\">Hifashishijwe&nbsp; igitabo cyitwa &ldquo;Duhinge Kijyambere , agatabo ka 2&rdquo; ko muri Kamena 2012, cya Minisiteri y&rsquo;Ubuhinzi n&rsquo;Ubworozi.</span></em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"color:#000000\">Yanditwe na NIYIGABA Etienne, email (eniyigaba@yeanrwanda.org)</span></em></span></span></p>\r\n','1',6533,3,'2017-08-16 19:15:00','Ifumbire, Ubutaka, Intungagihingwa',1,'online','',''),(256,'Ubuhinzi Bwacu: Ibitekerezo by\'abahinzi Borozi ku nsanganyamatsiko igira iti:’ Ubwiyongere bw\'Abaturage no guteganya ibiribwa bihagije mu gihe kizaza’','food forecasting.jpeg','<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ubuhinzi Bwacu: Ibitekerezo by&rsquo;abahinzi Borozi ku nsanganyamatsiko igira iti:&rdquo; Ubwiyongere bw&#39;Abaturage no guteganya ibiribwa bihagije mu gihe kizaza&rdquo;</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Bahinzi Borozi namwe mukunda ubuhinzi Mwaramutse , uyu munsi taliki ya 13 Kanama 2017 tugarutse mu Kiganiro UBUHINZI BWACU, Turaganira ku nsanganyamatsiko igira iti<strong>:&ldquo;Ubwiyongere bw&#39;Abaturage no guteganya ibiribwa bihagije mu gihe kizaza.&rdquo;</strong> Abaturage bagenda biyongera umunsi ku munsi, ubutaka buhingwaho ntago bwiyongera, Kwiyongera kw&#39;abaturage kujyana no guteganya ikizabatunga . Abahinzi Borozi batanze ibitekerezo muri iki kiganiro ari benshi kandi turabashimira kuba bitabiriye.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byagiye byibanda kuri izi ngingo sikurikira:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Wumva hakorwa iki ngo tubashe guteganya ibiribwa bihagije </span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Icyakorwa ngo ubwiyongere bw&#39;abaturage bujyane n&#39;ubwiyongere bw&#39;umusaruro</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Uburyo busanzwe buhari bwo guteganya ibiribwa .</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Imbogamizi zigarara mu guteganya ibiribwa </span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ingamba n&#39;inama mu guteganya ibiribwa bijyanye n&#39;ubwiyongere bw&#39;abaturage</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ubutaka duhingaho ntibwiyongera ariko abaturage turiyongera, Uburyo bwo kugira food forecasting bwagakwiye kumenyekana cyane cyane kugeza ku rwego rwo hasi ku muturage mu rugo rwe, akenshi usanga tubyara ariko tukaba tutateganyije icyo abo tubyara bazarya, ibi rero bizana inzara ihoraho mu rugo kandi iyo ingo nyinshi zimeze gutya ni igihugu niho kiba kigana.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Uyu yatangiye agira ati: &ldquo;Mugire amahoro!Njye ndifashisha imwe mu mibare ya FAO Igaragaraza ko abatuye isi baziyongeraho 31% kugeza muri 2050. Ku buryo nibura 70% bazaba bari mu bihugu biri mu nzira y&#39;amajyambere. Ugiye kuvuga ubwiyongere mbere nambere twoye kubwumva nk&#39;inenge ahubwo nka opportunity mugihe imibereho nayo yatejwe imbere</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Wumva hakorwa iki ngo tubashe guteganya ibiribwa bihagije?</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Mbere na mbere mbona bigoye guteganya ibiryo mu Rwanda bijyanye n&#39;ubwiyongere bw&#39;abarutuye. Ariko nanone biroroshye mu gihe ibarurishamibare rikozwe neza kdi rigashingirwaho bihamye mu igenamigambi ryinzego zose bireba.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Abafatanyabikorwa mu buhinzi bakwiye kugira iki kibazo icyabo, umuhinzi agahinga azi ko urugo rwe abantu biyongera ijanisha iri n&rsquo;iri, umuhinzi agahinga kandi azi neza ubwiyongere bw&rsquo;isoko rye.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Minisiteri y&rsquo;Ubuhinzi n&rsquo;iy&rsquo;igenanamigambi bagakwiye gukorera hamwe bishoboka bagahugura Abafatanyabikorwa mu buhinzi ukuntu hateganywa ibiribwa bijyanye n&rsquo;ubwiyongere bw&rsquo;abaturage (Food Demand- Supply Forecasting and Population Growth colleneality).&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Icyakorwa ngo ubwiyongere bw&#39;abaturage bujyane n&#39;ubwiyongere bw&#39;umusaruro</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;umuvuduko w&#39;ubwiyongere n&#39;imuturire biratwara ubuso buhingwaho&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Abaturage bagomba kubyara abo bashoboye kubonera ibiribwa, MINISANTE irasabwa imbaraga mu gushishikariza abaturage kuboneza imbyaro, MINAGRI igakora ISOBANURAMPAMVU (concept note) rihamye.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;ababa mu mijyi nayo ubwayo iriyongera abagakoze ubuhinzi cyangwa abatunzwe nabwo bakagabanuka umunsi kuwundi. Ibi bigahuza n&#39;imibare ivuga ko muri 2020 abazaba bakora/batunzwe n&#39;ubuhinzi bazaba ari 50%. Ko bari 90+% , 40+% bazaba batunzwe n&#39;iki? Bari he? Bakora iki? Umusaruro wabonekaga se ba 90+% bakiwukora uzaba ukiboneka? Dutekereze kuri iki kibazo&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Icyakorwa cyambere ni ubuvugizi mugushishikariza abanyarwanda kubyara bake bahwanye nubushobozi. Kuko hari famille(imiryango) isabwa kugaburira abana 7 nta na 1ha y&rsquo;ubutaka buhingwa igira ntanindi source of income bagira. Ibi nibyo bitera kutihaza kubiribwa.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Gukoresha neza ubutaka buke dufite abahinzi bagahinga bafumbira kandi bakoresheje indobanure.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Ikindi mu buryo bwo guteganyiriza ibihe bishobora guterwa n&#39;ibiza , guteganya food demand (ibiryo bizakenerwa) mu nzagihe, byafasha mu kuzahangana no kugira ikigega gishyitse cy&#39;ibiribwa mu gihugu.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Techniques z&#39;ubuhinzi zitanga umusaruro uhagije mbona kugeza ubu tutarazigeraho! Simbona cyane ubwiyongere bw&#39;abaturage ko iriyo ntandaro y&#39;ibura ry&#39;ibiribwa, ahubwo uburyo bwo guhinga butanga umusaruro ni cyo kibazo gihatse ibindi.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Dukeneye ikigo cyihariye cyangwa unite yihariye yaba ikora kugiti cyayo cyangwa ikorera muri RAB ishinzwe iteganyabiribwa no guhunika mu rwego rwo kugoboka Bibaye ngombwa&rdquo; </span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo; Leta nishyire imbaraga mukugabanya ukwiyongera kw&rsquo;abaturage, hashyirweho amategeko, planning familial volontaire ntihagije&rdquo; </span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo; Ikintu cy&rsquo;imiturire no guhitamo ahubakwa gikwiye kwigwaho kuko tukivuze iminsi kandi kibonwa na buri wese ariko ntagikorwa. Aha mbona imiturire itagomba kurebwa gusa na minisiteri y&lsquo;ibikorwa remezo gusa ahubwo na MINAGRI ikabigiraho ijambo n&rsquo;umwanzuro ufatika.&rdquo; </span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Kuri iki kibazo cy&#39;ubwiyongere bw&#39;abatuye isi kubijyanisha no kwihaza mubyo kurya , tugomba kwibanda muguhindura imirire cyane cyane twibanda kuri cereals n&#39;imboga kuko urebye nk&#39;imirire y&#39;abanyarwanda aho usanga umuntu atetse inkono yuzuye ibishyimbo, ibijumba, amateke, imyumbati n&#39;ibindi nkabyo byagorana guhaza society!!! Twahindura imirire twibanda kuri complete diety , kuko uzasanga ubutaka wahingaho ibijumba bihagije abantu 100 n&#39;ubwo wahingaho umuceri, ingano cg ibigori byahaza abantu 100 ntaho buhuriye!!! Ikindi ubutaka wakororeho amafi, inkoko cg ubwo wahingaho imboga zahaza abantu 100 butandukanye cyane n&#39;ubwo wahingaho bush bean zahaza abantu 100!&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Nyuma yo guhindura imirire twakwibandaho ni ukongera productivity per unity area kuri medium duhingaho, ibyo twabigeraho twongera technology mubuhinzi tutibagiwe gukoresha imbuto(varieties) zitanga umusaruro kurusha izindi kandi tukagerageza guhinga buri crop aho yakwera neza aho gushora menshi tujya guforca ikirere, ubutaka, n&#39;izindi conditions zisabwa kugirango igihingwa runaka cyere ahantu runaka&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Uburyo busanzwe buhari bwo guteganya ibiribwa .</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Simpamya ko buhari bunoze. Ku rwego rwa rubanda ntabuhari. Ku rwego rwa Leta na ho ntabwo. Igikorwa ni ihunika ry&#39;igihe gito (short time food reserve) naryo ridatanga igisubizo ku bwiyongere bw&#39;abaturage n&#39;ikenerwa ry&#39;ibiribwa.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Uburyo busanzwe bwo guhiga ko umusaruro w&rsquo;Ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi ukwiye kwikuba 8% ni bwiza ariko inzego zishinzwe Ubuhinzi dukwiriye kujya duhiga abo tuzagaburira bakijuta aho guhiga ubwiyongere by&rsquo;ibiribwa gusa tutazi abo bizatunga. Iyi ngingo ni ingenzi kuko hari abanyapolitiki bamwe bakigira iturufu yabo ngo bakunde babone ubutegetsi.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Imbogamizi zigarara mu guteganya ibiribwa</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Bisaba imibare ya gihanga n&rsquo;ibarurishamibare rikoreshwa mu bukungu (Econometrics) kugirango abo bireba babishobore bacyeneye guhugurwa ubutitsa.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Mbona ntazaba zihari mugihe icyo dukora ari ihunika.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Inama isumba izindi ni ukubanza icyi kibazo buri wese akakigira icye. Abikorera bagashyiraho ibiro ngishwanama (consultancy bureau) zajya zigisha buri byiciro iyo mibare yo kujyanisha ubwiyongere by&rsquo;Abaturage n&rsquo;ubw&rsquo;ibiribwa babikoze neza nkeka ko Leta n&rsquo;imishinga bikorana byabatera ingabo mu bitugu.&rdquo; </span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Techniques z&#39;ubuhinzi ntiziragera kubo zigenewe ndavuga umuhinzi wo hasi ngo yongere umusaruro neza. Ubuhinzi buracyakorwa cyane n&#39;abantu badafite ubushobozi (abakene) bityo investissement (ishoramari)yabo iri hasi cyane ntibitume umusaruro uba mwiza . Imirima yageragezaga kwera ibihingwa ngandurarugo iragenda ishyirwaho inyubako n&#39;amashyamba nabyo bituma ahavaga ibishyimbo hagabanuka ,Icyakorwa&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ingamba n&#39;inama mu guteganya ibiribwa bijyanye n&#39;ubwiyongere bw&#39;abaturage</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Hakwiye kwitabwaho iteganya biribwa ritari ihunika (Food production forecasting not Food stocking) bikozwe na Leta. Ibi bigahuzwa nibarurishamibare ku mibereho yabaturage.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Bitewe n&#39;uko abakora ubuhinzi bagabanuka urusorongo, hakwiye ingamba n&#39;imirongo ya politiki ihamye ( serious measures and core agricultural policies) zizunganira ubuhinzi ndetse hakitabwa cyane ku ishoramari mu buhinzi ku buryo hazibwa icyuho cy&#39;abatabukora bavuzwe ruguru.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Ikindi ni uko ibihugu byose bidashingiye ku buhinzi. Urugero ni Djibuti itunzwe no gutumiza iburibwa hanze. Bisobanuye ko niba igenamigambi rigaragaje ko umusaruro wacu utazaduhaza kabone n&#39;aho ishoramari mu buhinzi ryatejwe imbere bizaba ngombwa gutumiza ibiribwa hanze. Bisobanuye ko hakwiye ingamba zinoze zo guteza imbere ubukungu bw&#39;igihugu n&#39;umuturage ny&#39;irizina. Iki kititaweho / kitagezweho tuzahora mu cyuho cy&#39;ibiribwa (Permenent food insecurity)&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Iyi topic ni nziza cyane. Ikibabaje ni uko abapoliticiens bashobora kuba batabitekerezaho. Ndumv&agrave; ibyavuzwe byakwandikwa neza bikagezwa kunzego bireba ariko buri rwose rugaragarizwa uruhare rwarwo kugirango ubwiyongere bw&#39;abaturage bijyane no guteganya ibibatunga kandi na buri rugo rumenye uruhare rwarwo. Hategurwa n&#39;ibiganiro mpaka kuri iyi topic ku maradio na TV&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Fond de garanties Ku bahinzi bizakurura abishoboye(big farmers) bashoremo agatubutse kuko bazaba babona ko ntagihombo bazahura nacyo&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;Gukora imibare igaragza ibiribwa bizaba bikenewe mu gihe runaka bitewe n&rsquo;abaturage bazaba batuye igihugu. Tukamenya iteganyabiribwa rihari tugahinnga tuzi ngo mu myaka icumi hazaba hakenewe ibiribwa bingana gutya.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Icyitonderwa:</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byose ntago byagarajwe hano bitewe n&rsquo;uko ari ikiganiro kirekire cyane hagiye hatoranywamo imirongo migari ikavugwa muri make. Amazina yabatanze ibitekerezo ntago yagaragajwe muri iyi nkuru gusa amagambo yose ari mu utwuguruzo n&rsquo;utwugarizo (&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;) yose yandikuwe uko yanditse mu kiganiro na ba nyirayo.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ikiganiro nk&rsquo;iki kiba buri ku Cyumweru.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ushaka gukurikira ibi biganiro ukaba uri umuhinzi/umworozi cyangwa umugoronome/veterineri ku rwego urwo arirwo rwose nawe wasaba kujya k&rsquo;urubuga rwa YEAN Whatsapp unyuze kuri nimero ikurikira: +250 788 845 727 ,wakurikira <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/YEANRWANDA/\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">YEAN kuri facebook</span></a> cyangwa <a href=\"https://twitter.com/YEAN_Rwanda\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">kuri twitter #UbuhinziBwacu @YEAN_Rwanda</span></a></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"color:#000000\">Yanditwe na NIYIGABA Etienne, email (eniyigaba@yeanrwanda.org)</span></em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n','3',14301,3,'2017-08-17 20:34:03','Ubuhinzi Bwacu',0,'online','',''),(257,'Dusobanukirwe umuganura n\'isano yawo n\'ubuhinzi n\' ibihembwe by\' ihinga mu Rwanda','umuganura photo.jpg','<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><strong>Dusobanukirwe umuganura n&rsquo;isano yawo n&rsquo;ubuhinzi n&rsquo; ibihembwe by&rsquo; ihinga mu Rwanda</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\">Umuganura mu Rwanda ni ibirori bitari ibyavuba kuko bifite inkomoko mu bihe bya kera u Rwanda rugitegekwa n&rsquo;abami. Ni ibirori byizihizwaga n&rsquo;Abanyarwanda bigatangizwa n&rsquo; umwami bishimira umusaruro w&rsquo;ubuhinzi. Byakorwaga mu byiciro: Ibirori byambere byo kuganura byabaga muri Mutarama ubwo uburo bwabaga bweze icyo gihe hagakorwa ibirori byo kuziganura byitwaga &ldquo;Umurorano&rdquo;. Ibirori by&rsquo; umurorano byakurikirwaga n&rsquo; umuganura nyirizina byakorwaga mbere gato y&rsquo;umuhindo ahagana muri Kanama ( y&rsquo; Ubu). Gusa umurorano ntiwari wamamaye cyane bitewe n&rsquo; uko mu Rwanda hose atariko babuhingaga.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\">Umuganura wo mu kwezi kwa munani bishimira umusaruro w&rsquo;amasaka wo wari uzwi cyane mu gihugu kandi ugahabwa agaciro gakomeye. Wabaga ugamije kwishimira umwero w&rsquo;amasaka. Kuba umuganura warakorerwaga ku mwero w&rsquo;amasaka n&rsquo;uburo ntibisobanuye ko nta yindi myaka yabaga yarahinzwe, ahubwo ni uko uburo n&rsquo;amasaka ari zo mbuto nkuru ( ziruta izindi) mu muco nyarwanda).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><strong>Intangiriro y&rsquo;umuganura n&rsquo;imitegurire yawo</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\">Nta gihe kizwi nyir&rsquo;izina umuganura waba waratangiye kwizihizwa, cyakora uruhererekane-mvugo rucishiriza ko watangiye ku ngoma ya Gihanga Ngomijana, ahayinga mu kinyejana cya cyenda. Ikizwi neza ni uko kwizihiza ibirori by&rsquo;umuganura byaciwe mu 1925 bikozwe n&rsquo;abakoroni ndetse umwiru wari ishinzwe iyo mihango witwaga Gashamura bamwirukana mu gihugu. Gusa nyuma y&rsquo;icyo gihe abantu bakomeje kwizihiza umuganura mu miryango yabo.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\">Mu nzira y&rsquo; umuganura (imihango yari yaragenewe ibirori by&rsquo; umuganura) hagaragaramo uko ubirori byabaga biteguye neza aho abashinzwe imyiteguro yabyo bari abiru b&rsquo;abatsobe) bakomoka kuru Musana. Ubusanzwe iyo nzu yo kwa Musana ikaba yari ifite inshingano zo guhinga uburo n&rsquo;amasaka byari bigenewe gukoreshwa mu birori by&rsquo; umuganura. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\">Ibirori by&rsquo; umuganura umwami umwamikazi n&rsquo; umugabe kazi babigiragamo uruhare cyane. Ibyo birori byakomerezaga mu miryango abakuru b&rsquo; imiryango bakabigiramo uruhare ndetse bikab abityo mu ngo nyir&rsquo;izina. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\">Umuganura wizihizwaga bavuga umutsima w&rsquo;amasaka bigatangirira I Bwami umwami umugabekazi, umwamikazi n&rsquo; umwiru mukuru bakora ikimenyetso cyo guturira,kwarika no guhakura umutsima ubundi ibirori bigakomereza mu miryango. Cyakora ntibyari ihame ko kuganura bikorwa barya umutsima gusa kuko mu miryango wasangaga bashigishe amarwa, umusururu, Inturire cyangwa se igikoma cy&rsquo;amasaka. Umukuru w&rsquo;umuryango ni we wabanzaga gusomaho cyangwa kurya abandi bagize umuryango bagakurikiraho. Umuganura w&rsquo;umusaruro w&rsquo;amasaka ni wo wari umunsi mukuru w&rsquo; igihugu kuko amasaka yahingwaga mu duce twose tw&rsquo; igihugu.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\">Uko ibihe byagiye bihinduka ni na ko umuganura wagiye uhindura isura. Ibi bishimangirwa n&rsquo;uko izari imbuto nkuru zunganiwe n&rsquo;zindi. Imwe mu mpamvu amasaka yari imbuto nkuru n uko yavagamo ibinyobwa nk&rsquo;amarwa umurururu igikoma, akavamo n&rsquo;ibiribwa nk&rsquo;umutsima n&rsquo;impengeri. Ibirori bnyayoborwaga n&rsquo; umwami na byo byacitse ahagana mu mpera z&rsquo;ingoma ya Musinga kuganura bisigara muri rubanda mu miryango.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><strong>Umuganura uhura ute n&rsquo; ihinga</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\">Umwaka w&rsquo; ubuhinzi ugira ibihembwe bitatu. Igihembwe cya mbere gitangira mu gihe cy&rsquo; umuhindo utangira mu kwezi kwa cyenda kikarangira muri Gashyantare. Iki ni cyo gihe umurorano wakorwaga kera. Igihembwe cya kabiri kitangirana na Werurwe kigasozwa na Kamena aho usanga hirya no hino isarura ririmbanyije ndetse mu kwezi gukurikira amasaka akaba asarurwa anahunikwa. Ni muri iki gihembwe ugereranyije n&rsquo; ingangabihe y&rsquo; icyo gihe ibirori by&rsquo;Umuganura byatangiraga gutegurwa bitegura imboneka za Kanama. Igihembwe cya gatatu cy&rsquo; ihinga gitangirana na Nyakanga kikageza muri Nzeri ni cyo cyahuriranaga na bya birori by&rsquo;umuganura ndetse muri iki gihembwe niho umwami yatangizaga igihembwe cya mbere cy&rsquo;ingengabihe y&rsquo;ihinga y&rsquo;icyo gihe. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\">N&rsquo;ubwo Abanyarwanda batari barize icyo gihe, bakoresheje ibimenyetso gakondo bamenyaga ko imvura iri mu mezi yo guhanguka. Mu nzira y&rsquo; umuganura hagaragaramo ko amasuka yacuriwe mu Buberuka (amaberuka) atarakora hasi yamurikirwaga umwami na we akayafatira imbere ye agaterura akabwira wa mwiru ati &ldquo;<em>ngaho genda uhinge kandi weze</em>&rdquo;. Muri make umwami rakaba atanze uruhushya ku mugaragaro rwo gutangira igihembwe cy&rsquo; ihinga mu gihugu cyose. Nk&rsquo;uko bigaragara mu mihango y&rsquo;inzira y&rsquo;ubwiru y&rsquo;umuganura, ihinga ryatangiriraga mu nkuka z&rsquo;ibishanga bitewe n&rsquo;uko icyo gihe imvura yabaga itararimbanya. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\">Nyamara ingengabihe isanzwe dukurikiza ubu itandukanye gato n&rsquo;iyakoreshwaga kera (<em>tuzabigarukaho ubuhataha</em>). Kuba rero ihinga ryaratangizwaga ariko bagatangirira mu nkuka z&rsquo;ibishanga byumvikanisha neza ko icyo gihe imvura yabaga itaragwa ngo ihamye. Cyakora rubanda rwanakomerezagaho gusekera/ kurima ibisigati bitegura imvura y&rsquo;&rsquo;umuhindo. Muri ibi bihe kandi habaga hanakusanywa amakuru y&rsquo; ikirere hifashishijwe amavubiro yari hirya no hino mu gihugu. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\">Kuba umuganura warakorwaga muri Kanama bifite igisobanuro kuko babaga bitegura imfura y&rsquo; amezi y&rsquo;umwaka Nyarwanda &ldquo;Nzeri&rdquo;. Ukwezi kwa Nzeri ni ko kwari ukwezi kwa mbere k&rsquo; umwaka wo hambere. Ibi bisobanuye ko uko twita Mutarama muri iki gihe mbere y&rsquo;abakoroni Atari ko kwari ukwa mbere. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\">Umushakashatsi Pag&egrave;s mu bushakashatsi yakoze ku mezi n&rsquo; umwaka by&rsquo; u Rwanda rwo hambere yagaragaje ko umwaka watangiraga muri Nzeri kandi ukagira amezi 13. Bitewe n&rsquo; uko mu mpera za Nyakanga bamaze guhunika imvura yatangiraga kugwa. Ni yo mpamvu Kanama yo hambere yabagamo iyo bita &ldquo;Gatumba gatoya&rdquo; na &ldquo;gatumba kanini&rdquo;.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><strong>Ese hari isano iri mu migendekere y&rsquo;umuganura wo hambere n&rsquo; uw&rsquo;ubu?</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\">Hari byinshi byahindutse mu mitegurire y&rsquo; umuganura wo hambere n&rsquo; uw&rsquo;ubu. Isano ya mbere ni uko umuganura ategurwaga mu rwego rw&rsquo; igihugu kandi igategurwa n&rsquo; umwiru ubishinzwe ukayoborwa n&rsquo; umwami. Ikindi ni uko umuganura wo hambere wabaga mu mu isarura ry&rsquo;amasaka. Bitewe n&rsquo; ihindagurika ry&rsquo; imibereho y&rsquo;Abanyarwanda n&rsquo; imiyoborere y&rsquo; igihugu hari ibyagiye bihinduka bitewe n&rsquo; ibyo ubuyobozi bw&rsquo; igihugu bubona biboneye.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\">Nk&rsquo;ubu, umuganura wo hambere na wo wabaga izingiro ry&rsquo;ubusabane hagati y&rsquo; imiryango n&rsquo;abaturanyi nk&rsquo;uko ubu bimeze. Kuba Minisiteri y&rsquo; Ubuhinzi n&rsquo; ubworozi buri ntangiriro y&rsquo;igihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga itangiza ku mugaragaro igihembwe cy&rsquo; ihinga mu gihugu, bigaragaza neza agaciro ubuyobozi buha ubuhinzi. Cyakora aho bisa n&rsquo; ibitandukaniye ni uko amakuru ku itangira ry&rsquo; igihembwe cy&rsquo; ihinga adatangarizwa mu muganura nka kera. Ibi bishobora kuba biterwa n&rsquo;uko usanga ubu imitegurire y&rsquo;umuganura ishingiye kuri Minisiteri y&rsquo; umuco kurusha Minisiteri y&rsquo; ubuhinzi n&rsquo; ubworozi. Ikindi ni uko kera umwami yatangazaga rimwe igihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga mu muganura nyamara ubu Minisiteri y&rsquo;Ubuhinzi n&rsquo; ubworozi yo yita ku gutangaza no gutangiza ku mugaragaro ibihembwe by&rsquo;ihinga byose uko ari bitatu.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><em>Tubifurije umuganura muhire wa 2017</em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif\"><em>Yateguwe na Niyigaba Fid&egrave;le, (email: nfidelis12@yahoo.fr) ushinzwe itangazamakuru muri Nile Basin Discouse akaba n&rsquo;impuguke mu muco nyarwanda.</em></span></span></p>\r\n','1',6009,3,'2017-08-22 23:25:03','Igihembwe cy\'Ihinga, Umuganura',0,'online','',''),(259,'Kuhira: Ingaruko zo kubura kw\'amazi k\'umusaruro w\'ibihingwa, Igihe igihingwa gikenera amazi cyane, n\'ingero z\'ibihingwa n\'igihe bikeneramo amazi menshi.','160331226180901839.jpg','<p>Kuhira ni ukongera amazi mu murima kugirango&nbsp; ubutaka bukomeze buhehere mu gice imizi iba irimo kugirango igihingwa gikure neza kandi gitange umusaruro mwiza kandi mwinshi .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubuhinzi bukozwe bugendeye ku kugwa kw&rsquo;imvura nk&rsquo;isoko yonyine yo kobona mazi ibihingwa bikoresha kugirango bikure bugira ingaruka mbi k&rsquo;umusaruro kuko imvura ishobora kugwa cyangwa ntigwe ititaye ku kuba umuhinzi yarahinze cyangwa atarahinze . Ni ngombwa rero ko tumenya ibijyanye no kuhira kugirango twunganire amazi y&rsquo;imvura twongera amazi mu murima kugirango twuzuze amazi igihingwa gikenera ngo gitange umusaruro mwiza.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Twuhiza amazi angana ate inshuro zingahe?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Ibi biterwa n&rsquo;amazi igihingwa dushaka kuhira gikenera. Amazi igihingwa gikenera abarwa muri milimetero ku munsi (mm/umunsi) cyangwa milimetero ku kwezi (mm/ukwezi) . Amazi akenewe kongerwa mu murira wuhira kandi nanone angana n&rsquo;amazi igihingwa gikenera ukuyemo amazi y&rsquo;imvura yaguye. Mu busanzwe twagakwiye kuhira buri munsi ariko bitewe n&rsquo;uko bisaba imirimo myinshi n&rsquo;igihe kinini twuhira dushyiramo intera wenda y&rsquo;iminsi ibiri, itanu, icumi bitewe n&rsquo;igihingwa ariko ugakora ku buryo ya ntera wasizemo y&rsquo;igihe amazi wuhiye azaba agihagije kugeza igihe uzongera kuhirira.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Muri make ni kangahe dukwiye kuhira?: Kenshi gahagije kugirango igihingwa kiticwa no kubura amazi. Twuhiza amazi angina ate? :Amazi angana n&rsquo;ayo igihingwa cyakoresheje&nbsp; kuva ku gihe uheruka kuhirira.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyo umaze kuhira igihingwa kiba kibasha gukoresha amazi ku buryo bworoshye cyane ariko uko hagenda hashira iminsi nyuma yo kuhira utarongera kuhira igihingwa kigenda kibura imbaraga zo gukoresha amazi aba asigaye mu butaka. Ugomba kuhira mbere y&rsquo;uko igihingwa gitangira kwerekana ibimenyetso byo kubura amazi kuko iyo cyambyerekanye kiba cyamaze guta ubushobozi bumwe buzakigeza ku musaruro wifuzwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Amazi ashobora gushyirwa mu murima&nbsp; ashobora guterwa n&rsquo;ibintu bitatu:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Ubwoko bw&rsquo;ubutaka</li>\r\no<li>Uburebure bw&rsquo;imizi y&rsquo;igihingwa</li>\r\no<li>Uburyo bwo kuhira bukoreshwa</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Ubwoko bw&rsquo;ubutaka:</em> Bugena amazi menshi ashoboka ashobora gufatwa mu butaka. Ubutaka b&rsquo;umusenyi bushobora gufata amazi make, muri ubu butaka bw&rsquo;umusenyi kuko buhitisha amazi cyane bisaba kubira kenshi ukoresheje amazi make buri nshuro wuhiye. Naho k&rsquo;ubutaka bw&rsquo;ibumba cyangwa inombe kuko bwo budahitisha amazi cyane bisaba kubira inshuro nke ariko ukoresha amazi menshi buri nshuro wuhiye.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Uburebure b&rsquo;imizi y&rsquo;igihingwa:</em> ibihingwa bifite imizi migufi, amazi make ashobora kuguma mu gice kirimo imizi gusa ukuhira kenshi. Naho ku bifite imizi miremire bikenera n&rsquo;amazi menshi kuburyo wakuhira gake ariko ugashyiramo amazi menshi. Ibihingwa bikiri bito bigira imizi migufi ugereranyije n&rsquo;ibikuze niyo mpamvu iyo ukimara gutera cyangwa kubiba , igihingwa biba bikeneye amazi make ariko inshuro nyinshi kurusha mu gihe kimaze gukura.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Uburyo bwo kuhira bukoreshwa:</em> Amazi ashobora kwinjira mu butaka hakoreshejwe uburyo ubu n&rsquo;ubu bigomba kureberwa mu murima. Urugero , ugiye gukoresha kuhira ushyira amazi mu murima nko mu muceri amazi menshi ashobora kwinjira mu butaka mu gihe wuhiye inshuro imwe kurusha uko waba ugiye kuyashyiramo ukoresheje kuhira hakoreshejwe utwuma tuyanyanyagiza mu murima, gusa mu kuhira ku buso buto uburyo bukoreshwa aba ari ingenzi kugirango umenye inshuro uzuhira ibihingwa byawe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingaruko zo kubura kw&rsquo;amazi k&rsquo;umusaruro w&rsquo;ibihingwa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu busanzwe mu murima wuhirwa ibihingwa ntago byakagombye kugira ingaruka zo kubura amazi kuko amazi agomba gushyirwamo mbere y&rsquo;uko ibimenyeho by&rsquo;ibura ry&rsquo;amazi ku bihingwa bigaragara.&nbsp; Gusa bishobora kudashoboka kuhira kuri cya gihe koko igihingwa gikeneye amazi. Urugero umugezi ushobora gukama cyangwa ukagira amazi make mu gihe akenewe na benshi, guhitamo gusaranganya amazi make ufite ku buso bunini kugirango buri muhinzi wese aboneho nubwo aba ari make kuyo yari akeneye. Muri icyo gihe cyo kubura kw&rsquo;amazi ni ngombwa kumenya:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Igihingwa kigirwaho ingaruka nyinshi no kubura amazi,igihingwa kizagira umusaruro muke nikitabona amazi.</li>\r\no<li>Igihe igihingwa gikenera amazi cyane mu mikurire yacyo.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Birumvikana ko hari ibintu &nbsp;byatuma uhitamo kuhira cyane igihingwa runaka nk&rsquo;inyungu gitanga ukurikije n&rsquo;ibindi, ibi biterwa n&rsquo;umuhinzi uko abyumva.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko ibihingwa byangizwa no kubura kw&rsquo;amazi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Muri rusange ibihingwa bihingwa hakenewe gusarurwa ibibabi byabyo cyangwa imbuto ziribwa nibyo bikunda kugirwaho ingaruka nyinshi zo kubura amazi kurusha ibihingwa bihingwa hagamijwe&nbsp; gusarurwa impeke cyangwa imbuto</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibihingwa byihanganira kubura amazi:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Imyumbati</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Ipamba</li>\r\no<li>Uburo</li>\r\no<li>Inkori</li>\r\no<li>Amasaka</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibihingwa byihanaganira gake kubura amazi</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Alfalfa</li>\r\no<li>Citrus</li>\r\no<li>Inkeri</li>\r\no<li>Ubunyobwa</li>\r\no<li>Soya</li>\r\no<li>Ibihwagari</li>\r\no<li>ingano</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibihingwa byihanganira biri mu rugero kubura amazi</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Ibishyimbo</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Amashu</li>\r\no<li>Ibigori</li>\r\no<li>Ibitunguru</li>\r\no<li>Amashaza</li>\r\no<li>Urusenda</li>\r\no<li>Inyanya</li>\r\no<li>Imyungu</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibihingwa bitihanganira/byangizwa vuba no kubura amazi</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Urutoki</li>\r\no<li>Imboga (z&rsquo;ubwoko bwose)</li>\r\no<li>Umuceri wo mubishanga</li>\r\no<li>Ibijumba n&rsquo;ibirayi</li>\r\no<li>Ibisheke</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Nk&rsquo;uko bigaragara muri ibi bihingwa tubagejejeho, umuceri, urutoki, ibijumba n&rsquo;ibirayi,ibisheke byose ntibyihanganira kubura kw&rsquo;amazi , bivuzeko niyo habaho kubura amazi guke umusaruro ubivaho uragabanyuka cyane. Kubura kw&rsquo;amazi bigomba kwirindwa muri ibi bihingwa .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibihingwa nk&rsquo;amasaka, uburo byo bigaragaza kwihanganira kubura amazi ,niba rero habayeho ibura ry&rsquo;amazi cyangwa izuba rigacana mu gihe kitari kinini umusaruro wabyo ntago uzagirwaho ingaruka cyane</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Niba ibihingwa byinshi bitewe mu murima wuhirwa tuvuge nk&rsquo;ubunyobwa, amasaka na Dodo ariko amazi akaba adahagije , mbere na mbere uzabanza kuhira imboga(dodo) kuko arizo zicwa cyane no kubura amazi kurusha ibindi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Igihe igihingwa gikenera amazi cyane mu mikurire yacyo</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubuzima bw&rsquo;ibihingwa bimara igihembwe kimwe cy&rsquo;ihinga mu murima bushobora kugabaygwamo ibice bitatu:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><em>Igihe igihingwa kigitangira gukura:</em> kuva ku gutera kugeza kigize 10% by&rsquo;igihingwa cyose</li>\r\no<li><em>Igihe igihingwa kirimo gukura:</em> kuva kigize 10% kugeza kigize 70% by&rsquo;igihingwa cyose</li>\r\no<li><em>Igihembwe kigeze hagati:</em> harimo kuzana indabo n&rsquo;imbuto zizatanga umusaruro zitangiye kwikora</li>\r\no<li><em>Igihembwe kirangira:</em> harimo kwera kw&rsquo;igihingwa no kugisarura.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Muri rusange twavugako igice cy&rsquo; Igihembwe kigeze hagati&nbsp; aricyo amazi aba akenewe cyane bivuzeko aramutse abuze iki gihe umusaruro ugabanyuka cyane. Ibi biterwa n&rsquo;uko aribwo igihingwa kiba gikeneye amazi menshi. Igihe igihingwa kitabangamirwa cyane no kubura kw&rsquo;amazi ni &ldquo;Igihembwe kirangira&rdquo; . iki gihe igihingwa kiba kirimo kwera no gusarurwa. Mu gihe igihingwa gisarurwa cyumye bizagira ingaruka nto k&rsquo;umusaruro , gusa n&rsquo;ibihingwa bisarurwa bigitoshye nka dodo nabyo kubura kw&rsquo;amazi muri iki gihe byabigiraho ingaruka.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Igihe igihingwa kigitangira gukura&rdquo; na &ldquo;Igihe igihingwa kirimo gukura&rdquo; byo biri hagati na hagati ugereranyije n&rsquo;ibyo tuvuze haruguru. Ibihingwa bimwe iyo bibuze amazi muri ibi bihe bishaka uko biyabona wenda bikazana imizi miremire.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu murima uhinzemo igihingwa kimwe, ariko umurima wose ukaba utaraterewe rimwe, amazi akaba ari make abahinzi bagirwa inama yo kuhira ibihingwa bigeze ku gihe &ldquo;Igihembwe kigeze hagati&rdquo;(harimo kuzana indabo n&rsquo;imbuto zizatanga umusaruro zitangiye kwikora).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingero z&rsquo;ibihingwa bimwe n&rsquo;igihe bikeneramo amazi menshi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Urutoki : Igihe cyose</li>\r\no<li>Ibishyimbo: Mu gihe bizana ururabo no gukora imisogwe/imiteja</li>\r\no<li>Amashu: Igihe ari kubumba no mu gihe ari kwera</li>\r\no<li>Amacunga: Mu gihe azana indabo no gukora imbuto</li>\r\no<li>Ipamba: Mu gihe rizana indabo no gukora ipamba</li>\r\no<li>Imizabibu: Mu gihe ikura no kuzana indabo kurusha igihe cyo gukura kw&rsquo;imbuto</li>\r\no<li>Ubunyobwa: Mu gihe buzana indabo no gukora imbuto</li>\r\no<li>Ibigori: mu gihe bitangiye guheka no gupakira imiheko</li>\r\no<li>Ibitunguru: Mu gihe igice cyo mu butaka kiri kubyimba</li>\r\no<li>Amashaza: mu gihe ari kuzana ururabo&nbsp; no gupakira mu misogwe</li>\r\no<li>Urusenda: igihe cyose</li>\r\no<li>Inanasi: igihe zirimo gukura mbere y&rsquo;uko zana</li>\r\no<li>Ibijumba/ibirayi: Mu gihe biri gushora no gukora ibijumba</li>\r\no<li>Umuceri:&nbsp; mu gihe bizana ihundo no kuzana ururabo</li>\r\no<li>Amasaka: mu gihe bizana ihundo no kwera k&rsquo;amahundo</li>\r\no<li>Soya: Mu gihe izana ururabo no gupakira mu misogwe</li>\r\no<li>Ibisheke: Igihe bitangiye gukura bishibuka bizana n&rsquo;ingingo</li>\r\no<li>Ibihwagari: Mu kuzana ururabo kuruta mu kwera kwabyo</li>\r\no<li>Itabi: mu kuzana ururabo</li>\r\no<li>Watermelon (imyungu): mu kuzana indabo no gukura k&rsquo;umwungu wazo</li>\r\no<li>Ingano: mu kuzana ururabo.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em><span dir=\"ltr\">Iyi ni inyigisho ya FAO yashyizwe mu Kinyarwanda na NIYIGABA Etienne (<a class=\"Xx\" dir=\"ltr\" href=\"mailto:eniyigaba@yeanrwanda.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" tabindex=\"-1\" target=\"_blank\">eniyigaba@yeanrwanda.org</a>) </span></em></strong></p>\r\n','3',2865,40,'2017-10-05 20:45:00','Ubuhinzi bwacu',0,'online','',''),(260,'UBWISHINGIZI BW\'UBUHINZI N\'UBWOROZI','New Microsoft Office Publisher Document.jpg','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Nkuko bimaze kumenyererwa ku cyumweru&nbsp; guhera saa mbiri &nbsp;ku mbuga nkoranyambaga zose za YEAN tuba turi mu kiganiro <strong>UBUHINZI BWACU</strong> , kuri iki cyumweru 5 Ugushyingo 2017&nbsp; twaganiriye ku ngingo igira iti <strong>&quot;</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> <strong>UBWISHINGIZI BW&#39;UBUHINZI N&#39;UBWOROZI.</strong> </span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&quot;</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">. Aho abahinzi n&rsquo;aborozi bagiye bagaruka ku kamaro kanini k&rsquo;iyi gahunda nziza ifitiye ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi muri rusange.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Minisiteri y&rsquo;ubuhinzi n ubworozi mu rugendo rwo guhindura ubuhinzi/ubworozi gakondo&nbsp; bukaba ubuhinzi/ubworozi bw&rsquo;ubucuruzi busagurira isoko nkuko bitegenyijwe mu mushinga wa MINIGRI PSTA III ndetse no mu cyerecyezo cy&rsquo;u Rwanda cya 2020. Bitewe n ibiza abahinzi n&rsquo;aborozi bahura nabyo mu mirimo yabo y&rsquo;ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi, leta yatangije gahunda nziza yo kwishinganisha ku bikorwa by&rsquo;ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi (agriculture and livestock insurance), ubu bwishingizi bukazakorwa mu bufatanya n&rsquo;ibigo bifite ubunararibonye muri iyi gahunda y&rsquo;ubwishingizi. Igeragezwa kuri iyi gahunda rikaba ryarakozwe hamwe biciye muri gahunda ya HINGA URISHINGIWE. Ubu bwishingizi kurubu buri kugaragara m&rsquo;ubworozi cyane cyane bw&rsquo;inka, ikigo kugeza ubu kizwi gitanga ubwishingizi ni SONARWA.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Mu iki kiganiro hagaragayemo ibitekerezo byinshi byose byagiye bigaruka kuri ibi bice&nbsp; bikurikira: </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>*uruhare rw&#39;umuhinzi/umworozi mu gushyiraho iyi gahunda nziza y&#39;ubwishingizi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Abahinzi n&rsquo;aborozi barishimira cyane gahunda zigenda zijyaho mu guteza imbere imirimo y&rsquo;ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi, uyu mworozi aragira ati &ldquo;<em>Iyi gahunda yo kwishinganisha ni nziza kuko izafasha cyane aborozi bazayitabira kuko umworozi ntazongera guhangayikishwa n&#39;inkuba kandi nizajyaga zipfa zivurwa zizajya zishyurwa.bityo aborozi barashishikarizwa kwitabira iyi gahunda&rdquo;</em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">*<strong>Ibyashingirwaho mu gushyiraho iyi gahunda yo kwishingira</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Kukirebana n&rsquo;ibyashingirwaho muri iyi gahumda abahinzi n&rsquo;aborozi bakomeje bagaragazako hakwiye kungurana ibitekerezo kugira gahunda irusheho kugera&nbsp; kuwaba ayifuza uyu muhinzi yaravugize ati&rdquo; <em>kubyashingirwaho mugutanga ubwishingizi mbona hashingirwa kuribi bikurikira:1) kuba uhinga cg yorora abikora nk&rsquo;umwuga 2) ubuso bukorerwaho 3) umumaro bifitiye abanyarwanda n&rsquo;igihugu muri rusange.&rdquo;. </em>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Abandi bakomeje bavugako hanagenderwa no k&rsquo;ubyiciro byacu by&rsquo;ubudehe bityo abahinzi n&rsquo;aborozi bato bato iyi gahunda ikabunganira mu biza bahura nabyo m&rsquo;ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">*<strong>uruhare rw&#39;ibigo byikorera n&#39;ibya leta mu gushyiraho iyi gahunda nziza yo kwishingana</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Hakenewe kubanza kwigisha cyane ubukangurambaga bugakorwa inzego zose zigashyiramo imbaraga cyane.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Korohereza abahinzi n&rsquo;aborozi mu kugezwaho iyi gahunda, uyu muhinzi ati&rdquo; <em>harebwa uburyo n&rsquo;iyi gahunda yashyirwaho nkunganire&rdquo;</em></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">*<strong>Imbogamizi</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Uyu mworozi gayize ati&rdquo;<em>Nubusanzwe ikintu cy&#39;ubwishingizi dusanzwe tukizi mubindi bitari ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi aho kwishingana bisaba nyiri ukwishingana kugira icyo atanga yishinganisha ibye. Akenshi iyo urebye ikiguzi cy&#39;ubwishingizi ex:imodoka,inzu,ubucuruzi,... usanga ibiciro byihagazeho. Aha ngarutse k umurimo wacu w&#39;ubuhinzi/ubworozi nkasanga izi zishobora kuzaba zimwe mumbogamizi zituma umuhinzi/umworozi atibona muri gahunda haramutswe hadafashwe ingamba ndetse na politike zigishijweho inama kumpande zombie</em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Undi ati&rdquo;<em>Insurance company ziragora cyane</em> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Uyu muhinzi nawe yatanze urugero kuri company agira ati <em>nigize kubaza coop&nbsp; imwe muri kirehe impamvu Itagikorana n;ubwishingizi bansubije bati: bimwe mu bibazo duhura nabyo byatuma dufata ibwishingizi ni izuba kandi company y&rsquo;ubwishingizi yo igendera kubipimo bya satelite mukuvuga ko agace runaka kabonye imvura batitaye ingano yayo ndetse na village yabonetse. bo bafata akarere kose. kandi murabizi hari ubwo umvura igwa agace kamwe akandi mwegeranye ntigwe.&nbsp; ingero zirahari..... aha rero niho ibigo byagashyize imparaga bikagafata ibipimo on villages basis. pana kureba district yose cg sector yose.</em> bigasaba imbaraga za meteorwanda etc...</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">*<strong>Ibisubizo kuri izo mbogamizi</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Abahizi n abororo batanze bimwe mu busibizo ko hacyenewe ingamba ndetse na politike zigishijweho inama kumpande zombie.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Uyu ati <em>gahunda ni niza guusa leta ishyiremo imbaraga Ubu bwishingizi hakwiye kubamo nkunganire ya leta &#39;as long as farmers are not yet professionals, and their returns are not yet enough compared to their production&rsquo;</em>.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ikindi abahinzi <em>bifujeko iyi gahunda igomba gushyirwamo imbara kurwego rwa coop not on individual farmers level.</em> Uyu mworozi ati &ldquo;<em>muborozi ho nkeka ko bishoboka kureba umworozi kigiti cye ariko muhinzi ho results zab nkeya&rdquo;.</em> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Undi muhinzi ati &ldquo;<em>izo company of crop and livestock ensurance bagomba kureba ibijyanye n ibiciro byabo maze bakamenya bakita no kunyungu umuhinzi ategeganya muri ubwo buhinzi&rdquo;</em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">*Imyanzuro</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Banki nkuru ishyirashyiraho &quot;IKIGEGA CYIHARIYE CYUNGANIRA UBUHINZI (Agriculture Guarantee Fund) ngo yirengere ibibazo (risks) ziri mu buhinzi n.ubworozi.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Iyi gahunda ishyizwe mubikorwa neza byaba muri motivation zituma ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi bwitabirirwa na benshi, cyane cyane urubyiruko ndetse n&#39;abashoramari</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi bugakorwa hagamijwe umusaruro wo k&rsquo;urwego rwo hejuru</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Guhinga no korora twabanje kumenya iby&#39; ingenzi bituma tubona umusaruro.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Kongera ishoramari mu&nbsp; buhinzi&nbsp; rigamije umusaruro</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Gukora ubuhinzi budahungabanywa n ihindagurika ry ikirere</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Icyitonderwa:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byose ntago byagarajwe hano bitewe n&rsquo;uko ari ikiganiro kirekire cyane hagiye hatoranywamo imirongo migari ikavugwa muri make.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Amazina yabatanze ibitekerezo ntago yagaragajwe muri iyi nkuru gusa amagambo yose ari mu utwuguruzo n&rsquo;utwugarizo (&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;) yose yandikuwe uko yanditse mu kiganiro.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ikiganiro nk&rsquo;iki kiba buri ku Cyumweru.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ushaka gukurikira ibi biganiro ukaba uri umuhinzi/umworozi cyangwa umugoronome/veterineri ku rwego urwo arirwo rwose nawe wasaba kujya k&rsquo;urubuga rwa YEAN Whatsapp unyuze kuri nimero ikurikira: +250 788 845 727 ,wakurikira YEAN kuri facebook cyangwa kuri twitter #UbuhinziBwacu @YEAN_Rwanda</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n','3',1955,40,'2017-11-12 09:00:00','ibijumba',0,'online','',''),(261,'Ubuhinzi bwacu: Ibitekerezo by\'Abahinzi ku ngingo igira iti :Abize ubuhinzi n\'ubworozi mu gukora imirimo y\'ubuhinzi n\'ubworozi','QQ20171125184736.jpg','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Nkuko bimaze kumenyererwa ku cyumweru &nbsp;guhera saa mbiri &nbsp;ku mbuga nkoranyambaga zose za YEAN tuba turi mu kiganiro </span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>UBUHINZI BWACU</strong></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;, kuri iki cyumweru 19 Ugushyingo 2017 twaganiriye ku ngingo igira iti </span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>&quot;</strong></span></span></strong>&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>ABIZE UBUHINZI N&#39;UBWOROZI MU GUKORA IMIRIMO N&#39;IBIKORWA BY&#39; UBUHINZI/UBWOROZI</strong></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>&quot;.</strong></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;Aho urubyiruko rukora, rwize ndetse n&rsquo;ururi gukora ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi ruhurira mu ihuriro rya YEAN bagiye batanga ibitekerezo bitandukanye bitewe n&rsquo;uko babona urubyiruko ndetse n&rsquo;imirimo/ibikorwa by&rsquo; ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi muri rusange.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Mu iki kiganiro hatanzwe ibitekerezo byinshi byose byagiye bigaruka kuri ibi bice &nbsp;bikurikira: </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>Ni uruhe ruhare abize ubuhinzi/bworozi kugeza ubu bafite mu buhinzi/bworozi? </strong></span></span></strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Ikiganiro gitangira abitabiriye ku mbuga zose bishimiye iyi nsanganyamatsiko ubona bakereye kuyitangaho ibitekerezo kandi niko byagenze. Turagenda tubibagezaho uko byagiye bitangwa nta gihinduweho.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&laquo;&nbsp;Abize ubuhinzi n&#39;ubworozi bafite uruhare rukomeye mu iterambere ry&#39;ubuhinzi kuko ababukora batarabwize usanga bagirwa inama n&#39;ababwize kumigirire ya buri munsi kugira ngo beze banorore neza&nbsp;&raquo;. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&laquo;&nbsp;Impamvu zituma abize ubuhinzi bamwe batabukora bakajya mubindi akenshi usanga ari uko babura capital (igishoro) nkanjye nihereyeho mfite igishoro sinajya mubindi kuko nzi neza inyungu ziba mubuhinzi n&#39;ubworozi, kuko mbukurikirana umunsi k&rsquo;umunsi, indi mpamvu ni uko usanga akenshi igiciro cy&rsquo;ibikomoka k&rsquo;ubuhinzi gihindagurika cyane bitewe n&#39;uko value and supply chains za crops zitakozweho ubushakashatsi ngo amakuru yazo amenyekane, ikindi ni uko inganda( food processing industries) na post harvest handlings bikiri poor (bigikennye) cyane bigatuma abize ubuhinzi bagira impungenge zo gushora mubuhinzi kuko akenshi umusaruro utakara ni mwinshi bigatuma batizera maximising. Impamvu rero bigira mubindi si uko batazi ko bushobora kunguka ahubwo ni izo mpamvu zitandukanye zibitera&nbsp;&raquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&laquo;&nbsp;Uruhare abize ubuhinzi/bworozi kugeza ubu bafite mu buhinzi/bworozi: Nibo bakora imirimo ya leta cg y&#39;imishinga ijyanye n&#39;ikigoronomu n&#39;iyamamazabuhinzi&nbsp;&raquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati : &laquo;&nbsp;Uruhare ni ruto kuko UBUHINZI henshi buvangirwa n&#39;Abanyapolitiki, Abakuru b&#39;inzego z&#39;Umutekano n&#39;Abashoramari babona amasoko mu buhinzi (Gutunganya ibishanga, abacuruza inyongeramusaruro n&#39;abandi banyabubasha) aba bantu nta jambo Agoronomu agira imbere yabo, icyo bashatse n&#39;ubwo Agoronomu aba abona cyabangamira Ubuhinzi gishyirwa mu bikorwa byakwanga bikitirirwa imyumvire micye ya Agoronomu kenshi akanirukanywa ku kazi&nbsp;&raquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&laquo;&nbsp;Uruhare rw&#39;abize ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi ruracyari ruto ugereranije n&rsquo;umusaruro twagakwiye kuba dutanga aho usanga tudahera iwacu aho dutuye ngo tubanze duhindure uburyo bukoreshwa kuva kera budatanga umusaruro ngo tube twakora improvement duhereye hato hagaragarira buri wese kuko nkeka ko umuturage atapfa gutinyuka ngo akugishe inama kubera wize agriculture cg veterinary mu gihe atabona byibuze ibyo wakoze birenze ibye yaheraho avuga ko ubimurusha!&nbsp;&raquo; &nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>Impamvu zituma abize ubuhinzi/ bworozi batabukora bakajya mu yindi myuga.</strong></span></span></strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu yatangiye agira ati&nbsp;:&nbsp;&laquo;&nbsp;Murakoze cyaneeeeee ku nsanganyamatsiko nziza nibaza Ko itureba twese abari hano, Icyo navuga nuko abantu bize ubuhinzi nubworozi tutaragera kukigero gishimishije cyo gukora ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi nubwo dukomeje kugerageza ariko haracyari byinshi byo gukora, imwe mu mpamvu ituma abantu basiga ubuhinzi bakajya mubindi nuko nta favorable environment yo kubikora ihari ikindi nuko Hari abakibifata nka last option carrier nyamara kurijye mbona ari first option&nbsp;&raquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&laquo;&nbsp;Impamvu zituma abize ubuhinzi/ bworozi batabukora bakajya mu yindi myuga:Akenshi nta gishoro cg ubutaka bwo guhingaho/kororeraho baba bafite farm management experience and skills rarely acquired in their university education 3)sometimes they are risks averse, meaning abize ubuhinzi /ubworozi baba bazi risks nyinshi zibubamo zishobora gutuma umuntu yahomba kandi ntako atagize bityo bagahitamo kureka gukora uwo mwuga bize . </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">For ex :pests , diseases, climate change effects, &nbsp;and so on&rdquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati&nbsp;: &laquo;&nbsp;1)Bituruka ku mateka y&#39;ubuhinzi mu Rwanda aho bwakozwe kuva kera n&#39;umuryango ugamije gushakira abawugize ibibatunga bikomeza bityo ari ubuhinzi bw&#39;umuryango ababyize bumva ko batize kuza guhindura ubuhinzi bwo mu muryango wabo ahubwo ari ugukorera Leta cg undi wabaha inshingano runaka bahemberwa bityo ugasanga abize ubuhinzi ntibagaragara mu mirimo y&#39;ubuhinzi nyirizina bakoresha ibyo bize ahubwo baragaragara mu gukurikirana &quot;Monitoring&quot; no gushyiraho ingamba &quot;policing&quot; kandi ayo &nbsp;masomo afite abandi bayize bakabaye babikora. Imirimo mu buhinzi bwacu iracyari mike kuburyo abize ubuhinzi bose badashobora kujyamo kandi ubushake n&#39;ubumenyi bwacu mu guhanga imirimo mu buhinzi biri hasi bigatuma bamwe bahitamo gushakiriza ahandi&nbsp;&raquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati&nbsp;:&nbsp;&laquo;&nbsp;impamvu abantu twize ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi tutabikora nuko bikunda guhomba inshuro nyinshi bitewe n&rsquo;ikirere (imvura nyinshi cg izuba ryinshi) ikindi kandi isoko ntabwo riri stable ibyo bituma iyo imyaka yeze igiciro kijya hasi nubundi </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">ugahomba.ikindi kandi inputs zirahenze ntabwo output iri proportional na inputs ziba zakoreshejwe ibyo bigatuma wayashora ahandi ushobora gushora macye ukunguka menshi kandi na risk zo guhomba ziri hasi&nbsp;&raquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu nawe yamwunganiye agira ati&nbsp;:&nbsp;&laquo;&nbsp;Ikindi nabonye mumyigire yacu abantu bize cyangwa biga ubuhinzi mumashuli yisumbuye, amakuru na kaminuza ni uko usanga nta mwarimu ubwira abanyeshuli ko bazahinga ahubwo usanga babashishikariza kuzakorera abandi, ibigo bikora ubuhinzi na leta , umunyeshuli rero arangiza kwiga atarigeze afashwa cg akangurirwa business zijyanye no guhinga no korora, kuko akenshi unasanga nko mu mashuri ntamahuriro ashishikariza abantu gukora ibyo bize babishoramo imari aho kujya gusaba akazi, &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Namwe mwibuke abarimu batwigishije ibyo batubwiraga! Ntigiraga bati ibi birabazwa mubizamini by&#39;akazi!&nbsp;&raquo;. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&laquo;&nbsp;Erega igitera kuba tudakora ubuhinzi twikorera ikinini nakigarutseho, ni financial support(gufashwa mu bijyanye no kubona igishoro) kuko nkanjye mfite igishoro byibuze cya 5 Million ntiwampa akazi kampemba net salary ya 600 000frw ngo nkemere keretse kanyemerera gukurikirana imishinga yanjye y&#39;ubuhinzi, biterwa n&#39;iki rero! Ni uko n&#39;ibigo by&#39;imari bitatwizera ngo bibe byatuguriza mumishinga y&#39;ubuhinzi iki kiri mumpamvu natwe twamaze kumenya inyungu ziri mukwikorera mubuhinzi n&#39;ubworozi tutari kubikora kandi tuzi nezako twunguka&nbsp;&raquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati: &ldquo;Mwakoze kuri iyi topic. Ndimo ndiga ubuhinzi muri U.S and I am planning to come back and work with you to advance our sector. But urebye ubuhinzi bw&rsquo;iwacu aho kuba business umuntu wese yakifuza kujyamo ahubwo barabuhunga kubera risks zirimo. Nkubu hari about 100 scholars bari muri buffet foundation barimo kwiga Agriculture hano, ariko iyo uganiriye nabo uba wumva nabo batazi ikintu bizaza ngo bakore mu Rwanda&rdquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Iki kiganiro nikiza cyane indi nama natanga nuko usanga abantu bakiva kuntebe y&rsquo;ishuri ntagaciro bahabwa bagafatwa nkaho ntacyo bazi igihe cyose ugasanga nabatanga akazi baragaha abo baziranye ndetse ntibarebe k&rsquo;ubushobozi bw&rsquo;umuntu bashaka gukoresha ahubwo bagatanga akazi bagendeye kumaranga mutima ibyo bituma nk&rsquo;umuntu uri able ahita acika intege igihe abonyeko ibyo yize ntagaciro yahawe mo agahita yishakira ahandi yerekeza&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Nashora nte mubuhinzi runaka cyangwa ubworozi runaka ntazi byibuze quantity ikenewe buri munsi ya product nzaba nshoyemo, Niba tutazi ingano ya carrots zikewe buri munsi tutazi iziboneka n&#39;aho izo ziboneka ziva, ubwo nashora nte mubuhinzi bwa carrots koko? Ubushakashatsi burakenewe cyane kuko nibwo butanga umurongo w&#39;ibiriho n&#39;ibikenewe hagakorwa igenamigambi rishingiye kubikenewe&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu yatanze igitekerezo kigufi cyane ati: &ldquo;Ni ukubera ko abafata ibyemezo nta kamaro kanini babona mu bize Ubuhinzi kuko bo bashyiramo ko n&#39;utarabwize abukora&rdquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Igituma abagoronome naba v&eacute;t&eacute;rinaire batandukira bakajya muzindi domaine hazamo no kubura aho gukorera no gushaka guhera kuri byinshi aho guhera kuri bike ngo ugende uzamuka: urugero ukumva ko utatangira umushinga w&#39;ubuhinzi udafite ubutaka buhagije kandi bumwe twita ko ari buto twabuheraho tukazagera kubundi!&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Ukombibona:1.Impamvu abize ibi bintu batabikora icya mbere abanyarwanda dufite indwara yo kwumva ko niba warize byanze bikunze uzategereza ko ubona akazi kaguhemba monthly salary, nta wiga ateganya ko azagera hanze ngo byange ,ikindi twiga theory kubishyira mu bikorwa bikaba ingorabahizi, Ikindi ubuhinzi burahenze kubukoramo business nkurikije uko nabibonye,bisaba kwitanga kugira ube umuhinzi w&#39;umwuga. Bisaba kwihangana ni business utasonzera kuko si ikintu ukora uno munsi ngo ejo uhite ubona umusaruro,iyi ni imwe mu mpamvu zituma abantu bigira mu yindi myuga ibaha udufaranga kuburyo bwihuse&rdquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Abarangije amashuri vuba nta butaka dufite bwo gukoreraho ubwo buhinzi/ubworozi dore ko no kubugura bikoshwa bityo tukaba tutabona amafaranga yo kugura/gukodesha ubutaka ngo duhite tubona n&#39;ayo kubushoramo ibyo bituma abize ubuhinzi/ubworozi bagana ibindi bibasaba igishoro bafite cyangwa gukorera abandi mubitajyanye na domain. Urugero: Ntabwo wakora ubuhinzi bw&#39; ibirayi udafite ubutaka cyangwa igishoro gitubutse.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>Imbogamizi Abize ubuhinzi/bworozi bahura nazo mu gukora uyu mwuga</strong></span></span></strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu yagize ati: &ldquo;Imbogamizi Abize ubuhinzi/bworozi bahura nazo mu gukora uyu mwuga:1)kutabona igishoro 2) kutabona hands on field practical and farm management experience 3)kutabona bimwe mu bikoresho bibafasha mu buhinzi bwa kijyambere bw&#39;umwuga. Urugero: tillers machine ntoya kandi zidahenze, milking machine, izindi agric.machineries 4) ingendoshuri mu bindi bihugu /uturere ngo bige uko urubyiruko rw&rsquo;ahandi rukora uyu mwuga&rdquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Ikindi nk&rsquo;ubu different pest and disease ntabwo hazwi yield loss % zishobora guteza bityo umuntu akaba yamenya investment yashyira muri control measures&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&ldquo;Nta huriro ribavugira bafite n&#39;ababavugira basanze mu kazi nta jambo bahabwa&rdquo;. </span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Imwe mu mbogamizi ni uko ubuhinzi buhenze ku muntu utarigeze akazi cyangwa utabifitemo experience ihagije&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Abayobozi b&#39;inzego z&#39;ibanze baba bazi ko ibintu bihagaze ariko bakavuga ibyiza gusa kugirango bagaragare neza&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Ubutaka busigaye bukoreshwa uko buri wese abyumva bikabangamira ubuhinzi cyane&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Uburyo bwo kugeza inputs kubahinzi ntibunoze, zigera kubahinzi zicyererewe cg rimwe zikabura ubundi zikaboneka&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Imikoreshereze/imitangire y&#39;inguzanyo z&#39;ubuhinzi itanoze neza&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Uko bigaragara abaveterineri barakora ndetse n&#39; abagoronome mugihe k&#39;ihinga baragaragara. Njye mbona abize ubuhinzi/ubworozi hakiburamo gukunda umwuga wacu. Aha nkagaruka nk&rsquo;umuntu wize ubuhinzi/ubworozi agaca ahantu akabona hahinze nabi cyangwa itungo runaka ntirimeze neza hanyuma tukabirenza amaso. Nk&rsquo;ababyize tubukunde kandi dutange umusanzu wacu&rdquo;.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>Ibisubizo kuri izo mbogamizi</strong></span></span></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&laquo;&nbsp;Ibisubizo rero ibyinshi leta yarabitangiye nko gushyiraho kunganirwa muri crops and animals insurance bizatuma ibigo by&#39;imari bitinyuka bihe inguzanyo abashaka gushora m&rsquo;ubuhinzi n&#39;ubworozi. Ikindi ni ibigega nka BDF byunganira urubyiruko n&#39;abandi bashaka gushora m&rsquo;ubuhinzi kuri guarantee basabwa n&#39;ibigo by&#39;imari n&#39;ubwo iki kigo cyo &nbsp;mbona hari ibitaragerwaho nshingiye kuri policy yanditse gifite nkahuza n&#39;ibyo kimaze gukora n&#39; igihe kimaze. Arongera ati&nbsp;:&nbsp;&laquo;&nbsp;Igisigaye ni ugukora ubushakashatsi kuri value chains na supply chains za crops zose cyane cyane imboga kugirango hashobore no kubaho organisations mubahinzi bahinga crops zimwe Wenda nk&#39;abahinga amashu bakaba baziranye bafite ihuriro bikaba byaba igisubizo kirambye hamenyekanye approximate quantity ikenewe mugihugu, ibi byaba igisubizo kubibazo byinshi biriho harimo na importation ya crops cyangwa animal products kandi dushobora kubiproducinga imbere mugihugu, Ibi byatuma abantu bize ubuhinzi babukora kuko byagabanya impungenge abenshi bagira kubijyanye n&#39; isoko rihindagurika&nbsp;&raquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Ibisubizo kuri izo mbogamizi:1) Kwegera Banks zitanga inguzanyo mu buhinzi 2)gusaba inzego zose bireba kugeza agric. Machineries at the available reach to farmers (ntoya, ziri affordable, kdi zikora efficiently kurusha man power) 3) urubyiruko kugira ubushake bwo kwiga, kumenya no gukora ubuhinzi, atari theory gusa 4) YEAN community ifatanyije na MINAGRI n&#39;abandi bafatanya bikorwa, gutegura ingendoshuri imbere mu gihugu no hanze yacyo, zigenewe abize ubuhinzi /bworozi bashaka gukora uwo mwuga&nbsp;&raquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati&nbsp;: &laquo;&nbsp;1)Kwigira kuri gahunda ya Israel abize ubuhinzi bakagira umwanya munini wo &nbsp;kwimenyereza umwuga 2)Guhurizahamwe abize ubuhinzi bagahabwa inshingano zo kubukora &nbsp;kandi bagakurikiranwa&nbsp;&raquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati&nbsp;:&nbsp; &laquo;&nbsp;Icyakorwa: hashakwe uburyo market yaba stable ubundi ikijyanye na inputs zihenze cyongerwemo ingufu subsidy zijye no ku miti apana ifumbire na seeds zimwe na zimwe gusa&nbsp;&raquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&laquo;&nbsp;Nk&#39;igisubizo rero habaho campaigns zo gushishikariza abantu gukora ibyo bize bigahera mumashuli no mumahuriro y&#39;urubyiruko rwize ubuhinzi&nbsp;&raquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&laquo;&nbsp;Uko mbyumva rero: Leta nishore amafaranga muri researches (ubushakashatsi) and extension (iyamamazabuhinzi) kurenza ibindi byose birimo gushyirwa imbere, kandi CAVM n&rsquo;icyahoze ari ISAR bihabwe amafaranga yo gukora ama researchers mbere ko twahita twirukira mu bikorwa. </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Abanyeshuli bahabwe ama trainings na practices nyinshi mbere na mbere&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Research ifatika on productivity, &nbsp;cost benefit analysis for agric value chains nabyo biri mu byatuma investment mu buhinzi ziyongera&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati: &ldquo;1) Hakorwe ubushakashatsi kubijyanye na value and supply chains ari nabyo bizerekana ibyo dukeye n&#39;ibihari ibihari dufate imyanzuro ya distribution hose mugihugu, kuko Niba twejeje ikintu runaka aha n&#39;aha ahandi kitaheze nta buryo buhari bwo guhana amakuru kubahinga n&#39;abacuruzi, kuko usanga umuntu yejeje Wenda nk&#39;inyanya ari Nyagatare akabura isoko Atari uko zeze hose mugihugu ahubwo ari ya value and supply chain idasobanutse 2) Hakorwe ubushakashatsi mubanyarwanda hamenyekane ingano ya buri kiribwa gikenewe hashingiwe hagendewe kubikunda kuribwa cyane, noneho hazako ingengabihe y&#39;imihingire hashingiwe kumibare ya buri ngano y&#39;ibikenewe, cyane cyane kubidahunikwa 3) Hashyirweho ingamba zo kugabanya gahoro gahoro ibiribwa bitumizwa hanze kandi byera neza mu Rwanda&rdquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Hakagombye kumenyekana nimibarare yabize iyi agriculture ndetse veternary ariko bakajya bavangura ibintu umuntu akajya mucyo yize niba Ari crop science ashingwe ibihingwa be gufata abize guteza imbere icyaro cyangwa ubutaka no kuhir &nbsp;ndetse n&rsquo;ibindi ngo bivangwe kuko rimwe narimwe usanga umuntu abirimo nawe agasa nushakisha kubera ko ibyo yize hari abandi babirimo bitagenewe&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Ababyize bagomba kubikunda kuko ntawushobora kuguha agaciro utakihesheje. Minisiteri y&#39;Ubuhinzi irasabwa kongerera ubushobozi bw&#39;Amahugurwa abize Ubuhinzi ingeri zose ndetse igaharanira no kubagiraho ijambo kuko UBUHINZI ariyo ibubazwa. Hari nk&#39;abagoronomu bo mu nzego z&#39;ibanze ureba ugasanga MINAGRI itabahugura kandi aribo begereye ABAHINZI ariko kandi ugasanga abo mu bigo biyishamikiyeho yewe n&#39;Umupalanto kaminuza zo hanze barazizengurutse. Ese nta kuntu Abagoronomu b&#39;Imirenge n&#39;Utugari baba abakozi ba MINAGRI batijwe inzego z&#39;ibanze kandi tuzi aho bikorwa neza (E.g: Mu bitaro bya Gisirikari bya Kanombe hari abakozi b&#39;abasirikari batijwe Minisiteri y&#39;UBUZIMA kandi bitanga umusaruro&rdquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Ibisubizo: nugushyiraho ihuriro ry&#39;abize ubuhinzi n&#39;ubworozi bagahabwa inshingano kdi bakajya bakurikiranwa kdi bakongera bakazirikana ko aribo bagomba kugaragaza </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">impinduka nziza mu buhinzi nubworozi nkabantu babizi babyize kdi babisobanukiwe kurusha abandi nubwo tutakwirengagiza ko hari ushobora kubikurusha ataruko yabyize ahubwo aruko yabikoze akisanisha nabyo cyane kukurusha wowe wabyize!&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Kimwe mu bisubizo Leta nishyiremo imbaraga ihe motivation uwagerageje gutangira uyu mwuga imworohereze ku buryo bufatika inkunga zose zishoboka aziboneho kuko twese kubona akazi ntibyakunda nibinaba ngombwa Leta itange ubutaka busorerwa make aba bagoronome bibumbire hamwe baterwe inkunga bakore kandi bizagabanya ubushomeri n&#39;umusaruro uboneke&rdquo;.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati: &ldquo;1) Abayobozi bose bagomba kuvugisha ukuri uko ibintu bihagaze kugirango decision makers babone aho bakosora, ikindi hagombye kubaho projects z&#39;ubuhinzi muri buri gace zigakora research bakamenya inputs zicyenewe buri hantu 2)Gahunda y&#39;imikoreshereze y&#39;ubutaka yahabwa imbaraga ndetse ubutaka bwagenewe ubuhinzi bugaterwa imbago bugatandukanywa n&#39;ubwagenewe ibindi bikorwa 3) Uburyo inputs zigera kubahinzi bwakosorwa bugashyirwamo abantu benshi kandi babizi bikaba competition kuko ubu uburyo bikorwa ubona bigamije inyungu z&#39;ubucuruzi kuruta uko biba bigamije guteza iyi sector imbere 4)Abize ubuhinzi/ubworozi bakwifashishwa muri mobilization (animateurs rural) buri muntu wese ukora muri iki gice (ubuhinzi/ubworozi) cyangwa bagafashwa mugukora imishinga igamije guteza imbere ubuhinzi/ubworozi 5) Koroshya uburyo inguzanyo zitangwa cyane cyane zigahabwa groups z&#39;abasobanukiwe ubuhinzi/ubworozi kurusha abantu kugiti cyabo kuko bo ubona bashaka kuzijyana mumishinga idafitanye isano n&#39;ibyo bazacyiye bigatuma uru rwego ruguma gusigara inyuma</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu yatanze igitekerezo cye mu cyongereza gusa ati: &ldquo;there is need of 6 main solutions to overcome clarified challenges as follow: 1) promotion of Selling price fixation by farmers according to their &nbsp;expenses and needed benefit (like 25% of production cost) as done for &nbsp;other commercial commidities (isabune, processed rice and coffee, ...); and hence, 2 ) in complementality to agri insurence subsidy &nbsp;being initiated, there is need of Crop produces price &nbsp;subsidy by government to avoid risks of &nbsp;price fluctuation due to external incoming products; 3) Starting from small available resources (land, other capitals as done for other business such as Sigarettes, solt and soap and parafin-peteroli, one pig, ... ) and then we expand accordingly. But point 1 and 2 should first be well managed to avoid fear; 4) Refleshing minds of existing agronomists and veterinaries (farming as a business skills based training) to start farming as a business; 5) Planning proposed Research to be conducted as we progress for perfection, &nbsp;given that we have some preliminary information ( i) incoming Food products from abroad (fruits, babana, vegetables, maize grains, ... ), ii) scarcity of food in Rwanda especially in some period such as in Appril,.... ; 6) Giving Agri and vet technicians enough space (decision making) for managing &nbsp;agriculture in their respective areas of work&rdquo;. </span></span></li>\r\no<li><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&ldquo;Mbona icyangombwa ari ugukunda ubuhinzi kubabyize bibaye &nbsp;inshingano twabibyaza umusaruro kuko mba numva umuhinzi aho ari hose aho tugenda twajya twitegereza nabyo birigisha kuko mubuhinzi nuguhora twiga&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>Icyitonderwa:</strong></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byose ntago byagarajwe hano bitewe n&rsquo;uko ari ikiganiro kirekire cyane hagiye hatoranywamo imirongo migari ikavugwa muri make hirindwa gusubiramo ibyavuzwe..</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Amazina y&rsquo;abatanze ibitekerezo ntago yagaragajwe muri iyi nkuru gusa amagambo yose ari mu utwuguruzo n&rsquo;utwugarizo (&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;) yose yandikuwe uko yanditse mu kiganiro.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Ikiganiro nk&rsquo;iki kiba buri ku Cyumweru.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Ushaka gukurikira ibi biganiro ukaba uri umuhinzi/umworozi cyangwa umugoronome/veterineri ku rwego urwo arirwo rwose nawe wasaba kujya k&rsquo;urubuga rwa YEAN Whatsapp unyuze kuri nimero ikurikira: +250 788 845 727 ,wakurikira YEAN kuri facebook cyangwa kuri twitter #UbuhinziBwacu @YEAN_Rwanda</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n','3',2886,40,'2017-11-25 21:00:00','Ubuhinzi bwacu',0,'online','',''),(264,'UBUHINZI BWACU:  Ibitekerezo by\'abahinziborozi b\'urubyiruko ku nsanganyamatsiko igira iti: ’IBARURISHAMIBARE RY\'UBUHINZI N\'UBWOROZI’','agriculture statistics.jpg','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Nkuko bimaze kumenyererwa ku cyumweru &nbsp;guhera saa mbiri &nbsp;ku mbuga nkoranyambaga zose za YEAN tuba turi mu kiganiro </span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>UBUHINZI BWACU</strong></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;, kuri iki cyumweru 12 Ugushyingo 2017 &nbsp;twaganiriye ku ngingo igira iti </span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>&quot; IBARURISHAMIBARE RY&#39;UBUHINZI N&#39;UBWOROZI &quot;</strong></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">. </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Aho abahinzi n&rsquo;aborozi bagiye bagaruka ku kamaro kanini ko guhinga no korora hagenderewe k&rsquo;ungano y&rsquo;ibyo isoko ricyeneye ikindi hagemdewe ku bipimo by&rsquo;imibare k&rsquo;umusaruro w&rsquo;ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi muri rusange.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Mu iki kiganiro hagaragayemo ibitekerezo byinshi byose byagiye bigaruka kuri ibi bice &nbsp;bikurikira: </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>Nk &#39;umuhinzi/umworozi birakwiye gukora ibikorwa bigendeye ku mibare</strong></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu muhinzi yaravuze ati&nbsp;&ldquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>Birakwiye rwose kuko ari ngombwa kumenya aho uvuye mu mibare ifatika ndetse n&#39; aho wifuza kugera. &nbsp;Urugero: Abahinzi bakagize aho bandika ibyashowe (input calculations) ndetse ngo anabare ibyo azasarura (output/production calculations) kugira ngo azabigereranye arebe ko yungutse cg yahombye (Benefit = Output - (input + charges). Iyi mibare iyo Umuhinzi/Mworozi atabikoze mu byukuri ntamenya urugero rw&#39;ingamba afatira ihinga ritaha. Ikindi umuhinzi agomba kumenya umubare w&#39;abo agomba guhingira i.e. Umuryango we + indiririzi (parasites) ndetse n&#39;isoko. Ibi iyo atabimenye ni kumwe ahinga ugasanga nawe ntibimuhagije, ugasanga yabuze amafaranga yo kwishyurira umuryango we ubwishingizi mu buhinzi (CBHI~Community based Health Insurance), iyo uwo muhinzi yaba afite umwana muto akabura icyo agura imfashandyo (ubwo niho havuka imirire mibi bwaki igatongora) yewe uwo muhinzi akanabura n&#39;amafaranga yo kugura imyambaro ye n&#39;iy&#39;ab&#39;umuryango we (bakambara imyenda ishaje twita ibicocera ni ba bana tubona mu byaro bambaye ikabutura zicitse ku bibuno), bikanagera yewe n&#39;aho umuhinzi anabura n&#39;isabune ugasanga afite umwanda ku mubiri (aranuka) no ku myambaro&rdquo;.</em></span></span></em>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Bityo rero birakwiyeko umuhinzi/umworozi akoraimirimoye ashingiye ku mibare ifatika bikamuha icyerekezo cy&rsquo;umusaruro ukwiye kuboneka no kugeraho mu bushobozibwe ashoboye kandi afite.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>Uruhare n&#39;ubumenyi rw&#39;umuhinzi/umworozi mu kubona no gukoresha amakuru ajyanye n imibare</strong></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu muhinzi ati &ldquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>Ibi njye ndabitangirira ku muhinzi na agoronome umufasha mu buhinzi bwe; Kugirango umuhinzi afashwe mu kubona imibare ikoreshwa, tukamenya ngo nahinze ahangana gute? bahateye imbuto ingana ite? nakoresheje amafaranga angana ate mpinga? nateye umuti ungana ute? nakoresheje ifumbire ingana ite? Ibi abahinzi benshi ntibabibara kandi agoronome yagakwiye kubafasha kumenya gukora iyi mibare, umuhinzi akamenya guhinga ku murongo. Umuhinzi ufite iyi mibare yose ntashobora guhomba uko bibonetse kose iyo igihe cyagenze neza, niyo byabaho amenya uburyo azava mu gihombo. Umuhinzi/mworozi ufite iyi mibare iwe yafasha cyane ibigo bishinzwe ibarurishamibare&rdquo;.</em></span></span></em></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Undi ati&nbsp;&ldquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>ibarurishamibare ni ubumenyi bushingira mu ikusanyamakuru hagamijwe kureba igipimo rusange cy&#39;imibare igendanye n&#39;icyiciro kigamijwe. Ibi rero bituma ntekereza ko nta ruhare &nbsp;na ruto umuhinzi/mworozi yagira mu kubona ayo makuru no kuyakoresha cyakora uruhare rwe ni ngombwa mu gushyira mu bikorwa ingamba zashyizweho &nbsp;hashingiwe ku ishusho rusange yagaragajwe n&#39;ibarurishamibare&rdquo;</em></span></span></em></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati&nbsp;: &ldquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>Uruhare ni rucye ahubwo usanga benshi banabyigishwa ariko bikaba amasigaracyicaro. &nbsp;urugero: raporo ya NISR igaragaza ikigero cy&#39;abakora (Labour Force Survey February 2017) itubwira ko mu bahinzi 70% uRwanda rufite gusa 45.9% aribo byitwa ko bafite akazi (niba ntibeshye) ubwo abo bandi ~24.1% bitwa Abahinzi bahingira kuramuka (subsistance Agriculture) bakaba bafatwa n&rsquo;urwego mpuzamahanga nk&#39;abadafite akazi (unemployed people&rdquo;).</em></span></span></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>Uruhare rw&#39;ibigo byikorera n&#39;ibya leta m&rsquo;ubushakashatsi n&rsquo;ubusesenguzi b&rsquo;amakuru no kuyatangaza</strong></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati &ldquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>Aba ubwabo ni bo babumbatiye uruhare rukomeye mu kubona no gusakaza amakuru ku ibarurishamibare. Imikoranire yabo niyo ihuza ireme ry&#39;ayo makuru aba azabafasha guha umurongo umuhinzi n&#39;umworozi mu mikorere ye ya buri munsi. Niyo mpamvu ibarurisha mibare muri iyi myuga ntaho rireba umuhinzi mworozi mu buryo butaziguye (direct). Umuhinzi ntahangayikishwa n&#39;ubwiyongere bw&#39;abaturage bazabura ibyo kurya azahangayikishwa no guhinga akeza akihaza akanagurisha. Ingaruka ku rhare rw&#39;ibarurishamibare mu buhinzi bworozi, ruzwi kandi rubonwa n&#39;ibi bigo na Leta kurusha umuturage.&rdquo;</em></span></span></em></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Undi ati &ldquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>Leta itegura imirongo myiza (good policies) Eg: EDPRSII &amp; &nbsp;PASTA (Strategic Plans for the Transformation of Agriculture) yewe ikanaherekezwa n&#39;izindi gahunda nko kunganira Abahinzi kugura inyongeramusaruro (input &amp; motorized water pumps subsidies) ariko ikibazo kikaba bamwe mu babishyiriweho batabibyaza umusaruro. Abikorera ntibashora byinshi mu buhinzi kubera batunguka vuba, usanga bigira mu gutanga serivisi kuko niyo ibaha inyungu zidatinda. Igitera ubwoba abikorera, mbona ari ukubona Abahinzi 70% bagira uruhare rwa 30% mu musaruro mbumbe w&#39;Igihugu (GDP national accounts). Inama : (1) Ubuhinzi/ubworozi n&#39;ubwo bwunguka butinze ariko iyo inyungu zije hari amahirwe 80% ko zigumaho;(2) Ubuhinzi nibwo butunze isi.&rdquo;</em></span></span></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati &ldquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>nshima ko abafatanyabikorwa bari kuza mu buhinzi basigaye bagera kuri terrain kuruta ko mbere bazaga intego ari ukurangiza budget yabo ariko umusaruro ukabura. &nbsp;Uyu munsi batangiye guhindura imikorere kdi iyi ngingo yo kubara igishoro n umusaruro wabyo barabyigisha gusa bikagera ku matsinda mato baba bakorana</em></span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">.&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>Imbogamizi</strong></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Abahinzi n&rsquo;aborozi kandibagaragaje zimwe mu mbogamizi&nbsp;:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati </span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>&ldquo; kudatanga amakuru hakurikijwe strates (consolidated lands, irrigated and non irrigated, ...) bityo ntumenye aho kongera imbaraga&rdquo;.</em></span></span></em></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati &ldquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>Imbogamizi zihari mbona zishingiye ku mikoranire y&#39;inzego zitandukanye mu guhuza amakuru no kuyashyira mu bikorwa hashingiwe ku igenamigambi. Si kenshi ibigo by&#39;abikorera n&#39;abikorera bashingira ku mibare-shusho yatanzwe na NISR mu gukora ibikorwa byabo. Ibi usanga bigonganisha inzego zitandukanye kuko niho uzasanga umuntu yubatse ikaragiro &nbsp;ubuyobozi bukamwemerera nawe agakora ibikorwa bikarangira abuse amata? Biba bitewe no kutagira baseline ngo amanye umubare w&#39;aborozi n&#39;amatungo borora (amagufi/ amaremare), niba agenewe umukamo cyangwa inyama, umubare w&#39;abafite inzuri, etc. Iyo abuze umusaruro yitana bamwana n&rsquo;abamuhamagaye gushora ibikorwa ibi bikagaruka kuri bwa buyobozi bubona amanota mabi mu mihigo</em></span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Undi ati &ldquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>indi mbogamizi: agaciro gacye gashobora guhabwa ubushakashatsi n&#39;inzego zishinzwe ibarurishamibare hamwe n&#39;inzego zishinzwe gushyira mu bikorwa. Ni kenshi imiryango itari iya Leta (NGOs, CSOs) ikora ikanamurika ubushakashatsi &nbsp;nyamara bigoye kubona bwiyambajwe mu igenamigambi cg ibarurishamibare. Ibi bigaruka kuri ya mikoranire kuko ni gake cg ntibiranabaho ko urwego rw&#39;igihugu rw&#39;ibarurishamibare rugirana ibiganiro nyunguranabitekerezo na CSOs nyamara ari ingenzi.</em></span></span></em></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">.uyu ati &ldquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>Kuba abahinzi bataritabira gukoresha imibare mu buhinzi bworozi bwabo&rdquo;,Abahinzi ntibajijukiwe n&#39;uburyo bwo gukoresha imibare mu gucunga ubuhinzi bworozi bwabo,Imibarurishamibare rikoresha indimi zitumvwa n&#39;abahinzi, Kutamenya neza igihomba cg inyungu byabayeho mu buhinzibworozi bwacu, Igenamigambi ridashingiye ku mibare nyayo riba ripfuye. Abashinzwe ubuhinzi bamwe babeshya imibare y&#39;ubuhinzi bworozi&rdquo;</em></span></span></em></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Undi ati&rdquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>Njye mbona n abahinzi bose bagere ku rwego rwo kubara ibyashowe n ibyinjiye hakirimo umworera kuko kugeza uyu munsi abatekinisiye turacyarwana na mobilisation kuruta gutanga technical support. &nbsp;Igihe umuhinzi azaba yamaze kujya ku murongo ngenderwaho nibwo no gushyira mu bikorwa agricultural technics bizakunda kdi mbona inzira ari ndende, Ikindi nuko ibyo abahinzi bakenera bitabonekera igihe ariko equips zashyizweho mu ntara zose zishobora kugira icyo zihindura. &nbsp;Inshingano za sector agronomist zo ziracyari nyinshi byo mubyumve&rdquo;</em></span></span></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>Ibisubizo kuri izo mbogamizi</strong></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati &ldquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>kwimakaza umuco w&#39;ihanahana n&#39;ihuzamakuru ku ibarurishamibare uhereye mu itegurwa ryayo involvement of stakeholders and stratifying samples&rdquo;</em></span></span></em></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Gugushyiraho urwego mpuzabikorwa (Sector Working Group) ruhuriyemo NISR, MINAGRI, MINALOC, P.S, CSOs.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Iyoroshyamakuru ashingiye ku ibarurishamibare yafasha mu gukora imfashamyumvire y&#39;umwuga</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Gufasha abahinzi mu gukoresha imibare mu bikorwa byabo. Kutabeshya imibare ngo hagaragare ko aho ushinzwe hejeje cyane kuko bigaruka abo ushinzwe(ubuhinzi)</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati &ldquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>Agronomists babone statistiques zikozwe neza kuri data analysis zabaye well collected ntamarangamutima yabayemo, &nbsp;ubundi bagahabwa umwanya, nabo bagakora inshingano zabo badakorera kujisho, &nbsp;ntakabuza Our Agriculture can shift from &nbsp;Subsistence to Market oriented Agriculture</em></span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&rdquo;</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Undi ati &ldquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>ubukangurambaga bwimbitse kugirango umuhinzi amenye akamaro kugukora umwuga we agendeye kumibare ifatika,kuko ni kenshi abahinzi bavuga ko iyo bejeje umyaka yabo abaguzi babahenda iyo bagiye kugurisha,nyamara wamubaza uti washoye angahe kugirango ubone nibuze 1kg cy&#39;ibigori ati simbizi,ibyo rero bihita bituma navuga nk&#39;inama: 1.Abahinzi babanze bigishwe gukorera ku ntego bityo bizatuma amenya ibyo yashoye 2.Turasaba ibigo by&#39;ubushakashatsi kujya bibanza gusobanurira abahinzi ikigamijwe ndetse byaba ngombwa mukugaragaza results bakaza bakongera bakereka abahinzi uko bimeze.&rdquo;</em></span></span></em></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Amatsinda yafasha guhindura byinshi ahawe imbaraga zikenewe</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>Uruhare rw&#39;( Umwarimu, Umuhinzi,Agoronome/veterineri na Leta) mu migendekere myiza y&#39;ibaruriahamibare</strong></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Abahinzi twumveko ari ingirakamaro gukoresha imibare kandi ko ari.ugufasha mu igenamigambi rya Leta, twirinda kubeshya imibare .</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Agronome/veterinerie bahabwe umwanya wo gukora inshinagnoze zo kwita &nbsp;k&rsquo;ubahinzi/abororozi </span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">personnal reseach and records keeping</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Abagoronome bihatire gufasha abahinzi mu kugira umuco wo gukoresha imobare mu bikorwa byabo.</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Uyu ati &ldquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>iyubakabumenyi ry&#39;abahinzi-borozi binyuze muri mobilization na mentorship bigomba gukorwa na Agronome / veternaire n&#39;abafashamyumvire. Icyo guverinoma igomba gukora ni uguhindura imibare mu butumwa bubumbatiye inyigisho zafasha wa muhinzi n&#39;abamwunganira &nbsp;mu murima</em></span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">.&rdquo; </span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>IBYIFUZO</strong></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;NISR, RAB, MINAGRI, IPAR n&#39;ibindi bigo bikora ibijyanye n&#39;ubushakakshatsi kubu hinzi babanze basobanurire abahinzi neza icyo ibarurishamibare aricyo, &nbsp;icyo rimaze ku muhinzi n&#39;igihugu ndetse no mugihe kizaza ku buhinzi bwabo</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">amatsinda ya Twigire Muhinzi ashyirwemo ingufu zihagije,bagasobanurirwa uko babara ibishoro kuberako abenshi mubahinzi bafite amatsinda babarizwamo byakunda kuko twumvikanye neza ko imibare ari ngombwa m&#39;ubuhinzi n&#39;ubworozi,</span></span></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">uyu ati &ldquo;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><em>ko njya mbona hari amakaye baha abaturage ngo y&#39;imihigo y&#39;ingo,buriya ntakuntu no m&rsquo;ubuhinzi n&#39;ubworozi byakorwa?&rdquo;</em></span></span></em></li>\r\no<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">umuhinzi umworozi ahabwe &nbsp;managerial skills zimufasha kunoza ubuhinzi no guhingira intego </span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><strong>Icyitonderwa:</strong></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Ibitekerezo byatanzwe byose ntago byagarajwe hano bitewe n&rsquo;uko ari ikiganiro kirekire cyane hagiye hatoranywamo imirongo migari ikavugwa muri make.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Amazina yabatanze ibitekerezo ntago yagaragajwe muri iyi nkuru gusa amagambo yose ari mu utwuguruzo n&rsquo;utwugarizo (&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;) yose yandikuwe uko yanditse mu kiganiro.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Ikiganiro nk&rsquo;iki kiba buri ku Cyumweru.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\">Ushaka gukurikira ibi biganiro ukaba uri umuhinzi/umworozi cyangwa umugoronome/veterineri ku rwego urwo arirwo rwose nawe wasaba kujya k&rsquo;urubuga rwa YEAN Whatsapp unyuze kuri nimero ikurikira: +250 788 845 727 ,wakurikira YEAN kuri facebook cyangwa kuri twitter #UbuhinziBwacu @YEAN_Rwanda</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n','3',1842,3,'2017-12-07 22:50:00','Ubuhinzi Bwacu',0,'online','',''),(265,'IMYANZURO Y\'INAMA YO KUNOZA UBUCURUZI BWIBIRAYI','QQ Photo20171212104210.jpg','<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">IMYANZURO Y</span><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">INAMA YO KUNOZA UBUCURUZI BWIBIRAYI</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Kuri uyu wa gatatu tariki 06/12/2017 mu cyumba cy</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">inama cya Fatima i musanze habereye inama nyungurana bitekerezo igamije kunoza ubucuruzi bw</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">ibirayi guhera mu gihembwe </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">cy</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">ihinga cya 2018A,ikaba yayobowe na nyakubahwa minisitiri w</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">ubucuruzi n</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">inganda. Inama yahuje inzego zitandukanye harimo MINAGRI,MINALOC,MINICOM,intara y</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">amajyaruguru n</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">iyiburengerazuba, inzego z</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">umutekano (RDF,police,NISS,Reserve force,DASSO). Abagize&ldquo;Food security task Force&rdquo;.ubuyobozi bw</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">uturere twa Rubavu,Nyabihu,Musanze,Burera,abahagarariye amakusanyirizo ,abayozi ba za koperative n</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">abahinzi b</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">ibirayi. Inama yitabiriwe n</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">abantu basaga 650.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">A.IBYAGANIRIWEHO</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">1</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">.kunoza ubucuruzi bw</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">ibirayi harebwa uruhererekane nyongeragaciro(value chain) kuva ku muhinzi kugeza ku muguzi wa nyu w</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">ibirayi</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">2</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">.Gushyiraho ibiciro byibirayi ku muhinzi,ku ikusanyirizo,ku muranguzi no ku</span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">&nbsp;&nbsp;m</span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">uguzi wa nyuma</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">3</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">.Gufatira hamwe ingamba zigamije kunoza ubucuruzi b</span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">w&#39;ibirayi</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">B.IMYANZURO YINAMA</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Nyuma yo kungurana ibitekerezo. Abitabiriye inama bafashe imyanzuro ikurikira:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">1.</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Amakusanyirizo yose agomba guhabwa amakoperative ahinga ibirayi akaba ariyo ayacunga kandi akagena imikorere yayo.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">2.</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Abayobozi b</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">uturere basabwe kwihutisha gahunda yo gushyiraho amakoperative no kunoza imikorere y&#39;ayari asanzwe&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">bagatanga raporo ku itariki ya 15/12/2017.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">3.</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Umusaruro wose w</span><strong><sup><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></sup></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">ibirayi ugomba kunyunzwa ku makusanyirizo.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">4.</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Hashyizeho ibiciro bikurikira:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border-image:none; border:medium; margin:0px 0px 0px 6px; width:399.95pt\">\r\no<tbody>\r\no<tr>\r\no<td style=\"background-color:transparent; height:15.7pt; vertical-align:top; width:76.75pt\">\r\no<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Ubwoko</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\no<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Bw</span></span></strong><sup><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">,</span></span></sup><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">ibirayi</span></span></strong></p>\r\no</td>\r\no<td style=\"background-color:transparent; border-color:#000000; height:15.7pt; vertical-align:top; width:80.8pt\">\r\no<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Igiciro gihabwa</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\no<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Umuhinzi</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\no<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">(Frw/1kg)</span></span></strong></p>\r\no</td>\r\no<td style=\"background-color:transparent; border-color:#000000; height:15.7pt; vertical-align:top; width:80.8pt\">\r\no<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Igiciro ku </span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\no<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Ikusanyirizo</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\no<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">(Frw/1kg)</span></span></strong></p>\r\no</td>\r\no<td style=\"background-color:transparent; border-color:#000000; height:15.7pt; vertical-align:top; width:80.8pt\">\r\no<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Igiciro bigeze I</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\no<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri\">Kigali (Frw/1kg)</span></span></strong></p>\r\no</td>\r\no<td style=\"background-color:transparent; border-color:#000000; height:15.7pt; vertical-align:top; width:80.8pt\">\r\no<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"color:#00