000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">125</span></span></span></span></p>\r\no</td>\r\no<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:116.9000pt\">\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">250-320</span></span></span></span></p>\r\no</td>\r\no<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:116.9000pt\">\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">&nbsp;2100-2300 g</span></span></span></span></p>\r\no</td>\r\no</tr>\r\no<tr>\r\no<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:116.8500pt\">\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span></span></span></span></p>\r\no</td>\r\no<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:116.8500pt\">\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">130</span></span></span></span></p>\r\no</td>\r\no<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:116.9000pt\">\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">260-350</span></span></span></span></p>\r\no</td>\r\no<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:116.9000pt\">\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2200-2400 g</span></span></span></span></p>\r\no</td>\r\no</tr>\r\no</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><strong>Icyitonderwa:</strong></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Izi ngero zishobora guhinduka cyane bitewe n&rsquo;akarere inkoko zirimo ndetse n&rsquo;ubwoko bwazo.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Byateguwe na Nshimiyimana Arcade (anshimiyimana@yeanrwanda.org), hifashishijwe Imfashanyigisho ku bworozi bw&#39;inkoko,Mata 2014, yateguwe na MINAGRI</span></span></span></span></em></p>\r\n',2,18,1,9013,40,'Inkoko',0,'2017-12-07 15:50:00','2024-09-11 13:55:34'),(279,'Dusobanukirwe n\'Indwara ya Rift Valley Fever ifata amatungo n\'abantu',NULL,'Rift_Valley_Fever.jpg','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>Dusobanukirwe n’Indwara ya Rift Valley Fever ifata amatungo n’abantu</strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Indwara ya Rift Valley Fever ni indwara iterwa na Virusi ya Rift Valley Fever Virus ifata amatungo yuza ndetse n’abantu. Iyi virus iba mu muryango wa <em>Bunyaviridae</em> ikaba ari umwihariko muri Afurika yo munsi y’ubutayu bwa Sahara. Iyi ndwara yakunze kwibasira ibihugu nka Kenya Somaliya, Tanzaniya, Madagasicari, Afurika y’Epfo, Misiri, Sudani n’ibindi .</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>Uko ikwirakwizwa</strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Iyi ndwara ya RVF yagaragaye bwa mbere muri Kenya mu nkengero z’ikiyaga cya Naivasha ahagana mu 1930 ubu ikaba imaze hafi ikinyejana muri Afurika yo munsi y’ubutayu bwa Sahara. Iyi ndwara yagaragaje ubukana bukomeye mu gihugu cya Misiri mu mwaka wa 1977 ubwo abantu ibihumbi ijana bayanduye abagera kuri 600 bakahasiga ubuzima naho muri Kenya niho yahitanye amatungo menshi mu mwaka wa 1950-1951 aho yahitanye intama zigera ku bihumbi 100. </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Iyi virusi itera RVF ikwirakwizwa n’umubu wo mu bwoko bwa <em>Aedos</em> iba mu bidendezi by’amazi igakwirakwizwa ku buryo bw’amagi y’iyo mibu. Ubundi bwoko bw’imibu nka <em>Culex </em>nayo yihutisha gukwirakwiza iyi ndwara. Imyamaswa zuza (nk’ihene, intama, inka) ndetse n’abantu bashobora kwandura . Amatungo yagaragayemo iyi ndwara araramburura cyane.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Abantu bandura iyi ndwara bitututse mu gukora ku maraso, umubiri w’amatungo yanduye iyi ndwara. Ibi bishobora kuba mu gihe cyo kubaga,</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">kuvura amatungo ndetse no gufasha amatungo kubyara. Abantu bacye bashobora kwanduzwa no kurumwa n’umubu ufite iyo ndwara . Kuba umuntu uyirwaye yayanduza undi ntago biraragara. </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Uko ukwirakwizwa guteye gutya: </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Virusi yayo ishobora gukwirakwizwa n’umubu w’ingore binyuze mu magi yawo.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Muri aya magi virusi igumamo imyaka myinshi mu gihe cy’izuba</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Imvura nyinshi ituma amagi afite ya virusi abyara imibu</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Iyo imibu yiyongereye ubushobozi bwo kwanduza amatungo buriyongera bityo n’uburyo amatungo yanduza abantu bukiyongera</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Iyo imatungo yanduye ari menshi bituma abaveterineri bayitaho bayavura, bikongera ibyago by’uko indwara ikwirakwira mu bantu.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Iyi ndwara yakunze kugaragare cyane abantu hane hakurikira: Mu bishanga byereye imigezi, ahantu harangwa no kuba imvura nke, ahantu huhirwa (hahora ibidendezi bituma imibu iba myinshi), no mu misozi miremire ihehereye. </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>Ibimenyetso n’uko ivurwa</strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Iyi Virusi ya RVF imara iminsi hagati 2-6 mu muntu mbere y’uko igaragaza ibimenyetso. Akenshi abantu bafashwe n’iyi ndwara nta bimenyetso bagaragaza cyangwa bakagaragaza bicye birimo umuriro. Abarwayi bayo bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso baba bafite umuriro, bagacika intege, kubabara mu rutirigongo ndetse no kuzungera. Umurwayi ashobora gukira mu minsi hagati y’2 n’icyumweru kimwe.</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Umubare mucye w’abanduye iyi ndwara (8-10%) bagaragaza ibimenyetso bikomeye birimo:</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Kubabara amaso </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Kugira ibibazo mu bwonko bishobra guteza umutwe, Koma, ibi ariko bigaragra gacye ku kigero cya 1% cy’abafashwe n’iyi ndwara bishora kuvamo n’urupfu ariko ku buryo bucye cyane.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Kuva Imyuna nabyo bigaragara kuri bacye mubafashwe n’iyi ndwara (1%) ariko mubabigaragaje 50% bishobora kubaviramo urupfu.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>Ikigero cyo kwandura iyi ndwara n’ibyo yangiza</strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Ugereranyije abantu 1% mu banduye iyi ndwara nibo yica ariko ku matungo uyu mubare uriyongera cyane kuburyo amatungo ahaka yose 100% araramburura. Ku nyigo yakozwe ku bantu byagaragaye ko kuba mu cyaro no kurara hanze ahantu hagaragaye iyi ndwara byongera ibyago byo kurumva n’imibu ikwirakwiza iyi ndwara. Abaveterineri, abakora mu matungo, ababazi, aba bose baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyi ndwara. </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>Uko ivurwa</strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Kugeza ubu nta muti wihariye kuri iyi ndwara mu bantu urabaho.</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Mu matungo uburyo bwo gukumira ikwirakwiza ni ukuyakingira. Urukingo rukunze gukoreshwa ni Smithburn ariko hari izndi nkingo ziri gushakashakwa zishobora no gukorehswa ku bantu. </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\"><em>Yateguwe na NIYIGABA Etienne (eniyigaba@yeanrwanda.org)</em></span></p>\r\n',2,17,1,4647,3,'Rift Valley Fever',0,'2018-06-18 23:00:00','2024-08-09 01:54:57'),(4259,'Ubworozi bw\'Inkoko zitera amagi, aho ziba, kororoka, ibiryo byazo,umusaruro wazo',NULL,'Inkoko_amagi.jpg','<p><strong><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Ubworozi bw&rsquo;Inkoko zitera amagi, aho ziba, kororoka, ibiryo byazo,umusaruro wazo</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Aho ziba</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:38.8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Inkoko zigomba kuba ahantu zisanzuye kandi hari urumuri n&rsquo;umwuka bihagije.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:38.8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Dore umwanya bateganya uko ugomba kuba ungana :</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:38.8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">1m&sup2; ku mishwi 20 (umunsi umwe kugeza ku minsi 30);</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:38.8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">1m&sup2;&nbsp; ku bigwana 10 (ukwezi&nbsp; kugeza&nbsp; ku mezi 5);</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:38.8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span> &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:black; font-family:DengXian\">1</span><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">m&sup2; ku nkokokazi5&nbsp;&nbsp; zitera ;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:38.8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">inkoko zigomba kugira urugo rwo gutemberamo ku zuba. Urwo rugo rugomba kuba ruzitiye kugira ngo zitajya hanze yarwo.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:-0.13px; margin-right:38.6px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Kororoka</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48.46px; margin-right:38.73px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Inkokokazi itangira gutera imaze amezi 5,5 ivutse ;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48.46px; margin-right:38.73px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Irarira iminsi 21 ;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48.46px; margin-right:38.73px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Inkokokazi ishobora gutera idafite isake, ariko igatera&nbsp; amahuri ;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48.46px; margin-right:38.73px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Isake imwe irahagije ku nkokokazi 10 kugira ngo zitere amagi atari amahuri;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48.46px; margin-right:38.73px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Inkokokazi imaze umwaka itera igomba kuvanwa mu bworozi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:-0.13px; margin-right:38.6px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Igaburo</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:12.13px; margin-right:38.8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Kugira ngo inkoko zikure neza kandi zitange amagi menshi, zigomba kugaburirwa neza;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:12.13px; margin-right:38.8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Ku bashoboye kubona imvange, dore uko bagomba kuyitanga&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; kuri buri nkoko, ku munsi:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:11.6px; margin-right:38.73px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">-</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Icyumweru cya 1 ivutse: gr 15</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:11.6px; margin-right:38.73px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">-</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Icyumweru cya 8: gr 50</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:11.6px; margin-right:38.73px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">-</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Icyumweru cya 20: gr 100</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:11.6px; margin-right:38.73px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">-</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Icyumweru cya 22: gr 120</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:11.6px; margin-right:38.73px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">-</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Inkoko itera: gr 130</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:38.8px\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Umusaruro</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.13px; margin-right:38.73px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Inkoko yo mu bwoko bwa RIR (Rhode Island Red) ishobora gutera ku mwaka amagi 220 iyo yafashwe neza. Ni ukuvuga umusaruro w&rsquo;amagi wa 60% ;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.13px; margin-right:38.73px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Inkoko yo mu bwoko Derco, iyo ifashwe neza ishobora gutera amagi 250 ku mwaka. Ni ukuvuga umusaruro wa 69% ku mwaka&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.13px; margin-right:38.73px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Hari ubundi bwoko bushobora gutera amagi 300 ku mwaka, aha twavuga nka Warren ;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.13px; margin-right:38.73px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Inkoko isanzwe ya kinyarwanda ishobora gutera amagi 60 kugeza kuri 90 ku mwaka. Mu bwoko bwa kinyarwanda, hagenda habamo zimwe ziba nziza kuruta izindi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0.46px; margin-right:38.6px\"><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">NB: Izi ngero zishobora guhinduka cyane bitewe n&rsquo;akarere inkoko zirimo ndetse n&rsquo;ubwoko bw&rsquo;inkoko IBIRYO BIKENEWE KU NKOKO Z&rsquo;INYAMA</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:38.73px; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Ibyiciro by&rsquo;inkoko zitera amajyi</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:38.8px\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">o</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Imishwi y&rsquo;inko z&rsquo;amagi&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:38.8px\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">igomba gushyirwa ahantu hashyushye (ushobora gukoresha imbabura, cyangwa se amashanyarazi).&nbsp; Ubushyuhe bukenewe ku nkoko z&rsquo;inyama ni nabwo bukenewe ku nkoko z&rsquo;amagi.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:38.8px\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">o</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Ibigwana by&rsquo;inkoko z&rsquo;amagi</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:38.8px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ni ukuva ku cyumweru cya cyenda kugeza ku cyumweru cya 20 &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:1.06px; margin-right:38.8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Ni muri kiriya gihe inkoko zigomba gukurikiranwa, hagakorwa inking zose zabugenewe, isuku ikitabwaho ibiryo n&rsquo;amazi nabyo bikaba bihagije. &nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:-0.13px; margin-right:38.6px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Inkoko zitangiye gutera amagi.&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:32.13px; margin-right:38.8px\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\">Kuva ku cyumweru cya 20 kugeza inkoko zishaje (hafi ku byumweru 80), &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:32.13px; margin-right:38.8px\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Mbere y&rsquo;ibyumweru 2 ngo inkoko&nbsp; zitangire gutera, umworozi agomba gushyiramo udusanduka inkoko zizatereramo kugirango zizatangire gutera zaratumenyereye.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:32.13px; margin-right:38.8px\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">&bull;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Iyo inkoko zatangiye gutera amagi&nbsp; , umworozi agomba kunyura mu nzu y&rsquo;inkoko nibura incuro enye; mu gitondo mu masaa tatu; saa tanu; saa munani, no ku mugoroba mu ma saa kumi n&rsquo;imwe, kugirango akuremo amagi inkoko zimaze gutera.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:32.13px; margin-right:38.8px\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">&bull;</span> &nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000; font-family:Calibri; font-size:medium\">Gukuramo amagi inshuro nyinshi bituma zitayamena.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:32.13px; margin-right:38.8px\">Icyitonderwa: Iyi nyandiko tuyikesha Igitabo Agenda y&#39;Umuhinzi cya 2018 cyateguwe na Minisiteri y&#39;Ubuhinzi n&#39;Ubworozi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n',2,18,1,37562,3,'Inkoko ',0,'2018-10-26 01:08:00','2024-10-01 19:48:46'),(4285,'Uko inzuki zivanwa mu muzinga wa gakondo zishyirwa mu muzinga wa kijyambere',NULL,'inzuki2.jpeg','<p><strong>Uko inzuki zivanwa mu muzinga wa gakondo zishyirwa mu muzinga wa kijyambere</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Iby&rsquo;ibanze ugomba kuba ufite</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Ifumbero ( igikoresho gikoreshwa mugufuhera inzuki mugihe uhakura).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Umuzinga wa kijyambere ( langstroth, kenyane) biterwa n&rsquo;uwo ufite ugiye gukoresha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Waramaze gutegura neza ahazakorerwa ubworozi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Ufite imyambaro ikoreshwa mu bworozi. Urugero: bote, ga zigenewe gukoreshwa mu bworozi, head cover, n&rsquo;ibindi byose bicyenerwa kugirango inzuki zitakurya.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Twakomeje tujya ku muzinga, reba neza niba koko inzuki mu muzinga wa gakondo zirimo, usanze zirimo , fata ifumbero yawe ufuhere umwotsi ku nzuki ziri kuwa gakondo kugirango zibe zimere nkizitaye ubwenge, zirajya m&rsquo;uruhande rumwe ariko ibyo byose ubinyuza m&rsquo;umuryango (umunwa w&rsquo;umuzinga, aho inzuki zinjirira),</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sakambura uwa gakondo uwuvaneho umwanda bitaza gutuma u Rwiru rwihisha muri uwo mwanda. Tangira uhakure, niba inzuki zagiye m&rsquo;uruhande rumwe kandi niba urikubonamo ubuki, cyangwa ibinyagu ;&nbsp; bitereke mu kintu kindi niba wamaze kubikuramo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa</strong>: Uko uhakura usatira impuzo inzuki nazo niko zigenda zihunga umwotsi zibumbira&nbsp; mu mpuzo</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kugirango wirinde ko inzuki zigwa hasi, fata umuzinga utarimo inzuki ( empty) wakijyambere uwushyire hasi, kugirango nizigwa zijye zigwamo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa</strong>: Kuramo amakaderi, urayasubizamo nyuma.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umaze guhakura ubuki, ibinyagu, kunkumurira muri wawundi upfunduye inzuki, ariko witondere urwiru. Niba rwagiyemo muri wawundi wa kijyambere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa</strong>: akuma gatangira urwiru ugashyiramo mbere mu maso ya wawundi wa kijyambere</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pfundikira niba wamaze gukunkumurira muri wawundi wa kijyambere , nihashira akanya ukabona mumaso y&rsquo;umuzinga hari nzuki zinjira izindi ziri gukubita amababa ariko zitaguruka menyako urwiru rwagezemo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Inzuki Izisigaye muri wa wundi wa gakondo zisuke hasi iruhande rwa wawundi wa kijyambere. Kugirango zinjiremo neza zikuruwe naya pheromone y&#39;urwiru. Cyane cyane ibyana biba bitaramenya kuguruka.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umuzinga wa gakondo wusubize aho waturetse vuba kugirango inzuki zagiye guhova zitabura aho zinjira, aho kugirango zinjire muwundi byegeranye, ariko ukibuka ko mugihe ugiye kuzicuranura n&rsquo; imizinga byegeranye nayo uyi fuheraho umwotsi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Reka inzuki wasutse hasi zinjire muri uwo wa kijyambere noneho nawo uwuterure witonze wambaye imyambaro yabugenewe uwujyane aho wateguye kororera hari indabyo cyangwa hafi yaho zahova.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Noneho ya ma kaderi uyasubizamo mugihe urikubona ko inzuki zamaze gutuza muri wa wundi wa kijyambere</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gusa biba byiza iyo uwo wa kijyambere uwujyanye nimugoroba, wabanje kuwurekera iruhande rwuwacuranuwe, ibi impamvu bikorwa aya masaha nuko inzuki ziba zavuye guhova zose ziba zagarutse ikindi ziba zituje kuburyo zitagucika. Ikindi funga amaso yu wa kijyambere mugihe uri kuwutwara uwuvana aho uwa gakondo waruri uwujyana ahateguwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibibazo bishobora kubamo</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Harigihe umuzinga wa gakondo uba wuzuyemo inzuki nyinshi kuburyo bigoye kubona urwiru, bikugora ubibwirwa nuko ushyiramo inzuki zirigusohoka, niba ubibonye fata wawundi wagakondo ukunkumurire hasi n&rsquo;ubundi, wakomeza kurubura ukawucurika ukubita hasi (ushinze). Nukomeza kurubura shakira mumahango y&rsquo;umuzinga wagakondo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Igihe cyose umuntu afata inzuki, ibinyagu bifite ibyana byiza umuntu ashobora kubiha umuzinga wakijyambere, noneho inzuki washyizemo zigahita zibikoresha babyita &ldquo;kwatira&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa</strong>: Niba wamaze gushyira inzuki neza mu muzinga wa kijyambere ziteho uzihe byose bisabwa nawe bizaguha umusaruro mwiza.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-----------</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Icyitonderwa: Ibikubiye muri iyi nyandiko ni ibitekerezo by&rsquo;uwayanditse. Ntago bihagarariye cyangwa ari ibya YEAN.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Inyandiko yateguwe na <strong>Twahirwa Leonard&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>Twahirwa Leonard</em></strong><em> ni umuvumvu wabigize umwuga wize ubuzima bw&rsquo;amatungo (animal health) mu mashuli yisumbuye, naho muri kaminuza akurikira ibijyanye no kwita k&rsquo;urusobe rw&rsquo;ibinyabuzima (wildlife management), akaba yaranagize amahugurwa atandukanye ku bworozi bwa kinyamwuga bw&rsquo;inzuki. Akorera ubuvumvu mu turere twa Nyamagabe na Rusizi.</em></p>\r\n',2,24,1,8348,3,'Inzuki',0,'2020-01-24 06:15:00','2024-08-09 01:54:57'),(4287,'Intambwe icumi (10) watera nkâ€™umuntu ushaka kwinjira mu bworozi bw\'inzuki',NULL,'inzuki.jpeg','<p><strong><span style=\"color:#222222\">Intambwe icumi (10) watera nk&rsquo;umuntu ushaka kwinjira mu bworozi bw&#39;inzuki.</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">1. Intambwe ya mbere ni ukuba m&rsquo; umuryango w&rsquo;aborozi b&rsquo;inzuki mu gace utuyemo. Kuko musangira amakuru y&rsquo;uko ubworozi bw&rsquo;inzuki buhagaze ,uko bukorwa ukanabaherekeza mu kazi kose kajyanye n&rsquo;ubworozi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">2. Niba utamenyereye gukora mu nzuki birashoboka ko wakwiga ibyerekeranye nazo hamwe nabaho basanzwe bazoroye</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">3. Nanone ushobora kurumwa n&rsquo;inzuki mbere yuko wowe ubwawe utangira ubworozi bwazo, umworozi agomba kumvikana nazo kuko uba ungomba kuba inshuti n&rsquo;inzuki.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">4. Igihe wabaye umunyamuryango w&rsquo;aborozi b&#39;inzuki bo mugace utuyemo, mukagirana umubano. ibitekerezo by&rsquo;uko borora bizagenda byiyongera. Ibibazobi bizakurikira nyuma yo kumenya uko ubworozi bukorwa:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">-ni inde tuzakorana?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">-ni ibihe bikoresho nzakoresha?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">-ni he nzagurisha ibikomoka ku nzuki?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">5. Niba utangiye umushinga w&#39;inzuki ugomba kwishimira gukorana n&rsquo;umuntu umwe cyangwa babiri&nbsp; muri ako gace ugiye kororeramo, uhitemo aborozi babifitiye ubushobozi (ubumenyi) kandi bumvikana. Aho nawe ingufu zawe ziziyongera. Korora inzuki ubwawe no kwifashisha uburyo butandukanye n&rsquo;uburi aho utuye n&#39;intambwe zizaguteza imbere.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">6. Nibura tangirana ubwa mbere n&rsquo;imizinga ibiri gusa. Ibi bizaguha icyigereranyo cy&rsquo;uko wakongera imizinga bitewe n&rsquo;imbaraga washyize muri yayindi ibiri bigutere imbaraga n&rsquo;ishyaka bitewe n&#39;inyungu wavanye muri ya yindi ibiri watangiranye.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">7. Mugutegura shyiraho intego z&#39;ukuri.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">Icyitonderwa: Umushinga muto ugerwaho kuko umushinga muto biroroha kuwusobanura no kuwushyira mu bikorwa kuruta umushinga munini.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">8. Ugutsinda kw&rsquo;igitekerezo no kwemerwa mu ruhando rw&rsquo;abandi borozi bishobora guterwa n&rsquo;uburyo usobanura umushingwa wawe. IGa gusobanura ibyo ukora ku rugero ruhagije.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">9. Ibikoresho ukoresha biterwa n&rsquo;imiterere yahantu uri: Ugomba guhitamo ibikoresho bitewe n&rsquo;ahantu uri, n&#39;abatekenisiye bahari, bakagufasha guhitamo ubwoko bw&#39;imizinga n&#39;ibikoresho wakoresha utangira ubworozi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">10.Kumenya abantu bakora ibikoresho byifashishwa mubworozi bw&#39;inzuki kugirango bijye biguha icyizere cy&rsquo;uwo muzajya mukorana n&rsquo;ubuzirangenge bwabyo.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:left\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><em>Icyitonderwa: Ibikubiye muri iyi nyandiko ni ibitekerezo by&rsquo;uwayanditse. Ntago bihagarariye cyangwa ari ibya YEAN</em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:left\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><em>Inyandiko yanditswe na <strong>Twahirwa Leonard&nbsp;</strong></em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:left\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><strong><em>Twahirwa Leonard</em></strong><em> ni umuvumvu wabigize umwuga wize ubuzima bw&rsquo;amatungo (animal health) mu mashuli yisumbuye, naho muri kaminuza akurikira ibijyanye no kwita k&rsquo;urusobe rw&rsquo;ibinyabuzima (wildlife management), akaba yaranagize amahugurwa atandukanye ku bworozi bwa kinyamwuga bw&rsquo;inzuki. Akorera ubuvumvu mu turere twa Nyamagabe na Rusizi.</em></span></p>\r\n',2,24,1,20875,3,'Inzuki',0,'2020-03-19 08:40:00','2024-09-25 18:24:48'),(4288,'Youth leading agriculture extension: Meet Angelique, a YEAN PEALE Extension Officer in Musanze District, Northern Rwanda',NULL,'/uploads/media-1705175778539-129426030.jpeg','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">Uzamukunda Angelique lives in Musanse, she has a bachelor’s degree in crop science from the university of Rwanda, College of agriculture and veterinary medicine (UR-CAVM). She manifested interests to join YEAN Private Extension and Advisory Learning Experience (PEALE) together with other 136 candidates shortlisted from the whole cohort of  650 fresh graduates (382 M, 268f)  from UR-CAVM cohort of the year 2022. At the time of her enrollment for the YEAN PEALE program in February 2023, Angelique was not connected to the community and extension programs like other new job seekers and she did not have a twitter account, a LinkedIn page or a professional membership in any agri value chain platforms. When asked about the reason she is joining the program, Angelique mentioned that she wants to learn more about modern agriculture, recent advances in the agriculture sector and get an experience of working with farmers for her to advance her career and perhaps find ways to start her own agribusiness. She completed the core engagement stage of the program and got the opportunity to be considered in the first cohort of YEAN  extension officers deployed in Musanze (her home), Nyabihu, Rubavu, Kicukiro, Gasabo, Rwamagana and Kayonza districts to be part of AIRTEA 3</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 0.6em;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">rd</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\"> party project ‘</span><span style=\"color: rgb(34,34,34);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 12pt;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">Youth Leading changes in Resilient Private Extension and Advisory Services for Job and Wealth Creation</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">’ implemented by a consortium of YEAN, RAB and UNILAK. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\"></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:none;\"><img src=\"https://lh7-us.googleusercontent.com/naTyxwJel-lTD3UdVmN-XoGxgVsgnHIl2orhNfvm3TR6r9DwHWgHCb5nN_zgGVrFMVjPQeq_9iy10YIoENRNjLLPnklV-tcrgsazGDBT4R-BTFi35vJEmyJkHwkH_jw76H5HiXehYnYd\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: ;width: \"/></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">Angelique wished to increase her knowledge and experience while impacting her community and playing a significant role in the objectives of YEAN of young people leading agriculture transformation in their communities. In her first action plan as YEAN PEALE Extension Officer deployed in Musanze, Angelique planned to train individual farmers and cooperatives on modern agriculture, soil conservation and other good agricultural practices. Angelique is pursuing her goal with the YEAN and AIRTEA project with commitment and dedication to impact her community. Angelique is providing extension services to her community’s farmers cooperatives. She works with the KOTEMUSHI cooperative in the Musanze District, Shingiro sector, with 143 members (41F, 102M) on 15Ha, a cooperative</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 12pt;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\"> of </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">smallholder farmers</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 12pt;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\"> that produces Irish potato and other crops like Onion</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">. She is coaching farmers on applying good agricultural practices ensuring that farmers adhered to the recommended inputs standards.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\"><strong>About YEAN PEALE</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: transparent;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">YEAN Private Extension and Advisory Learning Experience is a youth led learning program co-designed for aspiring youth to become private extensionists. The program increases the level of skills for aspiring extension agents in response to the growing demand from the farming communities. Youth selected to attend YEAN PEALE complete 3 stages. The CORE ENGAGEMENT STAGE: which is the first and mandatory One month online learning phase followed by the  BLENDED LEARNING STAGE where in  5 to 7 months selected candidates commit for 5 to 10 days a month for community and practical engagement in the agricultural value chain. The last stage is the PEER TO PEER LEARNING STAGE. Participants who have completed at least 3 of 6 modules of New Extensionist Learning Kit (NEKL) and 18 days of community work join the peer to peer learning stage. Under this final learning stage, some learners decide to continue their career as program peer to peer coaches (extension professionals) while others gain more exposure to secure economic opportunities (further studies, employment). As of December 2023, the YEAN PEALE program had 135 learners (87 male, 48 female) with 18 successfully linked to agriculture opportunities. </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n',1,2,1,244,40,NULL,0,'2024-01-14 04:56:18','2024-09-14 21:22:14'),(4289,'Empowering Agriculture and harnessing agripreneurship: The Effectiveness of Youth-Led Extension Services',NULL,'/uploads/media-1713540091039-136306539.jpeg','<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat;\">Tackling the potential of youth-led extension services turns out to be a game changer in the field of agriculture, where creativity and resilience to shocks caused by climate change are critical. These services, led by young people, give agricultural activities a new outlook and a dynamic approach, which increases their overall effectiveness.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat;\">The ability of youth-led agriculture extension services to establish connections with rural communities other young farmers is one of its main advantages and it’s one of the reasons YEAN has opted for this approach which leads to increased engagement of young people in agriculture. These young leaders -as we call them- effectively disseminate important information on improved and climate smart practices, market trends, sustainable practices, and advanced agriculture techniques since they have relatable communication styles couple with knowledge. This relevance encourages participation and trust, which increases the adoption of recommended agricultural practices among farmers.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat;\">Furthermore, there\'s no doubt that youth-led extension programs are frequently marked by a strong sense of passion and excitement. This enthusiasm is demonstrated by aggressive outreach programs, creative problem-solving techniques, and a readiness to try out innovative ideas. Such energy injects a renewed sense of vigour into agricultural communities, inspiring innovation, and resilience in the face of challenges like climate change and market fluctuations.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat;\">In addition, by enabling young people to serve as agricultural extension agents, the urgent problem of youth unemployment is addressed while simultaneously developing the next generation of agricultural leaders. Through offering them chances for skill enhancement, leadership directions, and guidance, YEAN cultivates a group of capable individuals who can spearhead the advancement of sustainable agriculture, innovations in agribusiness and ensure food security.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat;\">YEAN has chosen this single path of youth-led agriculture extension services which represent a potent force for positive change in agricultural communities. YEAN is working with our partners organizations and farmer’s associations and has deployed around 80 youth who are proactively working with farmers providing proximity extension and advisory services. We believe in their capacity to inspire, create, and connect what makes them so powerful; in the end, they clear the path for a more robust and prosperous agricultural future. YEAN aims to reach 150,000 farmers by year 2025 through youth led private extension and advisory services provision which is a contribution to our long term vision of transforming traditional subsistence agriculture into agribusiness through youth innovations as skilled and powerful weapon for leading the change toward sustainable livelihood.</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,1,171,784,NULL,0,'2024-04-20 00:21:31','2024-09-18 04:20:48'),(4290,'Empowering Rwanda\'s agripreneurs: the Agribusiness Innovation and Incubation Hub(AIIH) at UNILAK and the case for women-specific cohorts',NULL,'/uploads/media-1723135644630-585426771.jpeg','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Arial;\">The YEAN Agribusiness Innovation and Incubation Hub (AIIH) at the University of Laic Adventist of Kigali (UNILAK), launched in 2023 with support from AIRTEA project,  successfully incubated its first cohort of 22 young entrepreneurs. The program, designed to nurture the next generation of Rwandan agripreneurs with a focus on climate-resilient agribusiness, provided a structured and learner cantered experience that included workshops, mentorship, networking opportunities, and access to essential resources. The program\'s emphasis on innovation, sustainability, and collaboration aimed to create a lasting positive impact on Rwanda\'s agricultural sector. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Arial;\">The AIIH program at UNILAK stands as a testament to the transformative power of empowering young people to lead the charge in agricultural innovation. The success stories emerging from the program underscore its effectiveness in nurturing entrepreneurial talent and fostering a vibrant agricultural ecosystem. However, the disparity in participation between male and female entrepreneurs highlights the need for targeted interventions to ensure greater inclusivity. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Arial;\">The underrepresentation of women in the first cohort, with only 7 out of 22 participants, signals the existence of barriers that prevent young women from fully engaging in such opportunities. These barriers may include societal expectations, limited access to resources, and a lack of confidence. Addressing these challenges necessitates a multi-faceted approach. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Arial;\">One potential solution is the establishment of women-specific cohorts within the AIIH program. This would create a safe and empowering space for young women to learn, collaborate, and grow together. It would also allow for tailored mentorship and support that addresses the unique challenges faced by women entrepreneurs in the agricultural sector. Additionally, targeted outreach and awareness campaigns can be implemented to encourage more young women to apply for the program and pursue their entrepreneurial aspirations. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Arial;\">YEAN as a gender sensitive enterprise, believes that promoting gender inclusivity and creating an environment where young women can thrive, its programs continuously unlock the full potential of Rwanda\'s entrepreneurial talent and contribute to a more equitable and prosperous agricultural sector. The success of the first cohort, despite the gender gap, demonstrates the program\'s effectiveness and highlights the immense potential for even greater impact with increased female participation. The AIIH program at UNILAK is not just an incubator for businesses; it is a catalyst for change, empowering young people to become leaders in sustainable agriculture and drive Rwanda\'s economic growth. </span></p>\r\n',2,17,1,90,40,NULL,0,'2024-08-09 01:47:24','2024-09-25 18:24:26');
