INSERT INTO `post` VALUES (16,3,'Soya ni yera ahantu hatandukanye kandi ivamo ibintu binyuranye byatuma uwayihinze yihaza mu mafaranga ayikomokaho',0,0,'2017-03-13 01:54:10','images/soya.jpg',''),(14,3,'What a  plant need ',0,3,'2017-03-10 09:19:29','images/what a plant needs.jpg','/giselijah@gmail.com/simpungai3@gmail.com'),(17,3,'Abantu baturiye amazi ku biyaga, imigezi, inzuzi nahandi haboneka amazi turakangurirwa gukoresha ayo mazi hakoreshejwe uburyo bwose bushoka kugirango turamire imyaka mu gihe cy\'imvura',0,0,'2017-03-13 01:58:55','images/682814871064056529.jpg',''),(18,3,'Share your Story,inspire and get inspired more Hello again ! Did you know that you can expand your activities and get more customers , inspire and get inspired as well by taking picture, writing down a blog/story, making a short documentary of your Farmin',0,0,'2017-03-13 02:03:23','',''),(19,3,'Umusaruro ugomba kwitabwaho hakaba uburyo bwo kuwubika neza mu gih eutarajya kwisoko, mu gihe wagezeyo, no mu gihe utegerejwe kugurishwa , iyo ibi bitabaye haba ikibazo cyo kuwutakaza buhoro buhoro',0,1,'2017-03-13 02:06:04','images/745202595538799141.jpg',''),(30,3,'Muraho neza, Bahinzi borozi dusangiye umwuga , Murakaza neza kuri uru rubuga YEAN yadutehuriye ngi tubashe gusangira amakuru nk\'abantu bafite umwuga umwe kandi bagamije kubaho kinyamwugan mu buhinzi bworozi\r\n\r\nAha rero Ushobora kuhashyira amafoto ukandika ibyo ushaka gusangiza abandi bahinzi yaba uko Iwanyu ubuhinzi bumeze, yaba uko umusaruro wifashe , yaba kubaza , kunganira no gusangira ubumenyi kugirango turusheho kubaka ubuhinzi bworozi bw\'umwuga , dufashe igihugu gutera imbere binyuze mu Buhinzi Bwacu. \r\n\r\nMurakoze Murakaza neza .',0,3,'2017-03-29 16:48:05','',''),(29,3,'YEAN Community is a network of registered and non registered (Virtual online) farmers interacting on YEAN platforms where we share information online.\r\n\r\nIt is now a nice story and amazing community growing faster with about 3500 members and we are working days and nights to increase the number allowing farmers to interact and exchange ideas virtually every single second.\r\n\r\nIt is a diversified community putting together in farm farmers, agronomists at any level of administration and private entities, investors and policy makers.\r\n\r\nIt makes very easier for farmers to interact, breaking social barriers, allowing farmers meet up and contact any information\'s owner directly for more accurate information.',0,0,'2017-03-29 16:24:55','',''),(33,3,'Muraho neza, Bahinzi borozi dusangiye umwuga , Murakaza neza kuri uru rubuga YEAN yadutehuriye ngi tubashe gusangira amakuru nk\'abantu bafite umwuga umwe kandi bagamije kubaho kinyamwugan mu buhinzi bworozi Aha rero Ushobora kuhashyira amafoto ukandika ibyo ushaka gusangiza abandi bahinzi yaba uko Iwanyu ubuhinzi bumeze, yaba uko umusaruro wifashe , yaba kubaza , kunganira no gusangira ubumenyi kugirango turusheho kubaka ubuhinzi bworozi bw\'umwuga , dufashe igihugu gutera imbere binyuze mu Buhinzi Bwacu.\r\n\r\nMurakoze Murakaza neza .',0,0,'2017-04-03 07:40:18','',''),(35,314,'Muraho?\r\nUru rubuga ni rwiza cyane, ruziye igihe, ijwi ry\'umuhinzi rizumvikana ndetse tunagere no kubindi byinshi kandi byiza.\r\n\r\nDukeneye gukoresha neza uru rubuga ngo runafashe bamwe kubona experience muri byinshi. urugero ni nko kwandika inkuru ku buhinzi, gutanga amakuru ajyanye n\'ubuhinzi iwacu muri cartier n\' ibindi.\r\n\r\nIsakazamamakuru ku muhinzi n\'ubworozi rihereye kuri njye nawe twageza uyu mwuga kuri benshi kandi tukagera kuri byinshi.',0,1,'2017-04-04 12:12:29','',''),(36,212,'Amahoro bavandi.  Mbashimiye uru rubuga kuko ruzatuma tumenyekanisha ubuhinzi bwacu. \r\nNkuko nabibabwiye ndi rwiyemezamirimo mu buhinzi bw ibihumyo nkaba nkora imigina ikunzwe na benshi mu gihugu kandi nkaba mfasha abahinzi bahinga ibihumyo n abashaka kubihinga ku bibazo byose bahura nabyo.  Nkorera mu Ntara y amajyepfo, Akarere ka Nyanza, Umurenge wa Busasamana. \r\nMuri iyi minsi ndi kuzenguruka Intara zose mpugura abagore bo mu Itorero ry Abadventiste bazwi ku izina rya Mifem ikaba gahunda yateguwe n Itorero ry Abadventiste b umunsi wa 7 mu kiciro cy ashore. \r\nNatangiye kandi guhugura amatsinda, amakoperative y abahinzi b ibihumyo mu Ntara y amajyepfo ku nkunga y Ikigo cy Igihugu gishinzwe guteza imbere amazi n amashyamba muri Ministeri y Umutungokamere. \r\nBuri wese Ukeneye amakuru mu buhinzi bw ibihumyo yambaza nkamufasha cyangwa agasura aho nkorera i Nyanza. \r\n\r\n\r\nTwige gukira dukoresheje ubutaka buto ',0,1,'2017-04-04 13:36:20','',''),(39,263,'Mbere nambere mbanje gushimira uwatekerereje ububuryo mbona kuri nge aringirakamaro buje kudufasha kumenyekanisha ibyo dukora \r\nnge ndi rwiyemezamirimo ukiri muto arko ushoboye \r\nnoroye inkoko byubunyamwuga nkaba mfite ituragiro gakondo ryinkoko rimfasha guhaza isoko ryimishwi ibyo byose mbikora muburyo budasanzwe kuburyo uhageze wakumirwa cyane ko ntakenera courant electrique nkuko musanzwe mubimenyereye  ururubuga rero ruje ndukeneye kugirango mbasangize ibyo nabashije kugeraho namwe mumpe inama ',0,3,'2017-04-05 20:55:05','',''),(44,4,'Hello YEAN Mwaramutse gute?',0,2,'2017-04-06 06:37:29','',''),(47,160,'Mwaramutse neza nshuti z\'ubuhinzi namwe mubukora',0,1,'2017-04-06 07:19:08','',''),(48,160,'kubungabungaibidukikije byitaweho ubuhinzi nabwo butera imbere\r\n',0,0,'2017-04-06 07:44:51','images/rwanda-environmental-profile.pdf',''),(32,3,'Soil Map of Rwanda   Knowledge of the soils, their properties and their spatial distribution, is indispensable for the agricultural development of Rwanda as it opens opportunities for a more rational management of its land resources. A conventional national soil survey in Rwanda (scale 1:50,000) started in 1981 and was completed in 1994\r\n\r\nAbout 2,000 described and analysed soil profiles characterised the map units of 43 soil maps at scale 1:50,000 covering the Rwandan territory\r\n\r\nThe database was further extended with topographic data and climatic records at different temporal resolutions while the generation of simplified soil maps at scale 1:250,000 illustrated the diversity in land resources at national level. In order to make this huge amount of information more effectively for clients\' needs and to facilitate users\' access, an automation of the data was carried out by the Laboratory of Soil Science at Ghent University, in collaboration with the Rwanda Ministry for Agriculture, Livestock and Forestry\r\n\r\nThe Belgian Technical Cooperation coordinated the cooperation between these participants, while the project was financed by the Directorate-General for Development Cooperation, Brussels. On each of the topographic maps of Rwanda (scale 1:50,000), different themes were digitized and stored as separate coverages\r\n\r\nThe soil data were digitally stored (i) as a polygon theme, representing the digitized version of the soil mapping units that were manually drawn on the topographical maps and (ii) as a point theme, indicating the observation points (soil profiles and augerings)\r\n\r\nThe final lay-out of the 43 maps for publishing was established by use of ArcView\r\n\r\nIn each of these 43 ArcView projects, the soil profiles theme was used to make a connection with the Access Data Base which contains the general soil profile data, physical and chemical analysis data of the horizons, graphs showing correlations between these parameters, and the soil map explanatory reports\r\n\r\nThe 3-dimensional digital terrain model of each map was made in ArcView. Digital thematic maps not only for traditional agricultural purposes, but also for settlement planning, disaster-preparedness planning, high-input agriculture, and so on, can be derived from the digital inventory and plotted automatically\r\n\r\nThe system allows easy updating, modification or reorientation depending on the requirements of the different Ministerial departments who are going to use it\r\n\r\nAs such, the land resources information can be used more efficiently and accurately and will assist the Government of Rwanda in investigating specific agricultural and environmental issues in appreciable time limits. Comments to the content:ann.verdoodt@UGent.be. Last modified: 2008-06-03 08:43:00',0,0,'2017-04-03 07:03:43','',''),(49,160,'The first national forestry policy was put in place in 2004 after 16 years of existence of the forestry law. This led to a confusing and unusual situation whereby in one way or another, the forestry policy was influenced by an old law given the socio-economic and politico changes, Rwanda has undergone since 1988 and as a result of such impasse, none of the two tools did perform as expected.\r\n\r\nAt national level, this policy needed revision to accommodate EDPRS 2008-2012 targets related to forestry sector. EDPRS provides that the forestry sector will require interventions that include designing and implementing a reforestation strategy with diverse species, as well as inventorying and mapping national forest resources to provide the basis for a 10-year national forestry plan.\r\n\r\nThe 2011 National forestry policy set clear target to increase national forest cover and for the forestry sector to play increasing role in national economy. National economic growth requires more energy leading sometimes to over exploitation of national forest resources and shrinking of land due to the high population density and agricultural activities that make unavailability lands of reforestation and afforestation.\r\n\r\nThe overall goal of this policy is to make the forestry sector one of the bedrocks of economy and national ecological balance for sustainable benefits to all segments of the society.\r\n\r\nIn aggregate, the preferred options map out pillar on which development of the forestry sector in the country will depend on.  The preferred options are proposed on the basis of deep analysis and they contribute to attain the sectoral vision as outlined in Vision 2020. Each option represents a strategic direction that encapsulates the minimum set of investments needed to implement the forestry policy. Those options are the following:\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n    Permanent forest estate keeping\r\n    Forest-based industries promotion\r\n    Capacity building in the forestry sector, including strengthening institutions, forestry research and enhancement of forestry training\r\n    Urban and Peri-urban Forests development\r\n    Farm forestry enhancement\r\n    Promotion of profitable and productive forest plantation business\r\n    Establishment, rehabilitation and conservation of watershed protection forests\r\n    Supply of improved high quality tree seed and other germplasm\r\n    Conservation and wisely use of forest biodiversity\r\n\r\nAs EDPRS II predicts, MINIRENA will ensure that there is an equitable balance between forest protection and wood supply. Rural communities will be supported in wood production through training and workshops in seed handling, tree nursery management, forest harvesting, wood processing, timber drying and forest extension. Agro-forestry and soil research will also be supported by MINAGRI to help harness the sustainability of farming systems.\r\n\r\n ',0,0,'2017-04-06 07:53:00','',''),(50,160,'Palmer seems to have a better will to survive than any other weed, but tools exist to defeat it.',0,0,'2017-04-06 09:22:25','',''),(51,322,'Nishimiye kuba ndi muri ino community',0,2,'2017-04-06 16:08:49','',''),(52,3,'Bahinzi/Borozi bakunzi b\'ubuhinzi/ubworozi banyamuryango ba YEAN Community mwiriweho neza.\r\n\r\nDukomeze \"Twibuke Jenoside yakorewe Abatutsi,turwanya ingengabitekerezo ya Jenoside, dushyigikira ibyiza twagezeho\". \r\n\r\nUmwe muri twe ejo yatanze igitekerezo cy\'uko twafasha umuryango watewe n\'abagizi ba nabi bakabicira inka, maze twese dushyigikira iki gikorwa twemezako twakwishakamo ubushobozi bugakusanywa hamwe, hanyuma tuka mushumbusha inka m\'urwego rwo kwifatanya nawe no kumufasha gukomeza kubona amata n\'ifumbire. \r\n\r\nNi muri urwo rwego nkuko twese twabyifuje,ko iki gikorwa cyakorwa mbere y\'uko iki cyumweru cy\'icyunamo kirangira. \r\n\r\nBuri munyamuryango wa YEAN Community ushaka kwifatanya n\'abandi muri iki gikorwa arasabwa *GUTANGA UKO YIFITE*. \r\n\r\nAmafaranga aroherezwa hakoreshejwe Mobile Money na TigoCash kuri nimero zikurikira (MTN:0788845727 na Tigo: 0728845727) ya Nshimiyimana Arcade.\r\n\r\nUwohereza amafaranga asabwe kumenyesha Arcade ko abikoze. \r\n\r\nNidufatanya byose birashoboka kandi Ubuhinzi/Ubworozi Bwacu buzakomeza gutera imbere tubigizemo uruhare. \r\n\r\nNB: Uko igikorwa nyir\'izina kizakorwa na gahunda yacyo turabibagezaho vuba.\r\n\r\nDukomeze tugire Icyunamo kiza.\r\n\r\n\r\nByanditse kuwa 7/4/2017\r\n\r\nYEAN Team\r\n\r\nwww.yeanrwanda.org\r\n\r\n',0,1,'2017-04-07 17:15:17','',''),(53,3,'Bahinzi Borozi dusangiye umwuga mwaramutse, \r\n\r\nNk\'uko mwabimenyeshejwe , abanyamuryango ba YEAN Community bashyize hamwe imbaraga mu gitekerezo cyagizwe cyo gushumbusha umuryango wiciwe inka muri Kicukiro mu Mujyi wa Kigali, Iki gikorwa kirenda kugerwa ku Musozo aho biteganyijwe ko ejo kuwa 18 Mata 2017 aribwo azayihabwa. \r\n\r\nAbifuza gufatanya n\'ikipe izajya kuyitanga iduhagarariye twese , babigaragaza hanyuma gahunda n\'isaba igikorwa kizabera birabageraho mumasaha aza kuza. \r\n\r\nMurakoze',0,0,'2017-04-17 06:49:35','',''),(54,4,'Ubu twerekeje Kicukiro gusura umuryango tuzaha inka ejo. \r\n',0,1,'2017-04-17 12:40:38','',''),(55,350,'Bahinzi borozi dusangiye umwuga,nifuza korora inkoko zo mubwoko bwa Kuroiler,uwandusha amakuru ahagije aho nakura icyororo,ibijyanye n\'ibiryo byazo,n\'andi makuru ashoboka kuri zo yamfasha.Byumwihariko uwaba azoroye yambwira nkamusura tukungurana ibitekerezo.\r\nmurakoze cyane ',0,2,'2017-04-24 12:51:45','',''),(56,3,'Know what\'s wrong with your maize.',0,1,'2017-04-25 06:06:55','images/maize desease .jpg',''),(66,3,'ITANGAZO RY\' INGEMWE ZIGURISHWA\r\n\r\nUyu muhinzi yitwa Twizerimana Marcel akorera i Musanze, afite ingemwe z Ibinyomoro 2000 akeneye umukiriya , Izi ngemwe ze zahita ziterwa .\r\nNimero ze  ni 0733430156 cyangwa 0782726774',0,0,'2017-05-14 11:09:25','',''),(58,333,'Mwiriwe neza. Nifuza gukora ubworozi bw amafi mu byuzi, Haba Hari ufite umushinga kuri ubu bworozi akamfasha?',0,0,'2017-04-27 15:16:23','',''),(61,4,'Plant deficiency guide',0,0,'2017-04-28 11:07:16','images/image.jpeg',''),(62,314,'Icyumweru gishize kuva taliki 26 na 27 Mata 2017, Nitabiriye ihuriro nyafurika ry\'urubyiruko n\'abafatanyabikorwa barwo rya Banki nyafurika itsura amajyambere ryitwa Africa Youth Agripreneurs Forum IBADAN muri Nigeria-- wari umwanya mwoza wo kuganira kuri gahunda zitandukanye zigenewe urubyiruko ruri mu buhinzi.\r\nRYAF niyo yari ihagarariye young agripreneurs mu Rwanda. ni ngombwa ko dukomeza gukorana n\'inzego za leta ngo imishinga myiza iteza urubyiruko muri Africa ishobore kugera ku rubyiruko rw\'u Rwanda ruri mu buhinzi.\r\n',0,1,'2017-04-29 19:33:46','images/img_-p3zof2.jpg',''),(67,3,'INGEMWE ZIBANGURIYE Z\'IBITI BY\'IMBUTO : Uyu muhinzi yitwa Eulade Nzayinambaho akaba atuye mu Karere ka Karongi Umurenge wa Gishyita, akaba afite ingemwe zibanguriye z\'ibiti by\'imbuto z\'amacunga (Orange) zo mu Bwoko bwa Mandolin na Valencia zigera kuri 1000. Uwaba azikeneye yahamagara kuri 0783688589. ',0,0,'2017-05-14 11:27:29','',''),(64,3,'Umunsi mwiza w\'abakozi\r\n\r\nBahinzi Borozi namwe mukunda ubuhinzi, Nk\'uko mubimenyereye buri kwezi tugira umuhinzi ntangarugero w\'urubyiruko twizihiriza ibikorwa bye , tukabitangaza ku mbuga zacu zose ngo bimenywe kandi twishimira intambwe agezeho.\r\nUku Kwezi kwa Gicurasi turizihiza NZAYINAMBAHO Eulade, ukora ingemwe nziza z\'imbuto mu karere ka Karongi\r\nSoma inkuru y\'ubuhinzi bwe http://yeanrwanda.org/article.php?id=243',0,1,'2017-05-01 04:16:06','images/eulade nzayinambaho2.jpg',''),(77,3,'Farmer of the Month \r\n',0,0,'2017-06-08 14:05:07','images/nyirabagwiza magnifique banner 2.jpg',''),(82,387,'Ndifuza ko mwampuza numuntu uhugura abandi muguhinga ibihumyu kuko nifuza kubikora,',0,2,'2017-06-23 05:29:38','',''),(83,3,'Kigali hari kubera imurikabikorwa ry\'Ubuhinzi, guhera tariki ya 22-27 Kamena 2017, rifite insanganyamatsiko igira iti \" Koresha ikoranabuhanga mu ihinduka ry\'Ibihe hagamijwe kuzamura ibereho myiza y\' Abahinzi n\'aborozi.\" Rirabera ku Murindi mu karere ka Gasabo',0,0,'2017-06-24 04:11:07','images/171492675570071519.jpg',''),(84,3,'Kuri uyu munsi wo Kwibohora nkuko twari twabibamenyesheje, YEAN Community twasuye umuryango mu rwego rwo kuwuremera tukawushyikiriza agatabo ka compte twabafungurije tugashyiraho inkunga kugira umuryamgo ubashe kubona ubwatsi bw\'inka zabo. \r\n\r\nTwakiriwe neza ndetse twifatanya n\'abandi mu birori byo kwizihaza umunsi wo kwibohora.\r\n\r\nMuri ibi birori twahahwe umuwanya maze tuvuga abo turibo ndeste nmikitugenza ariko kubabwira igikorwa twakoreye umuryango wa Mukurira Ferdinand tuwushyikiriza agatabo ka compte iriho inkunga imbere y abayobozi ndetse n abaturage bari bahari. Gitifu w\'umurenge uw\'akagali ndetse n\'umu commanda gisirakre ndeste nu wa polisi mu murenge ,umukuru w\'umudugudu ndetse n\'abaturage bashimiye igikorwa cyacu. Bityo bashimira iyi nkunga twabateye. Umuryango ndetse n\'ubuyobozi burashimira uruhare rwa YEAN Community mu gufasha uyu muryango.\r\n\r\nNkomeza nanjye gushimira buri umwe wese wagize uruhare urwarirwo rwose muri iki gikorwa.',1,1,'2017-07-05 03:30:03','images/697654991144934535.jpg','/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(85,3,'YEAN WhatsApp\r\n\r\n18/7/2015-18/7/2017 Imyaka 2 irashize uru rubuga rudufasha gusangira amakuru anyuranye ateza imbere ubuhinzi bwacu. \r\n\r\nYEAN irashimira buri wese uri hano n\'undi wese wagize uruhare ngo dukomeze dutezanye imbere mu gusobanukirwa n\'igikenewe ngo ubuhinzi bworozi bwacu butere imbere \r\n\r\nHari abamaze imyaka ibiri bari aha  n\'abamaze itagezeho ariko uruhare rwa buri wese rwabaye indashyikirwa mu rugendo turimo. \r\n\r\nNdabashimiye \r\n\r\nNiyigaba Etienne \r\nNshinzwe imvuga nkoranyabahinzi za YEAN',1,4,'2017-07-18 15:20:41','','/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(86,3,'Ikigori kimwe mu mwobo kiba gihagije, mu kugabanya competition y\'ibihingwa',1,0,'2017-07-27 08:32:24','images/photogrid_1501143194891.jpg','/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(87,3,'Ushaka kureba Inkuru zose twabagejejeho , Nyura kuri website www.yeanrwanda.org hanyuma ujye kuri Iyamamazabuhinzi, ushobora guhitamo kureba izijyanye n\'Ubuhinzi, Ubworozi cyangwa inkuru z\'Ikiganiro Ubuhinzi Bwacu nk\'uko bigaragara kuri iyi foto.',1,0,'2017-07-28 04:20:31','images/iyamamazabuhinzi.jpg','/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(88,362,'Mwiriwe Ndashaka amakuru ku muntu ufite imishwi y\'inkoko zimaze amezi 2 zivutse akampa number ye\r\nTel:0783766708\r\nWhatsapp 0788333808',1,1,'2017-07-28 10:57:08','','/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(89,396,'Mfite imishwi imaze ibyumweru 2  yo mubwoko bwa SASSO( inkoko ifite resistance nk\' inyarwanda , ikaba itanga amagi 4x kurusha inyarwanda zisanzwe,zikaba amasake meza ameze nk\' inyarwanda uretse ko zo ziba nini kuburyo apres 2 mois iba ifite hagati  2-3kg.\r\nUzikeneye wampamagara kuro 0783688589(whatsap nbr) cg 0783941240',0,2,'2017-07-28 13:56:49','images/dsc_0332.jpg','/niyonzimagerard012@gmail.com'),(90,396,'Sasso chicks of 2 weeks',1,0,'2017-07-28 14:11:22','images/dsc_0321.jpg','/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(91,3,'Rwanda Agriculture Zone / Uturere tw\'ubuhinzi mu Rwanda',1,0,'2017-08-16 08:49:43','images/rwanda agriculture zones.jpg',''),(92,3,'Mwaramutse Bahinzi Borozi, Ndabararitse ntimuzabure mu kiganiro UBUHINZI BWACU cyo kuri iki cyumweru ni ukuva saa mbiri za mugitongo ku mbuga nkoranyambaga za YEAN arizo WhatsApp na Facebook. Twabateguriye insanganyamatsiko nziza cyane. \r\n\r\nMboneyeho no Guha ikaze abageze kuri uru rubuga bashya muri iki cyumweru. Mwisanzure mutangaze ibyo mushaka bijyanye n\'ubuhinzi bworozi tubamo buri munsi. Umwanya ni uwanyu.',1,1,'2017-08-19 04:36:57','','/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(93,3,'Mwaramutse bahinzi borozi Dukomeze twitabira gukoresha uru rubuga . Ubutumwa bugiyeho bugera ku bantu benshi nkuko tubugenza kuri Whatsap. Gusa kuri WhatsApp ho ntago bigera ku bantu bose babishatse. Ariko aha bigera ku muntu wese urebye aha. \r\n\r\nUmunsi mwiza. ',1,0,'2017-08-22 04:36:13','','/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(108,3,'NOHELI NZIZA N\'UMWAKA MUSHYA MUHIRE WA 2018\r\n\r\nMuhinzi-Mworozi munyamuryango wa YEAN Community turagusuhuje,\r\nUyu mwaka wa 2017 wabaye umwaka mwiza kuri YEAN yose , wabaye umwaka wo gutanga ibitekerezo byiza no guhana amakuru mu bikorwa byacu by\'ubuhinzibworozi ngo dufatanye twese gutera imbere no guteza imbere uyu mwuga. Abanyamuryango twahungukiye inshuti, abafatanyabikorwa ndetse n\'abakiriya , twahungukiye amakuru anyuranye kandi yatwubatse mu mpande zose z\'ubuhinzibworozi bwacu. Twabonye ko gukora ubuhinzibworozi bw\'umwuga bishoboka kandi ko dukomeje guhana amakuru gutya byakorohera buri wese kugira ubumenyi butuma abasha kongera umusaruro mu bikorwa bye no kubikora kinyamwuga\r\n\r\nTuragushimira uburyo wagize uruhare mu gusangiza abandi amakuru no guteza imbere umwuga wacu. Ibyo abanyamuryango ba YEAN Community bagiye bagaragaza nk\'ibitekerezo bikwiye kugezwa ku bafata ibyemezo twagerageje kubikora ndetse n\'ibindi byose turacyabikoraho. Umwaka utaha byose bizagenda bigarukwaho kandi twizerako bizatanga umusaruro mwiza.\r\nTwifuzako Uyu mwaka twafatanya mu gutangaza amakuru cyane y\'ubuhinzibworozi dukora kugirango dufatanye gutera abandi imbaraga zo gukora ubuhinzi bw\'umwuga, twifuza kandi ko YEAN Community yakwaguka amakuru akabasha kugera kuri benshi, ushobora kubigiramo uruhare nawe ushishikariza abandi bahinzi kwifatanya natwe.\r\n\r\nTuboneyeho no kubifuriza Noheli Nziza n\'umwaka mushya Muhire wa 2018. Tuzawukoremo byiza byinshi , TUZAHINGE TWEZE, TWORORE ZOROROKE.\r\n\r\nIkipe ya YEAN.',1,2,'2017-12-23 03:31:12','images/happy new year 2018 2.jpg','niyigabat@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(109,390,'Yean mwese ndabasuhuje\r\nMbifurije Noheli nziza n\'umwaka mushya muhire wa 2018\r\nMureke dukore kdi twiteze imbere',1,1,'2017-12-29 16:05:53','','safarisalaam@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(110,390,'Mwese ndabasuhuje kubifuza korara ibigagari ( Pintade) Inuma na Oie mutugane \r\nCg muduhamagare kuri \r\n07883500001 Whatsup\r\n0788310600',1,1,'2017-12-29 16:12:31','','safarisalaam@gmail.com/niyigabat@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(111,40,'Mwaramutseho neza Bahinzi/Borozi namwe mukunda ubuhinzi/ubworozi.\r\nImana ishimwe kuba dutangiye umwaka amahoro. Uhoraho nahe umugisha ibikorwa byacu byose, imirima yere, amatungo yororoke,ikirere kiduhire, igihugu cyacu kigire amahoro. \r\nNshimiye buri wese uri hano kuruhare rwe muguteza imbere ubuhinzi n\'ubworozi.\r\nKu ruhare rw\'ikipe ya YEAN nifuje kubifuriza Umwaka mushya muhire wa 2018. Uzatubere umwaka wo kwesa imihigo, dufatanya mu guhangana n\'inzitizi ziri mu mwuga wacu.\r\n\r\nHappy New Year 2018????',1,0,'2018-01-01 06:29:34','','nshimarcade@gmail.com/muritheos@yahoo.fr/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(112,40,'Mwaramutseho neza Bahinzi/Borozi namwe mukunda ubuhinzi/ubworozi.\r\nImana ishimwe kuba dutangiye umwaka amahoro. Uhoraho nahe umugisha ibikorwa byacu byose, imirima yere, amatungo yororoke,ikirere kiduhire, igihugu cyacu kigire amahoro. \r\nNshimiye buri wese uri hano kuruhare rwe muguteza imbere ubuhinzi n\'ubworozi.\r\nKu ruhare rw\'ikipe ya YEAN nifuje kubifuriza Umwaka mushya muhire wa 2018. Uzatubere umwaka wo kwesa imihigo, dufatanya mu guhangana n\'inzitizi ziri mu mwuga wacu.\r\n\r\nHappy New Year 2018????',1,3,'2018-01-01 06:30:13','','nshimarcade@gmail.com/muritheos@yahoo.fr/fridolinho@gmail.com/niyigabat@gmail.com'),(113,40,'Murwego rwo kunoza imikoranire no kubona/gusangira amakuru/ubumenyi/ubunararibonye mu buhinzi/ubworozi mwiyandikishe ndetse munuzuze imyirondoro yanyu neza kugira hatagira ucikanwa n ubuhinzi n\'ubworozi bwacu.',2,1,'2018-01-03 06:46:00','images/img-20170403-wa0025.jpg','nshimarcade@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com/niyigabat@gmail.com'),(114,3,'Mbifurije umwaka mushya muhire wa 2018, \r\n\r\nDukomeze guharanira gusangira amakuru n\'ubumenyi mu mwuga wacu w\'UbuhinziBworozi. UmuhinziMworozi ufite amakuru y\'ibyo akora niwe ubasha kugera neza ku ntego yifuza. \r\n\r\nDukomeze tugambirire guhaza isoko ryacu ibiribwa no gusagurira amahanga. UbuhinziBworozi butubere isoko y\'amafanga n\'ubukungu burambye.',1,0,'2018-01-04 03:36:49','','niyigabat@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(117,4,'Happy Easter to you all.',1,0,'2018-03-31 09:30:07','images/dzhpuvyu8aacasc.jpg','fridolinho@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(118,526,'Am Uwamahoro Justine, the Chairlady of Board of Members of Agaciro Agro-mechanical Innovations which is a newly registered Rwandan company whose mission is to raise water for irrigation by small scale farmers using power of moving waters. I would like to share ideas, brainstorm together with my fellow Rwandese in agribusinesses. My contacts are +250780677485. We can also chat through whats app',2,6,'2018-04-18 09:51:29','','agaciro.a.innovations@gmail.com/agaciro.a.innovations@gmail.com/niyigabat@gmail.com /agaciro.a.innovations@gmail.com/agaciro.a.innovations@gmail.com/agaciro.a.innovations@gmail.com/manipthegrede@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(119,3,'KU BIJYANYE N\'IMBUTO NYAYO YO GUTERA\r\n\r\nImbuto uteye igira ingaruka ku musaruro uzabona. Kumenya neza no gutegura neza imbuto ugiye gutera ni kimwe mubyo abahinzi bakwiye kwitaho. Iyo uteye imbuto mbi umusaruro uba mucye cyane. Iyo uteye imbuto utizeye neza nabyo ni kimwe. Iyo uteye imbuto ivangavanze atari imbuto imwe ubona umusaro ariko nubwo waba mwiza Ntago ubashaka kumenya neza mu mibare uburyo umurima wawe watanze umusaruro. Twite rero ku mbuto dutera kandi Twite ku gutera imbuto Nziza ibyara umusaruro mwiza.',1,0,'2018-04-19 05:06:07','images/img-20180202-wa0012.jpg','niyigabat@gmail.com /fridolinho@gmail.com'),(120,3,'KU BIJYANYE N\'IMBUTO NYAYO YO GUTERA\r\n\r\nImbuto uteye igira ingaruka ku musaruro uzabona. Kumenya neza no gutegura neza imbuto ugiye gutera ni kimwe mubyo abahinzi bakwiye kwitaho. Iyo uteye imbuto mbi umusaruro uba mucye cyane. Iyo uteye imbuto utizeye neza nabyo ni kimwe. Iyo uteye imbuto ivangavanze atari imbuto imwe ubona umusaro ariko nubwo waba mwiza Ntago ubashaka kumenya neza mu mibare uburyo umurima wawe watanze umusaruro. Twite rero ku mbuto dutera kandi Twite ku gutera imbuto Nziza ibyara umusaruro mwiza.',1,0,'2018-04-19 05:06:48','images/img-20180202-wa0012.jpg','niyigabat@gmail.com /fridolinho@gmail.com'),(127,481,'Nashatse kuboherereza amafoto yazo biranga kandi mwihangane kunyandiko nabandikiye\r\nharaho ntakase kandi biringombwa ubworero gusoma nugushishoza. I say be sorry once again ',1,1,'2018-04-23 18:52:47','','manipthegrede@gmail.com/niyigabat@gmail.com /fridolinho@gmail.com'),(122,3,'Mu bworozi bw\'ingurube ni byiza gutangirira Kuri ku mubare mukeya, nubwo waba ufite ubushobozi bwo korora nyinshi, bisaba kubanza kumenyera uburyo zororwamo n\'ibyo zicyenera hanyuma ukazagura uzi neza uko ubu bworozi bumeze n\'imbaraga bisaba.',2,0,'2018-04-19 05:31:03','','niyigabat@gmail.com /fridolinho@gmail.com/niyonzimagerard012@gmail.com'),(125,4,'Ninde wamenya aho nakura cg uko nabona imbuto nziza y\' ibitunguru by\'umweru. Murakoze',1,2,'2018-04-22 18:13:41','','fridolinho@gmail.com/niyigabat@gmail.com /fridolinho@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(126,481,'Bakunzi bubuhinzi byumvihariko abajene nimuze tubikore tubikunze kuko birimo inyungu nyinshi nubwo biturushya ariko aho ufite hose hahinge kijyambere maze wirebere ukuntu ukirigita ifaranga jye mpinga insina ariko nabitangiye banseka none ubu turinshuti  kandi urebye nashoye amabako yange uti rero ibaze umuntu wiga kaminuza yafashe isuka nihatari ariko iyo uzi icyo ushaka urayifata Imana idushoboze guhindura imyumvire ubu ndangije AGRIBUSINESS in UR \r\nMURAKOZE NINKUBUHAMYA NABAHAGA bwagufasha guhindura imyumvire yabandi',1,1,'2018-04-23 18:09:10','','manipthegrede@gmail.com/niyigabat@gmail.com /fridolinho@gmail.com'),(124,3,'KIRABIRANYA (Banana Xanthomonas Wilt)\r\n\r\nNi indwara iterwa na bagiteri igakwirakwizwa n’inzuki zitara ubuki ku nsina\r\nzirwaye nyuma zikajya ku nsina nzima, imibyare irwaye n’ibikoresho bidasukuye \r\nna byo bikwirakwiza iyi ndwara.\r\n\r\nIbimenyetso\r\n- Insina yafashwe, amakoma yayo ararabirana,\r\n- Umutumba wayo ukavamo amashyira y’umuhondo,\r\n- Amabere atangira kuneka atarakura; iyo umanyuye ibere imbere \r\nusangamo ibara ry’ikigina;\r\n- Umwanana urabora kandi ukuma.\r\n\r\nUburyo bwo kuyirinda no kuyirwanya\r\n\r\n-   Guca umwanana ukoresheje isando amabere ya nyuma akimara gusohoka\r\nmu mwanana,\r\n-   Gutera imibyare myiza nk’ivuye muri laburatwari,\r\n-   Gusukura ibikoresho hifashishijwe umuriro,\r\n-   Kwirinda kugendagenda mu murima urimo uburwayi haba abantu ndetse\r\nn’amatungo,\r\n-  Gutema no gutaba insina zirwaye.\r\n\r\nImfashanyigisho yose ku buhinzi bw\'urutoki  sure www.yeanrwanda.org',1,0,'2018-04-19 09:57:42','','niyigabat@gmail.com /fridolinho@gmail.com'),(130,407,'Agriculture drove Rwanda’s impressive growth over the past years and remains a key player of the country’s economy today, making up a third of GDP while employing 88% of the active population.\r\nLargely due to successful transformation of agriculture, poverty dramatically decreased from 80% in 1994to less than 45% of the population today. Again thanks to agriculture, most Rwandans are now food secure and can access more balanced diets.\r\n',1,0,'2018-05-20 06:35:13','','flodouardh2@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(131,407,'Agriculture drove Rwanda’s impressive growth over the past years and remains a key player of the country’s economy today, making up a third of GDP while employing 88% of the active population.\r\nLargely due to successful transformation of agriculture, poverty dramatically decreased from 80% in 1994to less than 45% of the population today. Again thanks to agriculture, most Rwandans are now food secure and can access more balanced diets.\r\n',1,0,'2018-05-20 06:36:33','','flodouardh2@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(129,3,'GUFATA NEZA AMATUNDA MU MURIMA\r\n\r\n*   Kuyubakira ingazi, hakoreshwa ingiga z’ibiti bifite m 2,70 z’uburebure, cm\r\n15 z’umurambararo; cm bagataba 60. \r\n \r\n*   Ni ngombwa gufasha urugemwe kurira rukagera kuri twa tugozi, ushyira\r\nhagati y’urugemwe n’utugozi umuhembezo;\r\n*   Kubagara no gusasira;\r\n*   Gukata Marakuja;\r\n*   Ikata ritereka igiti: hatoranywa ibishibu 2 bitarangwaho indwara, ibindi\r\nbigakatwa;\r\n*   Ikata rituma igiti cyera neza: bakata imitwe hejuru y’utujisho tuzabyara\r\nandi mashami, bituma igiti gikura vuba;\r\n*   Gukata udushami tutagifite imbuto cyangwa twangiritse;\r\n*   Ikata risazura igiti: gukatira igiti kuri cm 30 uvuye ku butaka iyo umusaruro\r\nutangiye kugabanuka;\r\n*   Kurwanya indwara n’ibyonnyi hakoreshejwe amoko yihanganira indwara\r\nno gutera imiti.\r\n\r\nKu zindi mfashanyigisho ku bihingwa bitandukanye wasura www.yeanrwanda.org',1,1,'2018-04-24 05:51:50','','niyigabat@gmail.com /emmagasigwa10@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(132,540,'The only problem in agriculture is that the Rural farmers, do not have access to market, they harvest but they get low income or they do kotsa umusaturo where farmers sell crops at low price before they harvest, we have to look beyond together to fight against these problem as Yean community members',1,0,'2018-05-20 14:42:04','','niyobuhungirogad01@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(133,540,'The only problem in agriculture is that the Rural farmers, do not have access to market, they harvest but they get low income or they do kotsa umusaturo where farmers sell crops at low price before they harvest, we have to look beyond together to fight against these problem as Yean community members',1,1,'2018-05-20 14:43:08','','niyobuhungirogad01@gmail.com/sibowellars@yahoo.com/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(134,548,'Ikibazo cy, amasoko twakiganiriyeho kenshi ariko hari igisubizo . ubundi amasoko aboneka iyo abantu bishyize hamwe bakaganira ku musaruro bafite barangiza bagashaka isoko bahereye ku bikorwa remezo nk , amahoteri nibindi ntitwibande kwihutira kubijyana mu masoko atwegereye gusa. \r\ntumenyekanishe kandi ibikorwa byacu aho turi bizadufasha kubona amasoko.\r\n\r\nIkindi ni ukwiga umuco wo guhunika kubera ko hari igihe duhendwa byeze nyuma bikabura.\r\n\r\nMurakoze',1,0,'2018-05-24 16:44:30','','nshimiyinn@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com'),(135,553,'muraho ,mwiriwe \r\n\r\nnitwa muhozadominique xavier   no rorora inkwavu,imbata,dendo  nkakora incubateur zifite ubushobozi bwo kurarira  amagi zikanayaturaga  agera (1000)  bikora  bya proffesional\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\ngua umuntu uzi ahantu bafite pellets   yandangira\r\n\r\nikindi tuvura amautungo ubwoko bwose \r\nndetse   na chirurugie  turazikora aho bibaye ngombwa',1,4,'2018-06-07 05:15:41','','muhozadominique89@gmail.com/niyigabat@gmail.com /fridolinho@gmail.com/giselijah@gmail.com/rosenyiramondo@gmail.com/vincentndayambaje305@gmail.com'),(171,4,'Farmer platform summit - YEAN Rwanda',0,1,'2018-12-09 08:46:24','images/whatsapp image 2018-12-09 at 10.29.28.jpeg','fridolinho@gmail.com/niyigabat@gmail.com'),(173,3,'YEAN Introduction flyer , Agapapuro gasobanura YEAN. ',1,0,'2018-12-11 06:43:58','images/yean flyer.jpg','niyigabat@gmail.com/ishimwelongin1@gmail.com'),(174,4,'Hello Our community is growing and am happy for that.',0,0,'2020-02-17 05:44:26','images/logo.png','fridolinho@gmail.com/fridolinho@gmail.com');
