nikora neza imbuto y ibishyimbo.\r\n','',0,0,NULL,NULL),(554,'member','blaiseshyaka95@gmail.com','455e022f3d3ca5c0c2aa108a6234c7db','Kaminuza A0|A0','2018-06-11 12:22:40','Blaise Pascal','SHYAKA','0787643380','male','1995-07-30 00:00:00','Southern Province','Muhanga','NYAMABUYE','Managing Director at AMPLE LTD; a pig farming company','Muhanga, Nyamabuye','I graduated from the University of Rwanda in the field of biotechnology. I attended a training program at Chonbuk National University in animal science and biotechnology. This is where I got the inspiration in the livestock farming sector. I eventually started a pig farm, with the aim of reducing meat production cost by harnessing pig feeding methods and livestock welfare. At AMPLE Ltd., my company, we aspire to make meat and meat products affordable to the people earning at least 1500 Rwf/day. ','',0,0,NULL,NULL),(549,'member','albertkaramira@gmail.con','ae79b1ff4b9070214f545376906d6b78','Kaminuza A0|A0','2018-06-01 09:15:13','Karamira','Albert','+250788480152','male','1984-05-14 00:00:00','Eastern Province','Rwamagana','Kigabiro','Inyanya','Gatsibo','Ubuhinzi bw\'inyanya bukorerwa hejuru ya 1ha','',0,0,NULL,NULL),(561,'member','adelinekampire12@gmail.com','e8606ba78e2b015bbd493a6a5a9a69e3','Kaminuza A0|A0','2018-07-03 16:09:26','KAMPIRE','Adeline','0784213161','female','1991-03-15 00:00:00','Kigali City','Gasabo','Gikomero','Ingurube','Rusororo','Ingurube nabonye zororoka ujyereranije nandi matungo magufi, kdi ibyogurya byazo ntabwo bihenze cyaneee! ','',0,0,NULL,NULL),(551,'member','dawechristianalain@gmail.com','bb88c6d0c94f777feebb3499cbd1711f','Kaminuza A0|A0','2018-06-03 14:50:27','Dawe ','Christian alain','0788941437','male','1992-03-24 00:00:00','Western Province','Rubavu','Nyundo','Inkwavu','Pfunda','Njye natangije umushinga winkwavu ubu hagiye kushira amezi arindwi mutangiye.kuko nabanjye kugura ubutaka nyuma mbonye utundi dufaranga nubaka ibiraro bwinkwavu.ubu mbandikira hashize iminsi atarenze 39 inkwa