0:00','Eastern Province','Nyagatare','Gatunda','Inyanya,ubutunguru','Nyamirembe','Minga Inyanya n, ubutunguru mbihinga nkurikije amabwiriza ndetse nibicyenerwa byose nko gukoresha amafumbire intera ,imbuto nziza nkabikora by a kinyamwuga doreko nize ubuhinzi muri kaminuza','',0,0,NULL,NULL),(575,'member','niyeppa2000@gmail.com','a9f0cb9367c5913a4c8b0a1a754fd8c1','Kaminuza A0|A0','2018-09-04 13:41:30','NIYIRERA','Epaphrodite','0787898776','male','1979-10-10 00:00:00','Southern Province','Muhanga','NYAMABUYE','Agriculture Facilitation','FH RWANDA','ANY','',0,0,NULL,NULL),(576,'member','minantony@yahoo.fr','d055167ae7a6888a5d5d11f1163cf4a6','Kaminuza A0|A0','2018-09-05 08:59:29','MINANI','Antoine','0781475364/0728551239','male','1990-10-01 00:00:00','Northern Province','Gakenke','RULI','Poultry production and Formulation of animal feeds','Ruli sector and Gakenke Sector','Mr. Antoine MINANI is a 28 years old young poultry farmer,he was born in Gakenke District, Ruli Sector in the family of farmers ,Minani has   Bachelor’s degree with honour in Agricultural Economics and Rural Development from University of Rwanda.\r\n\r\nHe started as smallholder farmer with 100 layers chicken in 2014 after the end of University, he found that there is no other chance of being employed or find a job, and choose to step down and doing poultry production.\r\n\r\nIn 2016, He received the fund from FAO in ASTF Project of a kit of 330 layers hens, basic training and technical supervision and he take decision of moving in Gakenke Sector, 38 km from Ruli sector in order to meet his buyers, through this chance he was changed his mind set and doing poultry production as a business to support creation of Decent rural youth employment in his rural area.\r\n In 2017, Minani started to encourage other youth of his age to be entrepreneur in poultry production, in order to fight against unemployment that was like a disease in his rural area, he helped 20 people to get good chicks in which 90% are youth with a total of 1585 chicken. He owned a company known as M-Poultry & Agribusiness Ltd with mission of promoting decent rural youth employment through Poultry production, by producing quality chicks formulation of animal feeds and processing of poultry product. It also support activities for animal production and use of poultry manure to increase annual crop yield.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nToday, Minani has two farm one in Gakenke sector and other in Ruli sector, all with 1500 chicken, he manage a hatchery with an incubator of 2112 eggs, he employ 7 labors in which 4 are youth, he is a role model of many people especially youth   in his rural area of how you can create the future yourself through poultry production. He is still working hard to include many youth in Agribusiness activities especially in poultry production but he is still suffering many key challenges:\r\nHe is still facing low capital in order to expand his project by reaching all youth who want to raise poultry as he has a high number of youth who want doing poultry production as a business, he want to include 100 youth in poultry production.\r\n','',0,0,NULL,NULL),(577,'member','nackykobes@gmail.com','2e451910fe8b384905f7b7fe247af9a0','Kaminuza A0|A0','2018-09-05 15:37:48','INGABIRE','TONA NANCY','0788230016','female','1988-08-05 00:00:00','Kigali City','Nyarugenge','NYAKABANDA','NDIFUZA GUHINGA MACADAMIA,URUTOKI,NI IBISHYIMBO','RWAMAGANA','KUGEZA UBU NTA EXPERIENCE MFITE NIYO MPAMVU NIFUJE KU JOINIG IYI GROUPE KUGIRANGO NIYUGURE AMAKURU MENSHI KANDI AFATIKA','',0,0,NULL,NULL),(578,'member','Frednkotanyi16@gmail.com','26861b4cd808f882e96171d2376ca7f8','KAminuzaA1|A1','2018-09-08 04:52:39','Nkotanyi','Fred','0788390479','male','1991-06-01 00:00:00','Kigali City','Gasabo','Kinyinya','Umuhinzi wamashu n\'imiteja','Gasabo/Kinyinya','Maze imyaka ine ( 4) nkorana na company y\'ubuhinzi bw\'imboga ihinga igihingwa cy\'imiteja nkaba nkora nkumukozi ushinzwe kureberera ibikorwa by\'ubuhinzi gukora ( farm supervisor